# <a name="required-diagnostic-data-for-office"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-103">Obvezni diagnostični podatki za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-103">Required diagnostic data for Office</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-104">Če si želite ogledati seznam Officeovih izdelkov, ki so zajeti v teh informacijah o zasebnosti, glejte [Kontrolnike zasebnosti, ki so na voljo za Officeove izdelke](products-versions-privacy-controls.md).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-104">For a list of Office products covered by this privacy information, see [Privacy controls available for Office products](products-versions-privacy-controls.md).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-105">Diagnostični podatki so uporabljeni za zaščito, posodobitev ter zaznavanje in odpravljanje težav v Officeu, poleg tega pa tudi za izboljšanje izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-105">Diagnostic data is used to keep Office secure and up-to-date, detect, diagnose and fix problems, and also make product improvements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-106">Ti podatki ne vključujejo uporabniškega imena ali e-poštnega naslova, vsebine datotek uporabnika ali informacij o aplikacijah, ki niso del Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-106">This data does not include a user's name or email address, the content of the user's files, or information about apps unrelated to Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-107">Ti diagnostični podatki so zbrani in poslani Microsoftu. V njih so podatki o odjemalski programski opremi za Office v napravi uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-107">This diagnostic data is collected and sent to Microsoft about Office client software running on the user's device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-108">Nekateri diagnostični podatki so obvezni, medtem ko so drugi izbirni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-108">Some diagnostic data is required, while some diagnostic data is optional.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-109">S kontrolniki zasebnosti lahko izbirate, ali nam boste poslali zahtevane ali izbirne diagnostične podatke, kot so na primer nastavitve pravilnikov za organizacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-109">We give you the ability to choose whether to send us required or optional diagnostic data through the use of privacy controls, such as policy settings for organizations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-110">S Pregledovalnikom diagnostičnih podatkov lahko vidite, kateri diagnostični podatki so nam poslani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-110">You can see the diagnostic data being sent to us by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-111">\***Obvezni diagnostični podatki** _ vključujejo najmanjšo nujno količino podatkov, potrebnih za zagotavljanje varnosti, posodobitev in pričakovanega delovanja Officea v napravi, v kateri je sistem nameščen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-111">\***Required diagnostic data** _ is the minimum data necessary to help keep Office secure, up-to-date, and performing as expected on the device it's installed on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-112">Z obveznimi diagnostičnimi podatki prepoznate težave z Officeom, ki so morda povezane z napravo ali konfiguracijo programske opreme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-112">Required diagnostic data helps to identify problems with Office that may be related to a device or software configuration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-113">Z njimi lahko na primer prepoznate pogoste zrušitve novo uvedenih Officeovih funkcij v določeni različici operacijskega sistema oz. onemogočene Officeove funkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-113">For example, it can help determine if an Office feature crashes more frequently on a particular operating system version, with newly introduced features, or when certain Office features are disabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-114">Z obveznimi diagnostičnimi podatki lahko hitreje zaznamo, diagnosticiramo in odpravimo te težave ter tako zmanjšamo njihov vpliv na uporabnike ali organizacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-114">Required diagnostic data helps us detect, diagnose, and fix these problems more quickly so the impact to users or organizations is reduced.</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-116">Izbirni diagnostični podatki za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-116">Optional diagnostic data for Office</span></span>](optional-diagnostic-data.md)

## <a name="categories-and-data-fields-that-are-common-for-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-167">Skupne kategorije in podatkovna polja za vse dogodke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-167">Categories and data fields that are common for all events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-168">Nekatere informacije o dogodkih so skupne za vse dogodke, ne glede na kategorije ali podatkovne podtipe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-168">There is some information about events that is common to all events, regardless of category or data subtype.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-169">Te skupne informacije, ki jih včasih imenujemo *podatkovne pogodbe* , so organizirane v kategorije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-169">This common information, which is sometimes referred to as *data contracts* , is organized into categories.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-170">Posamezne kategorije vključujejo polja, ta polja pa vsebujejo metapodatke in lastnosti posameznih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-170">Each category contains fields, and these fields are the metadata and properties of an individual event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-171">Te informacije si lahko ogledate s Pregledovalnikom diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-171">You can view this information by using the Diagnostic Data Viewer.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-172">Kategorije zbranih informacij o dogodkih lahko razdelite v dve skupini:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-172">The categories of information that is collected about events can be divided into two groups:</span></span>

  - [<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-173">Skupne informacije za vse dogodke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-173">Information common to all events</span></span>](#information-common-to-all-events)
  - [<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-174">Informacije, ki posebej podpirajo zbiranje diagnostičnih podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-174">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection</span></span>](#information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection)

### <a name="information-common-to-all-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-175">*Skupne informacije za vse dogodke*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-175">*Information common to all events*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-176">Informacije, skupne za vse dogodke, so zbrane v teh kategorijah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-176">Information common to all events is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="app"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-177">Aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-177">App</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-178">Informacije o aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-178">Information about the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-179">Vsa polja so nespremenljiva za vse seje določene različice aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-179">All fields are constant for all sessions of a given application version.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-180">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-180">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-181">**Branch** – Veja posamezne graditve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-181">**Branch** - The branch that the given build came from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-182">Omogoča, da določimo vrsto veje posamezne graditve ter tako izberemo ustrezne rešitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-182">Allows us to determine what type of branch a given build came from so that we can correctly target fixes.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-183">**InstallType** – Popisovalnik, ki določa način uporabnikove namestitve aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-183">**InstallType** - An enumerator that identifies how the user installed the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-184">Omogoča prepoznavanje morebitnih težav določenih namestitvenih mehanizmov, ki jih v drugih ni mogoče zaznati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-184">Allows us to determine if specific install mechanisms are creating issues that are not seen in other installation mechanisms.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-185">**Name** – Ime aplikacije, ki ustvarja podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-185">**Name** - The name of the application that is providing the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-186">Omogoča, da določimo, v kateri aplikaciji je prišlo do težave in tako pripravimo ustrezno rešitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-186">Allows us to identify which application is showing an issue so we know how to address it.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-187">**Platform** – Širša klasifikacija platforme, v kateri se izvaja aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-187">**Platform** - The broad classification of the platform on which the app is running.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-188">Omogoča, da določimo, v kateri platformi je prišlo do težav ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-188">Allows us to identify on which platforms an issue may be occurring so that we can correctly prioritize the issue.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-189">**Version** – Različica aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-189">**Version** - The version of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-190">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerih različicah izdelka je prišlo do težave ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-190">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

#### <a name="client"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-191">Odjemalec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-191">Client</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-192">Identifikator, povezan s primerkom sistema Office v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-192">Identifier related to an Office instance on a device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-193">Konstanta za vse seje vseh aplikacij določene različice namestitve za zbirke več aplikacij oz. konstanta za vse seje določene različice aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-193">Constant for all sessions of all apps of a given installation version for multi-app suites, or constant for all sessions of a given application version.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-195">**Id** – Enolični identifikator, ki je dodeljen odjemalcu ob času namestitve Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-195">**Id** - Unique identifier assigned to a client at install time of Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-196">Omogoča, da določimo, ali težave vplivajo na izbran nabor namestitev in koliko uporabnikov je zaznalo te težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-196">Allows us to identify whether issues are impacting a select set of installs and how many users are impacted.</span></span>

#### <a name="consent"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-197">Soglasje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-197">Consent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-198">Informacije o uporabnikovem soglasju za uporabo diagnostičnih podatkov in povezanih izkušenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-198">Information regarding the users consent for diagnostic data and connected experiences.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-199">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-199">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-200">**ControllerConnectedServicesSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik izbral uporabo izbirnih povezanih izkušenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-200">**ControllerConnectedServicesSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user's choice for optional connected experiences was made</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-201">**ControllerConnectedServicesState** – Označuje, ali ima uporabnik dostop do izbirnih povezanih izkušenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-201">**ControllerConnectedServicesState** – Indicates whether the user has access to optional connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-202">**ControllerConnectedServicesStateConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik izbral stanje izbirnih povezanih izkušenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-202">**ControllerConnectedServicesStateConsentTime** – Indicates when the user chose the status of optional connected experiences.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-203">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-203">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-204">**DiagnosticConsentConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik soglašal z uporabo diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-204">**DiagnosticConsentConsentTime** – Indicates when the user provided the consent for diagnostic data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-205">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-205">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-206">**DiagnosticConsentLevel** – Označuje raven soglasja za uporabo diagnostičnih podatkov, ki ga je podelil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-206">**DiagnosticConsentLevel** – Indicates what level of diagnostic data consent the user has given</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-207">**DiagnosticConsentLevelSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik soglašal z uporabo diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-207">**DiagnosticConsentLevelSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user had provided the consent for diagnostic data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-208">**DownloadContentSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki prenašajo spletno vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-208">**DownloadContentSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user made the choice to enable or disable connected experiences that that download online content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-209">**DownloadContentState** – Označuje, ali je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki prenašajo spletno vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-209">**DownloadContentState** – Indicates whether the user has chosen to enable or disable connected experiences that download online content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-210">**DownloadContentStateConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki prenašajo spletno vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-210">**DownloadContentStateConsentTime** – Indicates when the user made the choice to enable or disable connected experiences that download online content.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-211">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-211">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-212">**ServiceConnectionState** – Označuje, ali je uporabnik izbral, da želi oz. ne želi uporabljati vse povezane izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-212">**ServiceConnectionState** – Indicates whether the user has chosen to use or not use all connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-213">**ServiceConnectionStateConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik izbral, ali želi uporabljati vse povezane izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-213">**ServiceConnectionStateConsentTime** – Indicates when the user chose whether to use all connected experiences.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-214">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-214">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-215">**ServiceConnectionStateSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik izbral možnost uporabe vseh povezanih izkušenj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-215">**ServiceConnectionStateSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user provided the choice whether to use all connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-216">**UserCategoryValue** – Določa vrsto uporabnika, ki je podelil soglasje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-216">**UserCategoryValue –** Identified the type of user who made the consent.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-217">MSAUser, AADUser ali LocalDeviceUser.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-217">One of MSAUser, AADUser or LocalDeviceUser</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-218">**UserContentDependentSourceLocation** – Označuje, kako je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki analizirajo vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-218">**UserContentDependentSourceLocation** – Indicates how the user's choice to enable or disable was made for connected experiences that analyze content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-219">**UserContentDependentState** – Označuje, ali je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki analizirajo vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-219">**UserContentDependentState** – Indicates whether the user has chosen to enable or disable connected experiences that analyze content</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-220">**UserContentDependentStateConsentTime** – Označuje, kdaj je uporabnik omogočil oz. onemogočil povezane izkušnje, ki analizirajo vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-220">**UserContentDependentStateConsentTime** – Indicates when the user chose to enable or disable connected experiences that analyze content was made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-221">Datum bo prikazan kot človeško berljiv datum ali kot strojno kodiran datum, ki je videti kot veliko število.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-221">The date will appear as either a human readable date or as a machine encoded date that looks like a large number.</span></span>

#### <a name="device"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-222">Naprava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-222">Device</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-223">Informacije o operacijskem sistemu in graditvi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-223">Information about the operating system and build.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-224">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-224">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-225">**OsBuild** – Številka graditve operacijskega sistema, ki je nameščena v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-225">**OsBuild** - The build number of the operating system installed on the device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-226">Omogoča, da določimo, ali težave različno vplivajo na posamezne servisne pakete oz. različice določenega operacijskega sistema ter jih razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-226">Allows us to identify whether issues are impacting individual service packs or versions of a given operating system differently than others so we can prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-227">**OsVersion** – Glavna različica operacijskega sistema, ki je nameščena v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-227">**OsVersion** - The major version of the operating system installed on the device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-228">Omogoča, da določimo, ali nekatere težave vplivajo na določeno različico operacijskega sistema bolj kot druge ter jih razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-228">Allows us to determine if issues are impacting a particular operating system version more than other so we can prioritize issues.</span></span>

#### <a name="legacy"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-229">Starejša različica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-229">Legacy</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-230">Vsebuje ID aplikacije in različico operacijskega sistema za združljivost z obstoječimi starejšimi postopki zbiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-230">Provides an App Id and OS version for compatibility with existing legacy collection practices.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-231">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-231">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-232">**AppId** – Vrednost popisovalnika, ki označuje, katera aplikacija posreduje podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-232">**AppId** - An enumerator value representing which application is sending the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-233">Omogoča, da določimo, v kateri aplikaciji je prišlo do težave in tako pripravimo ustrezno rešitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-233">Allows us to identify which application is showing an issue so we know how to address it.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-234">**OsEnv** – Popisovalnik, ki določa, v katerem operacijskem sistemu se izvaja seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-234">**OsEnv** - An enumerator indicating which operating system the session is running on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-235">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerem operacijskem sistemu je prišlo do težav ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-235">Allows us to identify which operating system an issue happening on so we can prioritize issues.</span></span>

#### <a name="release"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-236">Izdaja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-236">Release</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-237">Informacije, povezane s kanalom izdaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-237">Information related to the release channel.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-238">Vsa polja so nespremenljiva za vse seje vseh aplikacij določene različice namestitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-238">All fields are constant for all sessions of all apps of a given installation version.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-239">Določa skupino vseh naprav znotraj ene faze cikla izdaje izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-239">Identifies a group of devices all in one phase of a product release cycle.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-240">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-240">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-241">**Audience** – Določa podskupino občinstva določene skupine občinstva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-241">**Audience** - Identifies a sub-audience of a given audience group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-242">Omogoča spremljanje podmnožic skupin občinstva za ocenjevanje razširjenosti in ravni pomembnosti težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-242">Allows us to track subsets of audience groups to evaluate prevalence and prioritization of issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-243">**AudienceGroup** – Določa krog, kjer so ustvarjeni podatki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-243">**AudienceGroup** - Identifies the ring where data is coming from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-244">Omogoča postopno uvajanje funkcij in prepoznavanje morebitnih težav, preden te dosežejo večji del uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-244">Allows us to roll out features in a staged fashion and identify potential issues before they reach most users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-245">**Channel** – Kanal, v katerem je izdan določen izdelek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-245">**Channel** - The channel that the product is being released through.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-246">Omogoča, da prepoznamo, ali določene težave različno vplivajo na kanale za uvajanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-246">Allows us to identify if an issue is impacting one of our rollout channels differently than others.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-247">**Fork** – Določa vejitev izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-247">**Fork** - Identifies the fork of the product.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-248">Omogoča mehanizem za združevanje podatkov v naboru številk graditve za prepoznavanje težav, povezanih z določeno izdajo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-248">Allows a mechanism to aggregate data across a set of build numbers to identify issues related to a given release.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-249">Seja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-249">Session</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-250">Informacije o seji obdelave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-250">Information about the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-251">Vsa polja so nespremenljiva za to sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-251">All fields are constant for this session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-252">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-252">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-253">**ABConfigs** – Določa nabor pilotnih različic, ki se izvajajo v določeni seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-253">**ABConfigs** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-254">Omogoča, da ugotovimo, katere pilotne različice se izvajajo v seji ter tako določimo, ali je pilotna različica izvor uporabnikovih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-254">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-255">**EcsETag** – Indikator sistema pilotnih različic, ki predstavlja pilotne različice, poslane v računalnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-255">**EcsETag** - An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-256">Omogoča, da določimo, katere pilotne različice morda vplivajo na določeno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-256">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-257">**Flags** – Zastavice za sledenje bitne maske celotne seje, trenutno osredotočene predvsem na možnosti vzorčenja in diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-257">**Flags** - Bitmask tracking flags applicable to an entire session, currently primarily focused on sampling and diagnostic data options.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-258">Omogoča nadziranje načina delovanja določene seje v primerjavi z diagnostičnimi podatki, ki jih ustvari seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-258">Allows us to control how a given session behaves in relation to the diagnostic data that the session generates.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-259">**Id** – Enolično identificira določeno podatkovno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-259">**Id** - Uniquely identifies a given session of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-260">Omogoča, da določimo vpliv težav tako, da ocenimo število prizadetih sej in prepoznamo morebitne skupne značilnosti teh sej.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-260">Allows us to identify the impact of issues by evaluating the number of sessions that are impacted and if there are common features of those sessions.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-261">**ImpressionId** – Določa nabor pilotnih različic, ki se izvajajo v določeni seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-261">**ImpressionId** - Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-262">Omogoča, da ugotovimo, katere pilotne različice se izvajajo v seji ter tako določimo, ali je pilotna različica izvor uporabnikovih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-262">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-263">**MeasuresEnabled** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali so podatki trenutne seje vzorčni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-263">**MeasuresEnabled** - Flag indicating if the current sessions data is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-264">Omogoča, da določimo, kako statistično oceniti podatke, zbrane v določeni seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-264">Allows us to determine how to statistically evaluate the data that is gathered from the given session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-265">**SamplingClientIdValue** – ID odjemalca, s katerim določimo, ali je del vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-265">**SamplingClientIdValue** - The id of the client used to determine if it is part of sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-266">Omogoča, da določimo, zakaj so bile posamezne seje vključene oz. izključene iz vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-266">Allows us to determine why an individual session was included or excluded from sampling.</span></span>
  
 - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-267">**SubAppName** – Za aplikacijo Office Mobile to polje označuje temeljno aplikacijo, uporabljeno za odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-267">**SubAppName** - For Office Mobile app, this field represents the underlying application being used to open a document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-268">Če na primer odprete Wordov dokument v aplikaciji Office, je v tem polju prikazana vrednost »Word«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-268">For example, if you open a Word document in Office app, this field will report the value of “Word”.</span></span>

 - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-269">**VirtualizationType** – vrsta ponazoritve, če se ta izvaja v Officeu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-269">**VirtualizationType** - Type of virtualization if Office is running in one.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-270">Na voljo so te vrednosti:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-270">The possible values are:</span></span> 
    - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-271">0 = Brez</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-271">0 = None</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-272">1 = Navidezno namizje sistema Windows</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-272">1 = Windows Virtual Desktop</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-273">2 = Windows Defender Application Guard</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-273">2 = Windows Defender Application Guard</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-274">3 = Windows Core OS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-274">3 = Windows Core OS</span></span>

#### <a name="user"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-275">Uporabnik</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-275">User</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-276">Na voljo so informacije o najemniku za inventarne številke komercialne programske opreme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-276">Provides tenant information for commercial software SKUs.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-277">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-277">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-278">**PrimaryIdentityHash** – Identifikator s psevdonimom, ki označuje trenutnega uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-278">**PrimaryIdentityHash** – A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-279">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** – Vrsta identitete, ki jo vsebuje polje »PrimaryIdentityHash«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-279">**PrimaryIdentitySpace** – The type of identity contained in the PrimaryIdentityHash.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-280">MASCID, OrgIdCID ali UserObjectId.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-280">One of MASCID, OrgIdCID or UserObjectId.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-281">**TenantGroup** – Vrsta najemnika, kamor sodi naročnina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-281">**TenantGroup** - The type of the tenant that the subscription belongs to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-282">Omogoča, da razvrstimo težave in določimo, ali je težava razširjena oz. omejena na določen nabor uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-282">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-283">**TenantId** – Najemnik, s katerim je povezana uporabnikova naročnina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-283">**TenantId** - The tenant that a user's subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-284">Omogoča, da razvrstimo težave in določimo, ali je težava razširjena ali omejena na določen nabor uporabnikov oz. določenega najemnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-284">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

### <a name="information-that-specifically-supports-diagnostic-data-collection"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-285">*Informacije, ki posebej podpirajo zbiranje diagnostičnih podatkov*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-285">*Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-286">Informacije, ki posebej podpirajo zbiranje diagnostičnih podatkov, so zbrane v teh kategorijah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-286">Information that specifically supports diagnostic data collection is collected in the following categories.</span></span>

#### <a name="activity"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-287">Dejavnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-287">Activity</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-288">Informacije, ki omogočajo razumevanje uspešno izvedenega dogodka zbiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-288">Information to understand the success of the collection event itself.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-289">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-289">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-290">**AggMode** – Sporoči sistemu, kako naj združi rezultate dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-290">**AggMode** - Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-291">Omogoča, da zmanjšamo količino prenesenih informacij iz uporabnikovega računalnika tako, da združimo rezultate dejavnosti v en dogodek, ki ga redno pošiljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-291">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user's machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-292">**Count** – Število izvajanj določene dejavnosti, če skupno število označuje združeni dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-292">**Count** - The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-293">Omogoča, da določimo, kolikokrat je bila dejavnost uspešno oz. neuspešno izvedena glede na način združevanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-293">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-294">**CV** – Vrednost, ki določa odnos med dejavnostmi in poddejavnostmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-294">**CV** - A value that identifies the relationship between activities and sub-activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-295">Omogoča, da lahko znova ustvarimo odnos med ugnezdenimi dejavnostmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-295">Allows us to rebuild the relationship between nested activities.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-296">**Duration** – Trajanje izvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-296">**Duration** - The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-297">Nam omogoča, da prepoznamo težave z učinkovitostjo delovanja, ki negativno vplivajo na uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-297">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the user's experience.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-298">**Result** . **Code** – Koda, ki jo določa aplikacija, za prepoznavanje določenih rezultatov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-298">**Result** . **Code** - An application defined code to identify a given result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-299">Omogoča, da določimo podrobnosti napake, kot je koda napake, s katero lahko razvrstimo težave in jih odpravimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-299">Allows us to determine more specific details of a given failure such as a failure code that can be used to classify and fix issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-300">**Result.Tag** – Oznaka za celo število, ki določa lokacijo v kodi, kjer je bil ustvarjen rezultat.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-300">**Result.Tag** - An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the result was generated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-301">Omogoča, da natančno določimo lokacijo v kodi, kjer je bil ustvarjen rezultat, ter tako razvrstimo napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-301">Allows us to distinctly identify the location in code where a result was generated which enables classification of failures.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-302">**Result** . **Type** – Vrsta kode rezultata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-302">**Result** . **Type** - The type of the result code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-303">Določa vrsto poslane kode rezultata, tako da lahko ustrezno obravnavamo vrednost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-303">Identifies what type of result code was sent so that the value can be correctly interpreted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-304">**Success** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bila dejavnost uspešna oz. neuspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-304">**Success** - A flag indicating if the activity succeeded or failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-305">Omogoča, da določimo, ali so bila uporabnikova dejanja v izdelku uspešno oz. neuspešno izvedena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-305">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-306">Prepoznamo lahko težave, ki vplivajo na uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-306">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

#### <a name="application"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-307">Aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-307">Application</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-308">Informacije o namestitvi aplikacije, kjer se zbirajo dogodki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-308">Information about the installation of the application from which the events are being gathered.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-309">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-309">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-310">**Architecture** – Arhitektura aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-310">**Architecture** - The architecture of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-311">Razvrstimo lahko napake, ki so morda značilne za določeno arhitekturo aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-311">Let's us classify errors that might be specific to an architecture of the application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-312">**Click2RunPackageVersion** – Številka različice paketa »zagon s klikom«, s katerim ste namestili aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-312">**Click2RunPackageVersion** - The version number of the Click-To-Run package that installed the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-313">Omogoča, da določimo, s katero različico namestitvenega programa je bil nameščen Office ter tako prepoznamo težave, povezane z namestitvijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-313">Allows us to identify which version of the installer was used to install Office so we can identify setup related issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-314">**DistributionChannel** – Kanal, v katerem je bila uvedena aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-314">**DistributionChannel** - The channel where the app was deployed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-315">Omogoča, da razdelimo dohodne podatke na particije ter tako ugotovimo, ali težave vplivajo na občinstvo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-315">Allows us to partition incoming data so we can determine if issues are impacting audiences.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-316">**InstallMethod** – Ali je bila trenutna graditev Officea nadgrajena iz starejše graditve, je bila povrnjena v starejšo graditev oz. gre za novo namestitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-316">**InstallMethod** - Whether the current build of Office was upgraded from an older build, rolled back to an older build, or a fresh install.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-317">**IsClickToRunInstall** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali gre za namestitev »zagon s klikom«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-317">**IsClickToRunInstall** - Flag indicating if install was a click to run install.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-318">Omogoča, da določimo težave, ko so morda značilne za namestitveni mehanizem »zagon s klikom«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-318">Allows us to identify issues that might be specific to the Click-To-Run install mechanism.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-319">**IsDebug** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je to graditev Officea za odpravljanje napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-319">**IsDebug** - Flag indicating if the Office build is a Debug build.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-320">Omogoča, da določimo, ali so vir težav graditve za odpravljanje težav, ki lahko delujejo na drugačen način.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-320">Allows us to identify if issues are coming from Debug builds which may behave differently.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-321">**IsInstalledOnExternalStorage** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil Office nameščen v zunanjo napravo za shranjevanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-321">**IsInstalledOnExternalStorage** - Flag indicating if Office was installed on an external storage device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-322">Določimo lahko, ali je težavam mogoče slediti v mesto zunanje shrambe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-322">Let's us determine if issues can be traced to an external storage location.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-323">**IsOEMInstalled** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je Office namestil proizvajalec strojne opreme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-323">**IsOEMInstalled** - Flag indicating if Office was installed by an original equipment manufacturer (OEM).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-324">Določimo lahko, ali je aplikacijo namestil proizvajalec strojne opreme ter tako razvrstimo in prepoznamo težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-324">Let's us determine if the application was installed by an OEM which can help us classify and identify issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-325">**PreviousVersion** – Različica Officea, ki je bila predhodno nameščena v računalniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-325">**PreviousVersion** - The version of Office that was previously installed on the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-326">Omogoča povrnitev na prejšnjo različico, če ima trenutna različica težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-326">Allows us to roll back to a previous version if the current one has an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-327">**ProcessFileName** – Ime datoteke aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-327">**ProcessFileName** - The name of the application filename.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-328">Omogoča določitev imena izvedljive datoteke, ki ustvarja podatke, saj je za isto ime aplikacije lahko na voljo več različnih imen datotek postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-328">Allows us to identify the name of the executable which is generating the data as there may be several different process filenames reporting as the same app name.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-332">**FirstRunTime** – Prvo izvajanje odjemalca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-332">**FirstRunTime** - The first time the client was run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-333">Omogoča nam vpogled v podatke o tem, koliko časa ima odjemalec že nameščen Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-333">Allows us to understand how long the client has had Office installed.</span></span>

#### <a name="device"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-334">Naprava</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-334">Device</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-335">Informacije o konfiguraciji naprave in zmogljivostih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-335">Information about device configuration and capabilities.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-336">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-336">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-337">**DigitizerInfo** – Informacije o digitalizatorju, ki ga uporablja računalnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-337">**DigitizerInfo** - Information on the digitizer used by the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-338">Omogoča razvrstitev podatkov glede na osrednjo napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-338">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-339">**FormFactor** – Določa dimenzije naprave, ki pošilja podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-339">**FormFactor** - Identifies what form factor the device sending the info is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-340">Omogoča razvrstitev podatkov glede na osrednjo napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-340">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-341">**FormFactorFamily** – Določa dimenzije naprave, ki pošilja podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-341">**FormFactorFamily** - Identifies what form factor the device sending the info is.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-342">Omogoča razvrstitev podatkov glede na osrednjo napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-342">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-343">**HorizontalResolution** – Vodoravna ločljivost zaslona naprav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-343">**HorizontalResolution** - The horizontal resolution of the devices screen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-344">Omogoča razvrstitev podatkov glede na osrednjo napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-344">Allows us to classify data based on device pivot.</span></span>

#### <a name="event"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-387">Dogodek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-387">Event</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-388">Informacije o dogodku, vključno z enoličnim identifikatorjem seje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-388">Event-specific information, including its unique identifier in the session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-389">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-389">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-390">**Contract** – Seznam morebitnih pogodb, ki jih dogodek uveljavlja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-390">**Contract** - A list of any contracts that the event is implementing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-391">Omogoča, da lahko ocenimo, kateri podatki so del posameznih dogodkov, tako da jih lahko učinkovito obdelamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-391">Allows us to evaluate what data is part of the individual event so that we can process it effectively.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-392">**CV** – Vrednost, s katero lahko identificiramo dogodke, ki so medsebojno povezani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-392">**CV** - A value that allows us to identify events that are related to one another.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-393">Te podatke uporabljamo za diagnostiko, da lahko določimo vzorce povezanega načina delovanja oz. povezanih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-393">Used for diagnostics to allow us to identify patterns of related behavior or related events.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-394">**Flags** – Informacije, s katerimi lahko spremenimo način odzivanja določenega dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-394">**Flags** - Information used to alter how a given event responds.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-395">Omogoča, da lahko upravljamo način obravnavanja določenega dogodka za namene prenašanja podatkov Microsoftu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-395">Used to manage how a given event is treated for the purposes of uploading the data to Microsoft.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-396">**Id** – Enolični identifikator dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-396">**Id** - A unique identifier for the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-397">Omogoča enolično identificiranje prejetih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-397">Allows us to uniquely identify the events that are being received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-398">**Level** – Označuje vrsto dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-398">**Level** - denotes the type of event.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-399">**Name** – Ime dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-399">**Name** - The name of the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-400">Omogoča določitev dogodka, ki ga je poslal odjemalec.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-400">Allows to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-401">**Rule** – Identifikator pravila, ki je ustvarilo podatke (če je te ustvarilo pravilo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-401">**Rule** - An identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-402">Omogoča določitev vira dela podatkov, tako da lahko preverimo veljavnost parametrov dogodkov in jih upravljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-402">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-403">**RuleId** – Identifikator pravila, ki je ustvarilo podatke (če je te ustvarilo pravilo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-403">**RuleId** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-404">Omogoča določitev vira dela podatkov, tako da lahko preverimo veljavnost parametrov dogodkov in jih upravljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-404">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-405">**RuleInterfaces** – Vsi vmesniki, ki jih uveljavi določeno pravilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-405">**RuleInterfaces** - Any interfaces that are implemented by the specific rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-406">Omogoča, da razvrstimo in uvozimo podatke glede na njihovo strukturo ter tako poenostavimo obdelavo podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-406">Allows us to classify and import the data based on its structure which simplifies data processing.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-407">**RuleVersion** – Identifikator pravila, ki je ustvarilo podatke (če je te ustvarilo pravilo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-407">**RuleVersion** - The identifier of the rule that generated the data if it was generated by a rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-408">Omogoča določitev vira dela podatkov, tako da lahko preverimo veljavnost parametrov dogodkov in jih upravljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-408">Allows us to identify the source of a piece of data so that we can validate and manage that events parameters.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-409">**SampleRate** – navedbo, Kolikšen odstotek uporabnikov pošilja ta del podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-409">**SampleRate** - An indication of what percentage of users are sending this piece of data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-410">Na ta način lahko izvedemo statistične analize podatkov in za zelo pogosta podatkovna mesta ne zahtevajo, da jih pošljejo vsi uporabniki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-410">This allows us to do statistical analysis of the data and for very common data points not require that to be sent by all users.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-411">**SchemaVersion** – Različica sheme, ki je uporabljena za ustvarjanje diagnostičnih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-411">**SchemaVersion** - The version of the schema used to generate diagnostic data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-412">Zahtevano za upravljanje podatkov, poslanih iz odjemalca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-412">Required to manage data being sent from the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-413">Omogoča, da lahko sčasoma spremenimo vrsto podatkov, ki jih pošilja odjemalec.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-413">This allows changes over time in what data is being sent from each client.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-414">**Sequence** – Števec, ki določa vrstni red ustvarjenih dogodkov v odjemalcu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-414">**Sequence** - A counter that identifies the order that an event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-415">Omogoča razvrstitev prejetih podatkov tako, da lahko prepoznamo korake, ki so odjemalce morda privedli do določnih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-415">Allows the data being received to be ordered so that we can identify what steps may have led to an issue that is impacting clients.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-416">**Source** – Izvorni cevovod, uporabljen za prenos podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-416">**Source** - The source pipeline that was used to upload the data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-417">Zahtevano za spremljanje posameznih cevovodov za prenašanje za zagotavljanje ustreznosti stanja sistema in lažje prepoznavanje težav s cevovodom za prenašanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-417">Required to monitor each of our upload pipelines for overall health and to help identify issues with the upload pipeline.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-418">Omogoča spremljanje posameznih cevovodov za prenašanje za zagotavljanje njihove skladnosti s predpisi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-418">This allows us to monitor individual upload pipelines to make sure they remain compliant.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-419">**Time** – Čas, ko je bil dogodek ustvarjen v odjemalcu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-419">**Time** - The time that the event was generated on the client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-420">Omogoča, da lahko sinhroniziramo in preverimo veljavnost vrstnega reda dogodkov, ustvarjenih v odjemalcu, ter izdelamo metriko učinkovitosti delovanja za navodila za uporabnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-420">Allows us to synchronize and validate the order of events generated on the client as well as establish performance metrics for user instructions.</span></span>
