#### <a name="legacy"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-427">Starejša različica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-427">Legacy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-428">Informacije, potrebne za združljivost starejše različice sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-428">Information needed for legacy system compatibility.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-429">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-429">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-430">**OsBuild** – Določena številka graditve operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-430">**OsBuild** - The specific build number of the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-431">Omogoča, da določimo, iz katere različice operacijskega sistema izhajajo diagnostični podatki ter tako razvrstimo težave po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-431">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-432">**OsBuildRevision** – Številka revizije graditve operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-432">**OsBuildRevision** - The revision number of the build of the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-433">Omogoča, da določimo, iz katere različice operacijskega sistema izhajajo diagnostični podatki ter tako razvrstimo težave po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-433">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-434">**OsMinorVersion** – Podrazličica operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-434">**OsMinorVersion** - The minor version of the operating system.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-435">Omogoča, da določimo, iz katere različice operacijskega sistema izhajajo diagnostični podatki ter tako razvrstimo težave po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-435">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-436">**OsVersionString** – Enolični niz, ki predstavlja številko različice operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-436">**OsVersionString** - A unified string representing the operating system build number.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-437">Omogoča, da določimo, iz katere različice operacijskega sistema izhajajo diagnostični podatki ter tako razvrstimo težave po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-437">Allows us to determine which version of the operating system the diagnostic data is coming from in order to prioritize issues.</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-438">Seja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-438">Session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-439">Informacije o seji obdelave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-439">Information about the process session.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-440">Ta kategorija vsebuje ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-440">This category contains the following fields:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-441">**ABConfigsDelta** – Spremlja razliko med trenutnimi podatki »ABConfigs« in prejšnjo vrednostjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-441">**ABConfigsDelta** - Tracks the difference between the current ABConfigs data and the previous value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-442">Omogoča spremljanje novih pilotnih različic v računalniku, tako da lahko določite, ali je nova pilotna različica morda kriva za težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-442">Allows us to track what new flights are on the machine to help identify if a new flight is responsible for an issue.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-443">**CollectibleClassification** – Razredi informacij, ki jih lahko zbira seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-443">**CollectibleClassification** - The classes of information the session can collect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-444">Omogoča filtriranje sej glede na razpoložljive podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-444">Allows filtering of sessions based on the data they would have.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-445">**DisableTelemetry** – Zastavica, ki označuje, ali je ključ »DisableTelemetry« nastavljen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-445">**DisableTelemetry** - Flag indicating if the DisableTelemetry key is set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-446">Omogoča, da si lahko ogledamo, ali je seja poročala le o diagnostičnih podatkih »EssentialServiceMetadata«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-446">Allows us to know if a session was not reporting diagnostic data other than EssentialServiceMetadata.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-447">**SamplingClientIdValue** – Vrednost ključa, s katerim je določeno vzorčenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-447">**SamplingClientIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-448">Omogoča, da lahko prepoznamo razlog za vzorčenje oz. izključitev iz vzorčenja za določeno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-448">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-449">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** – Vrednost ključa, s katerim je določeno vzorčenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-449">**SamplingDeviceIdValue** - The value of the key used to determine sampling.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-450">Omogoča, da lahko prepoznamo razlog za vzorčenje oz. izključitev iz vzorčenja za določeno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-450">Allows us to determine why a session was sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-451">**SamplingKey** – Ključ, uporabljen za določanje, ali je seja vzorčna ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-451">**SamplingKey** - The key used to determine whether the session is sampled or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-452">Omogoča prikaz podatkov, ki določajo, ali je seja vzorčna ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-452">Allows us to understand how individual sessions are making their choice of whether they are sampled or not.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-453">**SamplingMethod** – Način, uporabljen za določanje pravilnika vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-453">**SamplingMethod** - The method used to determine sampling policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-454">Omogoča razumevanje vrste podatkov, ki jih ustvarja seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-454">Allows us to understand what data is coming from a session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-455">**SamplingSessionKValue** – Dodatni metapodatki vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-455">**SamplingSessionKValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-456">Omogoča ocenjevanje statističnega pomena prejetih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-456">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-457">**SamplingSessionNValue** – Dodatni metapodatki vzorčenja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-457">**SamplingSessionNValue** - Advanced sampling metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-458">Omogoča ocenjevanje statističnega pomena prejetih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-458">Used to help evaluate statistical meaning of data that is received.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-459">**Sequence** – Enolični številski identifikator seje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-459">**Sequence** - A unique numeric identifier for the session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-460">Omogoča naročanje sej za analizo težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-460">Allows the ordering of sessions for analysis of the issues might have occurred.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-461">**Start** – Čas zagona seje postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-461">**Start** - The boot time of the process session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-462">Omogoča določitev časa začetka izvajanja seje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-462">Allows us to establish when the session started.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-463">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** – Vrednost, ki določa, katero raven diagnostičnih podatkov je izbral uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-463">**TelemetryPermissionLevel** - Value indicating what level of diagnostic data the user has opted into.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-464">Omogoča razumevanje ravni diagnostičnih podatkov, ki jih bo ustvarila seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-464">Allows us to understand what level of diagnostic data to expect from a session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-465">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** – Razlika med UTC-jem in lokalnim časom v minutah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-465">**TimeZoneBiasInMinutes** - The difference in minutes between UTC and the local time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-466">Omogoča normaliziranje časov UTC v lokalne čase.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-466">Allows normalization of UTC times back to the local time.</span></span>

## <a name="data-fields-that-are-common-for-onenote-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-467">Podatkovna polja, ki so skupna za dogodke storitve OneNote</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-467">Data fields that are common for OneNote events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-468">Naslednja podatkovna polja so skupna za vse dogodke storitve OneNote za Mac, iOS in Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-468">The following data fields are common for all events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-469">Kadar uporabljate pregledovalnik diagnostičnih podatkov, je prikazano ime »Dejavnost«, »ReportData« ali »Nepričakovano« za dogodke storitve OneNote za Mac, iOS in Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-469">When using the Diagnostic Data Viewer, events for OneNote on Mac, iOS, and Android will appear to have a name of Activity, ReportData, or Unexpected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-470">Če želite najti dejansko ime dogodka, izberite dogodek in si nato oglejte polje »EventName«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-470">To find the actual event name, select the event, and then look at the EventName field.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-471">**Activity_ActivityType** – označuje vrsto tega dogodka dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-471">**Activity_ActivityType** -  Indicates the type of this activity event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-472">Dejavnost je lahko normalna dejavnost ali dejavnost z visoko vrednostjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-472">An activity can be a normal activity or a high value activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-473">**Activity_AggMode** – sporoči sistemu, kako naj združi rezultate dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-473">**Activity_AggMode** -  Tells the system how to aggregate activity results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-474">Omogoča, da zmanjšamo količino prenesenih informacij iz uporabnikovega računalnika tako, da združimo rezultate dejavnosti v en dogodek, ki ga redno pošiljamo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-474">Allows us to reduce the amount of information uploaded from a user's machine by aggregating activity results into a single event that gets sent periodically.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-475">**Activity_Count** – število izvajanj določene dejavnosti, če pridobljeno število označuje združeni dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-475">**Activity_Count** -  The number of times the activity happened if the count is from an aggregated event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-476">Omogoča, da določimo, kolikokrat je bila dejavnost uspešno oz. neuspešno izvedena glede na način združevanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-476">Allows us to determine how often an activity succeeded or failed based on the aggregation mode of the activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-477">**Activity_CV** – vrednost, ki določa odnos med dejavnostmi in poddejavnostmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-477">**Activity_CV** -  A value that identifies the relationship between activities and sub-activities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-478">Omogoča, da lahko znova ustvarimo odnos med ugnezdenimi dejavnostmi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-478">Allows us to rebuild the relationship between nested activities.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-479">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** – čas, ko je dejavnost nedejavna in ne izvaja nobenega dejanskega dela, vendar se čas še vedno sešteva za pridobitev skupnega časa dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-479">**Activity_DetachedDurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time an activity is idle and not doing any real work, but the time is still count towards the total activity's time.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-480">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** – trajanje izvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-480">**Activity_DurationInMicroseconds** -  The length of time the activity took to execute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-481">Nam omogoča, da prepoznamo težave z učinkovitostjo delovanja, ki negativno vplivajo na uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-481">Allows us to identify performance issues that are negatively impacting the user's experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-482">**Activity_Expiration** – datum v številski obliki označuje, kdaj bo prišlo do ustavitve pošiljanja tega dogodka iz odjemalcev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-482">**Activity_Expiration** -  A date in numerical format indicates when this event will be stop sending from clients</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-483">**Activity_FailCount** – število, ki pokaže, kolikokrat je bila ta dejavnost neuspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-483">**Activity_FailCount** -  A number of times this activity has failed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-484">**Activity_Name** – kratko ime dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-484">**Activity_Name** -  A short name of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-485">Omogoča določitev dogodka, ki ga je poslal odjemalec.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-485">Allows to identify the event that was being sent from the client.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-486">**Activity_Namespace** – imenski prostor dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-486">**Activity_Namespace** -  A namespace of an event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-487">Omogoča združevanje dogodkov v skupine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-487">Allows to group the event into groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-488">**Activity_Reason** – niz, ki označuje razlog, zaradi katerega je dejavnost končana z določenim rezultatom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-488">**Activity_Reason** -  A string indicating the reason causing an activity to ends with a particular result.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-489">**Activity_Result** – zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bila dejavnost uspešna, neuspešna ali nepričakovano neuspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-489">**Activity_Result** -  A flag indicating if the activity succeeded, failed, or unexpectedly failed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-490">Omogoča, da določimo, ali so bila uporabnikova dejanja v izdelku uspešno oz. neuspešno izvedena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-490">Allows us to determine if actions the user takes in the product are succeeding or failing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-491">Prepoznamo lahko težave, ki vplivajo na uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-491">This allows us to identify issues that are impacting the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-492">**Activity_State** – zastavica označuje, ali je dogodek začetek ali konec dejavnosti uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-492">**Activity_State** -  A flag indicates whether an event is a start of a user activity or an end of a user activity.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-493">**Activity_SucceedCount** – število, ki pokaže, kolikokrat je bila ta dejavnost uspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-493">**Activity_SucceedCount** -  A number of times this activity is succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-494">**ErrorCode** – označuje kodo napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-494">**ErrorCode** -  Indicates an error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-495">**ErrorCode2** – označuje drugo kodo napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-495">**ErrorCode2** -  Indicates a second error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-496">**ErrorCode3** – označuje tretjo kodo napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-496">**ErrorCode3** -  Indicates a third error code if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-497">**ErrorTag** – označuje oznako, ki je povezana s kodo napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-497">**ErrorTag** -  Indicates the tag associated in code of an error if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-498">**ErrorType** – označuje vrsto napake, če je na voljo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-498">**ErrorType** -  Indicates the type of an error if available.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-499">**EventName** – enolično ime dogodka v aplikaciji OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-499">**EventName** -  A unique name of a OneNote's event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-500">Dogodki v aplikaciji OneNote uporabljajo to polje po meri za določanje enoličnega imena zaradi inženirske omejitve v preteklosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-500">OneNote events use this custom field to specify a unique name due to an engineering limitation in the past.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-501">**ExpFeatures** – označuje, ali je uporabnik vklopil stikalo za preskusne funkcije v aplikaciji OneNote ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-501">**ExpFeatures** -  Indicates whether a user has turn-on an experimental-feature switch in OneNote app or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-502">**ExpirationDate** – datum v številski obliki zapisa označuje, kdaj bo ustavljeno pošiljanje tega dogodka iz odjemalcev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-502">**ExpirationDate** -  A date in numerical format indicates when this event will be stop sending from clients</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-503">**IsConsumer** – označuje, ali je uporabnik potrošnik ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-503">**IsConsumer** -  Indicates whether a user is consumer or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-504">**IsEdu** – označuje, ali ima uporabnik status uporabnika v izobraževalnem najemniku ali ne</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-504">**IsEdu** -  Indicates whether a user is a user in education tenant or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-505">**IsIW** – označuje, ali je uporabnik poslovni uporabnik ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-505">**IsIW** -  Indicates whether a user is an enterprise user or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-506">**IsMsftInternal** – označuje, ali je uporabnik zaposleni družbe Microsoft ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-506">**IsMsftInternal** -  Indicates whether a user is a Microsoft employee or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-507">**IsPremiumUser** – označuje, ali ima uporabnik licenco Premium ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-507">**IsPremiumUser** -  Indicates whether a user has premium license or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-508">**Namespace** – imenski prostor dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-508">**Namespace** -  A namespace of the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-509">Omogoča združevanje dogodkov v skupine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-509">Allows to group the event into groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-510">**Release_AppStore** – zastavica označuje, ali je graditev pridobljena v trgovini z aplikacijami ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-510">**Release_AppStore** -  A flag indicates whether a build is coming from an app store or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-511">**Release_Audience** – določa podskupino občinstva za dano skupino občinstva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-511">**Release_Audience** -  Identifies a sub-audience of a given audience group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-512">Omogoča spremljanje podmnožic skupin občinstva za ocenjevanje razširjenosti in ravni pomembnosti težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-512">Allows us to track subsets of audience groups to evaluate prevalence and prioritization of issues.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-513">**AudienceGroup** – določa krog, kjer so ustvarjeni podatki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-513">**Release_AudienceGroup** -  Identifies the ring where data is coming from.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-514">Omogoča postopno uvajanje funkcij in prepoznavanje morebitnih težav, preden te dosežejo večji del uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-514">Allows us to roll out features in a staged fashion and identify potential issues before they reach most users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-515">**Release_Channel** – kanal, v katerem je izdelek izdan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-515">**Release_Channel** -  The channel that the product is being released through.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-516">Omogoča, da prepoznamo, ali določene težave različno vplivajo na kanale za uvajanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-516">Allows us to identify if an issue is impacting one of our rollout channels differently than others.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-517">**RunningMode** – označuje način zagona aplikacije, in sicer s strani uporabnika ali sistemskega procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-517">**RunningMode** -  Indicates how the app is launched either by user or by system process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-518">**SchemaVersion** – prikazuje trenutno različico sheme telemetrije v telemetrijskem prodajnem lijaku v OneNotu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-518">**SchemaVersion** -  Indicates a current telemetry schema version in OneNote's telemetry pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-519">**Session_EcsETag** – indikator sistema pilotnih različic, ki predstavlja pilotne različice, poslane v računalnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-519">**Session_EcsETag** -  An indicator from the flighting system that represents the flights sent to the machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-520">Omogoča, da določimo, katere pilotne različice morda vplivajo na določeno sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-520">Allows us to identify what flights might be impacting a given session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-521">**Session_ImpressionId** – določa nabor pilotnih različic, ki se izvajajo v dani seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-521">**Session_ImpressionId** -  Identifies the set of flights that are running in a given session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-522">Omogoča, da ugotovimo, katere pilotne različice se izvajajo v seji ter tako določimo, ali je pilotna različica izvor uporabnikovih težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-522">Allows us to identify which individual flights are running on a session so that we can determine if a flight is the source of an issue impacting users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-523">**SessionCorrelationId** – globalni enolični identifikator za sejo gostitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-523">**SessionCorrelationId** -  The globally unique identifier for the host's session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-524">**SH_ErrorCode** – označuje kodo napake, če je na voljo ob neuspehu dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-524">**SH_ErrorCode** -  Indicates an error code if available when an activity fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-525">**Tag** – oznaka za celo število, ki določa lokacijo v kodi, kjer je ustvarjen dogodek telemetrije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-525">**Tag** -  An integer tag that identifies the location in code where the telemetry event is generated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-526">**UserInfo_IdType** – niz označuje vrsto uporabniškega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-526">**UserInfo_IdType** -  A string indicates the type of a user's account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-527">**UserInfo.OMSTenantId** – najemnik, s katerim je povezana uporabnikova naročnina.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-527">**UserInfo_OMSTenantId** -  The tenant that a user's subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-528">Omogoča, da razvrstimo težave in določimo, ali je težava razširjena ali omejena na določen nabor uporabnikov oz. določenega najemnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-528">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-529">**UserInfo_OtherId** – seznam psevdonimnih identifikatorjev, ki niso primarni in predstavljajo uporabniške račune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-529">**UserInfo_OtherId** -  A list of non-primary pseudonymous identifiers representing user's accounts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-530">**UserInfo_OtherIdType** – seznam vrst računov, ki niso primarni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-530">**UserInfo_OtherIdType** -  A list of non-primary account types.</span></span>

## <a name="data-fields-that-are-common-for-outlook-mobile-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-531">Podatkovna polja, ki so skupna za dogodke aplikacije Outlook Mobile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-531">Data fields that are common for Outlook mobile events</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-532">Outlook Mobile zbira pogosta polja za vsak naš dogodek, tako da lahko zagotovimo, da je aplikacija posodobljena, varna in deluje po pričakovanjih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-532">Outlook mobile collects common fields for each of our events so that we can ensure the app is up-to-date, secure, and functioning as expected.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-533">Naslednja podatkovna polja so skupna za vse dogodke storitve Outlook za iOS in Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-533">The following data fields are common for all events for Outlook for iOS and Android.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-534">**aad_tenant_id** – ID najemnika stranke, če je na voljo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-534">**aad_tenant_id** - The tenant id of the customer if available</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-535">**account_cid** – identifikator s psevdonimom, ki označuje trenutnega uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-535">**account_cid** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-536">**account_domain** – ime domene računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-536">**account_domain** - Domain name of the account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-537">**account_puid** – globalni enolični identifikator uporabnika za Microsoftov potrošniški račun</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-537">**account_puid** - The globally unique user identifier for a consumer Microsoft account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-538">**account_type** – sledi tipu računa, kot so Office 365, Google Cloud Cache, Outlook.com itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-538">**account_type** - Tracks the account type such as Office 365, Google Cloud Cache, Outlook.com, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-539">**action** – ime dejanja dogodka (kot je arhiviraj, izbriši itd.), da lahko zaznamo težavo z določenimi izvedenimi dejanji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-539">**action** - The event action name (such as archive, delete, etc.) so we can detect issues with specific actions taken</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-540">**ad_id** – enolični identifikator za oglaševanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-540">**ad_id** - The unique advertising identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-541">**app_version** – trenutna različica aplikacije, ki je nameščena, da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki vplivajo na določeno različico aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-541">**app_version** - Current version of the app installed to help us detect issues affecting certain app version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-542">**AppInfo. ETag** – enolični identifikator za upravljanje izdaj naših funkcij, da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki vplivajo na izdane funkcije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-542">**AppInfo.ETag** - A unique identifier for managing release of our features to help us detect issues affecting certain features being released</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-543">**AppInfo.Language** – trenutna jezikovna nastavitev naprave, da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki vplivajo na določene jezike</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-543">**AppInfo.Language** - Currently language setting of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain languages</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-544">**AppInfo.Version** – trenutna različica aplikacije, ki je nameščena, da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki vplivajo na določene različice aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-544">**AppInfo.Version** - Current version of the app installed to help us detect issues affecting certain app versions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-545">**CI** – enolična oznaka naprave z značilnim psevdonimom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-545">**ci** - a pseudonymous app-specific device unique identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-546">**cid_type** – označuje, katero vrsto računa imate, na primer trgovski račun ali račun Outlook.com.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-546">**cid_type** - indicates what type of account it is, such as a commercial account or Outlook.com account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-547">**cloud** – kje v napravi se nahaja nabiralnik računa za zaznavanje težav določenega nabiralnika v oblaku, kot sta Office 365 ali GCC.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-547">**cloud** - Where the mailbox resides for the account on this device to help detect issues specific to a specific mailbox cloud, like Office 365 or GCC.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-548">**customer_type** – označuje vrsto stranke (potrošnik, komercialna stranka, tretja oseba itd.), da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki vplivajo na določene vrste strank</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-548">**customer_type** - Indicates the type of customer (consumer, commercial, third party, etc.) to help us detect issues affecting certain customer types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-549">**device_category** – označuje vrsto naprave (telefon, tablični računalnik itd.), da bomo lahko zaznali težave določene vrste naprav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-549">**device_category** - Indicates what type of device it is (phone, tablet, etc.) to help us detect device category specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-550">**DeviceInfo.Id** – enoličen identifikator naprave, da bomo lahko zaznali težave določene naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-550">**DeviceInfo.Id** - A unique device identifier to help us detect device specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-551">**DeviceInfo.Make** – znamka naprave (tj. Apple, Samsung, itd.), da bomo lahko zaznali težave določene znamke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-551">**DeviceInfo.Make** - The make of the device (i.e. Apple, Samsung, etc.) to help us detect device make specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-552">**DeviceInfo.Model** – model naprave (tj. iPhone 6s), da bomo lahko zaznali težave določenega modela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-552">**DeviceInfo.Model** - The device model (i.e. iPhone 6s) to help us detect device model specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-553">**DeviceInfo.NetworkType** – trenutno omrežje naprave v uporabi (Wi-Fi, mobilno omrežje itd.), da bomo lahko zaznali težave določenega omrežja naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-553">**DeviceInfo.NetworkType** - The current device network being used (WiFi, cellular, etc.) to help us detect device network specific issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-554">**DeviceInfo.OsBuild** – trenutna gradnja operacijskega sistema naprave, da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki vplivajo na določene gradnje operacijskega sistema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-554">**DeviceInfo.OsBuild** - The current OS build of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain OS builds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-555">**DeviceInfo.OsName** – ime operacijskega sistema (na primer iOS), da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki vplivajo na določene platforme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-555">**DeviceInfo.OsName** - The name of the OS (for example, iOS) to help us detect issues affecting certain platforms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-556">**DeviceInfo.OsVersion** – trenutna različica operacijskega sistema naprave, da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki vplivajo na določene različice operacijskega sistema</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-556">**DeviceInfo.OsVersion** - The current OS version of the device to help us detect issues affecting certain OS versions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-557">**DeviceInfo.SDKUid** – enolični identifikator naprave (podobno kot DeviceInfo.Id)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-557">**DeviceInfo.SDKUid** - The device unique identifier (similar to DeviceInfo.Id)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-558">**EventInfo.InitId** – ID, ki so uporablja kot del razvrščanja dogodkov prek našega prodajnega lijaka za telemetrijo, da bomo lahko zaznali korenski vzrok težave prodajnega lijaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-558">**EventInfo.InitId** - Id used as part of sequencing for event ordering through our telemetry pipeline to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-559">**EventInfo.SdkVersion** – različica kompleta za razvoj programske opreme, ki jo uporabljamo za pošiljanje telemetrije, da bomo lahko zaznali korenski vzrok težave prodajnega lijaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-559">**EventInfo.SdkVersion** - The SDK version we are using to send our telemetry to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-560">**EventInfo.Sequence** – zaporedje za razvrščanje dogodkov prek našega prodajnega lijaka za telemetrijo, da bomo lahko zaznali korenski vzrok težave prodajnega lijaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-560">**EventInfo.Sequence** - The sequence is for event ordering through our telemetry pipeline to help us detect the root cause of a pipeline issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-561">**EventInfo.Source** – nam pove, kateri del kode je poslal dogodek, da bomo lahko zaznali korenski vzrok težave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-561">**EventInfo.Source** - Tells us what part of the code sent the event to help us detect the root cause of an issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-562">**EventInfo.Time** – ura in datum, ko je bil dogodek posredovan z naprave, da bodo lahko naši sistemi uspešno upravljali z dohodnimi dogodki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-562">**EventInfo.Time** - The time and date the event was emitted from the device so our systems can successfully manage events coming in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-563">**eventpriority** – prioriteta telemetričnega dogodka glede na druge dogodke, da bodo lahko naši sistemi uspešno upravljali z dohodnimi dogodki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-563">**eventpriority** - The priority of the telemetry event relative to other events so our systems can successfully manage events coming in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-564">**first_launch_date** – prvi zagon aplikacije, da bomo lahko razumeli, kdaj se je težava začela</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-564">**first_launch_date** - The first time the app was launched so helps us understand when an issue first began</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-565">**hashed_email** – identifikator s psevdonimom, ki označuje e-poštni naslov trenutnega uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-565">**hashed_email** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user email</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-566">**is_first_session** – sledi temu, če je to prva seja aplikacije za namene iskanja in odpravljanja napak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-566">**is_first_session** - Tracks if this is the first session of the app for debugging purposes</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-567">**origin** – izvor dejanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-567">**origin** - The origination of an action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-568">Sporočilo, označeno kot prebrano, lahko na primer izvira iz seznama sporočil ali novega e-poštnega obvestila, kar nam pomaga zaznati težave glede na izvor dejanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-568">For example marking a message read can originate from message list or a new mail notification, this helps us detect issues based on action origination</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-569">**PipelineInfo.AccountId** – identifikator s psevdonimom, ki označuje trenutnega uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-569">**PipelineInfo.AccountId** - A pseudonymous identifier that represents the current user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-570">**PipelineInfo.ClientCountry** – trenutna država naprave za zaznavanje težav ali izpadov v določeni državi ali regiji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-570">**PipelineInfo.ClientCountry** - The current country of the device to detect country or region specific issues and outages</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-571">**PipelineInfo.ClientIp** – naslov IP, ki je povezan z napravo za iskanje in odpravljanje napak s povezavo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-571">**PipelineInfo.ClientIp** - The IP address the device is connected to debug connection issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-572">**PipelineInfo.IngestionTime** – časovni žig, kdaj smo prejeli telemetrijo za ta dogodek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-572">**PipelineInfo.IngestionTime** - Timestamp of when our telemetry ingestion happens for this event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-573">**Session.Id** – enolični identifikator za sejo aplikacije, da bomo lahko prepoznali težave določene seje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-573">**Session.Id** - A unique identifier for the app session to help identify session-related issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-574">**Session.ImpressionId** – enolični identifikator za upravljanje izdaj naših funkcij, da lahko zagotovimo uspešno izdajo funkcij za vse uporabnike in naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-574">**Session.ImpressionId** - A unique identifier for managing release of our features to ensure features are successfully released to all users and devices</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-575">**ui_mode** – ali uporabnik uporablja svetli ali temni način, da lahko razvrščamo napake uporabniške izkušnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-575">**ui_mode** - Is the user in light or dark mode, helps us triage UX bugs with dark mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-576">**UserInfo.Language** – jezik uporabnika za iskanje in odpravljanje napak pri prevajanju besedil</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-576">**UserInfo.Language** - The user's language to help debug translation text issues</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-577">**UserInfo.TimeZone** – časovni pas uporabnika za iskanje in odpravljanje napak koledarja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-577">**UserInfo.TimeZone** - The user's time zone to help debug calendar issues</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-578">Poleg tega so naslednja polja skupna za vse dogodke storitve Outlook za iOS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-578">In addition, the following fields are common for all events for Outlook for iOS.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-579">**DeviceInfo.NetworkProvider** – ponudnik omrežja naprave (tj. Verizon)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-579">**DeviceInfo.NetworkProvider** - The network provider of the device (i.e. Verizon)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-580">**gcc_restrictions_enabled** – nam pove, če so bile v aplikaciji uporabljene omejitve GCC, tako da lahko zagotovimo, da naše stranke GCC varno uporabljajo našo aplikacijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-580">**gcc_restrictions_enabled** - Tells us if GCC restrictions have been applied to the app so we can ensure our GCC customers are using our app securely</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-581">**multi_window_mode** – pove nam, ali je uporabnik v napravi iPad z več okni, ki nam pomaga pri zaznavi težav, povezanih z uporabo več oken.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-581">**multi_window_mode** – Tells us if the user on the iPad is using multiple windows to help us detect issues related to multi-window usage.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-582">**office_session_id** – enolični ID, ki sledi seji za povezane Officeove storitve, da lahko zaznamo težave določene integracije Officeovih storitev v Outlooku, kot je Word</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-582">**office_session_id** - A unique id tracking the session for connected Office services to help detect issues specific an Office service integration in Outlook like Word</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-583">**state** – če je bila aplikacija aktivna, ko je bil dogodek poslan, da bomo lahko zaznali težave določenih stanj aktivnih ali neaktivnih aplikacij</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-583">**state** - Whether the app was active when this event was sent to help detect issues specific to active or inactive app states</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-584">Poleg tega so naslednja polja skupna za vse dogodke storitve Outlook za Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-584">In addition, the following fields are common for all events for Outlook for Android.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-585">**aad_id** – identifikator imenika Azure Active Directory</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-585">**aad_id** - a pseudonymous Azure Active Directory identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-586">**DeviceInfo.NetworkCost** – označuje trenutni strošek omrežja naprave, ki prikazuje stanje Wi-Fi/mobilnega omrežja/gostovanja, da bomo lahko zaznali težave določenega omrežja naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-586">**DeviceInfo.NetworkCost** - Indication of devices current network cost which reflects the status of WiFi/Cellular/Roaming to help detect issues specific to device network</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-587">**is_app_in_duo_split_view_mode** – to nas bo obvestilo, da je bila aplikacija v načinu razdeljenega zaslona Duo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-587">**is_app_in_duo_split_view_mode** - This will let us know that the app was in Duo split-screen mode.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-588">Ta lastnost je nastavljena samo za naprave Duo (samo Android).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-588">This property is set only for Duo (Android only) devices.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-589">**is_dex_mode_enabled** – če je omogočen način Samsung DeX, da bomo lahko zaznali težave določenega načina DeX pri napravah Samsung</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-589">**is_dex_mode_enabled** - Whether Samsung DeX mode is enabled to help detect issues specific to DeX mode with Samsung devices</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-590">**is_sliding_drawer_enabled** – če je omogočen vmesnik s premikajočimi se predali, da bomo lahko zaznali težave, ki jih povzroča naš vmesnik s premikajočimi se predali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-590">**is_sliding_drawer_enabled** - Whether Sliding Drawer interface is enabled to help detect issues caused by our sliding drawer interface</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-591">**orientation** – fizična usmerjenost zaslona (pokončno/ležeče), da bomo lahko zaznali težave določene usmerjenosti zaslona</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-591">**orientation** - Physical orientation of the screen (portrait/landscape) to help detect issues specific to device orientation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-592">**os_arch** – arhitektura operacijskega sistema za napravo, da bomo lahko zaznali težave določenih operacijskih sistemov naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-592">**os_arch** - Operating System architecture for the device to help detect issues specific to device operation systems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-593">**process_bitness** – bitnost procesa (32- ali 64-bitni) za aplikacijo, da bomo lahko zaznali težave določene bitnosti naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-593">**process_bitness** - Process bitness (32 or 64 bit) for the application to help detect issues specific to device bitness</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-594">**webview_kernel_version** : Različica spletnega ogleda Chromium jedra v napravi, ki nam pomaga odkriti težave z združljivostjo, povezane z različico spletnega pogleda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-594">**webview_kernel_version** : The Chromium kernel version of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-595">**webview_package_name** : Ime paketa spletnega ogleda v napravi, ki nam pomaga odkriti težave z združljivostjo, povezano z različico spletnega pogleda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-595">**webview_package_name** : The package name of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-596">**webview_package_version** : Različica paketa spletnega ogleda v napravi, ki nam pomaga odkriti težave z združljivostjo, povezane z različico spletnega pogleda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-596">**webview_package_version** : The package version of webview on the device to help us detect compatibility issues related to the version of webview.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-610">**ponudnik** – identifikator paketa software Provider za enotno prijavo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-610">**provider** - the identifier for the provider software package for the SSO.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-611">**Zvezna država** – trenutno stanje računa (na primer vrednost: ni USPEla, ČAKAJOČa, dodana itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-611">**state** – current state of the account, (example value: FAILED, PENDING, ADDED etc.)</span></span>
 
#### <a name="officeclicktorunupdatestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-612">Office.ClickToRun.UpdateStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-612">Office.ClickToRun.UpdateStatus</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-620">**status** – Trenutno stanje posodobitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-620">**status** - Current status of the update</span></span>

#### <a name="officecompliancefileformatballotdisplayedonfirstboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-622">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotDisplayedOnFirstBoot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-622">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotDisplayedOnFirstBoot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-623">Označuje, ali je bilo Officeovo pogovorno okno z izbirami oblike zapisa datoteke prikazano uporabniku ob prvem/drugem zagonu aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint v sistemu Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-623">Indicates whether the Office File Format choice dialog box was shown to the user on first/second boot of Word, Excel, PowerPoint on Win32.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-624">Spremlja, ali je prikazano pogovorno okno »Glasovnica za FileFormat« – dogodek je poslan ob prvem/drugem zagonu aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint v sistemu Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-624">Tracks whether the FileFormat Ballot dialog box is displayed - event is sent at the first/second boot of Word, Excel or PPT Win32.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-625">Zbrana so naslednja polja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-625">The following fields are collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-626">**CountryRegion** – nastavitev regije države uporabnika v sistemu Windows</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-626">**CountryRegion** –  The users' country region setting in Windows system</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-627">**FileFormatBallotBoxAppIDBootedOnce** – označuje, v kateri aplikaciji (Word, Excel, PowerPoint) je bila obdelana logika prikaza glasovnice oblike zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-627">**FileFormatBallotBoxAppIDBootedOnce** –  In which app (Word, Excel, PPT) the file format ballot display logic was processed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-628">**FileFormatBallotBoxDisplayedOnFirstBoot** – označuje, kakšen je rezultat prikaza za glasovnico oblike zapisa datoteke (prikazan/ni prikazan kot nepričakovan/ni prikazan zaradi licence/ni prikazan zaradi lokacije).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-628">**FileFormatBallotBoxDisplayedOnFirstBoot** –  What is the display result for file format ballot (displayed/not displayed as unexpected/not displayed due to license/not displayed due to location).</span></span>

#### <a name="officecompliancefileformatballotoption"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-629">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotOption</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-629">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotOption</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-630">Spremlja, ali je prikazano pogovorno okno »Glasovnica za FileFormat« – dogodek je poslan ob prvem/drugem zagonu aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint v sistemu Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-630">Tracks whether the FileFormat Ballot dialog box is displayed - event is sent at the first/second boot of Word, Excel or PPT Win32.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-631">Označuje, ali je pogovorno okno z izbirami oblike zapisa datoteke prikazano ob prvem ali drugem zagonu aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint v sistemu Win32.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-631">Indicates whether the Office File Format choice dialog box is displayed on first or second boot of Word, Excel, or PowerPoint on Win32.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-632">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-632">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-633">**FileFormatBallotSelectedOption** – določa možnost oblike zapisa datoteke (OOXML/ODF), ki jo je uporabnik izbral v pogovornem oknu glasovnice oblike zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-633">**FileFormatBallotSelectedOption** – Identifies the file format option (OOXML/ODF) that was selected by the user through the file format ballot dialog box.</span></span>


#### <a name="officecorrelationmetadatautccorrelationmetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-634">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-634">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-635">Zbira metapodatke Officea prek UTC-ja in jih primerja z enakovrednimi podatki, zbranimi prek cevovoda telemetrije sistema Office za preverjanje ustreznosti in celovitosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-635">Collects Office metadata through UTC to compare with equivalent data collected through the Office telemetry pipeline to check correctness and completeness of data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-636">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-636">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-637">**abConfigs** – Seznam ID-jev funkcij za določanje, katere funkcije so omogočene za odjemalca ali prazne, ko ti podatki niso zbrani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-637">**abConfigs** - A list of feature IDs to identify which features are enabled on the client or empty when this data is not being collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-638">**abFlights** – »NoNL:NoFlights«, ko pilotne različice funkcij niso nastavljene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-638">**abFlights** - "NoNL:NoFlights" when the feature flights aren't set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-639">V nasprotnem primeru je izbrana možnost »holdoutinfo=unknown«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-639">Otherwise "holdoutinfo=unknown".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-640">**AppSessionGuid** – Identifikator določene seje aplikacije, ki se je začela z ustvarjanjem procesa in traja vse do konca procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-640">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-641">Dogodek je oblikovan kot standardni 128-bitni GUID, sestavljen iz 4 delov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-641">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-642">Ti štirje deli v vrstnem redu so (1) 32-bitni ID procesa (2) 16-bitni ID seje (3) 16-bitni ID zagona (4) čas ustvarjanja 64-bitnega procesa v UTC 100ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-642">Those four parts in order are (1) 32-bit Process ID (2) 16-bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64-bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-643">**appVersionBuild** – številka različice za gradnjo aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-643">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-644">**appVersionMajor** – Številka glavne različice aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-644">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-645">**appVersionMinor** – Številka podrazličice aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-645">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-646">**appVersionRevision** – Številka različice revizije aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-646">**appVersionRevision** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-647">**audienceGroup** – Ime skupine občinstva izdaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-647">**audienceGroup** - The release audience group name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-648">**audienceId** – Ime občinstva izdaje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-648">**audienceId** - The release audience name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-649">**channel** – Kanal, prek katerega se distribuira Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-649">**channel** - The channel by which Office was distributed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-650">**deviceClass** – Dimenzije naprave v operacijskem sistemu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-650">**deviceClass** - Device form factor from the OS</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-651">**ecsETag** – Identifikator preskusa za proces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-651">**ecsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-652">**impressionId** – GUID, ki označuje trenutni nabor funkcij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-652">**impressionId** - A guid indicating the current set of features.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-653">**languageTag** – Trenutna jezikovna oznaka za Office UI IETF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-653">**languageTag** - The current Office UI IETF language tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-654">**officeUserID** – Naključno ustvarjeni GUID za to namestitev Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-654">**officeUserID** - Randomly generated guid for this Office install</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-655">**osArchitecture** – Arhitektura operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-655">**osArchitecture** - Operating system architecture</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-656">**osEnvironment** – Celo število, ki označuje operacijski sistem (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-656">**osEnvironment** - An integer indicating the operating system (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-657">**osVersionString** – Različica operacijskega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-657">**osVersionString** - Operating system version</span></span>

#### <a name="officetargetedmessagingensurecached"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-702">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-702">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-703">Spremlja prenos paketa za Dynamic Canvas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-703">Tracks if a package for Dynamic Canvas was downloaded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-704">Obravnavamo ga kot konfiguracijo programske opreme, ker mora biti paket uspešno prenesen, da odjemalec lahko uporablja ustrezno izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-704">Considered a software configuration because the package must be successfully downloaded to enable the client to render the right experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-705">Še posebej je pomemben pri naročninah za potrošnike, kjer prek platna komuniciramo z uporabnikom, ki mu je potekla licenca.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-705">Is especially critical in consumer subscriptions where we use canvas to communicate to the user that the license has expired.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-706">Z njim spremljamo metapodatke paketa dinamične vsebine, prenesene z izdelkom in shranjene v predpomnilnik, ter rezultatov izvedenih postopkov za paket: napake pri prenosu, napake pri razpakiranju, napake pri preverjanju doslednosti, zadetki v predpomnilniku, uporabe paketa, uspešni prenosi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-706">Used to track metadata of a dynamic content package downloaded and cached by the product as well as results of operations performed on the package: download failures, unpacking failures, consistency checks failures, cache hits, package usages, download sources.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-707">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-707">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-708">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated** – Logična zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bila mapa predpomnilnika uspešno ustvarjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-708">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated -** Boolean flag indicating if cache folder creation succeeded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-709">**Data\_CdnPath – Izvorni naslov paketa.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-709">**Data\_CdnPath – source address of the package-**</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-710">**Data\_EnsureCached** – Logična zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil paket vsebine shranjen v predpomnilnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-710">**Data\_EnsureCached -** Boolean flag indicating if content package was cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-711">**Data\_ExistsAlready** – Logična zastavica, ki označuje, da je bil paket že prenesen v preteklosti in da je bil zaznan vnovični poskus prenosa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-711">**Data\_ExistsAlready -** Boolean flag indicating that the package was already downloaded before and there was another attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-712">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed** – Izvorni paket ni na voljo v izvorni datoteki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-712">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed -** source package not available in source</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-713">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder** – Težave z lokalnim diskom, zaradi katerih prihaja do napak pri ustvarjanju imenika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-713">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder -** local disk issues causing failure in directory creation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-714">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da je bil paket prenesen, vendar ga odjemalec ne more brati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-714">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed -** flag indicating if package was downloaded, but the client can't read it</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-715">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess** – Uspešni poskusi branja paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-715">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess -** successful attempts to read the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-716">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess** – Ni zaznanih težav z diskom ali konfiguracijo, ki bi preprečevale branje toka datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-716">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess -** no disk issues nor configuration issues which doesn't let the file stream to be read</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-717">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed** – Relativna pot ne pripelje do dostopnega mesta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-717">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed -** relative path doesn't point to accessible location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-718">**Data\_HashActualValue** – Zgoščena vrednost, pridobljena iz imena datoteke, ko je bil paket uporabljen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-718">**Data\_HashActualValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-719">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed** – Napaka z izračunom zgoščene vrednosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-719">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed -** error with calculation of a hash</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-720">**Data\_HashMatchFailed** – Neujemanje zgoščenih vrednosti imena datoteke in predpomnjenih vrednosti registra.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-720">**Data\_HashMatchFailed -** hash mismatch between the package name and registry values cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-721">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess** – Uspešno preverjanje doslednosti zgoščene vrednosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-721">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess -** hash consistency check success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-722">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed** – Paketa ni mogoče prenesti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-722">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed -** can't download the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-723">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData** – Preneseni paket ne vsebuje nobenih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-723">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData -** downloaded package contains no data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-724">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess** – Uspešen prenos paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-724">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess -** successful download of a package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-725">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess** – Stanja poskusov razpakiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-725">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess -** unpacking attempts statuses</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-726">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed** – Neuspešni poskusi odpiranja datoteke paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-726">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed -** failed attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-727">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess** – Uspešni poskusi odpiranja datoteke paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-727">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess -** successful attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-728">**Data\_SuccessHashValue** – Zgoščena vrednost, pridobljena iz imena datoteke, ko je bil paket prenesen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-728">**Data\_SuccessHashValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was downloaded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-729">**Data\_SuccessSource** – Platforma, za katero je bil paket prenesen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-729">**Data\_SuccessSource -** surface for which the package was downloaded</span></span>

Z njim ustvarjamo metrike ustreznosti stanja, grafikone in analize težav uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-797">Data regarding the success for failure of retrieving add-in entitlement data for the Office 365 tenant admin assigned add-ins. Used for health metrics, charts, and analysis of customer problems.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-804">**ServiceCallHResult** – Rezultat, ki ga vrne API klica storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-804">**ServiceCallHResult -** the result returned by the service call API</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitycatalogexchangegetlastupdate"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-808">Office.Extensibility.Catalog.ExchangeGetLastUpdate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-808">Office.Extensibility.Catalog.ExchangeGetLastUpdate</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-809">Podatki o uspešnem oz. neuspešnem pridobivanju posodobljenih podatkov o dodatkih, ki so bili dodeljeni najemniku storitve Office 365. Z njim ustvarjamo metrike ustreznosti stanja, grafikone in analize težav uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-809">Data regarding the success for failure of retrieving the need for updated data regarding the Office 365 tenant admin assigned add-ins. Used for health metrics, charts, and analysis of customer problems.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-810">»ExchangeGetLastUpdate« se vedno začne izvajati ob zagonu kot del kode gostitelja in določa, ali so bile dodelitve dodatkov spremenjene za uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-810">ExchangeGetLastUpdate will always run on boot as part of the host code and determine whether add-in assignments have changed for a user.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-811">Če je tako, potem Weldgen. Datoteka DLL bo naložena, tako da lahko pokličemo ExchangeGetEntitlements, da dobimo določene dodelitve (in ExchangeGetManifests bodo pozvani, da pridobijo nove manifeste, ki so potrebni).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-811">If so then osf.DLL will be loaded so we can call ExchangeGetEntitlements to get the specific assignments (and ExchangeGetManifests will be called to retrieve any new manifests that are needed).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-812"> Na zahtevo lahko prikličemo tudi »ExchangeGetEntitlements« (in »ExchangeGetManifests«), ko je zagnana gostiteljska aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-812">ExchangeGetEntitlements (and ExchangeGetManifests) could also be called on demand after host application has been running.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-813"> Veliki DLL se ne naloži, če ga ne potrebujemo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-813">The idea is to not load the large DLL if we don't need to.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-814"> Brez tega dogodka v polju »Required« ni mogoče prepoznati, da uporabniki niso uspešno pridobili njim dodeljenih dodatkov, če je bil prvi klic storitve neuspešen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-814">Without this event in Required, we would not be able to tell if users are failing to get add-ins assigned to them if that first service call fails.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-815"> To je tudi glavni pokazatelj morebitnih težav s preverjanjem pristnosti med povezovanjem s storitvijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-815">It's also the main signal for any auth problems we face talking to our service.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-816">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-816">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-817">**Abort** – Ali je bil gostitelj zaustavljen med klicem storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-817">**Abort -** whether the host was shut down during the service call</span></span>
