### <a name="application-feature-success-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1086">*Podtip uspešnosti izvajanja funkcije aplikacije*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1086">*Application feature success subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1087">Uspešnost delovanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1087">Success of application functionality.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1088">Omejeno na odpiranje in zapiranje aplikacij in dokumentov, urejanje datoteke ter skupno rabo datotek (sodelovanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1088">Limited to opening and closing of the application and documents, file editing, and file sharing (collaboration).</span></span>

#### <a name="accountaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1089">account.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1089">account.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1090">S tem dogodkom zagotovimo, da konfiguracija računa deluje uspešno, in ga uporabljamo za spremljanje stanja pri ustvarjanju računa, zmožnost dodajanja novih e-poštnih računov in za spremljanje ponastavitev računov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1090">Needed to ensure account configuration is operating successfully and is used to monitor health of account creation, ability to add new email accounts, and monitor soft account resets</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1091">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1091">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1092">**account_calendar_count** – število koledarjev v računu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1092">**account_calendar_count** - how many calendars the account has</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1093">**action** – vrsta izvedenega dejanja, npr. create_account, delete_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1093">**action** - type of action performed, e.g. create_account, delete_account.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1094">**duration_seconds** – trajanje dejanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1094">**duration_seconds** - duration of the action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1095">**entry_point** – vstopna točka dejanja, način, kako je uporabnik zagnal dejanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1095">**entry_point** - entry point of the action, how the user started the action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1096">**has_hx** – ali je v napravi nastavljen račun, ki uporablja našo novo storitev za sinhronizacijo pošte; ni nujno, da gre za račun, v katerem je bilo dejanje izvedeno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1096">**has_hx** - whether the device has an account that is using our new mail syncing service, not necessarily the account that the action was performed upon</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1097">**is_hx** – je račun, ki uporablja našo novo storitev za sinhronizacijo pošte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1097">**is_hx** - is the account using our new mail syncing service</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1098">**is_shared_mailbox** – ali dejanje pripada nabiralniku v skupni rabi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1098">**is_shared_mailbox** - whether the action pertains to a shared mailbox</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1099">**number_of_accounts** – skupno število računov, v katerih je bilo izvedeno dejanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1099">**number_of_accounts** - total number of accounts that the action is performed on</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1100">**result** – rezultat dejanja, npr. »uspelo« ali »ni uspelo«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1100">**result** - result for the action, e.g. success, failure.</span></span>
   
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1101">**server_type** – vrsta strežnika za račun, podobno polju account_type</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1101">**server_type** - the server type for the account, similar to account_type</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1102">**shared_type** – vrsta računa v skupni rabi (če je omogočena skupna raba računa)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1102">**shared_type** - type of shared account (if the account is shared)</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1103">**scope** – obseg dejanja; za brisanje računa, this_device ali all_devices</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1103">**scope** - the scope of the action; for delete account, this_device or all_devices</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1104">**total_calendar_accounts** – število računov koledarja v aplikaciji, ko je bilo izvedeno dejanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1104">**total_calendar_accounts** - count of calendar accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1105">**total_email_accounts** – število e-poštnih računov v aplikaciji, ko je bilo izvedeno dejanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1105">**total_email_accounts** - count of email accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1106">**total_file_accounts** – število računov datotek v aplikaciji, ko je bilo izvedeno dejanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1106">**total_file_accounts** - count of file accounts in the app at time of action</span></span>

#### <a name="accountlifecycle"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1107">account.lifecycle</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1107">account.lifecycle</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1108">Ta dogodek je zbiramo zato, da konfiguracija računa deluje uspešno, in ga uporabljamo za spremljanje stanja pri ustvarjanju računa, zmožnost dodajanja novih e-poštnih računov in za spremljanje ponastavitev računov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1108">This event is collected to ensure account configuration is operating successfully and is used to monitor health of account creation, ability to add new email accounts, and monitor soft account resets.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1109">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1109">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1110">**action** – vrsta dejanja, izvedena v računu, kot je na primer dodajanje, odstranjevanje ali ponastavljanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1110">**action** - The type of action performed on the account, such as add, remove, or reset</span></span>

#### <a name="addnewaccountstep"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1111">add.new.account.step</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1111">add.new.account.step</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1112">S tem dejanjem lahko zaznamo, v kolikšni meri je uporabnik dokončal postopek ustvarjanja novega obrazca računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1112">This event lets us detect how far the user has gotten in the create new account form.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1113">Označuje, kdaj se je uporabnik premaknil na naslednji korak oz. ali je postopek opustil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1113">It indicates when the user has moved to another step or if they have dropped off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1114">S temi informacijami lahko zaznamo, ali kateri od korakov ne deluje, in poskrbimo, da bo postopek ustvarjanja uporabniškega računa uspešen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1114">We need this information to detect if any steps are failing and to ensure user account creation was successful.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1115">Zbrano je sledeče polje:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1115">The following field is collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1116">**OTAddAccountCurrentStep** – ima lahko te vrednosti: profile_form, redirect_mobile_check, mobile_check_success</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1116">**OTAddAccountCurrentStep** - That can have the following values: profile_form, redirect_mobile_check, mobile_check_success</span></span>

#### <a name="apperror"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1117">app.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1117">app.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1118">Spremlja kritične napake aplikacije, da lahko preprečimo težave, ki bi lahko povzročile zrušitev vaše aplikacije ali vam preprečevala branje e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1118">Tracks critical app errors used so that we can prevent issues that could cause your app to crash or prevent you from reading email.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1119">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1119">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1120">**clientName** – ime odjemalca za datoteko v oblaku, v kateri se je pojavila napaka (če je na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1120">**clientName** - The name of the client for the cloud file where the error occurred, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1121">**cloudfile_error_type** – vrsta napake, ki se je pojavila v datoteki v oblaku (če je na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1121">**cloudfile_error_type** - The type of error that occurred for the cloud file, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1122">**cloudfile_response_name** – ime odziva za napako, ki se je pojavila v datoteki v oblaku (če je na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1122">**cloudfile_response_name** - The response name for the error that occurred for the cloud file, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1123">**component_name** – ime komponente aplikacije, v kateri se je pojavila napaka, na primer pošta ali koledar.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1123">**component_name** - The name of the component of the app where the error occurred, such as mail or calendar.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1124">**debug_info** – informacije o napaki, ki se je pojavila v datoteki v oblaku, s katerimi lahko ugotovimo vzrok napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1124">**debug_info** - Information on the error that occurred for the cloud file in order to be able to determine why the error happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1125">**error_origin_identifier** – izvor napake, ki se je pojavila v osnutku (če je na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1125">**error_origin_identifier** - Origin of the error that occurred on the draft that the error occurred, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1126">**error_type** – vrsta napake, ki se je pojavila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1126">**error_type** - The type of error that occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1127">Nekateri primeri vključujejo napake pri shranjevanju osnutka, pošiljanju osnutka in napake datoteke v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1127">Some examples include save draft, send draft, and cloud file error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1128">**exdate** – datum razširjenega pravila (velja le za napake pri ponavljajočih se sestankih) *[To polje je bilo odstranjeno iz trenutnih graditev Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših graditvah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1128">**exdate** - the extended rule date (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1129">**exrule** – vrednost razširjenega pravila (velja le za napake pri ponavljajočih se sestankih) *[To polje je bilo odstranjeno iz trenutnih graditev Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših graditvah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1129">**exrule** - the extended rule value (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1130">**has_attachments** – prikaže, ali ima osnutek, v katerem se je pojavila napaka, priloge (če so na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1130">**has_attachments** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on has attachments, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1131">**is_IRM_protected** – prikaže, ali je osnutek, v katerem se je pojavila napaka, zaščiten z upravljanjem pravic do informacij (če so na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1131">**is_IRM_protected** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on is protected by information rights management, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1132">**is_legitimate** – prikaže, ali je izvor napake v kodi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1132">**is_legitimate** - Reflects if the error comes from a programming error or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1133">Napake pri programiranju se obravnavajo kot nelegitimne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1133">Programming errors are considered non-legitimate.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1134">**is_local** – prikaže, ali je osnutek, v katerem se je pojavila napaka, sinhroniziran s strežnikom (če je na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1134">**is_local** - Reflects if the draft the error occurred on has synced to the server, if applicable.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1135">**is_recoverable** – prikaže, ali je napako mogoče obnoviti oz. gre za kritično napako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1135">**is_recoverable** - Reflects if the error can be recovered from or if it is a fatal error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1136">**rdate** – datum pravila ponovitve (velja le za napake pri ponavljajočih se sestankih) *[To polje je bilo odstranjeno iz trenutnih graditev Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših graditvah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1136">**rdate** - the date of the recurrence rule (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1137">**rrule** – samo pravilo ponovitve (velja le za napake pri ponavljajočih se sestankih) *[To polje je bilo odstranjeno iz trenutnih graditev Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših graditvah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1137">**rrule** - the recurrence rule itself (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1138">**rrule_error_message** – sporočilo o napaki pri razčlenjevanju pravila ponovitve (velja le za napake pri ponavljajočih se sestankih) *[To polje je bilo odstranjeno iz trenutnih graditev Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših graditvah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1138">**rrule_error_message** - recurrence rule parsing error message (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1139">**rrule_error_type** – vrsta napake pri razčlenjevanju pravila ponovitve (velja le za napake pri ponavljajočih se sestankih) *[To polje je bilo odstranjeno iz trenutnih graditev Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših graditvah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1139">**rrule_error_type** - recurrence rule parsing error type (only applies to appointment recurrence errors) *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1140">**status_code** – koda stanja za napako, ki se je pojavila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1140">**status_code** - The status code of the error that occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1141">Pomaga nam razumeti vzrok napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1141">This helps us understand the cause of the error.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1142">Vsi znaki so lahko tudi morebitne lastnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1142">All characters are also possible properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1143">Tako bolje razumemo znake v telesu in osnutku sporočila, v katerem se je napaka pojavila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1143">This helps us understand the characters in the body of the draft message when the error occurred.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1144">Na primer, »a«, »b« in »c« so morebitne lastnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1144">For example, "a", "b", "c" are possible properties.</span></span>

#### <a name="applaunchreport"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1145">app.launch.report</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1145">app.launch.report</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1146">S tem dogodkom lahko zaznavamo težave in jih odpravljamo, ko Outlook začne delovati počasneje ali neobičajno, kar uporabnikom otežuje uporabo aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1146">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook is starting slowly or incompletely, making it difficult for users to use our app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1147">Dogodek vključuje informacije o posebnih omogočenih lastnosti in o tem, kako dolgi so posamezni deli zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1147">This includes information on the specific features that were enabled and how long parts of the startup took.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1148">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1148">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1149">**is_agenda_widget_active** – prikaže, ali je gradnik dnevnega reda aktiven.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1149">**is_agenda_widget_active** - Tells us if the agenda widget is active.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1150">**is_alert_available** – prikaže, ali je bila aplikacija konfigurirana za omogočanje opozoril in obvestil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1150">**is_alert_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow alerts in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1151">**is_background_refresh_available** – prikaže, ali je bila aplikacija konfigurirana za osveževanje v ozadju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1151">**is_background_refresh_available** - Tells if the app has been configured to be able to refresh in the background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1152">**is_badge_available** – prikaže, ali je bila aplikacija konfigurirana za omogočanje značk in obvestil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1152">**is_badge_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow badges in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1153">**is_intune_managed** – prikaže, ali aplikacijo upravlja Intune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1153">**is_intune_managed** - Tell us if the app is managed by Intune.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1154">**is_registered_for_remote_notifications** – prikaže, ali je bila aplikacija registrirana za oddaljena obvestila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1154">**is_registered_for_remote_notifications** - Tell us if the app has been registered for remote notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1155">**is_sound_available** – prikaže, ali je bila aplikacija registrirana za omogočanje zvokov obvestil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1155">**is_sound_available** - Tell us if the app has been configured to allow sounds in notifications.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1156">**is_watch_app_installed** – prikaže, ali je v Outlooku nameščena aplikacija ure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1156">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the watch Outlook app has been installed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1157">**is_watch_paired** – prikaže, ali je Outlookova aplikacija ure seznanjena z glavno Outlookovo aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1157">**is_watch_paired** - Tell us if the watch Outlook app is paired with the main Outlook app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1158">**launch_to_db_ready_ms** – prikaže čas, ki ga je Outlook porabil od zagona do stanja pripravljenosti zbirke uporabe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1158">**launch_to_db_ready_ms** - Tell us the amount of time the Outlook app spent from launch to the database being ready.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1159">**num_calendar_accounts** – prikaže število računov koledarjev v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1159">**num_calendar_accounts** - Tells us the number of calendar accounts in the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1160">**num_cloud_file_accounts** – prikaže število računov shramb v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1160">**num_cloud_file_accounts** - Tells us the number of storage accounts in the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1161">**num_hx_calendar_accounts** – prikaže število računov koledarjev v aplikaciji, povezanih z našo novo storitvijo za sinhronizacijo pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1161">**num_hx_calendar_accounts** - Tells us the number of calendar accounts in the app that connect to our new mail syncing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1162">**num_hx_mail_accounts** – prikaže število poštnih računov v aplikaciji, povezanih z našo novo storitvijo za sinhronizacijo pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1162">**num_hx_mail_accounts** - Tells us the number of mail accounts in the app that connect to our new mail syncing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1163">**num_mail_accounts** – prikaže število poštnih računov v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1163">**num_mail_accounts** - Tells us the number of mail accounts in the app.</span></span>

#### <a name="calendaraction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1164">calendar.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1164">calendar.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1165">Se uporablja za nadzor morebitnih negativnih učinkov na vašo zmožnost izvajanja ključnih dejanj koledarja, kot sta ustvarjanje ali urejanje dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1165">Used for monitoring any possible negative impact on your ability to perform core calendar actions like creating or editing events.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1166">Dogodek lahko prav tako vključuje niz z imeni lastnosti in informacije o tem, ali so se spremenile.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1166">The event could also include a series of property names and if they have changed or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1167">Imena vključenih lastnosti, kot so »title_changed«, »online_meeting_changed« in »description_changed«, nam pomagajo pri razumevanju, ali je prišlo do težav pri urejanju določenih lastnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1167">For example, "title_changed", "online_meeting_changed", and "description_changed" are property names that are included to help us understand if there are any issues with editing certain properties.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1168">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1168">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1169">**account_sfb_enabled** – s tem dogodkom zagotovimo, ali je Skype za podjetja pravilno nastavljen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1169">**account_sfb_enabled** - Helps us make sure that Skype for Business is configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1170">**action** – vrsta dejanja, ki je bila izvedena v koledarju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1170">**action** - The type of action that was performed on the calendar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1171">Vključuje denimo opravila, kot so odpiranje, urejanje, dodajanje bližnjic, dremež itd. Pomaga nam zagotoviti, da koledar deluje po pričakovanjih in da vse funkcije delujejo pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1171">This includes things like open, editing, adding shortcut, snooze, etc. Helps us ensure our calendar experience is functioning as expected and nothing has broken</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1172">**action_result** – rezultat dejanja, izveden v komponentah koledarja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1172">**action_result** - Result of the action taken on calendar components.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1173">Vključuje lahko vrednosti, kot so »uspešno«, »neuspešno«, »neznano« in »časovna omejitev«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1173">This can include values such as success, failure, unknown, and timeout.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1174">Se uporablja za spremljanje stopnje uspešnosti za dejanja in določevanje, ali se je pri dejanjih koledarja pojavila razširjena težava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1174">Used to track the success rate of actions and determine if there is a widespread issue with calendar actions.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1175">**attendee_busy_status** – prosto/zasedeno stanje udeleženca, s katerim je povezano dejanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1175">**attendee_busy_status** - The free/busy status of the attendee that the action is related to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1176">Ta vrednost je lahko »prost«, »zaseden« ali »pogojno sprejeto«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1176">This value can be free, busy, or tentative.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1177">S tem dogodkom lažje razumemo, ali je prišlo do težave z dejanji, ki so povezana z določenim zasedenem stanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1177">Helps us understand if there is an issue with actions related to a certain busy status.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1178">**availability** – vrednost razpoložljivosti, če se je stanje »prost/zaseden« spremenilo med srečanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1178">**availability** - The availability value if the free/busy value has changed on the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1179">S tem dogodkom lažje razumemo, ali je prišlo do težav z določeno vrednostjo razpoložljivosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1179">Helps us understand if there are issues with setting a certain availability value.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1180">**calendar_onlinemeeting_default_provider** – vsebuje privzetega ponudnika spletnega srečanja za uporabo pri ustvarjanju strežniškega spletnega srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1180">**calendar_onlinemeeting_default_provider** - Contains the default online meeting provider for use with server-supported online meeting creation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1181">Vključuje vrste za Skype, Skype za podjetja, Hangout in Teams za podjetja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1181">This includes types of Skype, Skype for Business, Hangout, and Teams for Business.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1182">Ta dogodek uporabljamo pri diagnosticiranju težavi pri ustvarjanju spletnih srečanj določenih ponudnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1182">Helps us diagnose potential issues with creating online meetings on certain providers.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1183">**calendar_onlinemeeting_enabled** – ima vrednost »true«, če koledar podpira ustvarjanje strežniškega spletnega srečanja glede na privzetega ponudnika spletnega srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1183">**calendar_onlinemeeting_enabled** - True if the calendar supports server-supported online meeting creation based on a default online meeting provider.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1184">Pomaga nam razumeti, ali je prišlo do morebitnih težav v koledarjih z omogočenimi spletnimi srečanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1184">Helps us understand if there are any issues with online meeting enabled calendars.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1185">**calendar_type** – vrsta koledarja, v katerem je dogodek, po tem, ko je uporabnik uredil srečanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1185">**calendar_type** - The type of calendar an event is on after the user has edited the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1186">Morebitne vrednosti so »primarno«, »sekundarno«, »v skupni rabi« in »skupina«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1186">Possible values include primary, secondary, shared, and group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1187">S tem dogodkom lažje razumemo, ali je prišlo do težav z določeno vrsto koledarja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1187">Helps us understand if there are issues with a certain calendar type.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1188">**delete_action_origin** – izvor izvedenega dejanja izbrisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1188">**delete_action_origin** - The origin of the delete action performed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1189">Vključuje vrednosti, kot so orodna vrstica za krmarjenje in orodna vrstica v obliki kapsule.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1189">This includes values such as navigation bar toolbar and capsule toolbar.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1190">Pomaga nam razumeti, ali je prišlo do morebitnih težav pri brisanju srečanja iz določenega mesta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1190">Helps us understand if there are any issues with deleting a meeting from a certain location.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1191">**distribution_list_count** – število udeležencev, navedenih na seznamih prejemnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1191">**distribution_list_count** - Number of attendees which are on distribution lists.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1192">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko spremljamo, ali je prišlo do težav z udeleženci, navedenimi na seznamih prejemnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1192">Helps us track if there are issues with attendees that are on distribution lists.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1193">**guest_count** – število gostov v srečanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1193">**guest_count** - The number of guests on the meeting.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1194">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko zagotovimo, da so bili gostje dodani pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1194">Helps us make sure that the guests are being added correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1195">**is_all_day** – se uporablja skupaj z dogodkom »meeting_duration« za določanje, ali gre za celodnevno srečanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1195">**is_all_day** - Used along with "meeting_duration" to specify if this is an all-day meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1196">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo, ali je prišlo do morebitnih težav pri dejanjih, izvedenih v celodnevnih srečanjih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1196">Helps us understand if there are any issues with actions performed on all-day meetings.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1197">**is_location_permission_granted** – Ali je uporabnik aplikaciji odobril sistemsko lokacijsko dovoljenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1197">**is_location_permission_granted** – Whether user has granted system location permission to the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1198">Če je lokacijsko dovoljenje podeljeno, lahko aplikacija v uporabniškem vmesniku prikaže dodatne informacije o koristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1198">If location permission is granted, the app can show extra utility information in the user interface.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1199">Vedeti, ali je dovoljenje za lokacijo odobreno, nam bo omogočilo vedeti, kako pogosto se uporabnikom prikažejo dodatne informacije o uporabnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1199">Knowing if location permission is granted will allow us to know how often the extra utility information is being shown to users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1200">**is_organizer** – pomaga nam razumeti, ali je srečanja mogoče urejati in ali jih je organizator ustvaril pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1200">**is_organizer** - Helps us understand if meetings are able to be edited and created by the organizer correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1201">**is_recurring** – pomaga nam razumeti, ali je prišlo do težave, ki vpliva na ponavljajoča se srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1201">**is_recurring** - Helps us understand if there is an issue that specifically impacts recurring meetings.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1202">**launch_point** – začetna točka dejanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1202">**launch_point** - The launch point of the action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1203">Lahko vsebuje vrednosti, kot so glava gradnika, noga gradnika, celodnevni gradnik in bližnjica koledarja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1203">Can be values such as widget header, widget footer, widget all day, and calendar shortcut.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1204">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko razumemo kontekst, v katerem je bilo zagnano dejanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1204">Helps us understand the context that the action was started from.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1205">**location_count** – število lokacij, določenih pri ustvarjanju in urejanju dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1205">**location_count** - Number of locations that are set on event create and edit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1206">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko razumemo, ali je prišlo do težav pri ustvarjanji ali urejanju dogodkov z določenim številom mest.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1206">Helps us understand if there are any issues with creating or editing events with a certain number of locations.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1207">**location_selection_source_type** – vrsta vira za izbiro lokacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1207">**location_selection_source_type** - Type of the location selection source.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1208">Lahko vsebuje vrednosti, kot so predlog lokacije, po meri in obstoječe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1208">This can include values such as location suggestion, custom, and existing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1209">Pomaga nam diagnosticirati morebitne težave pri izbiri lokacije iz določenega vira.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1209">Helps us diagnose any issues with selecting a location from a certain source.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1210">**location_session_id** – ID seje za izbiro lokacije srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1210">**location_session_id** - ID of the meeting location chooser session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1211">Pomaga nam diagnosticirati morebitne težave pri izbiri lokacije srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1211">Helps us diagnose any issues with choosing a location to add to the meeting.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1212">**location_type** – vrsta izbrane lokacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1212">**location_type** - The type of location selected.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1213">Vsebuje vrste, kot so lokacija po meri, konferenčna soba in Bing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1213">Contains types such as custom location, conference room, and Bing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1214">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko razumemo težave pri dodajanju določenih vrst lokacij srečanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1214">Helps us understand issues with adding certain location types to the meeting.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1215">**meeting_duration** – trajanje srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1215">**meeting_duration** - The length of the meeting.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1216">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko za srečanja nastavimo pravilne čase.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1216">Helps us make sure that the meetings are being configured with the correct times.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1217">**meeting_insights_type** – vrsta vpogledov srečanja v podrobnosti dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1217">**meeting_insights_type** - The type of meeting insights in the event details.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1218">Vključuje datoteko in sporočilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1218">This includes file and message.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1219">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko določimo število prikaznih vpogledov srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1219">Helps us understand the number of meeting insights that are being shown.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1220">**meeting_type** – vrsta spletnega srečanja, povezanega z dejanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1220">**meeting_type** - The type of online meeting associated with the action.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1221">Vključuje vrste za Skype, Skype za podjetja, Hangout in Teams za podjetja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1221">This includes types of Skype, Skype for Business, Hangout, and Teams for Business.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1222">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko določimo, ali so spletna srečanja pravilno nastavljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1222">Helps us understand if the online meetings are configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1223">**origin** – izvor dejanja koledarja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1223">**origin** - The origin of the calendar action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1224">Vključuje vrste, kot so dnevni red, koledar, gradnik za dnevni red itd. S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko zagotovimo pravilno komunikacijo med komponentami koledarja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1224">This includes types like agenda, calendar, widget agenda, etc. Helps us better ensure the interaction within the calendar components are working correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1225">**recurrence_scope** – vrsta ponovitve srečanja (enkratna ponovitev ali niz).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1225">**recurrence_scope** - The type of recurrence of the meeting, either occurrence or series.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1226">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo, ali je prišlo do morebitnih težav pri urejanju različnih vrst ponovitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1226">Helps us understand if there are any issues with editing different meeting recurrence types.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1227">**reminder_time** – čas opomnika za srečanje (če se je spremenil).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1227">**reminder_time** - The reminder time of the meeting if it has changed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1228">S tem dogodkom zagotovimo, da se je čas opomnika za srečanje pravilno shranil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1228">Used to make sure the reminder time of the meeting is saved correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1229">**reminders_count** – število opomnikov za dogodek, če so se opomniki spremenili.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1229">**reminders_count** - Number of reminders on the event if the reminders have changed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1230">S tem dogodkom lahko diagnosticiramo težave z več opomniki dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1230">Helps us diagnose any issues with multiple reminders on an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1231">**sensitivity** – občutljivost srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1231">**sensitivity** - The sensitivity of the meeting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1232">Vključuje vrste, kot so »običajno«, »osebno«, »zasebno« in »zaupno«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1232">This includes types of normal, personal, private, and confidential.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1233">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo, ali je občutljivost srečanja nastavljena pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1233">Helps us understand if the sensitivity of the meeting is being configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1234">**session_duration** – trajanje seje v milisekundah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1234">**session_duration** - The length that the session lasted in milliseconds.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1235">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo, ali je prišlo do napak, ki povečujejo trajanje, zahtevano za izvedbo dejanja koledarja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1235">Helps us understand if there are issues that are increasing the amount of time needed to perform the calendar action.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1236">**shared_calendar_result** – rezultat dejanja, izvedenega v koledarju v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1236">**shared_calendar_result** - The result of an action performed on a shared calendar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1237">Razpoložljive možnosti so: »v redu«, »brez dovoljenja«, »neznano«, »lastnik na mestu uporabe« in »lastnik je skupina«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1237">Possible values include ok, no permission, unknown, owner on-prem, and owner is group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1238">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ocenimo zanesljivost dejanj, izvedenih v koledarjih v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1238">Helps us understand the reliability of actions performed on shared calendars.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1239">**time_picker_origin** – izvor izbirnika časa za dejanje shranjevanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1239">**time_picker_origin** - Origin of the time picker for a save action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1240">Vključuje vrednosti, kot so »več možnosti« in »manj možnosti«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1240">Includes values such as more options and fewer options.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1241">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo, kako je uporabnik shranil srečanje, in se prepričamo, da ta funkcija deluje pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1241">Helps us understand how the user navigated the flow to save the meeting and ensure that is functioning correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1242">**title** – samodejni naslov, predlagan iz vrednosti, določene v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1242">**title** - The auto-suggested title from app-defined values.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1243">Vključuje vrednosti, kot so »Klic«, »Kosilo« in »Skype«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1243">This includes values such as "Call", "Lunch", and "Skype".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1244">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo, ali je samodejni predlog nastavljen pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1244">Helps us understand if the title auto-suggestion is configured correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1245">**txp** – vrsta rezervacije dogodka (če je na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1245">**txp** - The type of booking or reservation on the event, if any.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1246">Vključuje vrste, kot so rezervacija dogodka, rezervacija leta, rezervacija najema avtomobila itd. S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo, ali kartice za rezervacijo delujejo pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1246">This includes types like event reservation, flight reservation, car rental reservation, etc. Helps us understand if the booking/reservation cards are performing correctly.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1247">**upcoming_event_count** – število prihajajočih dogodkov, prikazanih v pogledu prihajajočih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1247">**upcoming_event_count** - The number of upcoming events displayed in the upcoming events view.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1248">S pomočjo tega dogodka ugotovimo, ali je prišlo do težav s pogledom prihajajočih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1248">Helps us understand if there are issues with the upcoming events view.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1249">**upcoming_event_seconds_until_event** – število sekund, do začetka naslednjega dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1249">**upcoming_event_seconds_until_event** - The number of seconds until the next upcoming event starts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1250">S pomočjo tega dogodka ugotovimo običajne dogodke, ki so prikazani v pogledu prihajajočih dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1250">Helps us understand the typical events that are shown in the upcoming events view.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1251">**value** – podrobnosti dejanja, kot so trajanje zakasnitve alarma ali kategorija »Ponavljaj do«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1251">**value** - Action-specific detail such as alert delay length or repeat-until category.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1252">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko razumemo kontekst, v katerem je bilo izvedeno dejanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1252">Helps us understand the context that the action was performed.</span></span> 

#### <a name="combinedsearchuse"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1253">combined.search.use</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1253">combined.search.use</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1254">Se uporablja za nadzor morebitnega negativnega učinka na vašo zmožnost izvajanja ključnega iskanja, kot so iskanje pošte, stikov ali dogodkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1254">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform key search functionality such as searching for mail, contacts, or events.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1255">Naslednja polja so zbrana v operacijskih sistemih iOS in Android:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1255">The following fields are collected across iOS and Android:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1256">**account_switcher_action_type** – ta vrsta dejanja spremlja, ali je uporabnik uporabil preklopnik med računi v načinu preprostega odkrivanja ali je preklopil na drug račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1256">**account_switcher_action_type** - This action type tracks if the user used the account switcher either in simply discovery or if they decided to switch the account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1257">**action_type** – vrsta dejanja, ki je bila izvedena v funkciji iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1257">**action_type** - The type of action that was performed for search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1258">Določa, ali je bila zagnana funkcija iskanja, se ponavlja oziroma je bila končana ter prepozna, katera dejanja so bila izvedena med iskanjem, npr. ali je bil uporabljen mikrofon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1258">This identifies if a search has been started, in occurring, or ended and what actions were happening during the search, I.e. was the mic used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1259">Ta dogodek nam omogoča, da zagotavljamo natančna in pomenljiva iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1259">This is instrumental in ensuring accurate and helpful searches.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1260">**conversation_id** – enolični ID za posamezno sejo iskanja (npr. vsakič, ko uporabnik vnese element v iskalno polje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1260">**conversation_id** - Unique ID for every search session (i.e. every time the user enters the search box)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1261">**entrance_type** – določa način, kako je uporabnik zagnal poizvedbo iskanja na zavihku za iskanje, iz ničelne poizvedbe, naslova iskanja ali rezultata iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1261">**entrance_type** - This determines how the user started the search query, from the search tab, zero query, search heading, or search result.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1262">**has_contact_results** – ali so rezultati stika prikazani v poizvedbi iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1262">**has_contact_results** - Simple whether contact results are shown or not in the search query</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1263">**include_deleted** – ali so v rezultatih iskanja prikazane izbrisane možnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1263">**include_deleted** - whether the search is showing deleted options in the search results</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1264">**is_ics_external_data** – Zajame, če je dodan dogodek interni (tj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1264">**is_ics_external_data** - Captures if an added event is internal (i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1265">dodan v Outlooku v koledar Outlook) ali zunanji (tj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1265">added in Outlook to Outlook calendar) or external (i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1266">dodan iz druge e-poštne aplikacije, kot je Gmail za koledar Outlook).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1266">added from another email app such as Gmail to Outlook calendar).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1267">**is_network_fully_connected** – To je namig za razlog za iskanje brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1267">**is_network_fully_connected** - This is to get a hint of the reason behind the offline search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1268">Če je omrežje povezano in iskanje poteka brez povezave, je verjetno razlog časovna prekinitev strežnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1268">If the network is connected and the search is offline, then the reason is likely to be the server timeout</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1269">**is_offline_search** – ali je seja iskanja iskanje brez povezave na podlagi rezultatov iskanja, ki jih je vrnil hx</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1269">**is_offline_search** - whether the search session is offline search based on search results returned by hx</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1270">**re_enter_search_tab** – logična vrednost, ki ponazarja, ali je uporabnik pred izbiro rezultata preklopil na drug zavihek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1270">**re_enter_search_tab** - Boolean to indicate whether a user has switched tabs before selecting a search result</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1271">**result_selected_type** – kakšno vrsto prikazanih podatkov uporablja uporabnik. Npr. ali so prikazani vsi stiki, pogovori, dogodki itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1271">**result_selected_type** - What type of data that was displayed is the user interacting with I.e. see all contact, conversations, event, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1272">**search_conversation_result_data** – vsebuje podatke o pogovoru, izbranem med rezultati iskanja, vključno z vrsto računa (hx, ac itd.), ali je sporočilo shranjeno v storitvi v oblaku in ali je zamik strani prikazan na isti strani kot prvo sporočilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1272">**search_conversation_result_data** - This contains data about the conversation selected from a search result including account type (hx, ac, etc.), whether the message is held by a cloud service, and whether the page offset shown is the same page as the first message.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1273">**search_origin** – vir iskanja, npr. glasovni pomočnik, Cortana, vnos s tipkovnico itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1273">**search_origin** - Where did the search originate from, i.e. voice assistant, Cortana, keyboard input, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1274">**search_scope** – niz, ki prikazuje vrsto računa, izbrano za iskanje (npr. Exchange, Gmail itd.), ali če je bila izbrana možnost iskanja v vseh računih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1274">**search_scope** - A string indicating what type of account the user was searching in (I.e. Exchange, Gmail, etc.) or if it was in All Accounts.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1275">**search_suggestion_type** – prikazuje element za predlogom za iskanje, npr. ali gre za popravek črkovanja?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1275">**search_suggestion_type** - indicates what is behind the search suggestion, I.e. is a spell correction?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1276">Ali temelji na zgodovini?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1276">Based on history?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1277">Funkcija samodokončanja?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1277">Autocomplete?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1278">**search_request_reason** – prikazuje vzrok, zakaj je bila iz aplikacije poslana zahteva za iskanje, ter ponazarja komponento oz. dejanje uporabnika, priklicano s funkcijo iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1278">**search_request_reason** - Indicates the reason a search request was sent from the app, in effect indicating the component or user action which invoked a search.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1279">**search_result_filter_type** – prikazuje vrsto filtra, ki je bila uporabljena za funkcijo iskanja, ter prikazuje vso vsebino ali samo priloge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1279">**search_result_filter_type** - Indicates what type of filter was applied to search, show all or attachments only</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1280">Naslednja polja so zbrana v iOS aplikacijah Outlook Mobile:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1280">The following fields are collected across iOS applications of Outlook Mobile:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1281">**action** – vrsta dejanja, ki je bila izvedena v funkciji iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1281">**action** - the type of action that was performed for search.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1282">Določa, ali je bila zagnana funkcija iskanja, se ponavlja oziroma je bila končana ter prepozna, katera dejanja so bila izvedena med iskanjem, npr. ali je bil uporabljen mikrofon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1282">This identifies if a search has been started, in occurring, or ended and what actions were happening during the search, I.e. was the mic used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1283">Ta dogodek nam omogoča, da zagotavljamo natančna in pomenljiva iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1283">This is instrumental in ensuring accurate and helpful searches.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1284">**answer_result_selected_count** – število uspešnih iskanj; ali je uporabnik našel iskano osebo?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1284">**answer_result_selected_count** - tracks how many times the search was "successful" I.e. did the user find the person they wanted?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1285">Ali je bilo ustvarjeno e-poštno sporočilo?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1285">Composed an email?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1286">Ali je bilo sporočilo dodane med zaznamke?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1286">Bookmarked the message?</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1287">**contact_result_in_full_list_selected_count** – število, ko je uporabnik v pogledu polnega seznama izbral možnost »Prikaži vse stike« med sejo kombiniranega iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1287">**contact_result_in_full_list_selected_count** - tracks how many times the user asked to "see all contacts" in full list was selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1288">**contact_result_selected_count** – število izbranih rezultatov stikov med sejo kombiniranega iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1288">**contact_result_selected_count** - tracks how many contact results were selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1289">**conversation_result_selected_count** – število izbranih pogovorov med sejo kombiniranega iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1289">**conversation_result_selected_count** - tracks how many conversations were selecting during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1290">**mail_paging_gesture_count** – spremlja število izvedenih potez ostranjevanja iskanja pošte v seji združenega iskanja </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1290">**mail_paging_gesture_count** - tracks how many mail search paging gestures were performed within the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1291">**mail_requests_count** – sledi, koliko zahtev za iskanje po pošti je bilo poslanih v kombinirani iskalni seji</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1291">**mail_requests_count** - tracks how many mail search requests were sent within the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1292">**people_filter_selected_contacts_count** – sledi, koliko stikov je bilo izbranih v filtru ljudi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1292">**people_filter_selected_contacts_count** - tracks how many contacts were selected in the people filter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1293">**search_session_ended_type** – prikazuje mesto, kjer se je iskanje zaključilo, ker je bila poizvedba preklicana ali posodobljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1293">**search_session_ended_type** - Indicates where a search ended because it was canceled or the updated was the query</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1294">**search_suggestion_type** – prikazuje element za predlogom za iskanje, npr. ali gre za popravek črkovanja?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1294">**search_suggestion_type** - indicates what is behind the search suggestion, I.e. is a spell correction?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1295">Ali temelji na zgodovini?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1295">Based on history?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1296">Funkcija samodokončanja?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1296">Autocomplete?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1297">**see_all_contacts_selected_count** – kolikokrat je bila med sejo kombiniranega iskanja izbrana možnost »Prikaži vse stike«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1297">**see_all_contacts_selected_count** - tracks how many times "see all contacts" was selected during the combined search session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1298">**subtab_type** – spremlja, kje uporabnik izbere rezultat s katerega zavihka z rezultati</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1298">**subtab_type** -  tracks where the user has selected the result from which result tab</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1299">**top_mail_result_selected_count** – kolikokrat je uporabnik izbral prikazane najpomembnejše rezultate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1299">**top_mail_result_selected_count** - tracks how many times a user selects the top results provided to them.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1300">**ui_reload_result_count** – posname čas vnovičnega nalaganja uporabniškega vmesnika zaradi posodobitve nabora rezultatov (med ustrezno poizvedbo)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1300">**ui_reload_result_count** - records the times of reloading UI because of result set update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1301">**ui_reload_result_time** – posname celoten čas, porabljen za vnovično nalaganje uporabniškega vmesnika zaradi posodobitve nabora rezultatov (med ustrezno poizvedbo)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1301">**ui_reload_result_time** - records the total time spent on reloading UI because of result set update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>
