- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1303">**ui_reload_status_time** – posname celoten čas, porabljen za vnovično nalaganje uporabniškega vmesnika zaradi posodobitve stanja (med ustrezno poizvedbo)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1303">**ui_reload_status_time** - records the total time spent on reloading UI because of status update (during the corresponding query)</span></span>

#### <a name="composemailaccessory"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1304">compose.mail.accessory</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1304">compose.mail.accessory</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1305">S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo in odpravimo težave z dejanji ključnih komponent, da ne boste naleteli na težave pri prilaganju datoteke, zajemu fotografije kot priloge ali pošiljanju svoje razpoložljivosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1305">This event lets us detect and fix issues with key mail compose actions to prevent you from running into issues with attaching a file, taking a photo as an attachment, or sending your availability.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1306">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1306">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1307">**action** – ponazarja dejanje, ki se je poskušalo izvesti med zapisom dejanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1307">**action** - Tells us the action that was attempted when the action is logged.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1308">Nekateri primeri vključujejo prilaganje datoteke in prikaz več možnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1308">Some examples include attaching a file and presenting more options.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1309">**icon_name** – ponazarja ime ikone, ki je prikazana med zapisom dejanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1309">**icon_name** - Tells us the name of the icon that is being shown when the action is logged.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1310">**origin** – sporoča izvor dejanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1310">**origin** – Tells us the origin of the action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1311">Možni vrednosti sta quick_reply in full_screen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1311">Possible values are quick_reply and full_screen.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1312">**toolbar_type** – sporoča vrsto orodne vrstice, predstavljene na strani za sestavljanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1312">**toolbar_type** – Tell us the toolbar type which is presenting on compose page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1313">Možni vrednosti sta compose_actions in formatting.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1313">Possible values are compose_actions and formatting.</span></span>


#### <a name="conversationviewaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1314">conversation.view.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1314">conversation.view.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1315">Se uporablja za nadzor morebitnega negativnega učinka na vašo zmožnost ogledovanja e-poštnih sporočil in odgovarjanja nanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1315">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to view and reply to email messages</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1316">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1316">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1317">**contains_mention** – ponazarja, ali je bila v pogovoru uporabljena oznaka @, s katero si pomagamo pri odkrivanju težav pri e-poštnih objavah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1317">**contains_mention** - Tells us if the conversation had an @ mention applied to help us detect issues with email mentions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1318">**conversation_type** – ponazarja vrsto upodobljenega e-poštnega sporočila, na primer pogled enega sporočila ali pogled več sporočil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1318">**conversation_type** - Tells us what type of email message view was rendered, such as a single message view or multiple message views.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1319">S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko zaznavamo težave, povezane z določeno vrsto sporočila v našem pogledu e-poštnega pogovora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1319">Helps us detect issues related to a specific message type in our email conversation view.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1320">**reaction_origin** – pove nam, od kod je uporabnik reagiral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1320">**reaction_origin** – Tells us origin from where the user reacted</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1321">**reaction_type** – sporoči nam vrsto reakcije uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1321">**reaction_type** – Tells us the reaction type of the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1322">**suggested_reply_char_count** – število znakov v predlaganem odgovoru (če je na voljo), s katerim lažje zaznamo odstopanja in težave, povezane z našimi predlogi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1322">**suggested_reply_char_count** - Tells us how many characters the suggested replies we offer (if available) to help us detect anomalies and issues related to our suggestions</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1323">**suggested_reply_click_pos** – položaj upodobitve predlaganega odgovora (če je na voljo), s katerim lažje zaznamo težave z določenim predlogom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1323">**suggested_reply_click_pos** - Tells us which position the suggested reply (if available) is rendered so we can detect issues with a specific suggestion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1324">**suggested_reply_type** – označuje vrsto predlaganega odgovora za to dejanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1324">**suggested_reply_type** - indicates type of suggested reply for this action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1325">Možne vrednosti so text, send_avail in create_meeting.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1325">Possible values are text, send_avail, and create_meeting.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1326">**use_default_quick_reply_mode** – prikazuje, ali je bil uporabljen privzeti način hitrega odgovora, s katerim lažje zaznamo težave, povezane z izkušnjo hitrih odgovorov v e-pošti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1326">**use_default_quick_reply_mode** - Tells us if the default quick reply mode was used to help us detect issues related to the quick reply experience for email</span></span>

#### <a name="draftaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1327">draft.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1327">draft.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1328">Se uporablja za nadzor morebitnega negativnega učinka na vašo zmožnost ustvarjanja in shranjevanja osnutkov e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1328">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to create and save mail drafts.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1329">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1329">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1330">**action** – vrsta dejanja, npr. shrani ali zavrzi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1330">**action** - the type of action, e.g. save, discard.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1331">**draft_message_id** – ID sporočila osnutka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1331">**draft_message_id** - message ID of the draft</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1332">**is_groups** – ali je bil osnutek poslan skupinski mapi ali iz nje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1332">**is_groups** - whether the draft is being sent to/from a group folder</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1333">**origin** – vir osnutka, npr. podrobnosti sporočila, ustvari.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1333">**origin** - where draft was initiated, e.g. message detail, compose.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1334">**smart_compose_model_version** – spremlja, katero različico modela Smart sestavite uporabljamo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1334">**smart_compose_model_version** - tracks which version of smart compose model is being used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1335">**suggestions_requested** – označuje, koliko predlogov za pametno sestaviti je bilo zahtevano</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1335">**suggestions_requested** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions requested</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1336">**suggestions_results** – Smart sestavite rezultate predlogov, tj. sprejete, zavrnjene</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1336">**suggestions_results** - smart compose suggestions’ result, i.e. accepted, rejected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1337">**suggestions_returned** – označuje, koliko pametnih predlogov za sestavljanje je vrnjenih iz strežnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1337">**suggestions_returned** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions returned from server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1338">**suggestions_shown** – označuje, koliko pametnih predlogov za sestavljanje je prikazano uporabniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1338">**suggestions_shown** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions shown to the user</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1339">**thread_id** – ID za nit pogovora, s katerim je povezan osnutek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1339">**thread_id** - thread ID of the conversation draft is associated with</span></span>

#### <a name="draganddrop"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1340">drag.and.drop</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1340">drag.and.drop</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1341">V tem primeru lahko zaznamo, ali je bilo dejanje »povleci in spusti« uspešno ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1341">This event lets us detect if the drag and drop action was successful or not.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1342">Z njim poskrbimo, da izkušnja vlečenja in spuščanja pravilno deluje v vseh aplikacijah, tako kot dogodek vlečenja v Outlook kot tudi dogodek vlečenja, s katerim uporabnik vsebino odvleče iz Outlooka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1342">It is used to ensure that drag-and-drop experiences are working correctly across applications both as a drop event into Outlook and a drag event that leaves Outlook.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1343">S temi podatki lahko poskrbimo, da celotna izkušnja v drugih aplikacijah deluje v skladu s pričakovanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1343">With this data we are able to ensure that the end-to-end experience with other applications is working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1344">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1344">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1345">**action** – dejanje bo bodisi vlečenje bodisi spuščanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1345">**action** - Action will be either drag or drop</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1346">**location** – v primeru dejanja vleka bomo s tem izvedeli, s katerega mesta je uporabnik začel vlečenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1346">**location** - In case of a drag action, this will let us know from which location the user started the drag.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1347">V primeru dejanja spuščanja bomo s tem izvedeli, kjer je uporabnik izpustil datoteko, ki jo je vlekel.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1347">In case of a drop action, this will let us know where the user dropped the file which was being dragged.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1348">**vir** – če gre za dejanje spuščanja, nam to sporočite, na kateri lokaciji je uporabnik zagnal funkcijo» povleci «.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1348">**source** – In the case of a drop action, this will let us know from which location the user started the drag.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1349">Tako boste lažje odkrivali težave z določenim virom, kot je OneDrive ali datoteke, na določeno mesto za spuščanje, kot je na primer nova e-poštna sporočila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1349">This helps us better discover issues with a specific source like OneDrive or Files into a specific drop location, such as a new email.</span></span>

#### <a name="drawerevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1350">drawer.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1350">drawer.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1351">Se uporablja za nadzor morebitnega negativnega učinka na vašo zmožnost dostopanja do map v nabiralniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1351">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to access folders in your inbox</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1352">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1352">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1353">**add_calendar_option** – ponazarja vrsto koledarja, ki je bil dodan iz predala, npr. koledar zanimivosti, koledar pošte, koledar v skupni rabi, s katerim lahko lažje zaznamo težave, povezane z določenimi vrstami koledarjev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1353">**add_calendar_option** - Indicates the type of calendar being added from the drawer i.e. interesting calendar, mail calendar, shared calendar, to help us detect issues related to specific calendar types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1354">**calendar_accounts_count** – ponazarja število računov koledarja, s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane s številom računov, katerih lastnih ste.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1354">**calendar_accounts_count** - Indicates the number of calendar accounts to help us detect issues related to number of accounts you have</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1355">**calendar_apps_count** – ponazarja število aplikacij koledarja, nameščenih v napravi uporabnika, s katerim lahko zaznavamo težave, povezane z aplikacijami koledarja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1355">**calendar_apps_count** - Indicates the number of calendar apps present on the user's device to help us detect issues related to calendar apps</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1356">**drawer_type** – ponazarja vrsto predala: koledar, pošta ali ničelna poizvedba za zaznavanje težav, povezanih z vrsto predala.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1356">**drawer_type** - Indicates the drawer type: calendar, mail or zero query to help us detect issues related to the drawer type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1357">**from_favorites** – ponazarja, ali je bilo dejanje izvedeno iz priljubljenih, in nam pomaga zaznati težave, povezane s priljubljenimi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1357">**from_favorites** - Indicates if the action was taken from favorites to help us detect issues related to favorites</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1358">**group_calendar_count** – ponazarja število koledarjev za račun, s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane s koledarji skupine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1358">**group_calendar_count** - Indicates the number of calendars for the account to help us detect issues related group calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1359">**inbox_unread_count** – ponazarja število neprebranih sporočil v nabiralniku, s katerim lahko zaznamo težave pri prikazu števila neprebranih sporočil v mapi »Prejeto«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1359">**inbox_unread_count** - Indicates the number of unread messages in the inbox to help us detect issues with displaying inbox unread counts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1360">**interesting_calendar_accounts_count** – ponazarja število računov, ki so primerni za zanimive koledarje v napravi, s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane z zanimivimi koledarji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1360">**interesting_calendar_accounts_count** - Indicates the number of accounts which are eligible for interesting calendars on the device to help us detect issues related to interesting calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1361">**is_group_calendar** – ponazarja, ali gre za koledar skupine, in nam pomaga zaznati težave, povezane s koledarji skupine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1361">**is_group_calendar** - Indicates if the calendar is a group calendar to help us detect issues related group calendars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1362">**mail_folder_type** – ponazarja vrsto mape za pošto, npr. prejeto, osnutki itd., in nam pomaga zaznati težave, povezane z vrstami map.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1362">**mail_folder_type** - Indicates the mail folder type i.e. inbox, drafts, etc. to help us detect issues related to folder types.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1363">**mail_accounts_count** – ponazarja število računov pošte, s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane računi pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1363">**mail_accounts_count** - indicates the number of mail accounts to help us detect issues related mail accounts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1364">**selected_group_calendar_count** – ponazarja število koledarjev skupine, ki so izbrani in aktivni v uporabniškem vmesniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1364">**selected_group_calendar_count** - Indicates the number of group calendars which are selected and active in the UI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1365">**visibility_toggle** – ponazarja, ali je uporabnik vklopil/izklopil dani koledar, in nam pomaga zaznati težave, povezne s prikazovanjem oz. skrivanjem koledarjev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1365">**visibility_toggle** - indicates if the user is turning on or off a given calendar to help us detect issues related to showing or hiding calendars</span></span>

#### <a name="ipccreaterepublishinglicense"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1366">IpcCreateRepublishingLicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1366">IpcCreateRepublishingLicense</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1367">Zbira, ko uporabnik poskuša odpreti dokument, zaščiten z upravljanjem pravic do informacij ali uporabiti zaščito za upravljanje pravic do informacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1367">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1368">Vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride v zadnji fazi postopka, ko se izvede priklic API IpcCreateRepublishingLicense.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1368">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when the IpcCreateRepublishingLicense API call is made.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1369">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1369">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1370">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hierarhija odjemalcev, ki označuje, da se program izvaja v produkcijskem okolju ali v okolju razvijalcev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1370">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1371">**AppInfo.Name** – ime aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1371">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1372">**AppInfo.Version** – različica aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1372">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1373">**iKey** – ID strežnika za storitev pisanja dnevnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1373">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1374">**RMS.Duration** – Skupen čas za izvedbo API priklica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1374">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for API call to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1375">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – skupni čas minus zunanje operacije, kot je zakasnitev omrežja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1375">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1617">**RMS.StatusCode** – ID scenarija, ki ga določa API</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1617">**RMS.StatusCode** - Scenario Id defined by the API</span></span>


#### <a name="linkclickedaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1618">link.clicked.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1618">link.clicked.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1619">Dogodek se uporablja za spremljanje uspeha uporabnikov pri ogledu URL-ja v pogledu »Edge Web View« in izpolnjevanju standardnih spletnih scenarijev v tem spletnem pogledu, ne da bi se s tem soočile napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1619">The event is used to track users' success in viewing a URL in the Edge web view and completing standard web scenarios in that web view without facing errors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1620">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1620">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1621">**account_type** – če je bil pogled» Edge Web View «zagnan z e-poštnega sporočila ali dogodkom v Outlooku, vnesite račun, od koder je prišel URL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1621">**account_type** – if the Edge web view was launched from an email or event in Outlook, type of the account where the URL came from</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1622">**dejanje** – dejanje, ki ga opravi uporabnik znotraj Outlooka od trenutka, ko tapnete URL, da ko zapusti ta potek (odprla povezavo v pogledu» rob «, se stran ni naložila v spletnem pogledu, izvedla iskanje v spletnem pogledu, zaprla spletni pogled Edge, da bi odprla povezavo v spletnem brskalniku...)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1622">**action** – action performed by the user inside Outlook from the moment they tap on a URL to when they exit that flow (opened the link in the Edge web view, page failed to load in the web view, performed a search in the web view, exit the Edge web view to open the link in a web browser application, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1623">**trajanje** – trajanje uporabniške seje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1623">**duration** – duration of the user session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1624">**launch_type** – če se je zagnal pogled »Edge Web View«, je bil iz Outlooka, iz gradnika ali iz komponente OS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1624">**launch_type** – if the Edge web view was launched, was it from Outlook, from a widget, or from an OS component</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1625">**poreklo** – če je uporabnik izvajal dejanje v pogledu »Edge Web View«, je izvor tega dejanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1625">**origin** – if the user performed an action in the Edge web view, origin of that action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1626">**Napotitelj** – mesto URL-ja, na katerega uporabnik prisluškuje (e-pošta, dogodek v koledarju, kartica TXP itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1626">**referrer** – the location of the URL the user tapped on (email, calendar event, TXP card, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1627">**search_scope** – če je uporabnik izvajal iskanje v pogledu »Edge Web View«, obseg iskanja (vse, slike, videoposnetki itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1627">**search_scope** – if the user performed a search in the Edge web view, scope of that search (All, Images, Videos, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1628">**search_subtype** – če je uporabnik izvajal iskanje v pogledu »Edge Web View«, je bilo začetno iskanje ali rafinirano iskanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1628">**search_subtype** – if the user performed a search in the Edge web view, was it an initial search or a refined search</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1629">**session_summary_page_loaded_count** – število strani, ki jih uporabnik naloži med sejo v pogledu »Edge Web View«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1629">**session_summary_page_loaded_count** – number of pages loaded by the user during their session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1630">**session_summary_search_count** – število iskanj Bing, ki jih je opravil uporabnik med sejo v pogledu »Edge Web View«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1630">**session_summary_search_count** - number of Bing searches performed by the user during their session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1631">**session_summary_session_id** – identifikator za trenutno sejo uporabnika v pogledu »Edge Web View«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1631">**session_summary_session_id** – identifier for the present user session in the Edge web view</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1632">**txp** – če je bil pogled» Edge Web View «zagnan iz TXP kartice, vrste dogodkov za to kartico (jedilnica, Flight itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1632">**txp** – if the Edge web view was launched from a TXP card, event type for that card (dining, flight, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1633">**txp** – če je bil pogled »Edge Web View« zagnan iz TXP kartice, vrste dogodkov za to kartico (jedilnica, Flight itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1633">**txp_component** - if the Edge web view was launched from a TXP card, UI component type for that card</span></span>


#### <a name="mailaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1634">mail.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1634">mail.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1635">Uporablja se za nadzor morebitnega negativnega učinka na vašo zmožnost izvajanja kritičnih dejanj pošte (npr. izvajanje na pošte v nitnem načinu, zagotavljanje delovanje triažnih dejanj za pošto) in zagotavljanje, da naša poštna aplikacija ustrezno deluje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1635">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform critical mail actions (like running mail threaded mode, ensuring mail triage actions work) to ensure our app is functioning properly for mail.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1636">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1636">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1637">**račun** – račun, ki je izvajal dejanje *[to polje je bilo odstranjeno iz tekočih različic Officea, vendar se lahko še vedno prikaže v starejših različicah.]*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1637">**account** - the account which performed the action *[This field has been removed from current builds of Office, but might still appear in older builds.]*</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1638">**action** – spremlja vrsto izvedenega dejanja, npr. arhiviranje, brisanje, označevanje kot prebrano itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1638">**action** - tracks what type of action was taking, i.e. archive, delete, mark as read, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1639">**attachment_content_type** – vrsta vsebine prenesene priloge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1639">**attachment_content_type** - the content type of the downloaded attachment</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1640">**attachment_content_type_with_count** – spremlja število prilog v e-pošti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1640">**attachment_content_type_with_count** - tracks the number of attachments in email</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1641">**attachment_download_result** – rezultat (npr. usešno/neuspešno) za dejanje prenosa priloge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1641">**attachment_download_result** - the result (i.e. success/failure) for an attachment download action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1642">**attachment_download_time** – čas dejanja prenosa priloge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1642">**attachment_download_time** - the time for an attachment download action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1643">**attachment_extn** – datotečna pripona za preneseno prilogo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1643">**attachment_extn** - the file extension of the downloaded attachment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1644">**attachment_id** – identifikator sistema za preneseno prilogo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1644">**attachment_id** - the system identifier for the downloaded attachment</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1645">**attachment_size** – velikost prenesene priloge.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1645">**attachment_size** - the size of downloaded attachment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1646">**domain** – domena dokumenta, ki ga želite odpreti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1646">**domain** - domain of the document being opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1647">**duration** – spremlja, kako dolgo je trajalo dejanje kot niz v človeku berljivi obliki v angleščini (npr. 1 s, 4 ure).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1647">**duration** - tracks how long the action took as human-readable English string (e.g. 1s, 4h)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1648">**error** – sporočilo o napaki, povezani z dejanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1648">**error** - error message associated with the action</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1649">**event_mode** – vrsta izbranega načina dogodka, skupine ali drugo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1649">**event_mode** - what type of event mode it was in, groups or others.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1650">**Extension** – datotečna pripona povezave ali priloge, povezane s tem dejanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1650">**Extension** - file extension of link or attachment associated with this action</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1651">**internet_message_id** – ID sporočila za sledenje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1651">**internet_message_id** - tracking message ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1652">**is_group_escalation** – ponazarja, ali je bilo sporočilo, za katero se je dejanje izvedlo, poslano v nabiralnik uporabnika zaradi stopnjevanja (naročnina na skupino).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1652">**is_group_escalation** - indicates whether the message the action was taken on was sent to the user's mailbox because of an escalation (subscribed to group)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1653">**is_rule** – ponazarja, ali je izvedeno dejanje pošte ponastavilo klasifikacijo v fokusu/drugo klasifikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1653">**is_rule** - indicates if the mail action done is resetting a focused/other classification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1654">**is_threaded_mode** – ponazarja, ali je bilo sporočilo v nitnem načinu, npr. način združevanja sporočil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1654">**is_threaded_mode** - indicates whether the message was in threaded mode or not, i.e. how are the messages grouped</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1655">**is_unread** – ponazarja, ali je sporočilo, za katero se je izvedlo dejanje, neprebrano.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1655">**is_unread** - indicates whether message is unread that the action was taken on</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1656">**left_swipe_setting** – ponazarja dejanje, ki ga izvedete z levim podrsljajem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1656">**left_swipe_setting** - indicates what action was a set to be the left swipe</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1657">**message_id** – ID sporočila strežnika, ciljan za dejanje, ali seznam, ločen z vejicami, če je bilo izvedenih več dejanj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1657">**message_id** - server message id targeted for action, or comma-separated list if more than one item was in action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1658">**message_type** – ponazarja vrsto sporočila, za katero je bilo izvedeno dejanje\*\* – skupina ali drugo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1658">**message_type** - indicates what type of message type the action was taken on\*\* - group or other</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1659">**number_selected** – število elementov, ki jih je izbral uporabnik na seznamu sporočil in je ukrepal v več načinih izbora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1659">**number_selected** - the number of items the user selected on the message list and took action on during multiple selection mode.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1660">**origin** – vir dejanja, npr. podrsanje po celici, ničelna poizvedba, globoka povezava, e-poštni pogled, e-poštni seznam itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1660">**origin** - source of action, i.e. cell swipe, zero-query, deep link, email view, email list, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1661">**reported_to_msft** – ko je bila e-pošta posredovana v mapo z neželeno vsebino (neželena pošta) ali v koš (lažno predstavljanje), lahko uporabnik izbere, ali želi dejanje prijaviti Microsoftu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1661">**reported_to_msft** - after sending an email to junk (spam) or trash (phishing) they can choose to report their action to Microsoft.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1662">**retry** – ali je prišlo do vnovične izvedbe dejanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1662">**retry** - whether the action was retried</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1663">**right_swipe_setting** – ponazarja dejanje, ki ga izvedete z desnim podrsljajem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1663">**right_swipe_setting** - indicates what action was a set to be the right swipe</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1664">**shortcut** – ponazarja, ali je bila uporabljena bližnjica in katera bližnjica je bila uporabljena za načrtovanje sporočila, npr. pozneje, jutri, izberite čas itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1664">**shortcut** - indicates if a shortcut was used and what shortcut was used for scheduling a message i.e. later, tomorrow, choose time, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1665">**size** – velikost povezave ali priloge, povezane s tem dejanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1665">**size** - size of link or attachment associated with this action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1666">**source_folder** – spremlja vrsto izvorne mape, ko dejanje ponazarja na premik iz ene v drugo mapo, npr. v mapo »Prejeto«, koš itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1666">**source_folder** - tracks source folder type when action is indicating to move from one folder to other, i.e. to inbox, trash etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1667">**source_inbox** – ponazarja, v kateri nabiralnik bo poslana pošta (tj. s fokusom, drugo itd.) – stanje dejanja, npr. uspešno ali mesto neuspeha.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1667">**source_inbox** - indicates which inbox the mail action is taking place (i.e. focused, other, etc.) state - state of the action, i.e. success or point of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1668">**target_folder** – ponazarja vrsto ciljne mape pri premikanju e-poštnih sporočil iz ene mape v drugo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1668">**target_folder** - indicates target folder type when moving emails from one folder to other</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1669">**thread_id** – ID niza za pogovor, ciljan za dejanje, ali seznam, ločen z vejicami, če je bilo izvedenih več dejanj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1669">**thread_id** - thread id of the conversation targeted for action, or comma-separated list if more than one item was targeted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1670">**time_taken_to_fetch_access_token** – čas, zahtevan za pridobivanje sistemskega žetona za dostop in uporabo za odpiranje povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1670">**time_taken_to_fetch_access_token** - time taken to fetch a system access token to use for opening a link</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1671">**time_taken_to_fetch_drive_item** – čas, zahtevan za pridobivanje vira OneDrive ob kliku nanj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1671">**time_taken_to_fetch_drive_item** - time taken to fetch a OneDrive resource when clicked</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1672">**time_taken_to_fetch_embed_viewer_resource** – čas, zahtevan za inicializacijo vdelanega pregledovalnika pri odpiranju povezav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1672">**time_taken_to_fetch_embed_viewer_resource** - time taken to initialize the embedded viewer when opening links</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1673">**time_taken_to_load_embed_viewer** – čas, zahtevan za inicializacijo vdelanega pregledovalnika pri odpiranju povezav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1673">**time_taken_to_load_embed_viewer** - time taken to initialize the embedded viewer when opening links</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1674">**time_taken_to_load_link** – čas, zahtevan za dokončanje nalaganja povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1674">**time_taken_to_load_link** - time a load link action takes to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1675">**time_taken_to_tap_attachment** – čas med odpiranjem sporočila in klikom na Priloge</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1675">**time_taken_to_tap_attachment** - the time between opening the message and clicking on the attachment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1676">**time_taken_to_tap_link** – čas, ki ga je uporabnik porabil za ogled sporočila in klik povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1676">**time_taken_to_tap_link** - time the user took between viewing message and clicking a link</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1677">**txp** – ponazarja, ali je na voljo vrsta txp za element, povezan s pošto, za katero je bilo izvedeno dejanje, npr. rezervacija dogodka, rezervacija leta itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1677">**txp** - indicates if there is a txp type of item associated with the mail that action was taken on, i.e. event reservation, flight reservation, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1678">**type** – vrsta dokumenta, ki je bila odprta prek povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1678">**type** - document type being opened via link</span></span>

#### <a name="mailcompose"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1679">mail.compose</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1679">mail.compose</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1680">Uporablja se za nadzor morebitnega negativnega učinka na vašo zmožnost sestavljanja e-poštnega sporočila in odgovarjanja nanj, npr. težave pri možnosti »Odgovori vsem«, oblikovanje ali pošiljanje e-poštnega sporočila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1680">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to compose and reply to emails such as running into issues with reply-all, formatting your email, or sending your emails.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1681">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1681">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1682">**draft_message_id** – ID osnutka za pogovor, ki ga želite ustvariti kot osnutek, s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane z osnutki e-poštnih sporočil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1682">**draft_message_id** - The draft id of the conversation being created as a draft to help us detect issues related to draft emails</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1683">**message_id** – ID sporočila za pogovor, na katerega ste odgovorili ali vam je bil posredovan, s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane z določenim sporočilom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1683">**message_id** - The message id of the conversation being replied to or forwarded from to help us detect issues related to a specific message</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1684">**origin** – prikazuje vir sporočila, na primer možnost »Odgovori vsem«, »Sestavi novo sporočilo« ali »Hitri odgovor«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1684">**origin** - Tells us where the compose originated from, such as from a reply all, a new compose, or quick reply.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1685">Pomaga nam pri zaznavanju težav, povezanih z določeno vrsto vira odgovora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1685">Helps us detect issues associated with a specific reply origin type.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1686">**is_group_escalation** – ponazarja, ali je sporočilo stopnjevano sporočilo skupine, ki nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav pri sestavljanju, povezanih s skupinami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1686">**is_group_escalation** - Whether the message is an escalated group message so we can detect compose issues related to groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1687">**is_link** – ponazarja, ali je bil novi osnutek ustvarjen iz povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1687">**is_link** - Tells us if the new draft that was created was done from a link.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1688">Pomaga nam pri zaznavanju težav, povezanih z osnutki, ustvarjenimi iz povezav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1688">Helps us detect issues associated with drafts created from links.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1689">**is_force_touch** – ponazarja, ali je bil novi osnutek ustvarjen iz dejanja na dotik na silo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1689">**is_force_touch** - Tells us if the new draft that was created was done from a force touch action.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1690">Pomaga nam pri zaznavanju težav, povezanih z osnutki, ustvarjenimi s tem določenim dejanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1690">Helps us detect issues associated with drafts created from this specific action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1691">**is_groups** – ponazarja, ali je bil ta dogodek zagnan iz prostora skupine, in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav pri sestavljanju, povezanih s skupinami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1691">**is_groups** - Whether the event was started from the groups' space so we can detect compose issues related to groups.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1692">**source_inbox** – ponazarja izvorni nabiralnik, na primer ali je bil v fokusu ali je šlo za drug nabiralnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1692">**source_inbox** - Tells us the source inbox, such as whether it was a focused or other inbox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1693">**thread_id** – ID niti za pogovor, na katerega ste odgovorili ali vam je bil posredovan, s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane z določeno nitjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1693">**thread_id** - The thread id of the conversation being replied to or forwarded from to help us detect issues related to a specific thread</span></span>

#### <a name="meetingcalltoaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1694">meeting.call.to.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1694">meeting.call.to.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1695">Se uporablja za nadzor morebitnih negativnih učinkov na vašo zmožnost izvajanja ključnih dejanj srečanja, kot so ustvarjanje in urejanje srečanj in odgovarjanje nanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1695">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on your ability to perform critical meeting actions like creating, editing, and responding to meetings.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1696">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1696">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1697">**event_mode** – ponazarja, ali gre za dogodek skupine, in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav z dogodki skupine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1697">**event_mode** - Indicates whether this event was from a group or not to help us detect issues with group events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1698">**meeting_id** – ID srečanja, s pomočjo katerega lahko spremljamo težave za čas trajanja srečanja in zaznamo težave z določenimi srečanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1698">**meeting_id** - A meeting ID that helps us track issues throughout the lifetime of a meeting to help us detect issues with specific meetings</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1699">**meeting_provider** – ponazarja ponudnika spletnega srečanja, npr. Teams, Skype za podjetja, in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav z določenimi ponudniki spletnih srečanj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1699">**meeting_provider** - Indicates the provider for an online meeting, e.g. Teams, Skype for Business to help us detect issues with specific online meeting providers</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1700">**notify_type** – ponazarja vrsto odgovora za druge vrste računov in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav z različnimi vrstami računov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1700">**notify_type** - Indicates the response type for other account types to help us detect issues with different account types</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1701">**recurrence** – ponazarja pogostost srečanja, npr. enkratno srečanje ali niz srečanj, in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav pri nizih ponavljajočih se srečanj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1701">**recurrence** - Indicates how often this meeting occurs I.e. occurrence or series to help us detect issues with reoccurring meeting series</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1702">**response** – ponazarja vrsto odziva, kot je sprejem ali zavrnitev, v določenih vrstah računa in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav pri odzivanju na dogodke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1702">**response** - Indicates response type such as accept or decline on certain account types to help us detect issues with responding to events</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1703">**response_message_length** – ponazarja dolžino sporočila in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav pri odzivih na srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1703">**response_message_length** - Indicates how long the message length was to help us detect issues with meeting responses</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1704">**review_time_proposal_action_type** – ponazarja predlog novega časa v odzivu uporabnika in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav s predlaganjem novega časa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1704">**review_time_proposal_action_type** - Indicates a user response new time proposal to help us detect issues with proposing a new time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1705">**send_response** – ponazarja, ali je bil odziv poslan, in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav pri pošiljanju odzivov na povabilo na srečanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1705">**send_response** - Indicates whether a response was sent to help us detect issues sending meeting invite responses</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1706">**txp** – ponazarja vrsto, iz katere je bilo srečanje ustvarjeno, od rezervacij leta do dostavo, in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav s to vrsto srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1706">**txp** - Indicates what type of meeting it was generated from flight reservations and deliveries to help us detect issues with this type of meeting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1707">**with_message_enabled** – ponazarja, ali se uporabnik lahko odzove s sporočilom, in nam pomaga pri zaznavanju težav z odzivi na povabila na srečanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1707">**with_message_enabled** - Indicates whether a user can response with a message to help us detect issues with responding to meeting invites</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroiddocsuifileoperationsopendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1708">Office.Android.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1708">Office.Android.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1709">Ta dogodek se zbira za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo v platformi Android, in zabeleži dogodek odpiranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1709">This event is collected for Office applications running under Android platform and records when a file open operation takes place.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1710">Ta dogodek zagotavlja varnost pri odpiranju datoteke, posodobitve in učinkovito delovanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1710">The event helps in keeping the file open operation secure, up- to- date and performing properly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1711">Cilj zbiranja teh podatkov je nenehno izboljševanje učinkovitosti pri odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1711">The goal of collecting this data is to continuously improve the file open performance.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1712">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1712">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1713">**Data_AppDocsDuration** –čas, zahtevan za podplast med odpiranjem datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1713">**Data_AppDocsOperationDuration** - The duration spent in sub- layer during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1714">**Data_AppDuration** – čas, zahtevan za obdelavo aplikacije med odpiranjem datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1714">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1715">**Data_AppWarmUpGain** – pridobitev pri času zagona aplikacije, ki smo jo pridobili zaradi vnaprejšnjega zagona dela aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1715">**Data_AppWarmUpGain** - The gain in application boot duration we get because of pre-booting a part of the application beforehand.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1716">**Data_BootDuration** – čas, zahtevan za zagon aplikacije pri postopku za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1716">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of application boot in process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1717">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – v nekaterih scenarijih odpiranja datoteke je postopek zapiranja prej odprtega dokumenta izveden pred odpiranjem trenutnega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1717">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – In some file open scenarios, closing of a previously opened document takes place before the opening of the current document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1718">To časovno obdobje med nekaterimi postopki, ki se izvedejo v tem primeru, je zajeto v vrednosti niza v obliki zapisa \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1718">This time duration between some of the operations that take place in this case is captured in a string value which has the format \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1719">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja način za dostop datoteke, npr. samo za branje, branje in pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1719">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1720">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja vrsto asinhronega poteka, ki se uporablja za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1720">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1721">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja vrsto algoritma za razdruževanje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1721">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1722">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja stanje zaščite poslovnih podatkov datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1722">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1723">**Data_Doc_Ext** – Datotečna pripona datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1723">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1724">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – Ime gostitelja strežnika datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1724">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1725">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – globalni enolični identifikator (GUID), ki enolično določa ime gostitelja strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1725">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A Globally Unique Identifier (GUID) that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1726">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – GUID, ki enolično prepozna identiteto, uporabljeno za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1726">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1727">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje podrobno vrsto scenarija pri odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1727">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1728">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje V-/I-zastavice postopka za odpiranje datoteke, npr. ali je bila datoteka predpomnjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1728">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1729">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** – Ali je za datoteko omogočeno sodelovanje v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1729">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1730">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta s funkcijo postopnega odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1730">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1731">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – Ali datoteka podpira Officeovo storitev sodelovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1731">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1732">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta iz predpomnjene kopije brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1732">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1733">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – Ali je bila datoteka vnaprej pridobljena, preden se je zagnal postopek odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1733">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** - Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1734">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – Ali je na voljo lokalna različica datoteke, ki je sinhronizirana s strežnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1734">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1735">**Data_Doc_Location** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje mesto datoteke, npr. lokalno ali v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1735">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1736">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje razlog datoteke, ki je samo za branje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1736">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1737">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa ID vira strežnika datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1737">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource id of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1738">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto kanala v realnem času (RTC), ki ga uporablja datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1738">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real- time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1739">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – GUID, ki enolično določa ID dokumenta strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1739">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1740">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje protokol strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1740">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1741">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1741">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1742">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje različico strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1742">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1743">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – Celo število, ki se poveča za 1 za vsak postopek odpiranja datoteke v seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1743">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1744">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – niz, ki se uporablja za korelacijo odjemalskih in strežniških dnevnikov, po navadi je to neke vrste ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1744">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client- side and server- side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1745">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – Velikost datoteke v bajtih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1745">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - File size in bytes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1746">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto posebnega znaka, ki ga ima URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1746">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1747">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1747">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1748">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** – ali je bila datoteka odprta postopoma z vnaprej predpomnjenimi podatki WRS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1748">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre- cached WRS data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1749">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – niz, ki označuje, iz katere storitve je datoteka WOPI (Web Application Interface Protocol).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1749">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - A string indicating which service a Web Application Open Platform Interface Protocol (WOPI) file is from.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1750">**Data_ErrorId_Code** – koda napake, ki označuje napako v postopku zbiranja podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1750">**Data_ErrorId_Code** - An error code indicating a failure in the data collection operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1751">**Data_ErrorId_Tag** – oznaka v kodi za pomoč pri iskanju mesta okvare.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1751">**Data_ErrorId_Tag** - A tag in the code to help find the point of failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1752">**Data_FileOpenFlowMarkers** – preden se začne postopek odpiranja datoteke, se mora dokončati postopek vnaprejšnje obdelave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1752">**Data_FileOpenFlowMarkers** – Before the file open process begins, there is some pre-processing involved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1753">Čas, porabljen za vnaprejšnjo obdelavo, je zajet v vrednosti v obliki zapisa \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1753">This time taken for this pre-processing is captured in a string value which has the format \<functionId>\<functionValue>\<functionId>\<functionValue>...</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1754">**Data_FirstPartyProviderApp** – Če se datoteka, ki je odprta v programih Word, Excel ali PowerPoint ali Office, prikliče iz druge Microsoftove aplikacije, je tukaj zajeto ime te ponudniške storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1754">**Data_FirstPartyProviderApp** - If a file open on Word, Excel, or PowerPoint or Office apps is invoked from another Microsoft app, then the name of that provider app is captured here.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1755">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** – vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije ter trajanjem, ki vključuje trajanje klicev podfunkcij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1755">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which includes the duration of sub- function calls.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1756">**Data_InitializationReason** – oštevilčenje, ki označuje, način odpiranja datoteke, npr. element uporabniškega vmesnika, odpiranje sprožila aplikacija itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1756">**Data_InitializationReason** - An enumeration indicating how the file is opened, e.g. UI element, triggered by another app, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1757">**Data_Measurements** – vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije ter trajanjem, ki ne vključuje trajanje klicev podfunkcij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1757">**Data_Measurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which excludes the duration of sub- function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1758">**Data_OfficeMobileInitReason** – oštevilčenje, ki označuje vstopno točko pri odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1758">**Data_OfficeMobileInitReason** - An enumeration indicating the entry point of file open.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1759">**Data_RenderToInSpaceDuration** – trajanje med upodobitvijo in animacijo silhuete/platna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1759">**Data_RenderToInSpaceDuration** – The duration between render end and the silhouette/canvas animation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1760">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** – Trajanje upodabljanja za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1760">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** - The duration of rendering of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1761">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** – Vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije, časovnim žigom začetka in trajanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1761">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag, start timestamp and duration.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1765">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1765">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1766">**EventDate** – časovni žig ponovitve dogodka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1766">**EventDate** – Timestamp of the event occurrence</span></span>
