#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryexpansionfilesavailability"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1768">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesAvailability</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1768">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesAvailability</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1769">Omogočamo razširitvene datoteke kompleta Android Package Kit (APK) za Officeovo mobilno aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1769">We are enabling Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1770">Razširitvene datoteke APK so dodatne datoteke sredstev, ki jih lahko razvijalci aplikacije Android objavijo skupaj z aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1770">APK Expansion files are supplementary resource files that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1771">Ker želimo vedeti, kako zanesljive so razširitvene datoteke, zabeležimo zastavico, ki pri vsakem zagonu označuje, ali so razširitvene datoteke na voljo ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1771">To understand the reliability of the expansion files, we log a flag indicating whether expansion files are available or not at every boot.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1772">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1772">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1773">**Data_ExpansionFilesAvailable** – logična zastavica, ki označuje, ali so razširitvene datoteke APK na voljo v napravi ob trenutku zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1773">**Data_ExpansionFilesAvailable** - A Boolean flag that indicates whether APK Expansion files are available on the device at the time of app boot.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryexpansionfilesdownloader"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1774">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesDownloader</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1774">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesDownloader</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1775">Omogočamo razširitvene datoteke kompleta Android Package Kit (APK) za Officeovo mobilno aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1775">We are enabling Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1776">Razširitvene datoteke APK so dodatne datoteke sredstev, ki jih lahko razvijalci aplikacije Android objavijo skupaj z aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1776">APK Expansion files are supplementary resource files, that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1777">Ker želimo vedeti, kako zanesljiv je naš mehanizem za prenos razširitvenih datotek, zabeležimo zastavico, ki označuje, ali smo uspešno prenesli razširitvene datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1777">To understand the reliability of our expansion file download mechanism, we are logging a flag indicating whether we are successfully able to download expansion files.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1778">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1778">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1779">**Data_DownloadSuccess** – logična zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil prenos razširitvenih datotek APK uspešen, ko poskusimo izvesti prenos med zagonom aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1779">**Data_DownloadSuccess** - A Boolean flag that indicates whether APK Expansion files download is successful, whenever we attempt a download during app boot.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunecompliancerequest"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1780">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1780">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1781">Ta dogodek se zbira za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo v sistemu Android, vključno z aplikacijami: Office Mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint in OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1781">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, including Office mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and OneNote.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1782">Ta dogodek ponazarja poskus vpisa v račun organizacije, licenciran za Intune, za katerega je skrbnik organizacije pravilnik nastavil tako, da izvršuje pogojni dostop aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1782">The event indicates an attempt to sign-in to an Intune licensed organization account where the organization administrator has configured policy to enforce app conditional access.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1783">Uporablja se za razumevanje števila končnih uporabnikov, ki poskušajo aplikacije uporabiti v sklopu te konfiguracije pravilnika, in je združen z drugim dogodkom, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus, za zagotavljanje izvrševanja konfiguriranega pravilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1783">It is used to understand the number of end users who are attempting to use apps under this policy configuration, and is combined with another event, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus, to ensure the configured policy is enforced.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1784">Podatkovna polja se ne zbirajo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1784">No data fields are collected.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunecompliancestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1785">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1785">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1786">Ta dogodek se zbira za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo v sistemu Android, vključno z aplikacijami: Office Mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint in OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1786">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, including Office mobile, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, and OneNote.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1787">Ta dogodek ponazarja poskus vpisa v račun organizacije, licenciran za Intune, za katerega je skrbnik organizacije pravilnik nastavil tako, da izvršuje pogojni dostop aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1787">The event indicates an attempt to sign-in to an Intune licensed organization account where the organization administrator has configured policy to enforce app conditional access.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1788">Ta dogodek ponazarja stanje skladnosti aplikacije, v katero se je uporabnik vpisal, in se uporablja za preiskovanje okvar.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1788">This event indicates the compliance status of the application to which the user has signed-in and is used to investigate failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1789">Združen je z drugim dogodkom, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest, za zagotavljanje izvrševanja konfiguriranega pravilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1789">It is combined with another event, Office.Android.Intune.IntuneComplianceRequest, to ensure the configured policy is enforced.</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1790">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1790">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1791">**Data_ComplianceStatus** – označuje stanje skladnosti aplikacije med vpisom s kodo napake pri uspehu ali napaki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1791">**Data_ComplianceStatus** - Indicates the compliance status of the application during sign-in with a success or failure error code.</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1792">-1 – neznana napaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1792">-1 – Unknown error</span></span>
  -    <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1793">0 – aplikacija je skladna s pravilniki organizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1793">0 – The application is compliant with the organization policies</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1794">1 – aplikacija ni skladna s pravilniki organizacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1794">1 – The application is not compliant with the organization policies</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1795">2 – okvare, povezane s storitvijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1795">2 – Service related failures</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1796">3 – okvare, povezane z omrežjem</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1796">3 – Network related failures</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1797">4 – aplikacija ni uspela pridobiti žetona za preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1797">4 – Application failed to retrieve authentication token</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1798">5 – odziv storitve še ni bil prejet</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1798">5 – The response has not been yet received from the service</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1799">6 – aplikacija portala podjetja mora biti nameščena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1799">6 – The company portal application needs to be installed</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidodwxpssotelemetry"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1800">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1800">Office.Android.ODWXPSSO.Telemetry</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1801">S tem dogodkom boste lažje razumeli, s katero drugo Microsoftovo aplikacijo v napravi se je v naši aplikaciji izvedela tiha enotna prijava, s katere točke vnosa itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1801">This event helps in understanding with which other Microsoft app in the device, our app got silent single sign on, from which entry point and so on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1802">Prav tako pomaga pri razumevanju vzroka napake za neuspešno tiho enotno prijavo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1802">Also helps in understanding the failure reason for not getting silent single sign on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1803">Pridobivamo boljše vpoglede, na primer, iz katere Microsoftove aplikacije v napravi smo pridobili izkušnjo enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1803">We get better insights like from which Microsoft app in the device, we are getting single sign on experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1804">Ukrepi, kjer enotna prijava ne deluje pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1804">Act upon failures, where single sign on is not working as expected.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1805">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1805">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1806">**AccountType** – Označuje vrsto računa, s katerim je bila izvedena enotna prijava, denimo osebni Microsoftov račun ali službeni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1806">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which single sign on is happening, like personal Microsoft account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1807">**EntryPoint** – Označuje vstopno točko v aplikaciji, s katere je bil inicializiran poskus enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1807">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where single sign on attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1808">**ErrorCode** – Označuje kodo napake pri poskusu enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1808">**ErrorCode** - Indicates the error code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1809">**ErrorDescription** – Označuje sporočilo o napaki poskusa enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1809">**ErrorDescription** - Indicates the error message of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1810">**HResult** – Označuje rezultat kode stanja pri poskusu enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1810">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the single sign on attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1811">**ProviderPackageId** – Druga Microsoftova aplikacija v napravi, iz katere se je izvedla enotna prijava.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1811">**ProviderPackageId** - Other Microsoft app in the device from which single sign on is happening.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidphonenumbersignins"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1812">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1812">Office.Android.PhoneNumberSignIns</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1813">S tem dogodkom poskušamo razumeti, ali se je uporabnik prijavil ali vpisal z računom, povezanim s telefonsko številko, ali z računom, povezanim z e-poštnim naslovom osebnega Microsoftovega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1813">This event helps in understanding if user signed in or signed up with phone number-based account or email based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1814">S tem dogodkom določimo število uporabnikov, ki se prijavljajo ali vpisujejo z osebnim Microsoftovim računom, povezanim s telefonsko številko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1814">This event helps in knowing count of users signing in or signing up with phone number based personal Microsoft account.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1815">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1815">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1816">**EntryPoint** – Označuje vstopno točko v aplikaciji, s katere je bil inicializiran poskus vpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1816">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1817">**IsEmailMissing** – Ali je v podatkih profila računa naveden e-poštni naslov?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1817">**IsEmailMissing** - Is email missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1818">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** – Ali je v podatkih profila računa navedena telefonska številka?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1818">**IsPhoneNumberMissing** - Is phone number missing in the account profile information?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1819">**UserDecision** – Označuje izbiro uporabnika, kot je vpis ali prijava oz. poznejši vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1819">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidusersignindecision"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1820">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1820">Office.Android.UserSignInDecision</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1821">S tem dogodkom poskušamo razumeti, na kateri stopnji je prišlo do težave pri vpisu, zakaj vpis ni bil uspešen, koliko uporabnikov se je uspešno vpisalo iz določene vstopne točke v aplikaciji itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1821">This event helps in understanding at which stage user is dropping in sign in flow, why sign in is failing, how many users are getting signed in successfully from which entry point in the app and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1822">S tem dogodkom lažje usmerjamo podatke o vpisu, ki so nam v pomoč pri določanju, na kateri stopnji uporabniki naletijo na težave itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1822">This event helps with sign-in funnel data, which helps in understand at which stage users are getting dropped more and so on.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1823">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1823">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1824">**AccountType** – Označuje vrsto računa, s katerim je bil izveden poskus vpisa, denimo osebni račun ali službeni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1824">**AccountType** - Indicates the account type with which sign-in is attempted like personal account or work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1825">**AfterLicensingState** – Označuje stanje licence aplikacije po dokončanem vpisu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1825">**AfterLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state after sign-in completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1826">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** – Označuje, koliko prostih urejanj je poteklo, preden je bil izveden vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1826">**AllowedEditsWithoutSignIn** - Indicates how many free edits have lapsed before sign-in was attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1827">**BeforeLicensingState** – Označuje stanje licence aplikacije pred vpisom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1827">**BeforeLicensingState** - Indicates the app licensing state before sign-in attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1828">**CompletionState** – Označuje stopnjo dokončanja vpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1828">**CompletionState** - Indicates the stage of sign-in completion.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1829">**EntryPoint** – Označuje vstopno točko v aplikaciji, s katere je bil inicializiran poskus vpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1829">**EntryPoint** - Indicates the entry point in the app, from where sign-in attempt was initiated.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1830">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** – Označuje število pospešenih vpisov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1830">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1831">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** – Označuje število preklicanih pospešenih vpisov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1831">**HRDAutoAcceleratedSignUpQuitCount** - Indicates the count of accelerated sign-ups canceled.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1832">**HResult** – Označuje rezultat kode stanja za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1832">**HResult** - Indicates result status code of the sign-in operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1833">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** – Ali je dovoljen vpis z računom, povezanim s telefonsko številko?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1833">**IsPhoneOnlyAuthFeatureEnabled** - Is phone number-based sign-in allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1834">**LicenseActivationHResult** – Označuje stanje kode za poskus aktivacije licence.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1834">**LicenseActivationHResult** - Indicates the status code of license activation attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1835">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** – Označuje kodo sporočila iz storitve licenciranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1835">**LicenseActivationMessageCode** - Indicates the message code from licensing service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1836">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** – Ali so prosta urejanja dovoljena?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1836">**NoFreeEditsTreatmentValue** - Is free edits allowed or not?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1837">**SignUpAttemptCount** – Označuje število poskusov prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1837">**SignUpAttemptCount** - Indicates the count of sign-ups attempted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1838">**StartMode** – Označuje način, v katerem je bil zagnan poskus vpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1838">**StartMode** - Indicates the mode in which sign-in attempt was started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1839">**UserDecision** – Označuje izbiro uporabnika, kot je vpis ali prijava oz. poznejši vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1839">**UserDecision** - Indicates the choice made by user like sign-in or sign-up or sign in later.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1840">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1840">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1841">Ustvarjeno je ob zagonu odjemalca, če je končni uporabnik omogočil nadzorno ploščo za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1841">Generated on client startup when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1842">Zbira informacije o tem, kdaj je posrednik za telemetrijo sistema Office prenesel podatke v mapo v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1842">It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent has uploaded data to the share folder.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1843">Primarna uporaba tega dogodka je spremljanje ustreznosti stanja posrednika za telemetrijo sistema Office, sekundarna uporaba dogodka pa je ocena uporabe nadzorne plošče za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1843">The primary use of this event is to monitor the health of the Office Telemetry agent and the secondary use of the event is to estimate usage of the Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1844">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1844">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1845">**UploadTime** – časovni žig zadnjega uspešnega prenosa, ki ga je izvedel posrednik za telemetrijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1845">**UploadTime** - the timestamp of the last successful upload performed by the Telemetry Agent.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentscanandupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1846">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentScanAndUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1846">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentScanAndUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1847">Podatki so zbrani le, če je uporabnik omogočil nadzorno ploščo za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1847">Only collected when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1848">Zbira informacije o tem, kdaj se izvaja posrednik za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1848">It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent is executed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1849">  Ti podatki so zbrani le, če je nadzorna plošča za telemetrijo sistema Office omogočena in uporabljena za določanje ustreznosti stanja posrednika za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1849">This is only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard is enabled and is used to determine the health of Office Telemetry agent.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1850">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1850">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1851">**Data.AgentExit** – Časovni žig, ko se je posrednik za telemetrijo uspešno zaprl.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1851">**Data.AgentExit** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent exits successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1852">**Data.AgentScan** – Časovni žig, ko je posrednik za telemetrijo uspešno dokončal pregled.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1852">**Data.AgentScan** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completed a scan successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1853">**Data.AgentUpload** – Časovni žig, ko je posrednik za telemetrijo uspešno dokončal nalaganje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1853">**Data.AgentUpload** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completes the upload successfully</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompattelemetrydashboardresiliencycrashlog"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1854">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1854">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1855">Ti podatki so zbrani le, če je končni uporabnik (najverjetneje skrbnik) omogočil nadzorno ploščo za telemetrijo sistema Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1855">Only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard has been enabled by end user (most likely an admin).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1856">Zbira pojavitve dodatkov za Office in zrušitve dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1856">It collects the occurrence of Office Add-ins and documents crashes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1857"> Ti podatki so zbrani le, če je končni uporabnik omogočil nadzorno ploščo za telemetrijo sistema Office. Z njimi določimo morebitno povečano pojavitev dodatkov ali zrušitev dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1857">This is only collected when user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard and is used to determine if there is an increased occurrence of add-in or document crashes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1858">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1858">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1859">**Data.CollectionTime** – Časovni žig, kdaj je bil zabeležen dogodek zrušitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1859">**Data.CollectionTime** - Timestamp of when a crash event was logged</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappdocsappdocsdocumentoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1860">Office.AppDocs.AppDocs.DocumentOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1860">Office.AppDocs.AppDocs.DocumentOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1861">Ta dogodek je zbran za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo v platformah Android, iOS, Universal ali Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1861">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, iOS, Universal or Windows platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1862">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede datotečna operacija (ustvari/odpre/shrani/izvozi/itd.), uporablja pa se za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj glede na informacije o datotečnih operacijah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1862">The event records when a file operation (create/open/save/export/etc.) takes place and it is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on the file operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1863">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1863">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1864">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – ID aplikacije, ko ni znan preden je bil za postopek priklican konec poročila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1864">**Data_AppIdForReportEndBeforeAppKnown** – App ID when not known before report end called on the operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1865">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** – Stanje CanContinue, preden je priklican program za obravnavo začetka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1865">**Data_CanContinueFromOnBeforeOperationBegins** – CanContinue state, before the begin handler is invoked.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1866">**Data_DetachedDuration** – Trajanje, zahtevano za odpenjanje postopka dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1866">**Data_DetachedDuration** – The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1867">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja način za dostop datoteke, npr. samo za branje, branje in pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1867">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1868">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja vrsto asinhronega poteka, ki se uporablja za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1868">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1869">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja vrsto algoritma za razdruževanje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1869">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1870">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja stanje zaščite poslovnih podatkov datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1870">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1871">**Data_Doc_Ext** – Prvi 4 znaki datotečne pripone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1871">**Data_Doc_Ext** – The first 4 characters of the file extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1872">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – Ime gostitelja strežnika datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1872">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1873">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa ime gostitelja strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1873">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1874">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost identitete uporabnika, uporabljena za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1874">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open..</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1875">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje podrobno vrsto scenarija pri odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1875">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1876">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje V-/I-zastavice postopka za odpiranje datoteke, npr. ali je bila datoteka predpomnjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1876">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1877">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** – Ali je za datoteko omogočeno sodelovanje v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1877">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** – Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1878">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta s funkcijo postopnega odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1878">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1879">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – Ali datoteka podpira Officeovo storitev sodelovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1879">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1880">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta iz predpomnjene kopije brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1880">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1881">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – Ali je bila datoteka vnaprej pridobljena, preden se je zagnal postopek odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1881">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1882">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – Ali je na voljo lokalna različica datoteke, ki je sinhronizirana s strežnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1882">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1883">**Data_Doc_Location** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje mesto datoteke, npr. lokalno ali v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1883">**Data_Doc_Location** – An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1884">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje razlog datoteke, ki je samo za branje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1884">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1885">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa ID vira strežnika datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1885">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource id of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1886">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto kanala v realnem času (RTC), ki ga uporablja datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1886">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1887">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – GUID, ki enolično določa ID dokumenta strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1887">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1888">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje protokol strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1888">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1889">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1889">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1890">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje različico strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1890">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1891">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – Celo število, ki se poveča za 1 za vsak postopek odpiranja datoteke v seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1891">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1892">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – Niz, ki se uporablja za korelacijo odjemalskih in strežniških dnevnikov, po navadi je to neke vrste ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1892">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – A string used to correlate client-side and server-side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1893">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – Velikost datoteke v bajtih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1893">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – File size in bytes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1894">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto posebnega znaka, ki ga ima URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1894">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1895">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1895">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-1896">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta postopoma z vnaprej predpomnjenimi podatki WRS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-1896">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** – Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre-cached WRS data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2214">Ta dogodek je zbran za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo v platformah Android, iOS, Universal ali Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2214">This event is collected for Office applications running on Android, iOS, Universal or Windows platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2215">Dogodek zabeleži odpiranje datoteke z URL-ja, uporablja pa se za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj glede na informacije o odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2215">The event records when a file open operation takes place from a URL and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2341">**Activity_CV** – ID za povezovanje dogodkov v seji povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2341">**Activity_CV** - ID to correlate the events across the connection session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2342">**Activity_StartStopType** – Konec.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2342">**Activity_StartStopType** - Stop</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsappledocsuxiossaveasthroughfilemenu"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2344">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2344">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2345">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2345">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2346">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede operacija »Shrani kot«, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o datotečnih operacijah, kot so kategorije mest.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2346">The event records when a "Save as" operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2347">Operacija »Shrani kot« se izvede vsakič, ko uporabnik ustvari novo datoteko in jo shrani prvič ali ko shrani kopijo obstoječe datoteke na novo mesto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2347">A "Save as" operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2348">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2348">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2349">**Data_OriginServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija izvirnega mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2349">**Data_OriginServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the original location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2350">**Data_ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija novega mesta datoteke po dokončanem shranjevanju, na primer »SharePoint« , »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2350">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the new location of a file after the save is completed like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsappledocsuxmacatmentioninsertedatmention"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2351">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXMacAtMentionInsertedAtMention</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2351">Office.Docs.Apple.DocsUXMacAtMentionInsertedAtMention</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2352">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2352">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2353">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik »@« omeni drugega uporabnika, uporablja pa se za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi tega, kako uporabniki sodelujejo z drugimi uporabniki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2353">This event records when a user "@" mentions another user and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on how users collaborate with other users.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2355">**Data_CharactersTyped** – številska vrednost, ki označuje skupno število znakov vnesenega besedila »@« omembe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2355">**Data_CharactersTyped** - A numerical value that indicates the total number of characters typed in the "@" mention text.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2357">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2357">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2358">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik da dokument v oblaku v skupno rabo z uporabo izkušnje dajanja v skupno rabo OneDrive, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2358">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2359">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2359">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2360">**Data_ShareType** – vprogramiran niz, ki označuje, katera vrsta operacije za skupno rabo je bila dokončana, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »Kopiranje povezave«, »Več aplikacij« in »Teams«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2360">**Data_ShareType** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share operation was completed including but not limited to "Copy Link", "More apps", "Teams".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2361">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** – vprogramiran niz, ki označuje, kakšen način skupne rabe je bil aktiven, ko je bilo dokončano dajanje v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »ManageAccess«, »AtMentions« in »Skupna raba«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2361">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share mode was active when the share was completed including but not limited to "ManageAccess", "AtMentions", "Share".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2367">**Data_CoauthorCount** – številska vrednost, ki predstavlja skupno število oseb, ki trenutno urejajo isti dokument kot uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2367">**Data_CoauthorCount** - A numerical value that represents the total number of people who are currently editing the same document as the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2374">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** – število soavtorjev, ki so zapustili dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2374">**Data_CoauthorsLeft** - The number of co-authors that left the document.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuidocstagedocstagecreatenewfromtemplate"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2378">Office.DocsUI.DocStage.DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2378">Office.DocsUI.DocStage.DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2379">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2379">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2380">Dogodek zabeleži, ko je ustvarjena nova datoteka na osnovi izkušnje »Novo iz predloge«, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o ustvarjanju dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2380">The event records when a new file is created from the "New from template" experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on document creation information.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2383">**Data_InSearch** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila datoteka ustvarjena, ko je uporabnik iskal predlogo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2383">**Data_InSearch** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2384">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je zavihek »Osnovno« trenutno na voljo uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2384">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2385">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je izkušnja »Priporočeno« trenutno na voljo uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2385">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the "Recommended" experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2387">**Data_TemplateType** – klasifikacija za boljše razlikovanje vrste predloge, kar med drugim vključuje tudi predloge »V spletu«, predloge »Spletno iskanje« in predloge »Lokalno«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2387">**Data_TemplateType** - A classification to help distinguish the type of template like, but not limited to, "Online" templates, "Online search" templates, "Local" templates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2394">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2394">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2395">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede operacija za odpiranje datoteke, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o operaciji odpiranja datoteke, kot so kategorije mest »ServiceType« in prvi štirje znaki pripone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2395">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories "ServiceType" and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2396">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2396">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2397">**Data_Ext** – pripona datoteke, omejena na največ prve štiri znake pripone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2397">**Data_Ext** - The file extension limited to the first four characters of the extension or less.</span></span>
