#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationsopendocumentmeasurements"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2399">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2399">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenDocumentMeasurements</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2400">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformi iOS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2400">This event is collected for Office applications running under iOS platform.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2401">Dogodek se zabeleži ob odpiranju datoteke, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj glede na informacije o odpiranju datoteke, zlasti informacije o učinkovitosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2401">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information, especially performance information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2402">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2402">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2403">**Data_AppDuration** – Čas, zahtevan za obdelavo aplikacije med odpiranjem datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2403">**Data_AppDuration** - The duration spent in application processing during a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2404">**Data_BootDuration** – Čas, zahtevan za zagon postopka za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2404">**Data_BootDuration** - The duration of boot process of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2405">**Data_ClickOrigin** – Niz, ki označuje, izvirno mesto povezave, ko je uporabnik kliknil povezavo v Outlooku v sistemu iOS za odpiranje datoteke v Officeovi aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2405">**Data_ClickOrigin** - A string indicating which part the link was from when user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open a file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2406">**Data_ClickTime** – čas Unixa, ko je uporabnik kliknil povezavo v Outlooku v sistemu iOS za odpiranje datoteke v Officeovi aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2406">**Data_ClickTime** - The Unix epoch time when the user clicked a link in iOS Outlook to open the file in Office app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2407">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – vrednost niza, ki beleži čas med klici funkcij, v obliki zapisa z ID-jem in trajanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2407">**Data_ClosePreviouslyOpenedMarkers** – A string value logging the time duration between some function calls, in a format with function id and duration.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2408">**Data_DetachedDuration** – Trajanje, zahtevano za odpenjanje postopka dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2408">**Data_DetachedDuration** - The duration of detach process of an event.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2409">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja način za dostop datoteke, npr. samo za branje, branje in pisanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2409">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - An enumeration indicating the access mode of the file, e.g. read only, read write.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2410">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja vrsto asinhronega poteka, ki se uporablja za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2410">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** - An enumeration indicating the type of asynchronous flow used to open the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2411">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja vrsto algoritma za razdruževanje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2411">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - An enumeration indicating the type of chunking algorithm of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2412">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – Oštevilčenje, ki ponazarja stanje zaščite poslovnih podatkov datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2412">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - An enumeration indicating the enterprise data protection state of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2413">**Data_Doc_Ext** – Datotečna pripona datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2413">**Data_Doc_Ext** - File extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2414">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – Ime gostitelja strežnika datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2414">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - The server host name of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2415">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa ime gostitelja strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2415">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server host name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2416">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – GUID, ki enolično prepozna identiteto, uporabljeno za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2416">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the identity used to open a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2417">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje podrobno vrsto scenarija pri odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2417">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - An enumeration indicating the detailed scenario type of a file open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2418">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje V-/I-zastavice postopka za odpiranje datoteke, npr. ali je bila datoteka predpomnjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2418">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - An enumeration indicating the IO flags of a file open operation, e.g. if the file is cached or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2419">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** – Ali je za datoteko omogočeno sodelovanje v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2419">**Data_Doc_IsCloudCollabEnabled** - Whether or not the cloud collaboration is enabled for the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2420">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta s funkcijo postopnega odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2420">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened via incremental open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2421">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – Ali datoteka podpira Officeovo storitev sodelovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2421">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Whether or not a file supports Office Collaboration Service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2422">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta iz predpomnjene kopije brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2422">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Whether or not a file is opened from an offline cached copy.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2423">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** – Ali je bila datoteka vnaprej pridobljena, preden se je zagnal postopek odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2423">**Data_Doc_IsPrefetched** - Whether or not the file was prefetched before open operation happened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2424">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – Ali je na voljo lokalna različica datoteke, ki je sinhronizirana s strežnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2424">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Whether or not a cloud file exists locally and is synchronized with the server.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2425">**Data_Doc_Location** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje mesto datoteke, npr. lokalno ali v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2425">**Data_Doc_Location** - An enumeration indicating where the file is located, e.g. locally or in cloud.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2426">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje razlog datoteke, ki je samo za branje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2426">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - An enumeration indicating the read only reason of a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2427">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa ID vira strežnika datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2427">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server resource id of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2428">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto kanala v realnem času (RTC), ki ga uporablja datoteka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2428">**Data_Doc_RtcType** - An enumeration indicating type of real-time channel (RTC) used by the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2429">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – GUID, ki enolično določa ID dokumenta strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2429">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - A GUID that uniquely identifies server document ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2430">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje protokol strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2430">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - An enumeration indicating the server protocol of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2431">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2431">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - An enumeration indicating the server type of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2432">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje različico strežnika za datoteko v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2432">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - An enumeration indicating the server version of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2433">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – Celo število, ki se poveča za 1 za vsak postopek odpiranja datoteke v seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2433">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - An integer which is incremented by 1 for each file open operation in a session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2434">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – Niz, ki se uporablja za korelacijo odjemalskih in strežniških dnevnikov, po navadi je to neke vrste ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2434">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - A string used to correlate client-side and server-side logs, typically it is a kind of ID.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2435">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – Velikost datoteke v bajtih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2435">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - File size in bytes.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2436">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje vrsto posebnega znaka, ki ga ima URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2436">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - An enumeration indicating which kind of special character the file URL has.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2437">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – GUID, ki enolično določa URL datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2437">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - A GUID that uniquely identifies the file URL.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2438">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** – Ali je bila datoteka odprta postopoma z vnaprej predpomnjenimi podatki WRS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2438">**Data_Doc_UsedWrsDataOnOpen** - Whether or not the file was opened incrementally using pre-cached WRS data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2439">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – Niz, ki označuje, iz katere storitve je datoteka WOPI (Web Application Interface Protocol).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2439">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - A string indicating which service a WOPI (Web Application Open Platform Interface Protocol) file is from.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2440">**Data_HWModel** – vrednost niza, ki beleži model naprave iPad ali iPhone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2440">**Data_HWModel** – A string value logging the model of iPad or iPhone device.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2441">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** – Vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije ter trajanjem, ki vključuje trajanje klicev podfunkcij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2441">**Data_InclusiveMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which includes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2442">**Data_InitializationReason** – Oštevilčenje, ki označuje način odpiranja datoteke, npr. iz katerega elementa uporabniškega vmesnika oz. odpiranje sprožila aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2442">**Data_InitializationReason** - An enumeration indicating how the file is opened, e.g. from which UI element or triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2443">**Data_IsDocumentAlreadyOpen** – ne glede na to, ali je datoteka že odprta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2443">**Data_IsDocumentAlreadyOpen** – Whether or not the file is already open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2444">**Data_IsInterrupted** – ne glede na to, ali je bila odpiranje datoteke prekinjena z odpiranjem programa v ozadje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2444">**Data_IsInterrupted** – Whether or not the file open operation was interrupted by app transitioning to background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2445">**Data_Measurements** – Vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije ter trajanjem, ki ne vključuje trajanje klicev podfunkcij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2445">**Data_Measurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag and duration which excludes the duration of sub-function calls.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2446">**Data_OpenInPlace** – Ali je treba datoteko kopirati v vsebnik z varnostnimi omejitvami v Officeu, preden jo uporabnik lahko odpre.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2446">**Data_OpenInPlace** - Whether or not a file must be copied to the Office's sandboxed container before user can open it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2447">**Data_OpenStartTime** – Čas Unixa, ko je bil zagnan postopek odpiranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2447">**Data_OpenStartTime** - The Unix epoch time when the file open started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2448">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** – Trajanje upodabljanja za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2448">**Data_SilhouetteDuration** - The duration of rendering of the file open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2449">**Data_SourceApplication** – Niz, ki označuje ID snopa izvorne aplikacije, ko je postopek odpiranja datoteke sprožila aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2449">**Data_SourceApplication** - A string indicating the bundle ID of the source application when a file open was triggered by another app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2450">**Data_StopwatchDuration** – Trajanje od začetka do konca dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2450">**Data_StopwatchDuration** - The duration from beginning of the event to the end of the event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2451">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** – Vrednost niza, ki beleži čas, zahtevan za klice funkcij, v obliki zapisa z oznako funkcije, časovnim žigom začetka in trajanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2451">**Data_TimeSplitMeasurements** - A string value logging the time duration spent in some function calls, in a format with function tag, start timestamp and duration.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationsopenfilewithreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2452">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenFileWithReason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2452">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.OpenFileWithReason</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2453">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2453">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2454">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede operacija odpiranja datoteke, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o operaciji odpiranja datoteke, kot so kategorije mest »ServiceType« in mesto v aplikaciji, s katerega je uporabnik zahteval odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2454">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories "ServiceType" and from where within Application the user requested to open a file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2455">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2455">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2456">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** – to je logična vrednost, ki je zabeležena, če na podlagi pregleda poti datoteke menimo, da je morda iz mape, ki jo sinhronizira storitev DropBox.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2456">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** - This is a Boolean value that is logged if by inspecting the path of the file we think it might be from a folder that is sync'd by Drop Box.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2457">**Data_IsSignedIn** – označuje, ali je uporabnik pri shranjevanju datoteke vpisan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2457">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2458">**Data_OpenReason** – razlog za odpiranje je številska vrednost, ki označuje mesto v aplikaciji, s katerega je uporabnik odprl datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2458">**Data_OpenReason** - The open reason is a numerical value that indicates from where within the application a user opened a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2459">**Data_ServiceType** – abstraktna številska kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2459">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract numerical categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuifileoperationssavetourl"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2460">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.SaveToURL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2460">Office.DocsUI.FileOperations.SaveToURL</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2461">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2461">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2462">Dogodek zabeleži, ko se izvede operacija »Shrani kot«, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o operaciji za datoteko, kot so kategorije mest in prvi štirje znaki pripone.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2462">The event records when a "save as" operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2463">Operacija »Shrani kot« se izvede vsakič, ko uporabnik ustvari novo datoteko in jo shrani prvič ali ko shrani kopijo obstoječe datoteke na novo mesto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2463">A "save as" operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2464">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2464">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2465">**Data_FileExtension** – prvi štirje znaki pripone nove datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2465">**Data_FileExtension** - The first four characters of the new file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2466">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** – označuje, ali je operacija shranjevanja izvedena za novo datoteko ali kopijo obstoječe datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2466">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** - Indicates if the save operation is for a new file or a copy of an existing file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2467">**Data_IsSignedIn** – označuje, ali je uporabnik pri shranjevanju datoteke vpisan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2467">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2468">**Data_SaveErrorCode** – številska vrednost, ki je nastavljena, če pride do napake, in pomaga prepoznati vrsto napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2468">**Data_SaveErrorCode** - A numerical value that is set if there is an error to help identify the kind of error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2469">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** – navaja domeno za SaveErrorCode, kot to določa Apple SaveErrorDomains »so poljubni nizi, ki se uporabljajo za razlikovanje skupin kod«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2469">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** - Specifies the domain of the SaveErrorCode as defined by Apple SaveErrorDomains "are arbitrary strings used to differentiate groups of codes".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2470">**Data_SaveLocation** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2470">**Data_SaveLocation** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2471">**Data_SaveOperationType** – številska vrednost, ki jo določa skupina vrednosti NSSaveOperationType družbe Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2471">**Data_SaveOperationType** - A numerical value defined by Apple's NSSaveOperationType group of values.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicloudupsellshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2472">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2472">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellShown</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2473">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2473">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2474">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik izvede postopek za shranjevanje dokumentov v oblak v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2474">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2475">Ti podatki so uporabljeni za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj, povezanih s premikanjem dokumentov na mesta v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2475">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2476">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2476">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2477">**Data_FileStyle** – številska vrednost, ki označuje, v kakšnem primeru je bila prikazana izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov, npr. na preklopnem stikalu za samodejno shranjevanje ali gumbu »Skupna raba«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2477">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like from an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2478">**Data_FileType** – prvi štirje znaki pripone trenutne datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2478">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2479">**Data_InDocStage** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov prikazana v galeriji dokumentov ali v oknu dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2479">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2480">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je odprt tudi trenutni dokument, za katerega je prikazana izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2480">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2481">**Data_IsDraft** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila trenutna datoteka že kdaj shranjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2481">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2482">**Data_IsSheetModal** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov predstavljena modalno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2482">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicloudupsellupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2483">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2483">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CloudUpsellUpload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2484">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2484">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2485">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik prenese novo ali lokalno datoteko v oblak in rezultat te operacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2485">This event records when a user chooses to upload a new or local file to the cloud and the result of that operation.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2486">Ti podatki so uporabljeni za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj, povezanih s premikanjem dokumentov na mesta v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2486">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2487">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2487">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2488">**Data_FileStyle** – številska vrednost, ki označuje, v kakšnem primeru je bila prikazana izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov, npr. na preklopnem stikalu za samodejno shranjevanje ali gumbu »Skupna raba«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2488">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2489">**Data_FileType** – prvi štirje znaki pripone trenutne datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2489">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file's extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2490">**Data_InDocStage** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov prikazana v galeriji dokumentov ali v oknu dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2490">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2491">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali gre pri izbranem mestu za prenos dokumenta za privzeto mesto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2491">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** - A Boolean value that indicates if the selected location to upload the document to is the default location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2492">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je odprt tudi trenutni dokument, za katerega je prikazana izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2492">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2493">**Data_IsDraft** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila trenutna datoteka že kdaj shranjena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2493">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2494">**Data_IsSheetModal** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila izkušnja v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov predstavljena modalno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2494">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2495">**Data_LocationServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2495">**Data_LocationServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2496">**Data_UploadAction** – vprogramiran niz, ki označuje, ali je pri prenosu v strežnik šlo za operacijo premikanja ali kopiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2496">**Data_UploadAction** - A hard coded string that indicates whether the upload was a move or a copy operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2497">**Data_UploadResult** – vprogramiran niz, ki označuje rezultat poskusa prenosa v strežnik, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »Success«, »UserCancelledUpload« in »PreAuthFailed«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2497">**Data_UploadResult** - A hard coded string that indicates the result of the attempt to upload including but not limited to ''Success", "UserCancelledUpload", and "PreAuthFailed".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguicopylinkoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2498">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CopyLinkOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2498">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.CopyLinkOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2499">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2499">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2500">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik da dokument v skupno rabo v oblak z ustvarjanjem povezave do dokumenta v oblaku, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2500">This event records when a user chooses to share a document by generating a link to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2501">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2501">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2502">**Data_ ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2502">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2503">**Data_LinkType** – vprogramiran niz, ki opisuje vrsto izvedene operacije povabila, npr. »ViewOnly« in »ViewAndEdit«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2503">**Data_LinkType** - A hard coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like "ViewOnly" and "ViewAndEdit".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2504">**Data_ShareScenario** – vprogramiran niz z opisom mesta v uporabniškem vmesniku aplikacije, s katerega je bila datoteka dana v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »FileMenu«, »OpenTabShareActionMenu« in »RecentTabShareActionMenu«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2504">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguidocsuionedriveshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2505">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.DocsUIOneDriveShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2505">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.DocsUIOneDriveShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2506">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2506">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2507">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik da dokument v oblaku v skupno rabo z uporabo izkušnje dajanja v skupno rabo OneDrive, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2507">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2508">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2508">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2509">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** – številska vrednost, ki v primeru pojava napake pri izkušnji skupne rabe omogoča lažje prepoznavanje vzroka napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2509">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** - If the sharing experience experiences an error this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2510">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** – logična vrednost, ki v primeru vrednosti »true« označuje, da je bila operacija poenostavljenega dajanja v skupno rabo uspešno dokončana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2510">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** - A Boolean value that when true indicates that a lightweight sharing operation successfully completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2511">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** – številska vrednost, ki se v primeru uspešno dokončane operacije dajanja v skupno rabo uporablja za ugotavljanje vrste dokončane operacije dajanja v skupno rabo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2511">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** - When a share operation successfully completes this is a numerical value used to determine what kind of sharing operation was completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2512">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** – številska vrednost, ki omogoča lažje prepoznavanje vzroka napake, če se uporabniški vmesnik ne naloži.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2512">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** - If the user interface fails to load this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2513">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** – številska vrednost, ki zabeleži čas, ki je bil potreben za nalaganje spletnega uporabniškega vmesnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2513">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** - A numerical value that records the amount of time it took for the web user interface to load.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguiinvitepeople"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2514">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.InvitePeople</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2514">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.InvitePeople</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2515">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2515">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2516">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik povabi osebe v dokument v oblaku, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2516">This event records when a user chooses to invite people to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2517">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2517">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2518">**Data_ ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2518">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2519">**Data_InviteeCount** – skupno število stikov, povabljenih v dokument v okviru enega dejanja povabila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2519">**Data_InviteeCount** - The total number of contacts invited to a document in one invite action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2520">**Data_LinkType** – vprogramiran niz, ki opisuje vrsto izvedene operacije povabila, npr. »ViewOnly« in »ViewAndEdit«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2520">**Data_LinkType** - A hard-coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like "ViewOnly" and "ViewAndEdit".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2521">**Data_MessageLength** – številsko štetje skupnega števila znakov, poslanih v sporočilu s povabilom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2521">**Data_MessageLength** - A numerical count of the total number of characters sent in the invite message.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2522">**Data_ShareScenario** – vprogramiran niz z opisom mesta v uporabniškem vmesniku aplikacije, s katerega je bila datoteka dana v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »FileMenu«, »OpenTabShareActionMenu« in »RecentTabShareActionMenu«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2522">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguisendacopyoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2523">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.SendACopyOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2523">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.SendACopyOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2524">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2524">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2525">Dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik pošlje kopijo dokumenta, uporablja pa se za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi skupne rabe dokumentov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2525">The event records when a user chooses to send a copy of a document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2526">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2526">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2527">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je zavihek »Osnovno« trenutno na voljo uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2527">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2528">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je izkušnja »Priporočeno« trenutno na voljo uporabniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2528">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the "Recommended" experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2529">**Data_OperationType** – številska vrednost, ki označuje, katera vrsta operacije pošiljanja kopije se izvaja, npr. pošiljanje kopije v e-poštnem sporočilu ali pošiljanje kopije z nadzorom skupne rabe v storitvi družbe Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2529">**Data_OperationType** - A numerical value to indicate what kind of send a copy operation is taking place like sending a copy in an email or sending a copy through Apple's share control.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2530">**Data_ ServiceType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2530">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2531">**Data_ShareFileType** – vprogramiran niz z opisom vrste predmeta, ki se daje v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »Dokument«, »PDF« in »Slika«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2531">**Data_ShareFileType** - A hard coded string description of what type of object is being shared including but not limited to, "Document", "PDF", "Picture".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2532">**Data_ShareScenario** – vprogramiran niz z opisom mesta v uporabniškem vmesniku aplikacije, s katerega je bila datoteka dana v skupno rabo, kar med drugim vključuje tudi »FileMenu«, »OpenTabShareActionMenu« in »RecentTabShareActionMenu«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2532">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application's user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, "FileMenu", "OpenTabShareActionMenu", "RecentTabShareActionMenu".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2533">**Data_SharingService** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila datoteka ustvarjena, ko je uporabnik iskal predlogo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2533">**Data_SharingService** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

#### <a name="officedocsuisharinguiupsellshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2534">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.UpsellShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2534">Office.DocsUI.SharingUI.UpsellShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2535">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2535">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2536">Ta dogodek zabeleži, ko uporabnik pri poskusu dajanja dokumenta v skupno rabo izvede postopek za shranjevanje dokumentov v oblak v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2536">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow when trying to share a document.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2537">Te podatke uporabljamo za boljše razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj, povezanih s premikanjem dokumentov na mesta v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2537">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2538">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2538">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2539">**Data_FileOperationResult** – številska vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila operacija uspešna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2539">**Data_FileOperationResult** - A numerical value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2540">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali uporabnik izvede postopek za shranjevanje dokumentov v oblak v okviru prodaje dodatnih izdelkov iz izkušnje DocStage ali iz odprtega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2540">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** - A Boolean to indicate if a user is going through the upsell to cloud flow from the DocStage experience or from an open document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2541">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali uporabnik obdrži lokalno kopijo dokumenta, ki je predmet prenosa na mesto v oblaku, ali obstoječi dokument premakne na mesto v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2541">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** - A Boolean to indicate if the use chose to keep a local copy of the document being uploaded to a cloud location or move the existing document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2542">**Data_NewFileType** – abstraktna kategorizacija novega mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2542">**Data_NewFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of the new location of the file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2543">**Data_OriginalFileType** – abstraktna kategorizacija mesta datoteke, na primer »SharePoint«, »OneDrive«, »Lokalno«, »WOPI« itn., ne pa dejansko mesto datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2543">**Data_OriginalFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like "SharePoint", "OneDrive", "Local", "WOPI", etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2544">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali uporabnik trenutni dokument prenese na mesto v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2544">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** - A Boolean to indicate if the user chose to upload the current document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2545">**Data_UploadError** – številska vrednost, ki označuje vrsto napake, do katere pride, če operacija prenosa datoteke v strežnik ne uspe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2545">**Data_UploadError** - A numerical value that indicates the kind of error that occurred if an upload operation fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2546">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** – logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bil pogled prikazan v meniju »Skupna raba«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2546">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** - A Boolean value to indicate if the view was shown from the share menu.</span></span>

#### <a name="officefeedbacksurveyuiwin32toast"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2699">Office.Feedback.Survey.UI.Win32.Toast</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2699">Office.Feedback.Survey.UI.Win32.Toast</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2700">Sledi, ko je prikazan pozivnik ankete.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2700">Tracks when survey prompt is shown.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2701">Uporablja se za oceno stanja popravka postopka ankete ter za zagotavljanje, da se signal uporablja za analizo težav strank in za zdravje deluje pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2701">Used to assess the health of the survey prompt process as well as to ensure the signal used to analyze customer issues and health is working properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2702">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2702">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2703">**ExpirationTimeUTC** – datum/čas, ko bo Anketa potekla</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2703">**ExpirationTimeUTC** – date/time the survey will expire</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2704">**SurveyName** – prikazano je ime ankete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2704">**SurveyName** – name of survey shown</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2705">**SurveyId** – edinstven primerek kampanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2705">**SurveyId** – Unique instance of a campaign</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2706">**UniqueId** – ID za identifikacijo posameznega dela telemetrijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2706">**UniqueId** – Id to identify the individual piece of telemetry</span></span>

#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsiloadfilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2707">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiLoadFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2707">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiLoadFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2708">S tem dogodkom lahko prepoznamo, ali je bila datoteka uspešno odprta v plasti FIO.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2708">Allows us to know if a file successfully opened from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2709">Uporabljamo ga za zagotavljanje ustreznosti delovanja funkcij in nadzor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2709">Used for feature health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2710">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2710">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2711">**Activity.Group** – Oznaka, ki omogoča združevanje nabora dogodkov nadzora za upravljanje uspešnega delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2711">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2712">**Activity.IsHVA** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da je dogodek ključen za zagotavljanje uspešnega delovanja za uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2712">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2713">**Data.AsyncOpen** – Zastavica, ki označuje odpiranje vsebine, prejete potem, ko je bilo glavno telo dokumenta že odprto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2713">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate the open had content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2714">**Data.CacheFileId** – Povezava do telemetrije predpomnilnika Officeovih dokumentov za omogočanje analize posledic težav s predpomnilnikom na uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2714">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2715">**Data. CFREnabled** – označuje, da je za sejo omogočena možnost CacheFileRuntime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2715">**Data.CFREnabled** - Indicates that CacheFileRuntime is enabled for the session.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2716">**Data. CFRFailure** – označuje, da je CacheFileRuntime naletel na napako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2716">**Data.CFRFailure** - Indicated that CacheFileRuntime ran into error.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2717">**Data.CoauthStatus** – Poroča o stanju sodelovanja v dokumentu ob odpiranju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2717">**Data.CoauthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2718">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload** – Število vrnitev v strežnik, ki se uporablja za odpravljanje težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja in omrežjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2718">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2719">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload** – Število vrnitev v strežnik, ki se uporablja za odpravljanje težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja in omrežjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2719">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2720">**Data.DialogId** – To polje je nastavljeno, če je bilo pogovorno okno za UI prikazano med odpiranjem, in označuje, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilno sporočilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2720">**Data.DialogId -** Set if a UI dialog was displayed during Open, indicating a that a warning message was displayed to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2721">**Data.DidFallbackToDAV** – To polje je nastavljeno, če je bil dokument odprt s starejšim protokolom za prenos datotek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2721">**Data.DidFallbackToDAV -** Set if the document was opened using an older file transfer protocol</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2722">**Data.Doc.AccessMode** – Dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2722">**Data.Doc.AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2723">**Data.Doc.AssistedReadingReasons** – To polje je nastavljeno, če je za dokument izbrana elektronska zaščita podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2723">**Data.Doc.AssistedReadingReasons -** Set if the document has electronic data protection in place</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2724">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind –** Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2724">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2725">**Data.Doc.ChunkingType** – Enote, uporabljene za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2725">**Data.Doc.ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2726">**Data.Doc.EdpState** – Nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2726">**Data.Doc.EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2727">**Data.Doc.Ext** – Pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2727">**Data.Doc.Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2728">**Data.Doc.Extension** – Zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2728">**Data.Doc.Extension -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2729">**Data.Doc.FileFormat** – Različica protokola za obliko zapisa dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2729">**Data.Doc.FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2730">**Data.Doc.Fqdn** – Ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2730">**Data.Doc.Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2731">**Data.Doc.FqdnHash** – Enostranska zgoščena vrednost imena domene, ki omogoča identifikacijo stranke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2731">**Data.Doc.FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2732">**Data.Doc.IdentityTelemetryId** – Enostranska zgoščena vrednost identitete uporabnika, uporabljena za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2732">**Data.Doc.IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2733">**Data.Doc.IdentityUniqueId** – Zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2733">**Data.Doc.IdentityUniqueId -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2734">**Data.Doc.InitializationScenario** – Zabeleži način odpiranja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2734">**Data.Doc.InitializationScenario -** Records how the document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2735">**Data.Doc.IOFlags** – Poroča o predpomnjenih zastavicah, uporabljenih za nastavitev možnosti zahtev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2735">**Data.Doc.IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set request options</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2737">**Data.Doc.IsCloudCollabEnabled** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da storitev podpira sodelovanje v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2737">**Data.Doc.IsCloudCollabEnabled -** Flag indicating that the service supports Cloud Collaboration</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2738">**Data.Doc.IsIncrementalOpen** – Zastavica, ki označuje postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2738">**Data.Doc.IsIncrementalOpen -** Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2741">**Data.Doc.IsSyncBacked** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da v računalniku obstaja samodejno sinhronizirana kopija dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2741">**Data.Doc.IsSyncBacked -** Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2742">**Data.Doc.Location** – Označuje, v kateri storitvi je na voljo dokument (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2742">**Data.Doc.Location -** Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2745">**Data.Doc.PasswordFlags** – Označuje nastavljeno zastavico za branje ali branje/pisanje gesla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2745">**Data.Doc.PasswordFlags -** Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2746">**Data.Doc.ReadOnlyReasons** – Razlogi, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu »Samo za branje«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2746">**Data.Doc.ReadOnlyReasons -** Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2752">**Data.Doc.SessionId** – Prepozna določeno sejo za urejanje dokumenta v celotni seji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2752">**Data.Doc.SessionId -** Identifies a specific document edit session within the full session</span></span>

SizeInBytes«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2763">**Data.DocumentSizeInBytes -** Obsolete/redundant supplanted by Data.Doc. SizeInBytes</span></span>

#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsisavefilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2832">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2832">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2833">S tem dogodkom lahko prepoznamo, ali je bila datoteka uspešno shranjena v plasti FIO.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2833">Allows us to know if a file was successfully saved from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2834">Uporabljamo ga za zagotavljanje ustreznosti delovanja funkcij in nadzor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2834">Used for Feature Health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2835">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2835">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2836">**Activity.Group** – Oznaka, ki omogoča združevanje nabora dogodkov nadzora za upravljanje uspešnega delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2836">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2837">**Activity.IsHVA** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da je dogodek ključen za zagotavljanje uspešnega delovanja za uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2837">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2838">**Data.AsyncOpen** – Zastavica, ki označuje, da je bil odprt dokument z vsebino, prejeto potem, ko je bilo glavno telo dokumenta že odprto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2838">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate that the document was opened with content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2839">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered** – Diagnostika sledenja spremembam, vključno s podatki, da je bila zahtevana osnovna različica dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2839">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered -** Change tracking diagnostic indicating that the base version of the document was requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2840">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons** – Kode vzroka za blokirano stanje nalaganja (npr. samodejno shranjevanje je vklopljeno, dokument je v stanju prehoda).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2840">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons -** Reason codes for blocked upload state (e.g. Autosave is turned off, the document is transitioning)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2841">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting** – Nalaganje je blokirano, saj bi bil vnovičen poskus neuspešen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2841">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting -** Upload is blocked as it would fail if retried</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2842">**Data.CacheFileId** – Povezava do telemetrije predpomnilnika Officeovih dokumentov za omogočanje analize posledic težav s predpomnilnikom na uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2842">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2843">**Data.ChartType** – Zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2843">**Data.ChartType -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2844">**Data.CoauthStatus** – Poroča o stanju sodelovanja v dokumentu ob shranjevanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2844">**Data.CoAuthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2845">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext** – Poroča o kontekstu (spajanje/postopno odpiranje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2845">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext -** reports context (Merge/Incremental Open)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2846">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload** – Število vrnitev v strežnik, ki se uporablja za odpravljanje težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja in omrežjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2846">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2847">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload** – Število vrnitev v strežnik, ki se uporablja za odpravljanje težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja in omrežjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2847">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsUpload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

#### <a name="officefindtimeappfailedtostart"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2979">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2979">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2980">Podatki so zbrani, če aplikacije ni mogoče zagnati zaradi nepričakovane napake med zagonom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2980">Collected when app fails to start due to an unexpected error during startup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2981">S tem dogodkom spremljamo izjeme in zrušitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2981">Used to track exceptions & crashes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2982">Omogoča lažje spremljanje ustreznosti stanja aplikacije in odpravljanje težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2982">Helps monitor & debug app health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2983">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2983">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2984">**DateTime** – Časovni žig o času, ko je bil dogodek zabeležen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2984">**DateTime** - Timestamp of when the event is logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2985">**EventName** – Ime zabeleženega dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2985">**EventName** - The name of the event being logged</span></span>

#### <a name="officefirstrunappleactivationresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2986">Office.FirstRun.Apple.ActivationResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2986">Office.FirstRun.Apple.ActivationResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2987">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2987">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2988">Dogodek uporabljamo za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja postopka aktiviranja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2988">The event is used to monitor the health of our application activation flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2989">Te podatke zbiramo, da bi ugotovili rezultat aktiviranja naročnine na Office 365 skupaj s postopkom, ki se uporablja za aktiviranje (uporabniška izkušnja prvega zagona, postopek znotraj aplikacije, nakup itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2989">We collect data to figure out the outcome of the Office 365 subscription activation along with the flow used to activate (First Run Experience, In-App-Flow, Purchase, etc.).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2990">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2990">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2991">**Data_ActivationStatusCollectionTime** – časovni žig</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2991">**Data_ActivationStatusCollectionTime** – A timestamp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2992">**Data_ActivationStatusError** – koda napake pri aktivaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2992">**Data_ActivationStatusError** – An activation error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2993">**Data_ActivationStatusFlowType** – številska vrednost, ki označuje vrsto postopka aktiviranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2993">**Data_ActivationStatusFlowType** – A numeric value indicating the type of activation flow</span></span>

#### <a name="officefirstrunappleactivationstatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2994">Office.FirstRun.Apple.ActivationStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2994">Office.FirstRun.Apple.ActivationStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2995">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2995">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2996">Dogodek uporabljamo za ugotavljanje rezultata aktiviranja naročnine na Office 365 skupaj s postopkom, ki se uporablja za aktiviranje (FRE, postopek znotraj aplikacije, nakup itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2996">The event is used to figure out the outcome of the Office 365 subscription activation along with the flow used to activate (FRE, InApp, Purchase, etc.).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-2997">Zbiramo podatke, ki vsebujejo vrsto aktiviranja, vrsto postopka (FRE/DocStage/nakup) in ID storitve licenciranja za Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-2997">We collect data containing the Activation type, flow type (FRE/DocStage/Purchase) and Office Licensing Service ID.</span></span>
