<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3380">Ta dogodek je izbran za aplikacijo Office; posname izvajanje postopka odpiranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3380">This event is collected for the Office app for iOS, it records when a file open operation takes place.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3381">Zbrali smo te podatke, da bi zagotovili dobro učinkovitost delovanja za vse datoteke, ki se odpre v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3381">We collect this data to ensure good performance for all file opens on the app.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3382">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3382">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3383">**Data_Doc_ActivationFQDN** – ime domene aplikacije ponudnika za scenarij aktivacije datoteke (prijavljene so le informacije o aplikaciji 1. stranka).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3383">**Data_Doc_ActivationFQDN** - Domain name of the Provider app for a file activation scenario (only 1st party app info is being logged).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3384">**Data_Doc_CreateTelemetryReason** – Telemetry reason for PDF creation.(eg: Create from scan, using “picture to pdf” action, using “document to pdf” action, etc.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3384">**Data_Doc_CreateTelemetryReason** – Telemetry reason for PDF creation.(eg: Create from scan, using “picture to pdf” action, using “document to pdf” action, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3385">**Data_Doc_DownloadDurationms** čas za prenos datoteke v oblaku PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3385">**Data_Doc_DownloadDurationms** - Time to download a PDF cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3386">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** – časovni žig za konec prenosa datoteke v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3386">**Data_Doc_DownloadEndTime** - Timestamp for end of download of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3387">**Data_Doc_DownloadStartTime** – časovni žig za začetek prenosa datoteke v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3387">**Data_Doc_DownloadStartTime** – Timestamp for start of download of a cloud file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3388">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** – Enolični ID seje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3388">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** - Unique Id for a Document Session.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3389">**Data_Doc_Location** mestu, kjer se datoteka nahaja (lokalni, ODSP, iCloud, aplikacije tretjih oseb, wopi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3389">**Data_Doc_Location** - Location where the file sits (Local, ODSP, iCloud, third party files app, wopi</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3390">**Data_Doc_OpenCompletionTime** – časovni žig za konec odprtega delovanja datoteke PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3390">**Data_Doc_OpenCompletionTime** - Timestamp for end of open operation of a PDF file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3391">**Data_Doc_OpenDurationms** čas za odpiranje datoteke PDF v milisekundah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3391">**Data_Doc_OpenDurationms** - Time to open a PDF file in milliseconds.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3392">**Data_Doc_OpenStartTime** – časovni žig za začetek odprtega delovanja datoteke PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3392">**Data_Doc_OpenStartTime** - Timestamp for start of open operation of a PDF file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3393">**Data_Doc_TelemetryReason** – telemetrijo vzroka za odprti dogodek (npr.: odpiranje iz MRU ali brskanje, aktivacija datoteke, aktivacija protokolov itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3393">**Data_Doc_TelemetryReason** - Telemetry reason for the open event (eg: open from MRU or browse, File Activation, Protocol Activation, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3394">**Doc_RenderDurationms** časa, da postane datoteka PDF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3394">**Doc_RenderDurationms** - Time to render a pdf file</span></span>


#### <a name="officeofficemobilepdfviewerpdffileoperations"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3395">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOperations</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3395">Office.OfficeMobile.PdfViewer.PdfFileOperations</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3396">Dogodek je zbran za Officeovo aplikacijo za Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3396">The event is collected for the Office app for Android.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3397">Zabeleži, ko pride do dogodka odpiranja, zapiranja ali shranjevanja dokumenta .pdf, uporablja pa za razumevanje in določanje prednosti uporabniških izkušenj na podlagi informacij o delu z datotekami .pdf.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3397">It records when a .pdf open, close, or save operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize the user experience based on .pdf file operation information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3398">S tem dogodkom poskrbimo, da postopki odpiranja, zapiranja in shranjevanja dokumentov .pdf delujejo v skladu s pričakovanji, hkrati pa lahko izboljšujemo učinkovitost dela z datotekami .pdf.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3398">The event enables us to keep the .pdf open, close and save operations performing as expected, and to improve .pdf file operation performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3399">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3399">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3400">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** – enolični ID za sejo dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3400">**Data_Doc_FileOpSessionID** - Unique ID for a Document Session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3401">**Data_ErrorCode** – napaka, do katere pride zaradi neuspelih postopkov odpiranja datotek/neuspelih prenosov/preklica prenosov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3401">**Data_ErrorCode** - error in case of file open failures/download failures / download canceled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3402">**Data_ErrorMessage** – relevantna koda sporočilo-napaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3402">**Data_ErrorMessage** - relevant message-to-error code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3403">**Data_FailureReason** – če pride do napake pri odpiranju, to oštevilčenje določa vzrok za napako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3403">**Data_FailureReason** - In case of open failure, these enums define the reason for failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3404">**Data_FileGUID** – globalni identifikator za datoteko, ki je ustvarjena slučajno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3404">**Data_FileGUID** – Global identifier for the file which is random generated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3405">**Data_FileLocation** – lokacija datoteke, na primer: lokalno, ODSP, iCloud, itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3405">**Data_FileLocation** - Location where the file sits, ex: Local, ODSP, iCloud, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3406">**Data_FileOpenEntryPoint** – vhodna točka za odpiranje datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3406">**Data_FileOpenEntryPoint** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3407">**Data_FileSize** – velikost datoteke, v kateri se izvaja postopek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3407">**Data_FileSize** - Size of the file on which the operation is happening</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3408">**Data_NetworkRequestErrorResponse** – odziv z napako omrežja, ki ustreza kodi napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3408">**Data_NetworkRequestErrorResponse** – Network Error response corresponding to error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3409">**Data_NetworkRequestStage** – prikaz napake v primeru prenosa datotek pdf v oblak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3409">**Data_NetworkRequestStage** – Error stage in case of cloud pdf file download.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3410">**Data_OpenMode** – v katerem načinu je bil odprt dokument PDF, na primer: 0: način pogleda, 2: način podpisa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3410">**Data_OpenMode** - In which mode the PDF was opened, ex: 0: View mode, 2: Sign mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3411">**Data_PageCount** – število strani v datoteki PDF</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3411">**Data_PageCount** - Count of page in the PDF File.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3412">**Data_PasswordProtected** – označevalnik, ki označuje, ali je datoteka zaščitena z geslom ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3412">**Data_PasswordProtected** - Marker that tell whether the file is password protected or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3413">**Data_ProviderApp** – trenuten ponudnik aplikacije le v primeru aktivacije datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3413">**Data_ProviderApp** - currently providing provider app in case of file activation only</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3414">**Data_ReadOnly** – označevalnik, ki označuje, ali je datoteka samo za branje ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3414">**Data_ReadOnly** - Marker that tell whether the file is read-only or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3415">**Data_Result** – stanje postopka, ki se izvaja, na primer: true:success, false:failure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3415">**Data_Result** - The status of the operation being performed, ex: true:success, false:failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3416">**Data_Type** – vrsta postopka, uporabljenega za datoteko (odpri, zapri ali shrani)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3416">**Data_Type** - Type of file operation (open, close or save)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidstickynotesnotecreated"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3454">Office.OneNote.Android.StickyNotes.NoteCreated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3454">Office.OneNote.Android.StickyNotes.NoteCreated</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3455">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja za nadzor zmogljivosti, kjer uporabniki Samolepljivih listkov lahko ustvarjajo zapiske v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3455">Critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>   <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3456">Telemetrija se uporablja za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3456">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3457">Če uporabniki ne morejo ustvariti zapiska, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3457">If users can’t create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3458">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3458">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3459">**IsExportable** – zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil dogodek rezultat dejanja uporabnika ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3459">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3460">Mora biti nastavljen na vrednost true, ker je NoteCreated dejanje, ki ga je sprožil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3460">Should be set to True as NoteCreated is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3461">**NoteLocalId** – razlikovalni enolični identifikator, ki je dodeljen zapisku v času, ko uporabnik ustvari zapisek v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3461">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time of a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3462">**StickyNotes – SDKVersion** – številka različice, ki označuje različico Lepljivih zapiskov, ki jo uporablja uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3462">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3463">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerih različicah izdelka je prišlo do težave ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3463">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenoteandroidstickynotesnoteviewed"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3464">Office.OneNote.Android.StickyNotes.NoteViewed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3464">Office.OneNote.Android.StickyNotes.NoteViewed</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3465">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja za nadzor zmogljivosti, kjer si uporabniki Samolepljivih listkov lahko ogledujejo zapiske v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3465">Critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to view notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3466">Telemetrija se uporablja za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3466">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3467">Če si uporabniki ne morejo ogledati svojih zapiskov, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3467">If users can’t view their notes, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3468">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3468">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3469">**HasImages** – zastavica, ki označuje, so v ogledanem zapisku shranjene slike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3469">**HasImages** - A flag indicating whether the note viewed has images stored in it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3470">**IsExportable** – zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil dogodek rezultat dejanja uporabnika ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3470">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3471">Mora biti nastavljen na vrednost true, ker je NoteViewed dejanje, ki ga je sprožil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3471">Should be set to True as NoteViewed is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3472">**NoteLocalId** – razpoznavni enolični identifikator, ki je dodeljen zapisku v času, ko uporabnik ustvari zapisek v programu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3472">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3473">**StickyNotes – SDKVersion** – številka različice, ki označuje različico Lepljivih zapiskov, ki jo uporablja uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3473">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3474">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerih različicah izdelka je prišlo do težave ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3474">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3481">**CurrentPage** – Identifikator trenutno aktivne strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3481">**CurrentPage** - Identifier of the current active page</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3482">**CurrentSection** – Identifikator trenutno aktivnega odseka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3482">**CurrentSection** - Identifier of the current active section.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3483">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** – Privzeti dejavnik povečave platna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3483">**DefaultCanvasZoomFactor** - Default Zoom factor of the canvas.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3484">**InkStrokeCount** – Skupno število potez rokopisa od zadnjega dnevnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3484">**InkStrokeCount** - Total count of ink strokes since the last log.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3488">**InkStrokeWithTilt** – Število potez rokopisa z nagibom od zadnjega dnevnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3488">**InkStrokeWithTilt** - Count of ink strokes with tilt since the last log.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotenotebookmanagementopennotebook"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3534">Office.OneNote.NotebookManagement.OpenNotebook</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3534">Office.OneNote.NotebookManagement.OpenNotebook</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3535">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja za spremljanje možnosti uporabnikov OneNota za odpiranje zvezkov v OneNotu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3535">Critical signal used to monitor the ability of OneNote users to open notebooks in OneNote.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3536">Telemetrija, uporabljena za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in ustreznosti stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3536">Telemetry used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3537">Če uporabniki ne morejo odpreti zvezkov, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3537">If users can't open notebooks this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3538">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3538">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3539">**NotebookID** – enolični identifikator zvezka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3539">**NotebookID** - A unique identifier of a notebook.</span></span>

    
#### <a name="officeonenotesearchsearch"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3540">Office.OneNote.Search.Search</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3540">Office.OneNote.Search.Search</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3541">ID kritičnega signala, uporabljan za spremljanje možnosti OneNotovih uporabnikov za iskanje informacij na več tisoč straneh in v več tisoč zvezkih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3541">Critical signal ID used to monitor the ability of OneNote users to find information across thousands of pages and notebooks.</span></span>   <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3542">Telemetrija, uporabljena za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in ustreznosti stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3542">Telemetry used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3543">Če uporabniki ne morejo najti informacij v zvezkih, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3543">If users can't find information across notebooks this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3544">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3544">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3545">**PageSearchResultCount** – označuje število rezultatov iskanja, ki so najdeni v načinu iskanja strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3545">**PageSearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3546">**PageTimeToFirstResultInMs** – označuje količino časa, ki jo OneNote porabi za iskanje prvega ujemanja v načinu iskanja strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3546">**PageTimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match in a page search mode.</span></span>
    
-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3547">**PageTimeToLastResultInMs** – označuje količino časa, ki jo OneNote porabi za iskanje zadnjega ujemanja v načinu iskanja strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3547">**PageTimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3548">**PageTimeToMedianResultInMs** – označuje mediano časa, ki ga OneNote porabi za iskanje vseh ujemanj v načinu iskanja strani.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3548">**PageTimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches in a page search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3549">**SearchResultCount** – označuje število najdenih rezultatov iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3549">**SearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3550">**TagSearchResultCount** – označuje število rezultatov iskanja, najdenih v načinu iskanja oznak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3550">**TagSearchResultCount** - Indicates the number of search's results found in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3551">**TagTimeToFirstResultInMs** – označuje količino časa, ki jo OneNote porabi za iskanje prvega ujemanja v načinu iskanja oznak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3551">**TagTimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3552">**TagTimeToLastResultInMs** – označuje količino časa, ki jo OneNote porabi za iskanje zadnjega ujemanja v načinu iskanja oznak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3552">**TagTimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3553">**TagTimeToMedianResultInMs** – označuje mediano časa, ki ga OneNote porabi za iskanje vseh ujemanj v načinu iskanja oznak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3553">**TagTimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches in a tag search mode.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3554">**TimeToFirstResultInMs** – označuje količino časa, ki jo OneNote porabi za iskanje prvega ujemanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3554">**TimeToFirstResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the first match.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3555">**TimeToLastResultInMs** – označuje količino časa, ki jo OneNote porabi za iskanje zadnjega ujemanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3555">**TimeToLastResultInMs** - Indicates the amount of time OneNote takes to find the last match.</span></span>

-  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3556">**TimeToMedianResultInMs** – označuje mediano časa, ki ga OneNote porabi za iskanje vseh ujemanj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3556">**TimeToMedianResultInMs** - Indicates the median of time OneNote takes to find all matches.</span></span>

### <a name="officeonenotesigscriticalerrorencountered"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3557">Office.OneNote.SIGS.CriticalErrorEncountered</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3557">Office.OneNote.SIGS.CriticalErrorEncountered</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3558">Ta dogodek zajame kritični signal, ki se uporablja za nadzor ustreznosti stanja storitve Signal Ingestion Service (SIGS), tako, da izvede prijavo vsakič, ko je zaznana kritična napaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3558">This event captures a critical signal that is used to monitor the health of Signal Ingestion Service (SIGS), by logging whenever a critical error is encountered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3559">Kritične napake lahko blokirajo celotno storitev SIGS, zato s tem dogodkom lažje preprečimo morebitne takšne napake takoj, ko jih uporabniki zaznajo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3559">Critical errors can block the whole of SIGS, and this will help us catch any such issues as soon as they are encountered by users.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3560">V nasprotnem primeru bi nam uporabniki morali poročati o težavah, ki jih zaznajo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3560">Without this we will be dependent on users to report the problems they are facing.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3561">Če ne bi bilo na voljo takšne telemetrije, bi bil povprečni čas prejema takšnih napak precej daljši.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3561">Absence of such telemetry would make the turnaround time for such issues much higher.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3562">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3562">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3563">**ErrorCode** – Koda napake, ki jo je zaznal uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3563">**ErrorCode** - The code of the issue that was hit by the user.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-ios-onenotestickynotesnotecreated-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3564">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (na iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (na Android)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3564">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteCreated (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3565">To je kritični signal, ki se uporablja za nadzor zmogljivosti Lepljivih zapiskov za ustvarjanje zapiskov v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3565">This is a critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3566">Telemetrija se uporablja za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3566">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3567">Če uporabniki ne morejo ustvariti zapiska, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3567">If users can't create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3568">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3568">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3569">**NoteLocalId** – razpoznavni enolični identifikator, ki je dodeljen zapisku v času, ko uporabnik ustvari zapiski v programu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3569">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time of a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3570">**IsExportable** – zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil dogodek rezultat dejanja uporabnika ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3570">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3571">Mora biti nastavljen na vrednost true, ker je NoteCreated dejanje, ki ga je sprožil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3571">Should be set to True as NoteCreated is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3572">**StickyNotes – SDKVersion** – številka različice, ki označuje različico Lepljivih zapiskov, ki jo uporablja uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3572">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3573">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerih različicah izdelka je prišlo do težave ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3573">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestickynotesnoteviewed-on-ios-onenotestickynotesnoteviewed-on-android"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3574">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteViewed (na iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteViewed (na Android)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3574">Office.OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteViewed (on iOS), OneNote.StickyNotes.NoteViewed (on Android)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3575">To je kritični signal, ki se uporablja za nadzor zmogljivosti Lepljivih zapiskov za ustvarjanje zapiskov v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3575">This is a critical signal that is used to monitor the ability of Sticky Notes users to create notes in the app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3576">Telemetrija se uporablja za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3576">Telemetry is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3577">Če uporabniki ne morejo ustvariti zapiska, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3577">If users can't create a note, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3578">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3578">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3579">**HasImages** – zastavica, ki označuje, so v ogledanem zapisku shranjene slike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3579">**HasImages** - A flag indicating whether the note viewed has images stored in it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3580">**IsExportable** – zastavica, ki označuje, ali je bil dogodek rezultat dejanja uporabnika ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3580">**IsExportable** - A flag indicating whether this event was a result of a user action or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3581">Mora biti nastavljen na vrednost true, ker je NoteViewed dejanje, ki ga je sprožil uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3581">Should be set to True as NoteViewed is a user-triggered action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3582">**NoteLocalId** – razpoznavni enolični identifikator, ki je dodeljen zapisku v času, ko uporabnik ustvari zapisek v programu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3582">**NoteLocalId** - Distinguishable unique identifier assigned to a note at the time a user creates the note within the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3583">**StickyNotes – SDKVersion** – številka različice, ki označuje različico Lepljivih zapiskov, ki jo uporablja uporabnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3583">**StickyNotes-SDKVersion** - Version number indicating the version of Sticky Notes the user is using.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3584">Omogoča, da določimo, v katerih različicah izdelka je prišlo do težave ter te težave razvrstimo po pomembnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3584">Allows us to identify which versions of the product are showing an issue so that we can correctly prioritize it.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeonenotestoragenotebooksyncresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3585">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3585">Office.OneNote.Storage.NotebookSyncResult</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3586">Ta dogodek zabeleži rezultat sinhronizacije zvezka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3586">This event logs notebook sync result.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3587">Uporablja se za prikaz števila enoličnih ciljev sinhronizacije pri izračunavanju rezultata sinhronizacije za OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3587">It is used for figuring out how many unique sync targets when calculating OneNote sync score.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3588">Zbrana so naslednja polja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3588">The following fields are collected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3589">**CachedError_Code** – oštevilčena ali alfanumerična koda, ki se uporablja za določanje narave predpomnjene napake, in/ali razloga, zakaj se je pojavila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3589">**CachedError_Code** - a numbered or alphanumeric code used to determine the nature of the cached error, and/or why it occurred</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3590">**CachedError_Description** – opis predpomnjene napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3590">**CachedError_Description** -a description of the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3591">**CachedError_Tag** – označuje, kje v kodi je shranjena predpomnjena napaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3591">**CachedError_Tag** -indicate where in the code throws the cached error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3592">**CachedError_Type** – vrsta predpomnjene napake, na primer »Win32Error« itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3592">**CachedError_Type** -the type of the cached error, e.g. Win32Error, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3593">**ExecutionTime** – čas v milisekundah, porabljen za podvojitev zvezka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3593">**ExecutionTime** -time in milliseconds taken to replicate the notebook</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3594">**Gosid** – globalni ID prostora za predmete.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3594">**Gosid** -global object space ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3595">**IdentityType** – vrsta identitete, npr. Windows Live, ID organizacije itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3595">**IdentityType** -identity type, e.g. Windows Live, Org ID, etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3596">**InitialReplicationInSession** – označuje, ali je ta podvojitev prva podvojitev zvezka po odprtju ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3596">**InitialReplicationInSession** -is this replication the first notebook replication after open or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3597">**IsBackgroundSync** – označuje, ali je to sinhroniziranje ozadja ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3597">**IsBackgroundSync** -is this a background sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3598">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** – označuje, ali je predpomnjena napaka onemogočena ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3598">**IsCachedErrorSuppressed** -is the cached error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3599">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** – označuje, ali je predpomnjena napaka nepričakovana ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3599">**IsCachedErrorUnexpected** -is the cached error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3600">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** – označuje, ali je napaka sinhronizacije na ravni zvezka onemogočena ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3600">**IsNotebookErrorSuppressed** -is the notebook level sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3601">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** – označuje, ali je napaka sinhronizacije na ravni zvezka nepričakovana ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3601">**IsNotebookErrorUnexpected** -is the notebook level sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3602">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** – označuje, ali je napaka sinhronizacije odseka onemogočena ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3602">**IsSectionErrorSuppressed** -is the section sync error suppressed or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3603">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** – označuje, ali je napaka sinhronizacije odseka nepričakovana ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3603">**IsSectionErrorUnexpected** -is the section sync error unexpected or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3604">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** – označuje, ali je sinhronizacija zvezka z moderno vsebino strani izvedena ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3604">**IsUsingRealtimeSync** -is the notebook sync using modern page content sync or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3605">**LastAttemptedSync** – časovni žig, ko je bil nazadnje izveden poskus sinhronizacije zvezka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3605">**LastAttemptedSync** -timestamp when the notebook was attempted to be synced last time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3606">**LastBackgroundSync** – časovni žig, ko je bil izveden zadnji poskus sinhronizacije v ozadju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3606">**LastBackgroundSync** -timestamp when the latest background sync was attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3607">**LastNotebookViewedDate** – datum, ko je bil zvezek nazadnje gledan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3607">**LastNotebookViewedDate** -the date when the notebook was last viewed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3608">**LastSuccessfulSync** – časovni žig, ko je bil zvezek uspešno predhodno sinhroniziran.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3608">**LastSuccessfulSync** -timestamp when the notebook successfully synced before</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookmacdeleteaccountusage"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3701">Office.Outlook.Mac.DeleteAccountUsage</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3701">Office.Outlook.Mac.DeleteAccountUsage</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3702">Rezultat brisanja računa v Outlooku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3702">Result of deleting an account in Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3703">Podatke spremljamo, da zagotovimo, da ne pride do morebitnih konic napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3703">The data is monitored to ensure we don't see any spikes in failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3704">Z analiziranjem teh podatkov odkrijemo tudi področja, ki jih moramo izboljšati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3704">We also analyze the data to find areas of improvement.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3705">Z vsako izdajo se trudimo izboljšati to raven uspešnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3705">We aim to improve this success rate with each release.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3706">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3706">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3707">**AccountType** – vrsta računa, ki je konfiguriran.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3707">**AccountType** - type of account being configured</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3708">**AccountID** – identifikator računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3708">**AccountID** - account identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3709">**DeprovisionAccount** – označuje, ali je račun odstranjen iz strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3709">**DeprovisionAccount** - indicates whether account is removed from server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3710">**IsFastDelete** – označuje, ali je račun izbrisan v niti ozadja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3710">**IsFastDelete** - indicates whether account is deleted on background thread</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationclose"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3711">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Close</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3711">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Close</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3712">Podatki so zbrani ob zapiranju PowerPointovih predstavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3712">Collected when PowerPoint presentations are closed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3713">Ta dogodek vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav pri postopku zapiranja, ki vključuje shranjevanje in sinhroniziranje uporabnikovih podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3713">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the close process which entail persisting and syncing the user's data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3714">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanje postopka zapiranja in uspešnega shranjevanja uporabnikove vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3714">Microsoft uses this data to ensure that close is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3715">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3715">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3716">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – Ali ima ta dolgi vnos vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja »Data\_Doc\_\*«)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3716">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3717">Če je nima, zakaj?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3717">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3718">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bilo samodejno shranjevanje onemogočeno v tem dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3718">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string -** Predefined set of values of why was autosave disabled on this document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3719">(Napaka spajanja, napaka shranjevanja, pravilnik skupine itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3719">(Merge error, Save error, Group policy etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3720">**Data\_CloseReason:long** – Kako je bil izveden postopek zapiranja?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3720">**Data\_CloseReason:long -** How was close performed?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3721">Ali ste zaprli dokument?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3721">Closing document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3722">Ali ste zaprli aplikacijo?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3722">Closing app?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3723">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – Število neobravnavanih izjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3723">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Number of unhandled exceptions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3724">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long** – Čas odpete dejavnosti/neizvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3724">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3725">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long** – Način odpiranja dokumenta (samo za branje/branje in pisanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3725">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3726">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3726">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3727">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3727">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3728">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long** – Način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3728">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3729">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long** – Stanje zaščite podatkov podjetja za dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3729">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3730">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3730">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3731">**Data\_Doc\_Extenstion:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3731">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3732">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za obliko zapisa datoteke (bolj podrobno kot za pripono).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3732">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3733">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string** – Mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3733">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3734">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost mesta shrambe dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3734">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3735">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string** – Enolični GUID uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3735">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3736">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string** – Enolični identifikator identitete, ki je bila uporabljena za dokumente v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3736">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3737">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long** – Bitna maska za različne zastavice danega dokumenta, povezane z V/I.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3737">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3738">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto upravljanja pravic do informacij, ki velja za ta dokument (»Forward«, »Reply«, »SecureReader«, »Edit« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3738">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3739">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila že prejeta glava HTTP »IsCloudCollabEnabled«, ki njo je poslala zahteva OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3739">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3740">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** – Ali je bil dokument odprt postopoma (nova funkcija, ki odpre dokument tako, da ne prenese celoten dokument).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3740">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3741">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool** – Ali dokument podpira soavtorstvo z novo storitvijo OCS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3741">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3742">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** – Preverja, ali je bil dokument odprt v lokalnem predpomnilniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3742">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** verifies if document is being opened from local cache</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3743">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool** – Preverja, ali je bil dokument odprt v mapi, za katero je uporabljena aplikacija za povratno sinhronizacijo v storitvi OneDrive.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3743">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** verifies if document is being opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3744">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za mesto shranjevanja dokumenta (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, omrežje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3744">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3745">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti podrobnejše lokacije (mapa »Začasno«, mapa »Prenosi«, dokumenti storitve OneDrive, slike storitve OneDrive itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3745">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3746">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long** –Število soavtorjev, ko je bil dokument odprt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3746">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long -** Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3747">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za način šifriranja dokumenta z geslom (brez, geslo za branje, geslo za urejanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3747">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)-</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3748">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil ta dokument označen samo za branje (zaklenjeno v strežniku, dokončni dokument, zaščiteno z geslom za urejanje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3748">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3749">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost identifikatorja vira za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3749">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3750">**Data_Doc_RtcType –**  označuje, kako je bil kanal v realnem času (RTC) nastavljen za trenutno datoteko (onemogočeno, nepodprto, na zahtevo, vedno vklopljeno itn.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3750">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3751">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string –** nespremenljivi identifikator za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3751">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string -** immutable identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3752">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, ki jih protokol uporablja za komunikacijo s strežnikom (Http, Cobalt, WOPI itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3752">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3753">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto strežnika (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3753">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3754">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long** – Preverja, ali strežnik temelji na sistemu Office14, Office15 ali Office 16.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3754">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long -** verifies if server is based off Office14, Office15 or Office 16</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3755">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long** – Ustvarjeni GUID, ki prepozna primerek dokumenta v seji istega procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3755">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3756">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string** – Neprosojen niz, običajno »GridManagerID.FarmID«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3756">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string -** An opaque string, typically GridManagerID.FarmID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3757">Uporabni podatki za korelacijo odjemalskega in strežniškega dnevnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3757">Useful for correlating client-side and server-side log</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3758">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long** – Velikost dokumenta v bajtih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3758">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3759">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long** – Bitna maska, ki označuje posebne znake v URL-ju ali poti dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3759">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3760">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string** – Niz, ki prepozna ponudnika za shranjevanje dokumentov, npr. »DropBox«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3760">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string -** A string that identifies the document's storage provider, like "DropBox"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3761">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za stanje dokumenta Stream (na voljo, stalno onemogočeno, ni na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3761">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability:long -** Predefined set of values of status of document Stream(available, permanently disabled, not available)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3762">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost polnega URL-ja za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3762">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string -** hash of full URL of documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3763">**Data\_Doc\_UsedWrsDataOnOpen:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila datoteka odprta postopoma z vnaprej predpomnjenimi podatki WRS na strani gostitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3763">**Data\_Doc\_UsedWrsDataOnOpen:bool -** true if the file was opened incrementally using pre cached WRS data on the host</span></span>
