  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3765">**Data\_DocHasStorage:bool** – Ali ima ta dokument lokalno shrambo?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3765">**Data\_DocHasStorage:bool -** Does this document have local storage?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3766">**Data\_fLifeguarded:bool –** ali je bil dokument kdaj zavarovan (funkcija za samodejno odpravljanje težav z dokumenti brez pozivanja uporabnika)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3766">**Data\_fLifeguarded:bool -** Was document ever lifeguarded (feature to fix document errors by themselves without prompting user)?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3767">**Data\_IsDocAutoSaveable:bool -** Is presentation auto saveable?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3767">**Data\_IsDocAutoSaveable:bool -** Is presentation auto saveable?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3768">**Data\_IsDocDirty:bool** – Ali predstavitev vključuje spremembe, ki še niso shranjene?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3768">**Data\_IsDocDirty:bool -** Does presentation have changes that are not yet saved?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3769">**Data\_IsNewDoc:bool** – Ali je dokument nov oz. obstoječ?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3769">**Data\_IsNewDoc:bool -** Is new document or existing</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3770">**Data\_IsRecoveredDoc:bool** – Ali je bil dokument obnovljen?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3770">**Data\_IsRecoveredDoc:bool -** Is document recovered one?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3771">(Če se je prejšnja seja zrušila, je podokno za obnovitev dokumenta prikazano v naslednji seji).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3771">(If prior session crashed, we show document recovery pane on next session)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3772">**Data\_NewDocDiscarded:bool** – Ali je bila nova predstavitev zavržena brez shranjevanja?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3772">**Data\_NewDocDiscarded:bool -** Was new presentation discarded without being saved</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3773">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgCanceled:bool** – Če je v strežniku OCS čakajoče nalaganje in uporabnik zapre dokument, je uporabniku prikazano pogovorno okno s sporočilom, naj počaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3773">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgCanceled:bool -** If upload is pending on OCS while user closes document, dialog is popped up to user to wait.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3774">Katero možnost naj uporabnik izbere?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3774">Which option user chose?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3775">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgExpired:bool** – Ali je pogovorno okno samodejno poteklo (po 1 minuti)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3775">**Data\_OCSClosingDlgExpired:bool -** Did dialog expire (after 1 minute) on its own?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3776">**Data\_OCSClosingStatus:long** – Kakšno je končno stanje strežnika OCS (»In CSI«, »Closable«, »In OCS Transition«, »In CSI transition« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3776">**Data\_OCSClosingStatus:long -** What's final status of OCS (In CSI, Closable, In OCS Transition, In CSI transition, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3777">**Data\_OCSClosingWaitDurationMS:long** – Koliko časa je moral uporabnik čakati, da se je strežnik OCS naložil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3777">**Data\_OCSClosingWaitDurationMS:long -** How much time user had to wait for OCS to upload</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3778">**Data\_OCSHandleTransitionResult:long** – Vnaprej določen nabor vrednosti rezultatov prehoda, izvedenega med zapiranjem (poskus je bil že izveden, nadaljuj zapiranje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3778">**Data\_OCSHandleTransitionResult:long -** Predefined set of values of result of transition performed during close (Already tried, continue to close, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3779">**Data\_ServerDocId:string** – GUID za enolično identifikacijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3779">**Data\_ServerDocId:string -** GUID to uniquely identify a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3780">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long –** skupni čas dejavnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3780">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long -** Total time for Activity</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3781">**Data\_UserContinuedZRTClose:bool** – Ali je uporabnik izbral možnost »Nadaljuj« zapiranje, ko je bilo ob zapiranju dokumenta prikazano pogovorno okno?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3781">**Data\_UserContinuedZRTClose:bool -** Upon showing dialog on close, did user selected 'Continue' to close?</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationnewdocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3782">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3782">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3783">Dogodek je zbran, ko PowerPoint ustvari novo predstavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3783">Collected when PowerPoint creates a new presentation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3784"> Vključuje metrike uspešnosti, neuspešnosti in učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3784">Includes success failure and performance metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3785">Te informacije uporabljamo za zagotavljanje uspešnega ustvarjanja datotek brez kakršnega koli zmanjšanja učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3785">This information is used to ensure we can create files successfully and with no degradation in performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3786">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3786">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3787">**NewDocumentType** – Ali je nov dokument ustvarjen iz predloge oz. povsem na novo?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3787">**NewDocumentType** – Whether new document is created from template or just created blank?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3788">**FLifeguarded** – Ali je življenjski cikel dokumenta zaščiten (funkcija, ki obnovi stanje poškodovanega dokumenta brez pozivanja uporabnika)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3788">**FLifeguarded** – Is document life guarded (feature that restores corrupt document state without prompting user)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationopencompleteprotocol"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3789">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3789">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3790">Podatki so zbrani ob odpiranju PowerPointovih predstavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3790">Collected when PowerPoint opens presentations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3791">Ta dogodek vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride v zadnji fazi postopka odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3791">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the end stages of the open process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3792">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanja funkcije in učinkovitega postopka odpiranja predstavitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3792">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and there is no degradation to opening presentations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3793">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3793">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3794">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto protivirusnega pregleda (IOAV, AMSI, None itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3794">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long -** Predefined set of values of type of AntiVirus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3795">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za protivirusni pregled, ki se izvede za vsak odprti dokument (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3795">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long -** Predefined set of values of anti-virus scan that happens for every document opened (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3796">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool** – Ali je bil ta dokument zaprt in nato znova odprt?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3796">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool -** Was this document closed and reopened?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3797">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long** – Čas odpete dejavnosti/neizvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3797">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3798">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long** – Način odpiranja dokumenta (samo za branje/branje in pisanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3798">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3799">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3799">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3800">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3800">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3801">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long** – Način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3801">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3802">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long** – Stanje zaščite podatkov podjetja za dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3802">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3803">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3803">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3804">**Data\_Doc\_Extenstion:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3804">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3805">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za obliko zapisa datoteke (bolj podrobno kot za pripono).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3805">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3806">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string** – Mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3806">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3807">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost mesta shrambe dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3807">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3808">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string** – Enolični GUID uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3808">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3809">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string** – Enolični identifikator identitete, ki je bila uporabljena za dokumente v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3809">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3810">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long** – Bitna maska za različne zastavice danega dokumenta, povezane z V/I.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3810">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3811">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto upravljanja pravic do informacij, ki velja za ta dokument (»Forward«, »Reply«, »SecureReader«, »Edit« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3811">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3812">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila že prejeta glava HTTP »IsCloudCollabEnabled«, ki njo je poslala zahteva OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3812">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3813">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** – Ali je bil dokument odprt postopoma (nova funkcija, ki odpre dokument tako, da ne prenese celoten dokument).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3813">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3814">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool** – Ali dokument podpira soavtorstvo z novo storitvijo OCS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3814">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3815">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** – Ali je bil dokument odprt iz lokalnega predpomnilnika?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3815">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** Is document being opened from local cache?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3816">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool** –Ali je bil dokument odprt iz mape, za katero se uporablja aplikacija za povratno sinhronizacijo v storitvi OneDrive.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3816">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3817">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za mesto shranjevanja dokumenta (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, omrežje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3817">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3818">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti podrobnejše lokacije (mapa »Začasno«, mapa »Prenosi«, dokumenti storitve OneDrive, slike storitve OneDrive itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3818">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3819">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long** –Število soavtorjev, ko je bil dokument odprt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3819">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long -** Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3820">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za način šifriranja dokumenta z geslom (brez, geslo za branje, geslo za urejanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3820">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)-</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3821">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil ta dokument označen samo za branje (zaklenjeno v strežniku, dokončni dokument, zaščiteno z geslom za urejanje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3821">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3822">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost identifikatorja vira za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3822">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3823">**Data_Doc_RtcType –**  označuje, kako je bil kanal v realnem času (RTC) nastavljen za trenutno datoteko (onemogočeno, nepodprto, na zahtevo, vedno vklopljeno itn.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3823">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3824">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string –** nespremenljivi identifikator za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3824">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string -** immutable identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3825">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, ki jih protokol uporablja za komunikacijo s strežnikom (Http, Cobalt, WOPI itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3825">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3826">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto strežnika (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3826">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3827">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long** – Preverja, ali strežnik temelji na sistemu Office14, Office15 ali Office 16.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3827">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion:long -** verifies if server is based off Office14, Office15 or Office 16</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3828">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long** – Ustvarjeni GUID, ki prepozna primerek dokumenta v seji istega procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3828">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3829">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string** – Neprosojen niz, običajno »GridManagerID.FarmID«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3829">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext:string -** An opaque string, typically GridManagerID.FarmID.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3830">Uporabni dogodki za korelacijo odjemalskih in strežniških dnevnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3830">Useful for correlating client side and server-side logs</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3831">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long** – Velikost dokumenta v bajtih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3831">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes:long -** Document size in bytes</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3832">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long** – Bitna maska, ki označuje posebne znake v URL-ju ali poti dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3832">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3833">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string** – Niz, ki prepozna ponudnika za shranjevanje dokumentov, npr. »DropBox«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3833">**Data\_Doc\_StorageProviderId:string -** A string that identifies the document's storage provider, like "DropBox"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3834">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za stanje dokumenta Stream (na voljo, stalno onemogočeno, ni na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3834">**Data\_Doc\_StreamAvailability:long -** Predefined set of values of status of document Stream(available, permanently disabled, not available)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3835">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost polnega URL-ja za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3835">**Data\_Doc\_UrlHash:string -** hash of full URL of documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3836">**Data\_Doc\_UsedWrsDataOnOpen:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila datoteka odprta postopoma z vnaprej predpomnjenimi podatki WRS na strani gostitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3836">**Data\_Doc\_UsedWrsDataOnOpen:bool -** true if the file was opened incrementally using pre cached WRS data on the host</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3838">**Data\_ExecutionCount:long** – Kolikokrat je bil izveden protokol IncOpen pred izvedbo tega (OpenComplete) protokola.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3838">**Data\_ExecutionCount:long -** How many times we executed IncOpen protocol before executing this (OpenComplete) protocol</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3839">**Data\_FailureComponent:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti komponent, zaradi katerih tega protokola ni bilo mogoče izvesti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3839">**Data\_FailureComponent:long -** Predefined set of values of which component caused this protocol to fail?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3840">(Spor, CSI, Internal itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3840">(Conflict, CSI, Internal etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3841">**Data\_FailureReason:long –** nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vzroke okvare (FileIsCorrupt, BlockedByAntivirus itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3841">**Data\_FailureReason:long -** Predefined set of values of what's the failure reason (FileIsCorrupt, BlockedByAntivirus etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3842">**Data_FullDownloadRoundTripCount:long** – število izvedenih povratnih poti do strežnika za prenos celotnega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3842">**Data_FullDownloadRoundTripCount:long -** The number of roundtrips to the server taken to download the entire document.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3844">**Data\_MethodId:long** – Katera vrstica kode je bila zadnja izvedena v postopku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3844">**Data\_MethodId:long -** Internally which line of code was last one to be executed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3845">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long –** skupni čas dejavnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3845">**Data\_StopwatchDuration:long -** Total time for Activity</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3846">**Data\_TimeToEdit:long** Čas, potreben, da je dokument mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3846">**Data\_TimeToEdit:long -** Time it took for document to become editable</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsave"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3849">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3849">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3850">Podatki so zbrani, kadar koli PowerPoint izvede postopek shranjevanja s potjo sodobne kode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3850">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the modern code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3851">Dogodek vsebuje vrsto rezultata uspešne oz. neuspešne metrike učinkovitosti shranjevanja in pomembne metapodatke dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3851">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3852">Napake pri shranjevanju lahko privedejo do izgube podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3852">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3853">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanje funkcije in uspešnega shranjevanja uporabnikove vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3853">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3854">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3854">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3855">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – Ali ima ta dolgi vnos vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja »Data\_Doc\_\*«)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3855">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3856">Če je nima, zakaj?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3856">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3857">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long** – Trajanje pridobivanja dokumenta pred dogodkom shranjevanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3857">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long -** Time taken to raise Document Before Save Event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3858">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long** – Trajanje preverjanja revizije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3858">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to check revision</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3859">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long** – Trajanje shranjevanja makrov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3859">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to save macros</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3860">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long** – Trajanje čiščenja zastavice za samodejno shranjevanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3860">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear AutoSave flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3861">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long** – Trajanje čiščenja zastavice nečistega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3861">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear document dirty flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3862">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long** – Trajanje kloniranja dokumenta pred začetkom postopka shranjevanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3862">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clone document before starting the save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3863">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long** – Trajanje potrjevanja transakcije shranjevanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3863">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long -** Time taken to commit the save transaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3864">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – Nezaznane izvorne izjeme med izvajanjem dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3864">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3865">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long** – Čas odpete dejavnosti/neizvajanja dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3865">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3866">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long** – Način odpiranja dokumenta (samo za branje/branje in pisanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3866">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3867">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3867">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3868">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3868">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3869">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long** – Način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3869">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3870">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long** – Stanje zaščite podatkov podjetja za dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3870">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3871">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3871">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3872">**Data\_Doc\_Extenstion:string** – Pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3872">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3873">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za obliko zapisa datoteke (bolj podrobno kot za pripono).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3873">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3874">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string** – Mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3874">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3875">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost mesta shrambe dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3875">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash:string -** Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3876">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string** – Enolični GUID uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3876">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId:string -** Unique GUID of user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3877">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string** – Enolični identifikator identitete, ki je bila uporabljena za dokumente v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3877">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityUniqueId:string -** Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3878">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long** – Bitna maska za različne zastavice danega dokumenta, povezane z V/I.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3878">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags:long -** Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3879">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto upravljanja pravic do informacij, ki velja za ta dokument (»Forward«, »Reply«, »SecureReader«, »Edit« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3879">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights:long -** Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3880">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – Ima vrednost »true«, če je bila že prejeta glava HTTP »IsCloudCollabEnabled«, ki njo je poslala zahteva OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3880">**Data\_Doc\_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool -** True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3881">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** – Ali je bil dokument odprt postopoma (nova funkcija, ki odpre dokument tako, da ne prenese celoten dokument).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3881">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen:bool -** Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3882">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool** – Ali dokument podpira soavtorstvo z novo storitvijo OCS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3882">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported:bool -** Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3883">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** – Preverja, ali je bil dokument odprt v lokalnem predpomnilniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3883">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool -** verifies if document being is opened from local cache</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3884">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool** –Ali je bil dokument odprt iz mape, za katero se uporablja aplikacija za povratno sinhronizacijo v storitvi OneDrive.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3884">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked:bool -** Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3885">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za mesto shranjevanja dokumenta (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, omrežje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3885">**Data\_Doc\_Location:long -** Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3886">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti podrobnejše lokacije (mapa »Začasno«, mapa »Prenosi«, dokumenti storitve OneDrive, slike storitve OneDrive itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3886">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails:long -** Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3887">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long** –Število soavtorjev, ko je bil dokument odprt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3887">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors:long -** Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3888">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za način šifriranja dokumenta z geslom (brez, geslo za branje, geslo za urejanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3888">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags:long -** Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3889">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil ta dokument označen samo za branje (zaklenjeno v strežniku, dokončni dokument, zaščiteno z geslom za urejanje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3889">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3890">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string** – Zgoščena vrednost identifikatorja vira za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3890">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash:string -** Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3891">**Data_Doc_RtcType –**  označuje, kako je bil kanal v realnem času (RTC) nastavljen za trenutno datoteko (onemogočeno, nepodprto, na zahtevo, vedno vklopljeno itn.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3891">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3892">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string –** nespremenljivi identifikator za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3892">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId:string -** immutable identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3893">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, ki jih protokol uporablja za komunikacijo s strežnikom (Http, Cobalt, WOPI itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3893">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol:long -** Predefined set of values of which protocol is used to talk to server (Http, Cobalt, WOPI etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3894">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto strežnika (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3894">**Data\_Doc\_ServerType:long -** Predefined set of values of type of server (SharePoint, DropBox, WOPI)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3896">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long** – Ustvarjeni GUID, ki prepozna primerek dokumenta v seji istega procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3896">**Data\_Doc\_SessionId:long -** generated GUID that Identifies the instance of the document within the same process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3900">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long** – Bitna maska, ki označuje posebne znake v URL-ju ali poti dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3900">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars:long -** Bitmask indicating special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3930">**Data\_SaveType:long** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti vrste shranjevanja (SaveAs, Publish, Manual, OMSave itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3930">**Data\_SaveType:long -** Predefined set of values of save type (SaveAs, Publish, Manual, OMSave etc.)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3935">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3935">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3936">Podatki so zbrani, kadar koli PowerPoint izvede postopek »Shrani kot«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3936">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a Save As.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3937">Dogodek vsebuje vrsto rezultata uspešne oz. neuspešne metrike učinkovitosti shranjevanja in pomembne metapodatke dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3937">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3938">Napake pri shranjevanju lahko privedejo do izgube podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3938">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3939">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanje funkcije in uspešnega shranjevanja uporabnikove vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3939">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3940">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3940">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3941">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – označuje, ali ima ta dolgi vnos vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja »Data_Doc_\*«)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3941">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3942">Če je nima, zakaj?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3942">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3943">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – nezaznane izvirne izjeme med izvedbo dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3943">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3944">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – čas, v katerem je bila dejavnost ločena/ni bila izvajana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3944">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3945">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** – način odpiranja tega dokumenta (samo za branje | branje in pisanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3945">**Data_DstDoc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3946">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3946">**Data_DstDoc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3947">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3947">**Data_DstDoc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the new cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3948">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** – način shranjevanja dokumenta v SharePointu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3948">**Data_DstDoc_ChunkingType:long** - How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3949">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** – stanje zaščite podatkov podjetja za dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3949">**Data_DstDoc_EdpState:long** - Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3950">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** – pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3950">**Data_DstDoc_Ext:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3951">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** – pripona dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3951">**Data_DstDoc_Extension:string** - Document extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3952">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za obliko zapisa datoteke (bolj podrobno kot za pripono).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3952">**Data_DstDoc_FileFormat:long** - Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3953">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** – mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3953">**Data_DstDoc_Fqdn:string** - Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3954">**Data_DstDoc_FqdnHash:string** – zgoščena vrednost mesta shrambe dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3954">**Data_DstDoc_FqdnHash:string** - Hash of where document is stored</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3955">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityTelemetryId:string** – enolični GUID uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3955">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityTelemetryId:string** - Unique GUID of user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3956">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** – enolični identifikator identitete, ki je bila uporabljena za dejanje dokumentov v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3956">**Data_DstDoc_IdentityUniqueId:string** - Unique identifier of identity that was used for Shared Documents action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3957">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** – bitna maska za različne zastavice danega dokumenta, povezane z VI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3957">**Data_DstDoc_IOFlags:long** - Bitmask for various IO related flags for a given document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3958">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za vrsto upravljanja pravic do informacij, ki velja za ta dokument (»Posredovanje«, »Odgovarjanje«, »SecureReader«, »Urejanje« itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3958">**Data_DstDoc_IrmRights:long** - Predefined set of values of what type of Information Rights Management is applied on this document (Forward, Reply, SecureReader, Edit etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3959">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** – ima vrednost »true«, če je bila že prejeta glava HTTP »IsCloudCollabEnabled«, ki jo je poslala zahteva OPTIONS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3959">**Data_DstDoc_IsCloudCollabEnabled:bool** - True if the "IsCloudCollabEnabled" HTTP header has already been received from an OPTIONS request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3960">**Data_DstDoc_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** – označuje, ali je bil dokument odprt postopoma (nova funkcija, ki odpre dokument, ne da bi bilo treba prenesti celoten dokument).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3960">**Data_DstDoc_IsIncrementalOpen:bool** - Was document opened incrementally (new feature that opens document without needing to download entire document)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3961">**Data_DstDoc_IsOcsSupported:bool** – označuje, ali dokument podpira soavtorstvo z novo storitvijo OCS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3961">**Data_DstDoc_IsOcsSupported:bool** - Is Document supports coauthoring using new OCS service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3962">**Data_DstDoc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** – preverja, ali je bil dokument odprt v lokalnem predpomnilniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3962">**Data_DstDoc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy:bool** - verifies if document is being opened from local cache</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3963">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** –označuje, ali je bil dokument odprt v mapi, za katero se uporablja aplikacija za povratno sinhronizacijo v storitvi OneDrive.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3963">**Data_DstDoc_IsSyncBacked:bool** - Is document opened from folder that is using OneDrive sync back app</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3964">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za mesto shrambe dokumenta (lokalno, SharePoint, WOPI, omrežje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3964">**Data_DstDoc_Location:long** - Predefined set of values of where document is stored (Local, SharePoint, WOPI, Network etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3965">**Data_DstDoc_LocationDetails:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti podrobnejše lokacije (mapa »Začasno«, mapa »Prenosi«, dokumenti storitve OneDrive, slike storitve OneDrive itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3965">**Data_DstDoc_LocationDetails:long** - Predefined set of values of more detailed location (Temp folder, downloads folder, One Drive Documents, One Drive Pictures etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3966">**Data_DstDoc_NumberCoAuthors:long** –število soavtorjev v trenutku, ko je bil dokument odprt.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3966">**Data_DstDoc_NumberCoAuthors:long** - Number of coauthors at the time of opening of a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3967">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za način šifriranja dokumenta z geslom (brez, geslo za branje, geslo za urejanje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3967">**Data_DstDoc_PasswordFlags:long** - Predefined set of values of how document is encrypted with password (None, password to read, password to edit)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3968">**Data_DstDoc_ReadOnlyReasons:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil ta dokument označen samo za branje (zaklenjeno v strežniku, končni dokument, zaščiteno z geslom za urejanje itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3968">**Data_DstDoc_ReadOnlyReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why this document was marked read only (Locked on server, final document, password protected to edit, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3969">**Data_DstDoc_ResourceIdHash:string** – zgoščena vrednost identifikatorja vira za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3969">**Data_DstDoc_ResourceIdHash:string** - Hash of resource identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-3970">**Data_DstDoc_ServerDocId:string** – nespremenljivi identifikator za dokumente, shranjene v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-3970">**Data_DstDoc_ServerDocId:string** - immutable identifier for documents stored in cloud</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4036">Podatki so zbrani, kadar koli PowerPoint izvede postopek shranjevanja s potjo podedovane kode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4036">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the legacy code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4037">Dogodek vsebuje vrsto rezultata uspešne oz. neuspešne metrike učinkovitosti shranjevanja in pomembne metapodatke dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4037">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4038">Napake pri shranjevanju lahko privedejo do izgube podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4038">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4039">Microsoft uporablja te podatke za zagotavljanje ustreznega delovanje funkcije in uspešnega shranjevanja uporabnikove vsebine.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4039">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4040">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4040">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4041">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – označuje, ali ima ta dolgi vnos vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja »Data_Doc_\*«)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4041">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4042">Če je nima, zakaj?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4042">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4043">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – nezaznane izvirne izjeme med izvedbo dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4043">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4044">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – čas, v katerem je bila dejavnost ločena/ni bila izvajana.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4044">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4045">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** – način odpiranja dokumenta (samo za branje | branje in pisanje)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4045">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4046">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4046">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons:long** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4047">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4047">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4053">**Data_Doc_Fqdn:string** – mesto, kjer je dokument shranjen (SharePoint.com, live.net); na voljo samo za domene v storitvi Office 365.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4053">**Data_Doc_Fqdn:string** - Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

#### <a name="officetargetedmessagingabexperimentmessagetrigger"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4244">Office.TargetedMessaging.ABExperimentMessageTrigger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4244">Office.TargetedMessaging.ABExperimentMessageTrigger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4245">Spremlja število uporabnikov, ki prejemajo sporočila storitev BizBar in Dynamic Canvas storitve TMS (TargetedMessagingService).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4245">Tracks the number of users receiving BizBar and Dynamic Canvas messages from TargetedMessagingService (TMS).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4246">Ti podatki so ključni za razumevanje vrste in območij sporočil, ki jih prejemajo uporabniki. Z njimi lahko zagotovimo, da uporabniki prejmejo vsa sporočila, nujna za nadaljnjo uporabo izdelka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4246">This data is critical to understand what messages users are getting and on what surface so that we can ensure they are not missing any messages that may be critical to their continued use of the product.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4247">Te podatke potrebujemo tudi za natančno ocenjevanje naših poskusov in akcij v storitvi TMS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4247">Also needed to accurately measure the success of our experiments and campaigns run through TMS.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4248">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4248">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4249">**Data\_Surface** – Ime območja, kamor je storitev poslala sporočilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4249">**Data\_Surface** – Name of the surface that this service delivered message is meant for</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedrefreshsmartdiagram"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4396">Office.Visio.Shared.RefreshSmartDiagram</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4396">Office.Visio.Shared.RefreshSmartDiagram</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4397">Zajame vrednosti osveževanje diagrama, če je datoteka ustvarjena z vmesnikom DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4397">Captures diagram refresh failures when file is created through DV.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4398">Na ta način lažje odpravljamo napake in težave pri osveževanju podatkov v diagramu DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4398">This helps us debug the failures and issues in data refresh in a DV diagram.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4399">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4399">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4400">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** – ima vrednost true, če je bil osveženi diagram prvotno ustvarjen s povezovalnikom na osnovi zaporedja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4400">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true if the refreshed diagram was originally created using connector based on sequence" option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4401">**Data\_DialogError** : **string** – napaka med osveževanjem pametnega diagrama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4401">**Data\_DialogError** : **string** - error during refreshing smart diagram</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4402">**Data\_FileError:string** – niz napake, če povezana Excelova datoteka ni veljavna</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4402">**Data\_FileError:string** - error string when connected Excel file is invalid</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4403">**Data\_OverwriteSelected** : **bool** – ima vrednost true, če je uporabnik med osveževanjem izbral možnost za prepisovanje diagrama</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4403">**Data\_OverwriteSelected** : **bool** - true if user selected overwrite diagram option during refresh</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4404">**Data\_WarningShown** : **bool** – ima vrednost true, če je uporabnik med postopkom osveževanja podatkov prejel opozorilo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4404">**Data\_WarningShown** : **bool** - true if there was any warning shown to user during data refresh</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedwritebacktoexcel"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4405">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4405">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4406">Zajame vrednosti napak pri pisanju nazaj v Excelu, če je datoteka ustvarjena z vmesnikom DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4406">Captures Excel write back failures when file is created through DV.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4407">Na ta način lažje odpravljamo napake in težave pri pisanju podatkov nazaj v Excel v diagramu DV.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4407">This helps us debug the failures and issues in writing back data to Excel in a DV diagram.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4408">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4408">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4409">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** – vrednost true pomeni, da so povezovalniki ustvarjeni glede na nastavitve zaporedja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4409">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true means connectors are created based on sequence settings</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4410">**Data\_DataSourceType:string** – to polje ponazarja, ali je bil diagram ustvarjen iz možnosti »Tabela« oz. »ObsegPoMeri«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4410">**Data\_DataSourceType:string** - This filed indicates whether diagram is created from  "Table" or "CustomRange"</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4411">**Data\_DialogError:string** – vrsta napake po meri med ustvarjanjem pametnega diagrama v Excelu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4411">**Data\_DialogError:string** - Custom Error type while creating smart diagram through Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4412">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** – število oblik, ki so bile dodane med postopkom pisanja nazaj v Excelove funkcije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4412">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** - Number of shapes added during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4413">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** – število oblik, ki so bile izbrisane med postopkom pisanja nazaj v Excelove funkcije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4413">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** - Number of shapes deleted during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4414">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** – ima vrednost true, če je uporabnik izbral možnost prepisovanja podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4414">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** - true indicate user selected overwrite data option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4415">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da so bili izvorni podatki spremenjeni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4415">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** - true indicates source data is modified</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4416">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilo o posodobitvi podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4416">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** - true means data update warning shown to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4417">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilo zaradi formule v Excelu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4417">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user because of presence of formula in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4418">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilo, saj v Excelu ni prisoten identifikator naslednjega koraka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4418">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** - true indicates warning show to the user because next step Identifier missing in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4419">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** – vrednost true ponazarja, da je uporabnik prejel opozorilo, naj Excelove podatke pretvori v obliko zapisa za tabele</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4419">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user to convert Excel data to table format</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfilenewcreatenewfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4420">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4420">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4421">Ta dogodek označuje, da je bil ustvarjen nov dokument v Office Wordu, in spremlja, ali je bil postopek uspešen oz. neuspešen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4421">This event indicates that a new document is created in Office Word and tracks success or failure of the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4422">S tem dogodkom spremljamo ustreznost ustvarjanja novega dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4422">The event is used to monitor that new document creation is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4423">Ta dogodek uporabljamo tudi za ocenjevanje števila mesečnih aktivnih uporabnikov/naprav in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4423">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4424">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4424">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4425">**Data\_DirtyState** – Ali je bil dokument ustvarjen v nečistem stanju (s spremembami, ki jih je treba shraniti).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4425">**Data\_DirtyState** - whether the document was created in a dirty state (with changes that need to be saved)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4426">**Data\_ErrorID** – Identifikator napake v primeru napake postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4426">**Data\_ErrorID** - error identifier in case of operation failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4427">**Data\_MainPdod** – Identifikator dokumenta med sejo tega postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4427">**Data\_MainPdod** - The document identifier during this process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4428">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** – Označuje, ali je bil dokument ustvarjen s predlogo po meri.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4428">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** - indicates whether the document was created from a custom template</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenuserinitiatedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4429">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4429">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4430">V tem dogodku je navedeno, da je Office Word odprl dokument z zagonom uporabnika namesto na programski način Office Word. </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4430">This event indicates Office Word opens a document by user initiation instead of by Office Word programmatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4431">Poleg tega vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4431">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4432">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija za odpiranje datoteke deluje pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4432">The event monitors whether file-open is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4433">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4433">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4434">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4434">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4435">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4435">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4436">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4436">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4437">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega je morda mogoče odpreti datoteko, če ga pridobimo, preden uporabnik začne urejati dokument oz. se ga morda odloči shraniti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4437">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4438">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega morda lahko odpremo datoteko, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4438">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4439">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4439">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4440">**Data_BytesUnknown** – število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4440">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4441">**Data.Doc.AccessMode** – dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4441">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4442">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4442">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4443">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enote, uporabljene za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4443">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4444">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4444">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4445">**Data_Doc_Ext** – pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4445">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4446">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – različica protokola za obliko zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4446">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4447">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4447">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4448">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost imena domene, ki omogoča identifikacijo stranke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4448">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4449">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost identitete uporabnika, uporabljena za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4449">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4450">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – zabeleži način odpiranja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4450">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4451">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – poroča o predpomnjenih zastavicah, uporabljenih za nastavitev možnosti zahtev za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4451">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4452">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – dejanja, ki jih je dovolil pravilnik za elektronsko zaščito podatkov, ki velja za dokument/uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4452">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4453">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – zastavica, ki označuje postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4453">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4454">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – zastavica, ki označuje, da je storitev sodelovanja podprta v dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4454">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4455">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – zastavica, ki označuje, da je bila odprta kopija dokumenta brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4455">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4456">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – zastavica, ki označuje, da v računalniku obstaja samodejno sinhronizirana kopija dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4456">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4457">**Data_Doc_Location** – označuje, v kateri storitvi je dokument na voljo (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4457">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4458">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – označuje, v kateri znani mapi je na voljo lokalno shranjen dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4458">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4459">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – število souporabnikov v seji urejanja s sodelovanjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4459">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4460">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – označuje nastavljene zastavice za branje ali branje/pisanje gesla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4460">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4461">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – razlogi, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu »samo za branje«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4461">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4462">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** – anonimni identifikator dokumenta za diagnosticiranje težav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4462">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4463">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** – nespremenljivi anonimni identifikator dokumenta za diagnosticiranje težav</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4463">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4465">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – vrsta strežnika, ki zagotavlja storitev (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4465">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4466">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – različica strežnika, ki zagotavlja storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4466">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4467">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – različica strežnika, ki zagotavlja storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4467">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - the server version offering the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4468">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – diagnostične informacije zahtev storitve SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4468">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4469">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – indikator velikosti dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4469">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4470">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – indikator posebnih znakov v URL-ju ali poti dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4470">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>
