- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4473">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost za ustvarjanje naivnega identifikatorja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4473">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4474">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – vsebuje enolični identifikator za ponudnika storitve WOPI.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4474">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - Contains unique identifier of WOPI service provider</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4475">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** – identifikator prvega urejevalnika, ki je onemogočil preimenovanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4475">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** - Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4477">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** – vrednost celega števila, ki predstavlja vzrok za vsiljeni način za branje/pisanje pri datoteki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4477">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4479">**Data_LastLoggedTag** – enolična oznaka za mesto klica kode, ki se uporablja za prepoznavanje, ko poskušamo izvesti neuspešno odpiranje dvakrat zapored (uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4479">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4481">**Data_MainPdod** – identifikator dokumenta v postopku programa Microsoft Office Word.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4481">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4482">**Data_Measurements** – šifriran niz z razčlenitvijo časa različnih časov odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4482">**Data_Measurements** - Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4483">Uporablja se za diagnosticiranje uspešnost pri odpiranju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4483">Used to diagnose open performance.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4484">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** – napaka, ki onemogoča premik dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4484">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** - Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4485">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** – označuje, ali je omogočena pilotna različica za funkcijo premikanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4485">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4486">**Data_OpenInitiateKind** – vrsta scenarija, v katerem so uporabniki zagnali to operacijo za odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4486">**Data_OpenInitiateKind** – Type of the scenario where users started this file-open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4488">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** – enolična oznaka za mesto klica kode, ki se uporablja za prepoznavanje mesta v kodi, kjer poskušamo odpraviti napako pred odpiranjem datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4488">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify the place in code where we attempt to fix the file before opening it</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4489">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** – napaka, ki povzroča, da je funkcija preimenovanja za ta dokument onemogočena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4489">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** - Error that is causing for rename to be disabled for this document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4490">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** – označuje, ali je omogočena pilotna različica za funkcijo preimenovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4490">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4491">**Data_SecondaryTag** – enolična oznaka za mesto klica kode, ki se uporablja za dodajanje dodatnih podatkov o neuspehih pri odpiranju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4491">**Data_SecondaryTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4492">**Data_TemplateFormat** – oblika zapisa datoteke za predlogo, na kateri temelji dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4492">**Data_TemplateFormat** - File format of the template that the document is based on.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4493">**Data_UsesNormal** – označuje, ali odprti dokument temelji na navadni predlogi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4493">**Data_UsesNormal** - Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4494">**Data_VerboseMeasurements** – šifriran niz z razčlenitvijo časa različnih časov odpiranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4494">**Data_VerboseMeasurements** - Encoded string containing the detailed time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4495">Uporablja se za merjenje učinkovitosti delovanja, ki je omogočena le za interne obroče.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4495">Used to measure performance, only enabled for internal rings.</span></span> 



#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactcmdgosubsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4496">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4496">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4497">Ta dogodek označuje, da uporabnik shranjuje spremembe v nov dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4497">This event indicates that a user is saving their changes to a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4498">Dogodek nadzira ustreznost delovanja shranjevanja v nov dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4498">The event monitors whether saving to a new document is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4499">Ta dogodek uporabljamo tudi za ocenjevanje števila mesečnih aktivnih uporabnikov/naprav in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4499">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4500">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4500">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4547">Ta dogodek označuje, da Office Word pozove uporabnika k shranjevanju sprememb, ko ta poskuša zapreti dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4547">This event indicates Office Word prompts the user to save changes when it tries to close the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4548">Z njim Microsoft nadzira ustreznost delovanja funkcije shranjevanja dokumenta ob zapiranju ter tako prepreči morebitno izgubo podatkov v dokumentih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4548">It allows Microsoft to monitor whether save-at-quit works as expected to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4549">Dogodek nadzira, ali način shranjevanja ob zapiranju ustrezno deluje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4549">The event monitors whether save-at-quit is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4550">Ta dogodek uporabljamo tudi za ocenjevanje števila mesečnih aktivnih uporabnikov/naprav in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4550">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesavesaveassavefile"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4608">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4608">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4609">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word shranjuje dokument v nov dokument.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4609">This event indicates Office Word saves a document into a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4610">Microsoftu omogoča, da pri funkciji »Shrani kot« zazna napake, ki so pomembne za preprečevanje izgube podatkov v dokumentih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4610">It allows Microsoft to detect errors in save-as which is important to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4611">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Shrani kot« deluje običajno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4611">The event monitors whether save-as is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4612">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4612">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4613">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4613">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4614">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4614">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4615">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4615">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4616">**Data_AddDocTelemResDst** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka za ciljni dokument, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4616">**Data_AddDocTelemResDst** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event for the destination document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4617">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4617">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4618">**Data_AddDocTelemResSrc** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka za izvorni dokument, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4618">**Data_AddDocTelemResSrc** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event for the source document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4619">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4619">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4620">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4620">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4622">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4622">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4742">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled –** ponazarja, ali je omogočena funkcija »Vedno shrani«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4742">**Data\_FAlwaysSaveEnabled-** Indicates whether always-save was enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4782">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** – ID scenarija, ki ga je posredovala aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4782">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

#### <a name="readconversation"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4795">read.conversation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4795">read.conversation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4796">Uporablja se za nadzor morebitnih negativnih učinkov na stanje in učinkovitost upodabljanja e-poštnega sporočila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4796">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on the health and performance of rendering an email message</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4797">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4797">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4798">**above_40fps** – število okvirjev, upodobljenih nad 40 slik/s.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4798">**above_40fps** - count of frames rendered above 40fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4799">**above_50fps** – število okvirjev, upodobljenih nad 50 slik/s.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4799">**above_50fps** - count of frames rendered above 50fps</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4800">**above_55fps** – število okvirjev, upodobljenih nad 55 slik/s.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4800">**above_55fps** - count of frames rendered above 55fps</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4801">**adal_id** – ID za preverjanje pristnosti imenika Active Directory računa, enolični identifikator v Microsoftovem sistemu za preverjanje pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4801">**adal_id** - the account's active directory authentication ID, a unique identifier in the Microsoft authentication system</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4802">**component_name** – ime komponente/pogleda, ki je aktiven med filtriranjem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4802">**component_name** - the name of the component/view which is active during the filtering</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4803">**event_mode** – mesto v aplikaciji, kjer je uporabnik začel pogovor (skupina ali drugo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4803">**event_mode** - the place in the app that the user entered the conversation (groups or other)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4804">**internet_message_id** – ID sledenja za zadnje sporočilo v pogovoru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4804">**internet_message_id** - a tracking ID for the most recent message in the conversation</span></span>
      
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4805">**orientation** – usmerjenost zaslona ob dogodku (pokončna ali ležeča).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4805">**orientation** - the screen orientation at the time of the even (portrait or landscape)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4806">**recent_message_id** – ID zadnjega sporočila v pogovoru.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4806">**recent_message_id** - the ID of the most recent message in the conversation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4807">**suggested_reply_state** – Stanje predlaganih odgovorov za ta pogovor (ni na voljo, na voljo, prikazano, uporabljeno ali zavrženo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4807">**suggested_reply_state** - the state of suggested replies for this conversation (unavailable, available, shown, used, or discarded)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4808">**suggested_reply_types** – Označuje vrsto in število predlaganih odgovorov, prikazanih/uporabljenih za ta pogovor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4808">**suggested_reply_types** - indicates type and count of suggested reply shown/used for this conversation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4809">To je slovar.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4809">It’s a dictionary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4810">Na primer {text: 2, send_avail: 1}.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4810">For example {text: 2, send_avail: 1}.</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4811">**total_count** – Skupno število okvirjev, ki jih prikaže komponenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4811">**total_count** - total frames displayed by the component</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4812">**view_duration** – čas, ko si je uporabnik ogledoval komponento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4812">**view_duration** - how long the component was viewed by the user</span></span>

#### <a name="saveattempt"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4813">save.attempt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4813">save.attempt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4814">Omogoča, da določimo vpliv težav, ki jih povzročijo uporabniki pri poskusih shranjevanja datoteke, tako, da ocenimo število prizadetih sej in prepoznamo morebitne skupne značilnosti teh sej.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4814">Allows us to identify the impact of issues caused by users attempting to save a file by evaluating the number of sessions impacted and if there are common features of those sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4815">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4815">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4816">**file_type** – vrsta datoteke, ki jo je uporabnik poskusil shraniti (na primer. doc).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4816">**file_type** - The type of file the user tried to save (such as .doc)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4817">**origin** – izvor poskusa shranjevanja datoteke (npr. iz e-pošte), s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane s shranjevanjem datoteke iz določenega mesta v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4817">**origin** - Where the file save attempt originated from (such as from an email) so we can detect issues associated with saving a file from a specific place in the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4818">**token_type** – vrsta žetona, uporabljenega za preverjanje pristnosti računa za shranjevanje datoteke, s katero zaznavamo težave pri preverjanju pristnosti, povezane s shranjevanjem datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4818">**token_type** - the type of token used to authenticate the account in order to save the file to help us detect authentication issues associated with saving a file</span></span>

#### <a name="searchsubtabselected"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4819">search.subtab.selected</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4819">search.subtab.selected</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4820">Dogodek zbira točke izvora, zakaj je bil izbran podzavihek »sub_tab« iskanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4820">The event collects origin points for the reason a search sub_tab was selected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4821">Podzavihki so na voljo v vrstici za iskanje primarne aplikacije za filtriranje podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4821">The sub tabs sit under the primary app search bar to filter data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4822">S tem dogodkom lahko spremljamo tablete vrste entitete (vse, pošta, stiki in koledar), ki jih uporabniki uporabljajo, ko izvajajo svoja iskanj. Tako lahko poskrbimo, da mehanizmi filtrov iskanja delujejo pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4822">This event lets us track the entity type pills (all, mail, contacts and calendar) that users are using when they do their searches so we can ensure the search filter mechanisms are working properly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4823">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4823">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4824">**properties_general** – splošne lastnosti, ki jih zbira dogodek »all Aria«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4824">**properties_general** -The general properties that all Aria event is collecting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4825">**selected_reason** – Vzrok za izbor tabletke vrste, ki je lahko ena teh treh vrednosti (glif, ki je ikona): tap_on_header, tap_on_see_all, enter_search_mode, mail_glyph, calendar_glyph.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4825">**selected_reason** - The cause of the type pill getting selected, which could be one of the following values (glyph being an icon): tap_on_header, tap_on_see_all, enter_search_mode, mail_glyph, calendar_glyph.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4826">**subtab_type** – Izbrana tabletka vrste, ki je lahko ena od teh štirih vrednosti: vse, pošta, stik, dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4826">**subtab_type** - The type pill that got selected, which could be one of these four values: all, mail, contact, event.</span></span>

#### <a name="sendmessage"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4827">send.message</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4827">send.message</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4828">Uporablja se za nadzor morebitnih negativnih učinkov na učinkovitost in stanje pošiljanja e-poštnih sporočil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4828">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on the performance and health of sending email messages.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4829">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4829">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4830">**account** – spremlja račun, v katerem se je izvedlo dejanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4830">**account** - tracks the account which performed the action</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4831">**compose_duration** –spremlja skupni čas, ki ga je uporabnik porabil za sestavljanje sporočila, vključno s sejo z več osnutki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4831">**compose_duration** - tracks the total time user took to compose the message including multiple drafts session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4832">**draft_message_id** – spremlja ID sporočila za sestavljanje poslanega sporočila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4832">**draft_message_id** - tracks the compose message ID of the message being sent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4833">**event_mode** – spremlja način dogodka, če je na voljo za sporočilo (»skupine« ali »drugo«).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4833">**event_mode** - tracks the event mode if applicable to the message, ("groups" or "other")</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4834">**has_attachment** – označuje, ali sporočilo vsebuje priponke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4834">**has_attachment** - indicates whether message has any attachments</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4835">**has_mip_label** – označuje, ali je sporočilo označeno z oznako MIP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4835">**has_mip_label** - indicates whether a MIP label was stamped on the message or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4836">**is_group_escalation** – ali gre za stopnjevano sporočilo skupine. »Stopnjevano sporočilo« je sporočilo, poslano v nabiralnik uporabnika zaradi stopnjevanja (naročnina na skupino).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4836">**is_group_escalation** - is this a group escalated message, "escalated message" is a message that was sent to the user's mailbox because of an escalation (subscribed to group)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4837">**is_groups** – spremlja, ali je poslano sporočilo vrste »sporočilo skupine«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4837">**is_groups** - track whether message sent is a groups message or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4838">**key_stroke_count** – spremlja število pritiskov tipk za sporočilo, ki ga želite poslati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4838">**key_stroke_count** - tracks the keystrokes count for the message that is being sent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4839">**message_id** – spremlja ID sporočila, na katerega želite odgovoriti ali ga posredovati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4839">**message_id** - tracks the message ID being replied/forwarded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4840">**origin** – ponazarja mesto začetka ustvarjanja sporočila, npr. novo, odgovor, hitri odgovor itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4840">**origin** - indicates where compose was initiated, i.e. new, reply, quick reply etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4841">**send_draft_origin** – ponazarja mesto začetka pošiljanja, npr. ustvari ali hitri odgovor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4841">**send_draft_origin** - indicates where send was initiated, i.e. compose or quick reply</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4842">**smart_compose_model_version** – spremlja, katero različico modela Smart sestavite uporabljamo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4842">**smart_compose_model_version** - tracks which version of smart compose model is being used</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4843">**source_inbox** – ponazarja vrsto izvirnega nabiralnika za referenčno sporočilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4843">**source_inbox** - indicates source inbox type for reference message,</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4844">**suggested_reply_state** – Zajem stanja predlaganega odgovora za to poslano sporočilo, npr. ni na voljo, na voljo, prikazano, uporabljeno, zavrženo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4844">**suggested_reply_state** - capturing suggested reply state i.e., unavailable, available, shown, used, discarded for this sent mail</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4845">**suggested_reply_types** – Označuje vrsto in število predlaganih odgovorov, prikazanih/uporabljenih za to poslano e-poštno sporočilo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4845">**suggested_reply_types** - indicates type and count of suggested reply shown/used for this sent email.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4846">To je slovar.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4846">It’s a dictionary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4847">Na primer {text: 2,  send_avail: 1}.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4847">For example {text: 2,  send_avail: 1}.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4848">**suggestions_requested** – Označuje, koliko predlogov za pametno sestaviti je bilo zahtevano</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4848">**suggestions_requested** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions requested</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4849">**suggestions_results** – Smart sestavite rezultate, tj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4849">**suggestions_results** - smart compose suggestions’ result, i.e</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4850">sprejeto, zavrnjeno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4850">accepted, rejected</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4851">**suggestions_returned** – označuje, koliko pametnih predlogov za sestavljanje je vrnjenih iz strežnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4851">**suggestions_returned** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions returned from server</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4852">**suggestions_shown** – označuje, koliko pametnih predlogov za sestavljanje je prikazano uporabniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4852">**suggestions_shown** - indicates how many smart compose suggestions shown to the user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4853">**thread_id** – ponazarja ID niti za pogovor, ki ga želite posredovati ali odgovoriti nanj.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4853">**thread_id** - indicates thread ID of the conversation being replied/forwarded</span></span>

#### <a name="session"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4854">session</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4854">session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4855">Omogoča nam zaznavanje in odpravljanje primerov, kjer uporabljamo prevelik odstotek baterije vaše naprave, ter nam pomaga prepoznati morebiten vzrok.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4855">Allows us to detect and fix situations where we are using up too much of your device's battery and helps us identify what could be the cause.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4856">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4856">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4857">**battery_level** – ponazarja raven baterije v naravi, s katero lahko zaznamo, kdaj naša aplikacija negativno vpliva na stanje baterije vaše naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4857">**battery_level** - tells us the battery level on the device to help us detect when our app is causing a negative impact on your device's battery level</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4858">**has_hx** – dogodek, ki ponazarja, da račun uporablja našo novo storitev sinhronizacije, s katerim je mogoče zaznati težave, ki jih povzroči naša storitev sinhronizacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4858">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

#### <a name="settingsaction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4859">settings.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4859">settings.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4860">Ta dogodek zbere informacije o konfiguraciji v nastavitvah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4860">This event collects the configuration information in settings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4861">Podatki nam omogočajo, da zaznamo primere, kjer je možno negativno vplivanje na sposobnost uporabnikov, Konfigurirajte nastavitve aplikacije, na primer nastavitve obvestil, primarni poštni račun in konfiguracijo e-poštnega podpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4861">The data allows us to detect situations where there is possible negative impact on the users’ ability configure app settings, such as notification settings, primary mail account, and configuring the email signature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4862">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4862">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4863">**account_order_changed** – preveri, ali ste spremenili vrstni red računov, in zagotovi, da ta konfiguracija deluje pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4863">**account_order_changed** - To check if you changed the order of your accounts to make sure this configuration works properly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4864">**action** – morebitna dejanja, izvedena v nastavitvah, kot je brisanje računa, ki so nam v pomoč pri zaznavanju težav in zagotavljanju, da ni negativnega učinka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4864">**action** - possible actions taken in settings, such as deleting an account to help us diagnose issues and ensure no negative impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4865">**auth_type** – vrsta preverjanja pristnosti, ki ga uporablja račun, za razumevanje uporabljene plasti sinhronizacije v zaledju pri diagnosticiranju težav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4865">**auth_type** - The authentication type being used by the account, so we understand which backend sync layer we are using to help us diagnose issues</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4866">**changed_folder** – ponazarja, ali je bila spremenjena mapa, in nam pomaga diagnosticirati težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4866">**changed_folder** - Capturing whether a folder was changed to help us diagnose issues.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4867">**delete_scope** – ali je bil med brisanjem računa račun izbrisan iz te naprave ali iz vseh naprav v Outlooku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4867">**delete_scope** - During an account deletion, whether you deleted the account from this device or from all devices with Outlook.</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4868">**enabled_state** – ali so pravilno konfigurirane nastavitve za samodejne odgovore, shranjevanje stikov in blokiranje zunanjih slik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4868">**enabled_state** - Whether your auto reply, save contacts, and block external images settings are configured correctly</span></span>  

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4869">**notification_action** – če želite preveriti, ali ste konfigurirali kakšno dejanje obvestila za Triaging e-poštna sporočila, ki nam bodo v pomoč pri zagotavljanju, da ta nastavitev deluje uspešno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4869">**notification_action** - To check if you have configured any notification actions for triaging emails to help us make sure this setting is working successfully</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4870">**notification_action_number** – če želite preveriti, ali so dejanja obvestila (dejanje ena ali dejanje dve) pravilno konfigurirana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4870">**notification_action_number** - To check if your notification actions (action one or action two) are configured correctly</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4874">**alternate_app_icon_setting** – izbrana ikona nadomestnega programa (svetlo, temno)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4874">**alternate_app_icon_setting** - the selected alternate app icon (light, dark)</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4875">**auth_type** – ponazarja vrsto preverjanja pristnosti v zaledju, s katero zaznamo, ali je prišlo do težave z določeno vrsto računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4875">**auth_type** - indicates the back-end authentication type allowing us to know if there is an issue with a particular account type</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4877">**changed_folder** – določa, ali je bilo to dejanje arhivirano, načrtovano oz. je bilo izvedeno drugo dejanje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4877">**changed_folder** - determines whether this action was archived, scheduled, or another action.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4880">**in_app_language** – izbrani jezik v aplikaciji, vrsta niza (privzeto, en-US, FA, ru ipd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4880">**in_app_language** - the selected in-app language, string type (default, en-US, fa, ru etc.)</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4881">**notification_action_setting** – označuje podrobnosti o nastavitvah dejanja obvestila, ki so povezane s tem dejanjem, če je to mogoče.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4881">**notification_action_setting** - indicates the details of, if applicable, notification action settings related to this action</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4886">**server_type** – ponazarja vrsto strežnika v zaledju, s katero zaznamo, ali je prišlo do težave z določeno vrsto strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4886">**server_type** - indicates the back-end server type allowing us to know if there is an issue with a particular server type</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4887">**source** – ponazarja vir obvestil nastavitev, če je to ustrezno, ali za nastavitev »Ne motite«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4887">**source** - indicates what is the source of notifications, if applicable, from settings or do not disturb setting</span></span>
   - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4888">**swipe_setting** – ponazarja podrobnosti nastavitev podrsljajev, povezane s tem dejanjem (če so na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4888">**swipe_setting** - indicates the details of, if applicable, swipe settings related to this action</span></span>
     - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4889">**swipe_action** – ponazarja dejanje, ki ga je poskušal izvesti uporabnik, npr. dodajanje zastavice, brisanje, arhiviranje. Omogoča nam, da ugotovimo, katero dejanje je uporabnik želel izvesti in ali je bilo to opravilo uspešno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4889">**swipe_action** - indicates what the user was trying to do, i.e. flag, delete, archive, it allows us to determine what action the user wanted and if the action failed or not.</span></span> 
     - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4890">**swipe_direction** – ponazarja nastavljeno smer za poteze podrsljajev, npr. od leve proti desni ali od desne proti levi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4890">**swipe_direction** - indicates which way the user set up the swipe to be, i.e. left to right or right to left.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4891">S tem dogodkom lahko ugotovimo, ali je prišlo do težave z določeno smerjo podrsljaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4891">This allows us to determine if there is a problem with a particular swipe direction.</span></span>

S tem dogodkom preverimo, ali ta nastavitev deluje pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4895">**swipe_action** - To check if you have configured any swipe actions for triaging emails to help us make sure this setting is working successfully</span></span>

#### <a name="sidebaraction"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4897">sidebar.action</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4897">sidebar.action</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4898">Omogoča nam, da odkrijemo primere morebitnega negativnega učinka na vašo zmožnost konfiguracije nastavitev aplikacije, na primer nastavitve obvestil, vaš primarni e-poštni račun in konfiguriranje vašega e-poštnega podpisa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4898">Allows us to detect situations where there is possible negative impact on your ability configure your app settings, such as your notification settings, your primary mail account, and configuring your mail signature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4899">Podatkovna polja, ki so pogosta za Outlook Mobile za ta dogodek v napravah s sistemom iOS in Android:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4899">Data fields that are common for Outlook Mobile for this event on iOS and Android:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4901">**action** – spremlja vrsto izvedenega dejanja stranske vrstice, npr. zavrženo, izbran gumb pomoči, stranska vrstica pošte itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4901">**action** - tracks the type of side bar action occurred, i.e. dismissed, help button selected, mail side bar, etc.,</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4902">**from_favorites** – spremlja, ali je bilo dejanje izvedeno iz priljubljenega elementa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4902">**from_favorites** - tracks if the action is coming from an item in favorites</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4903">**mail_folder_type** – vrsta izbrane mape med dejanjem stranske vrstice (če je bilo to izvedeno).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4903">**mail_folder_type** - what type of folder was selected during the side bar action, if any.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4904">**sidebar_type** – spremlja vrsto stranske vrstice, povezane s tem dogodkom, npr. pošta ali koledar. S tem dogodkom lahko zagotovimo pravilno delovanje nastavitve priljubljenih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4904">**sidebar_type** - tracks the type of side bar associated with this event, i.e. mail or calendar to helps us ensure the navigation from the favorites setting works properly</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4905">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4905">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4906">**account_type** – ponazarja vrsto računa za preverjanje pristnosti, npr. Gmail, Outlook itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4906">**account_type** - indicates what authentication type the account is i.e. Gmail, outlook, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4907">**account_has_groups** – s tem dogodkom preverimo, ali so v računu skupine in ali so nastavljeno pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4907">**account_has_groups** - Helps us make sure if the account has groups, they are configured correctly</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4908">**calendar_accounts_count** – ponazarja število računov koledarja. S tem dogodkom preverimo, ali so vaši računi koledarja nastavljeni pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4908">**calendar_accounts_count** - Number of calendar accounts you have to help us make sure your calendar accounts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4909">**calendar_apps_count** – ponazarja število aplikacij koledarja. S tem dogodkom preverimo, ali so vaše aplikacije koledarja nastavljene pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4909">**calendar_apps_count** - Number of calendar apps you have to help us make sure your interesting calendar apps are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4910">**calendar_type** – ponazarja vrsto koledarja (primarni koledar, koledar skupine itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4910">**calendar_type** - The type of calendar you have (Primary calendar, Group calendar, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4911">**has_favorite_folders** – s tem preverimo, ali so priljubljene mape pravilno nastavljene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4911">**has_favorite_folders** - Helps us make sure favorite folders are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4912">**has_favorite_people** – s tem preverimo, ali so priljubljene osebe/priljubljeni stiki pravilno nastavljeni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4912">**has_favorite_people** - Helps us make sure favorite people/contacts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4913">**has_group_calendar** – s tem preverimo, ali imate koledarje skupine in ali so ti pravilno nastavljeni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4913">**has_group_calendar** - Helps us make sure if you have group calendars, they are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4914">**has_group_calendar_account** – s tem preverimo, ali imate koledarje skupine in ali so ti pravilno nastavljeni.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4914">**has_group_calendar_account** - Helps us make sure if you have group calendars, they are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4915">**has_group_toggled** – s tem preverimo, ali ste preklopili na koledarje skupine in ali je ta nastavitev pravilno nastavljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4915">**has_group_toggled** - Helps us make sure if you have toggled group calendars, this setting is configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4916">**interesting_calendars_accounts_count** – ponazarja število zanimivih računov koledarja. S tem dogodkom preverimo, ali so vaši računi zanimivih koledarjev nastavljeni pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4916">**interesting_calendars_accounts_count** - Number of interesting calendar accounts you have to help us make sure your interesting calendar accounts are configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4917">**mail_accounts_count** – skupno število e-poštnih računov v stranski vrstici. S tem preverimo, ali je ta nastavitev nastavljena pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4917">**mail_accounts_count** - The total number of mail accounts in the sidebar to make sure this is configured correctly</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4918">**mail_folder_type** – vrsta mape, ki jo je izbral uporabnik. S tem preverimo, ali je ta nastavitev nastavljena pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4918">**mail_folder_type** - The type of folder the user tapped on to make sure it's configured correctly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4919">Vključuje lahko mape z izbrisanimi elementi, neželeno pošto ali poslanimi elementi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4919">This could include Deleted folder, Spam, or your Sent folder.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4920">**mail_inbox_unread_count** – s tem zagotovimo, ali je število neprebranih sporočil prikazano in nastavljeno pravilno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4920">**mail_inbox_unread_count** - Helps us ensure the unread count is displayed and configured accurately</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4921">**mail_subfolder_depth** – s tem zagotovimo, da lahko uspešno prikažemo konfiguracije podmape za pošto uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4921">**mail_subfolder_depth** - Helps us ensure we can successfully display a user's mail subfolder configurations</span></span>

#### <a name="storeop"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4922">StoreOp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4922">StoreOp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4923">Zbira, ko uporabnik poskuša odpreti dokument, zaščiten z upravljanjem pravic do informacij ali uporabiti zaščito za upravljanje pravic do informacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4923">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4924">Vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride, ko se izvede operacija shranjevanja dovoljenj storitev za upravljanje pravic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4924">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when Rights Management Service license store operation is performed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4925">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4925">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4926">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hierarhija odjemalcev, ki označuje, da se program izvaja v produkcijskem okolju ali v okolju razvijalcev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4926">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4927">**AppInfo.Name** – ime aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4927">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4928">**AppInfo.Version** – različica aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4928">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4929">**iKey** – ID strežnika za storitev pisanja dnevnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4929">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4930">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** – ID scenarija, ki ga je posredovala aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4930">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4931">**RMS.ContentId** – ID vsebine v končni uporabniški licenci</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4931">**RMS.ContentId** - Content Id in End User License</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4932">**RMS.Duration** – Skupen čas za izvedbo API priklica</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4932">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for API call to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4933">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – skupni čas minus zunanje operacije, kot je zakasnitev omrežja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4933">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4934">**RMS.ErrorCode** – koda napake je vrnjena, če izvira iz operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4934">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4935">**RMS.HttpCall** – označite, ali je prišlo do operacije HTTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4935">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is HTTP operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4936">**RMS.LicenseFormat** – oblika licence: Xrml ali Json</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4936">**RMS.LicenseFormat** - The license Format: Xrml or Json</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4937">**RMS.OperationName** – ime operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4937">**RMS.OperationName** - Operation name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4938">**RMS.Result** – uspeh ali neuspeh operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4938">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4939">**RMS.ScenarioId** – ID scenarija, ki ga je določil odjemalec storitve za upravljanje pravic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4939">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4940">**RMS.SDKVersion** – različica odjemalca storitve za upravljanje pravic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4940">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4941">**RMS.ServerType** – vrsta strežnika za upravljanje pravic do storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4941">**RMS.ServerType** - The type of Rights Management Service Server</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4942">**RMS.StatusCode** – koda stanja rezultata operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4942">**RMS.StatusCode** - Status code of the operation result</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4943">**RMS.Url** – URL strežnika za upravljanje pravic do storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4943">**RMS.Url** - The URL of Rights Management Service Server</span></span>

#### <a name="watchappv2"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4944">watchAppV2</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4944">watchAppV2</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4945">S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo in odpravimo morebitne zmogljivostne težave v vaši napravi Apple Watch, kot so prejemanje obvestil ali odgovarjanje na e-poštna sporočila.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4945">This event allows us to detect and fix possible issues with capabilities on your Apple Watch such as receiving notifications and responding to emails.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4946">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4946">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4947">**app_action** – ponazarja vrste dejanj, ki jih je uporabnik izvedel v napravi Apple Watch, npr. »archive_message«. S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo težave, povezane z določenim dejanjem, kot je neuspešno arhiviranje sporočil v napravi Apple Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4947">**app_action** - Tells us the types of action the user took on the Apple watch, such as "archive_message" to help us detect issues related to a specific action such as being unable to successfully archive messages on the Apple Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4948">**is_watch_app_installed** – ponazarja, ali je uporabnik v napravo namestil aplikacijo Apple Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4948">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user has installed our Apple Watch app on their device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4949">**is_complication_enabled** – ponazarja, ali je uporabnik na zaslon naprave Apple Watch dodal Outlook. S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo težave, povezane z zasloni naprave Apple Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4949">**is_complication_enabled** - Tells us if the user has added Outlook to their Apple Watch screen to help us detect issues related to Apple Watch screens</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4950">**watch_os** – ponazarja nameščeno različico operacijskega sistema za napravo Apple Watch. S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo težave, povezane z določenimi različicami operacijskega sistema za napravo Apple Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4950">**watch_os** - Tells us the OS version of the Apple Watch they have installed to help us detect issues related to specific OS versions of the Apple Watch</span></span>


### <a name="application-status-and-boot-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4951">*Stanje aplikacije in podvrsta zagona*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4951">*Application status and boot subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4952">Določanje, ali je prišlo do specifičnih dogodkov funkcije, kot sta zagon ali zaustavitev, in funkcije, ki se izvaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4952">Determination if specific feature events have occurred, such as start or stop, and if feature is running.</span></span>

#### <a name="appstartup"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4953">app.startup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4953">app.startup</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4954">S tem dogodkom lahko zaznavamo težave in jih odpravljamo, ko Outlook začne delovati počasneje ali neobičajno, kar uporabnikom otežuje uporabo aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4954">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook is starting slowly or incompletely, making it difficult for users to use our app.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4955">Dogodek vključuje informacije o posebnih omogočenih lastnosti in o tem, kako dolgi so posamezni deli zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4955">This includes information on the specific features that were enabled and how long parts of the startup took.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4956">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4956">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4957">**attach_base_context_millis** – čas med zagonom osnovnega konteksta in funkcije onCreate().</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4957">**attach_base_context_millis** - time between the base Context starting and onCreate() starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4958">**device_ram_in_mb** – RAM, ki je na voljo v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4958">**device_ram_in_mb** - the RAM available on the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4959">**has_company_portal** – ponazarja, ali je nameščena aplikacija portala podjetja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4959">**has_company_portal** - whether the company portal app is installed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4960">**hx_okhttp_mode** – ali komponenta nove storitve za sinhronizacijo e-pošte uporablja način OKHttp za pošiljanje in prejemanje omrežnih zahtev, ki temeljijo na protokolu HTTP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4960">**hx_okhttp_mode** - whether the new email syncing service component is using OKHttp for sending and receiving HTTP-based network requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4961">**initial_activity_name** – dejavnost sistema Android, ki je zagnala aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4961">**initial_activity_name** - the Android Activity which launched the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4962">**manufacturer** – proizvajalec naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4962">**manufacturer** - the device manufacturer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4963">**model** – model naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4963">**model** - the device model</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4964">**on_create_millis** – čas, zahtevan za funkcijo onCreate().</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4964">**on_create_millis** - time taken in the onCreate() method</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4965">**on_resume_millis** – čas, zahtevan za funkcijo onResume().</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4965">**on_resume_millis** - time taken in the onResume() method</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4966">**time_until_attach** – čas med nalaganjem razreda in zagonom osnovnega konteksta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4966">**time_until_attach** - time between the class loading and the base Context starting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4967">**total_millis** – skupni čas od začetka nalaganja razreda do dokončanja nadaljevanja dejavnosti v sistemu Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4967">**total_millis** - total time from class loading start to Android Activity resume completion</span></span>

#### <a name="boottime"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4968">boot.time</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4968">boot.time</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4969">S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo, kdaj se pojavijo kritične napake aplikacije, ki lahko povzročijo zrušitev aplikacije ali resne težave, kot so prazne vrstice v vašem nabiralniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4969">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred that would cause your app to crash or experience serious issues like causing you to see empty rows in your inbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4970">Ta dogodek zbira informacije, s katerimi lahko kategoriziramo in razvrščamo težave pri dodeljevanju prioritet za učinke težav na uporabnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4970">This event collects information that allows us to categorize and classify issues to help prioritize the impact of issues on customers.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4971">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4971">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4972">**black_list_reason** – prikaže, ali je na voljo razlog, da prezremo te podatke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4972">**black_list_reason** - Tells us if there is a reason why we should disregard this data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4973">Nekateri primeri vključujejo zagon zaradi oddaljenega obvestila in zagon zaradi pridobivanja v ozadju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4973">Some examples include launching due to a remote notification and launching due to a background fetch.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4974">**step_premain** – Sporoča, koliko časa je Outlook potreboval od trenutka, ko je uporabnik tapnil ikono do »glavnega« koraka step0_main, določenega v tem dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4974">**step_premain** – Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the user tapping the icon to step0_main the “main” step defined in this document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4975">**step0_main** – Prikaže čas, zahtevan, da je Outlook prešel na korak »main«, ki ga je določila družba Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4975">**step0_main** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to get to the "main" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4976">**step1_appWillFinishLaunching** – prikaže čas, zahtevan, da je Outlook iz koraka »main« prešel na korak »appWillFinishLaunching«, ki ga je določila družba Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4976">**step1_appWillFinishLaunching** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "main" step to the "appWillFinishLaunching" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4977">**step2_appDidFinishLaunching** – prikaže čas, zahtevan, da je Outlook iz koraka »appWillFinishLaunching« prešel na korak »appDidFinishLaunching«, ki ga je določila družba Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4977">**step2_appDidFinishLaunching** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "appWillFinishLaunching" step to the "appDidFinishLaunching" step, which is a step defined by Apple.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4978">**step3_engineStarted** – prikaže čas, zahtevan, da je Outlook iz koraka »appDidFinishLaunching« prešel na zagon mehanizma aplikacije, ki obravnava shranjevanje in sinhronizacijo podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4978">**step3_engineStarted** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "appDidFinishLaunching" step to starting the engine of the app, which handles storing and syncing data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4979">**step4_runLoopFirstIdle** – prikaže čas, zahtevan, da je Outlook iz koraka» engineStarted « prešel na stanje, v katerem dodatno delo ni več potrebno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4979">**step4_runLoopFirstIdle** - Tells us the amount of time it has taken for Outlook to go from the "engineStarted" step to having no additional work to complete.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4980">**total_time** – prikaže skupni čas, ki ga je Outlook potreboval za dokončanje zagona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4980">**total_time** - Tells us the total amount of time it has taken for Outlook to complete the boot process.</span></span>

#### <a name="dnslookupop"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4981">DnsLookupOp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4981">DnsLookupOp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4982">Zbira, ko uporabnik poskuša odpreti dokument, zaščiten z upravljanjem pravic do informacij ali uporabiti zaščito za upravljanje pravic do informacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4982">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4983">Vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride, ko se izvede operacija iskanja informacij o strežniku DNS.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4983">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when DNS information lookup operation is performed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4984">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4984">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4985">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hierarhija odjemalcev, ki označuje, da se program izvaja v produkcijskem okolju ali v okolju razvijalcev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4985">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4986">**AppInfo.Name** – ime aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4986">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4987">**AppInfo.Version** – različica aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4987">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4988">**iKey** – ID strežnika za storitev pisanja dnevnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4988">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4989">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** – ID scenarija, ki ga je posredovala aplikacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4989">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4990">**RMS.Duration** – Skupen čas za izvedbo operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4990">**RMS.Duration** - Total time for the operation to complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4991">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – skupni čas minus zunanje operacije, kot je zakasnitev omrežja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4991">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4992">**RMS.ErrorCode** – koda napake je vrnjena, če izvira iz operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4992">**RMS.ErrorCode** - The error code returned if any from the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4993">**RMS.HttpCall** – označite, ali je prišlo do operacije http</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4993">**RMS.HttpCall** - indicate if there is http operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4994">**RMS.LicenseFormat** – oblika licence: Xrml ali Json</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4994">**RMS.LicenseFormat** - The license Format: Xrml or Json</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4995">**RMS.NoOfDomainsSearched** – število iskanih domen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4995">**RMS.NoOfDomainsSearched** - The number of domains searched</span></span>    

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4996">**RMS.NoOfDomainsSkipped** – število preskočenih domen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4996">**RMS.NoOfDomainsSkipped** - The number of domains skipped</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4997">**RMS.Result** – uspeh ali neuspeh operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4997">**RMS.Result** - Success or fail of the operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4998">**RMS.ScenarioId** – ID scenarija, ki ga je določil odjemalec storitve za upravljanje pravic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4998">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-4999">**RMS.SDKVersion** – različica odjemalca storitve za upravljanje pravic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-4999">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5000">**RMS.ServerType** – vrsta strežnika za upravljanje pravic do storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5000">**RMS.ServerType** - The type of Rights Management Service Server</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5001">**RMS.StatusCode** – koda stanja rezultata operacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5001">**RMS.StatusCode** - Status code of the operation result</span></span>

#### <a name="firstvisible"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5002">first.visible</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5002">first.visible</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5003">Ta dogodek nam sporoča, ko uporabnik prvič interno zažene aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5003">This event lets us detect the first time the app is launched intentionally by the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5004">Ta dogodek potrebujemo zato, da lahko poskrbimo uspešno delovanje aplikacije v graditvah proizvajalca strojne opreme (OEM).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5004">This event is required to ensure that the app is successfully working in Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) builds.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5005">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5005">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5006">**is_oem** – sledenje polja, ki označuje, ali se aplikacija izvaja v različici OEM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5006">**is_oem** - a field tracking that indicates whether the application is running on an OEM variant</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5007">**is_system_install** – polje, ki spremlja prisotnost vnaprej nameščene datoteke lastnosti, ki bi morala označevati, da je ta graditev OEM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5007">**is_system_install** - a field tracking the presence of a pre-installed property file that should indicate that this install is OEM</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5008">**manufacturer** – proizvajalec naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5008">**manufacturer** - device manufacturer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5009">**model** – model naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5009">**model** - device model</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5010">**systemFlagSet** – vrednost zastavice sistema Android (ApplicationInfo.FLAG_SYSTEM), ki označuje, ali je bila aplikacija nameščena kot del slike sistema naprave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5010">**systemFlagSet** - value of the Android system flag (ApplicationInfo.FLAG_SYSTEM) that indicates if the application was installed as part of the device's system image</span></span>

#### <a name="getuserop"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5011">GetUserOp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5011">GetUserOp</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidaccountstorageinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5078">Office.Android.AccountStorageInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5078">Office.Android.AccountStorageInfo</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidoffice16bootlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5086">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5086">Office.Android.AndroidOffice16BootLatency</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5091">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila aplikacija prekinjena med zagonom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5091">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to indicate if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5092">**CollectionTime** – Čas dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5092">**CollectionTime** - Time of event</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5093">**FileActivationAttempted** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je prišlo do poskusa aktivacije datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5093">**FileActivationAttempted** - Boolean to indicate if file activation as attempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5094">**FirstIdleOnAppThreadTimeInMilliSec** – Čas nedejavnosti za nit aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5094">**FirstIdleOnAppThreadTimeInMilliSec** - App thread idle time</span></span>
