#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationhanging"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5257">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5257">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5258">Zbira podatke, ko zagon Officeovega dodatka traja nepričakovano dolgo (> 5 s).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5258">Collects when an Office add-in takes unexpectedly long to launch (>5 sec).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5259">Uporablja se za zaznavanje in odpravljanje težav pri zagonih Officeovih dodatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5259">Used to detect and fix problems with Office add-ins launching.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5260">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5260">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5261">**AppId** – ID aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5261">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5262">**AppInfo** – podatki glede vrste dodatka (podokno opravil ali UILess ali znotraj vsebine itd.) in vrste ponudnika (Omen, SharePoint, datotečni sistem itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5262">**AppInfo** - data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5263">**AppInstanceId** – ID primerka aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5263">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5264">**AssetId** – ID sredstva aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5264">**AssetId** - asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5265">**IsPreload** – označuje, ali je dodatek vnaprej naložen v ozadju, da izboljšate učinkovitost delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5265">**IsPreload** – indicates if the add-in is being preloaded in background for improving activation performance</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5266">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** – števec aktiviranih dodatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5266">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5267">**RemoterType** – določa vrsto remoterja (zaupanja vreden, ni vreden zaupanja, Win32webView, zaupanja vreden UDF itd.), ki se uporablja za aktiviranje dodatka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5267">**RemoterType** - specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5268">**StoreType** – izvor aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5268">**StoreType** - origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5269">**TimeForAuth** – čas, porabljen za preverjanje pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5269">**TimeForAuth** - time spent on auth</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5270">**TimeForSandbox** – čas, porabljen za peskovnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5270">**TimeForSandbox** - time spent on the sandbox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5271">**TimeForServerCall** – čas, porabljen za klic strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5271">**TimeForServerCall** - time spent on the server call</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5272">**TotalTime** – skupni porabljeni čas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5272">**TotalTime** - total time spent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5273">**UsesSharedRuntime** – Označuje, ali aplikacija uporablja sharedRuntime ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5273">**UsesSharedRuntime** - indicates if the app uses sharedRuntime or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeofficemobileappactivationlaunch"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5274">Office.OfficeMobile.AppActivation.Launch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5274">Office.OfficeMobile.AppActivation.Launch</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5275">Ta dogodek prepozna prvo aktiviranje in naslednja aktiviranja v zunanjih sprožilcih, ki aktivirajo aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5275">This event identifies first time and subsequent activations through external triggers that activate the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5276">Aktiviranje aplikacije naloži določene odvisnosti, zaradi katerih aplikacija nemoteno deluje, ta dogodek pa zabeleži, če so bile ustrezno naložene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5276">App activation loads certain dependencies that are responsible for making the app run smoothly and this event will record if it loaded successfully.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5277">Zabeležen je tudi vir aktiviranja in namen aplikacije, ki je odgovoren za aktiviranje aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5277">It will also record the source of activation and app intent that was responsible for activating the app</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5278">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5278">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5279">**ActionName** – Preslikava celoštevilske vrednosti v ime dejanja/funkcije, ki je priklicana iz točke aktiviranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5279">**ActionName** - Integer value mapping to the name of the action/feature which is invoked from the activation point.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5280">**ActivationType** – Preslikava celoštevilske vrednosti v vir aktiviranja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5280">**ActivationType** - Integer value mapping to the source of activation</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5281">**IsActionTriggered** – Logična vrednost, ki določa, ali je bilo dejanje sproženo po uspešnem aktiviranju aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5281">**IsActionTriggered** - Boolean value determining whether the action got triggered after the successful activation of the app.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5282">**IsFirstRun** – Logična vrednost, ki določa, ali gre za prvo izvajanje aplikacije oziroma nadaljnja izvajanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5282">**IsFirstRun** - Boolean value determining whether it was the first run of the app or a subsequent run.</span></span>
 

#### <a name="officeofficemobilefrefirstrunsetup"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5283">Office.OfficeMobile.FRE.FirstRunSetup</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5283">Office.OfficeMobile.FRE.FirstRunSetup</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5284">Ta dogodek signala obveščanja o izvajanju programa bo izzval prvi zagon aplikacije po namestitvi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5284">The first run of the app after installation will trigger this heartbeat event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5285">Pomagal bo identificirati namestitve in samodejne nadgradnje iz starejših različic aplikacije, z njim pa bomo lahko identificirali napake v samodejnih nadgradnjah, vključno z nalaganjem knjižnice in napakami prenosov razširitve/jezikovnega paketa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5285">It will help identify installs and auto upgrades from older versions of the app and enable us to identify errors in auto-upgrades, including library loads and expansion/language package download failures.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5286">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5286">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5287">**IsFlightAssigned** – Logična vrednost, ki določa, ali je bil uporabnik del kakršne koli vnaprej dodeljene preskusne skupine, ki lahko sproži izpostavljenost določenim izkušnjam.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5287">**IsFlightAssigned** - Boolean value determining if the user was part of any preassigned flight group which can trigger exposure to certain experiences.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5288">**IsFRELoadSuccessful** – Celo število, ki omenja stanje rezultata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5288">**IsFRELoadSuccessful** - integer mentioning the result state</span></span>

#### <a name="onenoteappappbootcomplete-previous-name-officeonenoteandroidappappbootcomplete-officeandroidearlytelemetryappbootcomplete"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5289">OneNote.App.AppBootComplete *(previous name)* , Office.OneNote.Android.App.AppBootComplete, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.AppBootComplete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5289">OneNote.App.AppBootComplete *(previous name)* , Office.OneNote.Android.App.AppBootComplete, Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.AppBootComplete</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5290">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja, da lahko novi uporabniki (Microsoftov račun) prvič uspešno zaženejo in začnejo uporabljati OneNote.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5290">The critical signal used to ensure new consumer users (Microsoft Account) can successfully launch and use OneNote for the first time.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5291">Uporablja se za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5291">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5292">Če uporabniki prvič ne morejo zagnati aplikacije, bo to sprožilo dogodek z visoko stopnjo resnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5292">If users can't launch the app for the first time, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5293">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5293">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5294">**ACTIVITY_BOOT_TIME_IN_MS** – Čas, zahtevan, za ustvarjanje dejavnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5294">**ACTIVITY_BOOT_TIME_IN_MS** - Time taken to complete Activity creation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5295">**ACTIVITY_NAME** – Ime dejavnosti, odprte pri zagonu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5295">**ACTIVITY_NAME** - Name of the Activity opened when booted</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5296">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** – Označuje, ali se med zagonom prikaže pogovorno okno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5296">**ANY_DIALOG_SHOWN** - Indicates if any dialog is shown during boot time</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5297">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** – označuje, ali je bil zagon izvedeno prej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5297">**APP_SUSPEND_DURING_EVENT** - Indicates if the boot was preempted</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5298">**APP_THREAD_CREATION_WAIT_TIME_TIME_FOR_APP_THREAD_CREATION** – Čas, zahtevan za ustvarjanje niti aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5298">**APP_THREAD_CREATION_WAIT_TIME_TIME_FOR_APP_THREAD_CREATION** - Time taken to create Application threads</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5299">**AVAILABLE_MEMORY_IN_MB** – Skupni pomnilnik, ki je na voljo v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5299">**AVAILABLE_MEMORY_IN_MB** - Total memory available in device</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5300">**AVG_SNAPSHOT_POPULATION_TIME** – Pov. čas, zahtevan za pridobivanje struktur zvezka med uporabo aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5300">**AVG_SNAPSHOT_POPULATION_TIME** - Avg. time taken to fetch notebook structures while using the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5301">**BOOT_END_AT_VIEW** – Podkategorija imena dejavnosti (ime pogleda).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5301">**BOOT_END_AT_VIEW** - Sub-category of Activity name (Name of the View)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5302">**BOOT_SNAPSHOTS** – Podrobnosti o pridobljenih strukturah zvezka za računa, uporabljene v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5302">**BOOT_SNAPSHOTS** - Detail of notebook structure fetches for the account(s) used in App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5303">**COREAPP_STARTUP_ACCOUNT_SETUP_STARTUP_ACCOUNT_SETUP** – Čas, zahtevan za preverjanje in zagon izkušnje enotne prijave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5303">**COREAPP_STARTUP_ACCOUNT_SETUP_STARTUP_ACCOUNT_SETUP** - Time taken to check and initiate SSO experience</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5304">**CRASH_INTERACTION_DURING_BOOT > 0** – Če želite označiti, ali je med zadnjo sejo prišlo do zrušitve aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5304">**CRASH_INTERACTION_DURING_BOOT> 0** - To indicate if the App crashed during last session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5305">**DALVIK_HEAP_LIMIT_IN_MB** – Zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5305">**DALVIK_HEAP_LIMIT_IN_MB** - Obsolete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5306">**DELAY_LOAD_STICKY_NOTES** – Označuje, ali imajo samolepljivi listki zakasnitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5306">**DELAY_LOAD_STICKY_NOTES** - Indicates if the Sticky Notes with delay or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5307">**FISHBOWL_SHOWN_DURING_EVENT** – Označuje primerke z nesinhronizirano vsebino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5307">**FISHBOWL_SHOWN_DURING_EVENT** - Indicates instances where content in not synced</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5371">Ta dogodek je zbran vsakokrat, ko PowerPoint odpre datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5371">Collected whenever PowerPoint opens a file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5372">Vsebuje informacije o uspehu, podrobnosti o napaki, metriko učinkovitosti delovanja in osnovne podrobnosti o datoteki, vključno z vrsto oblike zapisa datoteke ter metapodatki dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5372">Contains success information, failure details, performance metrics, and basic details about the file including file format type and document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5373">Te informacije so zahtevane, da PowerPoint lahko uspešno odpira datoteke in pri tem ne izgublja na učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5373">This information is necessary to ensure PowerPoint can open files successfully with no degradation in performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5374">Z njimi lahko diagnosticiramo težave, ki jih odkrijemo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5374">It allows us to diagnose any problems we discover.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5375">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5375">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5376">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult –** ali ima ta vnos dnevnika vso zahtevano telemetrijo dokumenta (polja Data\_Doc\_\*)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5376">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5377">**Data\_AddDocumentToMruList –** trajanje izvedbe za način AddDocumentToMruList</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5377">**Data\_AddDocumentToMruList -** Method AddDocumentToMruList execution duration</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5378">**Data\_AlreadyOpened –** ali je bil ta dokument že odprt (v kontekstu iste seje procesa)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5378">**Data\_AlreadyOpened -** Was this document previously opened (within the context of same process session)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5379">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod –** nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti za protivirusni pregled (IOAV, AMSI, None itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5379">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod -** Predefined set of values of type of anti-virus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptdesktopbootime"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5547">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5547">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5548">Dogodek za zbiranje načina zagona za PowrPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5548">Collecting how PowerPoint is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5549">Vključuje podatke o zagonu PowerPointa v zaščitnem načinu, o načinu branja s pomočjo, makru, tiskanju, novem in praznem dokumentu, obnovitvi dokumenta, avtomatizaciji in podatke o tem, ali uporablja tehnologijo zagona s klikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5549">It includes boot PowerPoint in protected view, in assisted reading mode, from Macro, print, new and blank document, document recovery, from automation and if it is click- to-run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5550">Prav tako zbira čas, zahtevan za zagon PowerPointa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5550">It also collects how long it takes PowerPoint to boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5551">Ti podatki so ključnega pomena za zagotovitev pravilnega zagona PowerPointa iz različnih načinov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5551">This data is critical to guarantee PowerPoint performs well when booted from different modes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5552">Microsoft te podatke uporablja za zbiranje časa o dolgem zagonu pri odpiranju PowerPointa iz različnih načinov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5552">Microsoft uses this data to catch long booting time when opening PowerPoint from different modes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5553">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5553">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5554">**AssistedReading –** v načinu branja s pomočjo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5554">**AssistedReading -** in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5555">**Automation –** iz avtomatiziranega načina</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5555">**Automation -** from automation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5556">**Benchmark –** zagon preizkusa zmogljivosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5556">**Benchmark -** run performance benchmark</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5557">**Blank –** prazen dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5557">**Blank -** blank document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5558">**BootTime –** čas, zahtevan za zagon seje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5558">**BootTime -** session boot time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5559">**Embedding –** vgrajeni dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5559">**Embedding -** embedding document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5560">**IsC2R –** ali omogoča tehnologijo zagona s klikom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5560">**IsC2R -** is click-to-run</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5561">**IsNew –** nov dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5561">**IsNew -** new document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5562">**IsOpen –** je odprt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5562">**IsOpen -** is open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5563">**Macro1 –** zaženi makro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5563">**Macro1 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5564">**Macro2 –** zaženi makro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5564">**Macro2 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5565">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** – v ukazni vrstici je preveč presledkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5565">**NonStandardSpaceInCmdLine** – there is non-standard space in command line</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5566">**Print –** natisni dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5566">**Print -** print document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5567">**PrintDialog –** natisni dokument s pogovornim oknom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5567">**PrintDialog -** print document with dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5568">**PrintPrinter –** natisni dokument s tiskalnikom</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5568">**PrintPrinter -** print document with printer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5569">**ProtectedView –** v zaščitenem pogledu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5569">**ProtectedView -** in protected view</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5570">**Regserver –** registriraj PowerPoint kot strežnik COM</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5570">**Regserver -** Register PowerPoint as a COM server</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5571">**Restore –** obnovi dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5571">**Restore -** restore document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5572">**Show –** pokaži dokument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5572">**Show -** show document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5573">**Time –** čas seje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5573">**Time -** session time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5587">**Data\_CacheFileSize –** velikost datoteke, če je bila datoteka predpomnjena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5587">**Data\_CacheFileSize -** If the file was cached, the size of the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5589">**Data\_IsInCache –** ali je bila datoteka odprta oziroma predpomnjena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5589">**Data\_IsInCache -** Whether the file opened was cached</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5595">Za zagon Projecta vam ni treba odpreti datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5595">Project is booted without opening a file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5596">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da je uporabnik odprl Office Project brez povezane datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5596">This event indicates that a user has opened Office Project without an associated file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5597">Vključuje kritične podatke o uspešnosti, s katerimi je mogoče zagotoviti, da Project lahko zaženete.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5597">It contains critical success data of making sure Project can start.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5598">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5598">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5599">**Data\_BootTime –** čas, zahtevan za zagon Projecta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5599">**Data\_BootTime -** The amount of time it took to boot Project</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5600">**Data\_FileLoaded –** ima vrednost false, če ste datoteko odprli iz zunanjega oz. novega praznega projekta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5600">**Data\_FileLoaded -** False if opening from out-space or new blank project</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5621">Velja za vse vrste Officeovih aplikacij v okolju sistema Windows: win32 and UWP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5621">Applicable to all the Office windows-based applications: win32 and UWP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5622">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5622">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5623">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** pošlje osnovne informacije ob zagonu nove Officeove seje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5623">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** sends basic information upon the start of a new Office session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5624">Ta dogodek se uporablja za štetje števila enoličnih sej, zaznanih v dani napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5624">This is used to count the number of unique sessions seen on a given device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5625">Ta dogodek se uporablja kot signal obveščanja o izvajanju aplikacije, s katerim se zagotovi, ali se aplikacija izvaja v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5625">This is used as a heartbeat event to ensure that the application is running on a device or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5626">Poleg tega se uporablja tudi kot kritičen signal za splošno zanesljivost aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5626">In addition, it serves as a critical signal for overall application reliability</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5627">**AppSessionGuid** – identifikator določene seje aplikacije, ki se je začela z ustvarjanjem procesa in traja vse do konca procesa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5627">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5628">Dogodek je oblikovan kot standardni 128-bitni GUID, sestavljen iz 4 delov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5628">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5629">Ti štirje deli v vrstnem redu so (1) 32-bitni ID procesa (2) 16-bitni ID seje (3) 16-bitni ID zagona (4) čas ustvarjanja 64-bitnega procesa v UTC 100ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5629">Those four parts in order are (1) 32 bit Process ID (2) 16 bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64 bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5630">**processSessionId** – naključno ustvarjeni GUID za prepoznavanje seje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5630">**processSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5631">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** – logična vrednost konstante.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5631">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5632">Vedno ima vrednost true.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5632">Always true.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5634">Označuje, da gre pri trenutni Officeovi seji za sejo prenosa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5634">Indicates that the current Office session is a handoff session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5635">To pomeni, da je obravnava uporabnikove zahteve za odpiranje dokumenta prenesena na primerek iste aplikacije, ki se že izvaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5635">This means that handling of a user's request to open a document is being handed off to an already running instance of the same application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5637">**ParentSessionId** – ID seje, ki bo prevzela obravnavo uporabnikove zahteve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5637">**ParentSessionId** - The ID of the session that will be taking over handling of the users' request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5647">**SessionId** – naključno ustvarjeni GUID za prepoznavanje seje aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5647">**SessionID** - Randomly generated GUID to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5664">**Data_AppBootTime** – trajanja zagona aplikacije v milisekundah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5664">**Data_AppBootTime** - Duration taken for app to boot, in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopencmdfilemrupriv"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5670">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5670">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5671">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da je Microsoft Office Word odprl dokument s seznama nedavno uporabljenih elementov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5671">This event indicates Office Word opens a document from the Most Recent Used (MRU) list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5672">Poleg tega vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5672">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5673">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Odpri datoteko s seznama nazadnje uporabljenih datotek« deluje v skladu s pričakovanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5673">The event monitors whether fileopen-from-MRU is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5674">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5674">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5675">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5675">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5676">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5676">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5677">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5677">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5678">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega je morda mogoče odpreti datoteko, če ga pridobimo, preden uporabnik začne urejati dokument oz. se ga morda odloči shraniti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5678">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5679">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega morda lahko odpremo datoteko, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5679">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5680">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5680">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5681">**Data_BytesUnknown** – število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5681">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5682">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5682">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5683">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5683">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenffileopenxstzcore"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5737">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5737">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5738">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word odpira dokument, ki ga je uporabnik dvokliknil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5738">This event indicates Office Word opens a document who is double clicked by a user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5739">Poleg tega vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5739">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5740">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Odpri datoteko z dvoklikom« deluje v skladu s pričakovanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5740">The event monitors whether file-openfrom-file-double-click is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5741">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5741">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5742">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5742">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5743">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5743">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5744">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5744">Used for data quality diagnostics</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5745">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega je morda mogoče odpreti datoteko, če ga pridobimo, preden uporabnik začne urejati dokument oz. se ga morda odloči shraniti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5745">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5746">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega morda lahko odpremo datoteko, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5746">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5747">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5747">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5748">**Data_BytesUnknown** – število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5748">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5749">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5749">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5750">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5750">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5751">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5751">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5752">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5752">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5753">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enote, uporabljene za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5753">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5754">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5754">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5755">**Data_Doc_Ext** – pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5755">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenifrinitargs"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5804">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5804">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5805">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word odpira dokument s pomočjo aktivacije modula COM ali ukazne vrstice.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5805">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via COM activation or command line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5806">Prav tako vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5806">It also contains critical file open performance data, and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5807">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Odpri datoteko iz ukazne vrstice« deluje običajno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5807">The event monitors whether file-open-from-command-line is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5808">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5808">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5809">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5809">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5810">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes** – Poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5810">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes -** Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5811">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5811">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5812">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous –** število bajtov (stisnjenih), za katerega menimo, da lahko odpremo datoteko brez tega števila, če jih pridobimo, preden uporabnik želi začeti urejati dokument oz. ga morda shraniti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5812">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5813">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork –** število bajtov (stisnjenih), pri katerem morda še lahko odpremo datoteko brez tega števila, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5813">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5814">**Data\_BytesSynchronous –** število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5814">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5815">**Data\_BytesUnknown –** število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5815">**Data\_BytesUnknown -** Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5816">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode –** dokument je samo za branje ali omogoča urejanje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5816">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5817">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons** – Nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5817">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5818">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5818">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5819">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType** – Enote, ki se uporabljajo za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5819">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5820">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState –** nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5820">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5821">**Data\_Doc\_Ext –** pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5821">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5822">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat –** različica protokola za obliko zapisa dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5822">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5823">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn** – Ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5823">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5824">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash** – Enostranska zgoščena vrednost imena domene, ki omogoča identifikacijo stranke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5824">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5825">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags –** poroča predpomnjenje zastavice za nastavitev možnosti odprtih zahtev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5825">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5826">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId –** enosmerna razpršitev identitete uporabnika, ki je bila uporabljena za odpiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5826">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5827">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario –** zapiše način, uporabljen za odpiranje dokumenta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5827">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario -** Records how the document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5856">**Data\_LastLoggedTag –** enolična oznaka za mesto klica kode, ki se uporablja za prepoznavanje, ko poskušamo izvesti neuspešno odpiranje dvakrat zapored (se uporablja za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5856">**Data\_LastLoggedTag -** Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5862">**Data\_MoveFlightEnabled –** ali je omogočen let za funkcijo premikanja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5862">**Data\_MoveFlightEnabled -** Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5863">**Data\_PartsUnknown –** število delov dokumenta, za katere nismo uspeli pridobiti podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5863">**Data\_PartsUnknown -** the number of document parts that we couldn't get data for</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenloadfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5870">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5870">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5871">Ta dogodek ponazarja, da Microsoft Office Word odpira dokument s pomočjo pogovornega okna za odpiranje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5871">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via Open dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5872">Poleg tega vsebuje kritične podatke o učinkovitosti odpiranja datotek in z vidika uporabnika predstavlja dogodek za zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5872">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5873">Dogodek nadzira, ali funkcija »Odpri datoteko v pogovornem oknu za odpiranje datotek« deluje v skladu s pričakovanji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5873">The event monitors whether file-open-from-the-open-filedialog is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5874">Prav tako se uporablja za izračunane mesečne aktivne uporabnike/naprave in za metriko zanesljivosti v oblaku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5874">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5875">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5875">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5876">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – poroča, ali lahko pravilno dopolnimo druge vrednosti dogodka, povezane s telemetrijo dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5876">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5877">Uporablja se za diagnostiko kakovosti podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5877">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5878">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega je morda mogoče odpreti datoteko, če ga pridobimo, preden uporabnik začne urejati dokument oz. se ga morda odloči shraniti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5878">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5879">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), brez katerega morda lahko odpremo datoteko, vendar bi zato morali občutno spremeniti kodo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5879">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5880">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – število bajtov (stisnjenih), ki ga moramo pridobiti, preden lahko odpremo datoteko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5880">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5881">**Data_BytesUnknown** – število bajtov v delih dokumenta, za katerega menimo, da ga ne bomo našli.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5881">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don't expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5882">**Data_DetachedDuration** – koliko časa je bila dejavnost ločena od niti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5882">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5883">**Data.Doc.AccessMode** – dokument je samo za branje/ga je mogoče urejati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5883">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5884">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – nabor vnaprej določenih vrednosti, zakaj je bil dokument odprt v načinu vodenega branja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5884">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5885">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Označuje, ali se je odprla predpomnjena različica dokumenta v oblaku in katera logika asinhronega osveževanja je bila uporabljena.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5885">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5886">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – enote, uporabljene za postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5886">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5887">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – nastavitev elektronske zaščite podatkov dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5887">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5888">**Data_Doc_Ext** – pripona dokumenta (docx/xlsb/pptx itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5888">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5889">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – različica protokola za obliko zapisa datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5889">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5890">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – ime domene za OneDrive ali SharePoint Online.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5890">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5891">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost imena domene, ki omogoča identifikacijo stranke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5891">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5892">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – enostranska zgoščena vrednost identitete uporabnika, uporabljena za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5892">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5893">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – zabeleži način odpiranja dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5893">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5894">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – poroča o predpomnjenih zastavicah, uporabljenih za nastavitev možnosti zahtev za odpiranje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5894">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5895">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – dejanja, ki jih je dovolil pravilnik za elektronsko zaščito podatkov, ki velja za dokument/uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5895">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5896">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – zastavica, ki označuje postopno odpiranje dokumenta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5896">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5897">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – zastavica, ki označuje, da je storitev sodelovanja podprta v dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5897">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5898">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – zastavica, ki označuje, da je bila odprta kopija dokumenta brez povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5898">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

#### <a name="officeaccessibilityaccessibilitytoolsessionpresencewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5978">Office.Accessibility.AccessibilityToolSessionPresenceWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5978">Office.Accessibility.AccessibilityToolSessionPresenceWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5979">Omogoča nam, da odkrijemo uporabnikovo orodje za pomoč uporabnikom s posebnimi potrebami in njegovo ime.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5979">Allows us to detect that the user has an Assistive technology tool and its name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5980">S pomočjo tega dogodka vidimo, ali ima Officeov uporabnik težave z določenim orodjem za pomoč uporabnikov s posebnimi potrebami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5980">This allows us to understand if an Office user is experiencing issues with a specific Assistive Technology tool.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5981">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5981">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5982">**Data\_Data\_Jaws –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljal bralnik Jaws **Data\_Data\_Magic –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljalo orodje Magic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5982">**Data\_Data\_Jaws -** indicates if Jaws was running during the session **Data\_Data\_Magic -** indicates if Magic was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5983">**Data\_Data\_Magnify –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje povečave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5983">**Data\_Data\_Magnify -** indicates if Magnify was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5984">**Data\_Data\_Narrator –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljal pripovedovalec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5984">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** indicates if Narrator was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5985">**Data\_Data\_NVDA –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje NVDA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5985">**Data\_Data\_NVDA -** indicates if NVDA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5986">**Data\_Data\_SA –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje SA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5986">**Data\_Data\_SA -** indicates if SA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5987">**Data\_Data\_Supernova –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje Supernova</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5987">**Data\_Data\_Supernova -** indicates if Supernova was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5988">**Data\_Data\_SuperNovaessSuite –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje SuperNovaAccessSuite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5988">**Data\_Data\_SuperNovaessSuite -** indicates if SuperNovaAccessSuite was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5989">**Data\_Data\_WinEyes –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje WinEyes</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5989">**Data\_Data\_WinEyes -** indicates if WinEyes was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5990">**Data\_Data\_ZoomText –** ponazarja, ali se je med sejo uporabljajo orodje ZoomText</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5990">**Data\_Data\_ZoomText -** indicates if ZoomText was running during the session</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappledarkmode"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5991">Office.Apple.DarkMode</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5991">Office.Apple.DarkMode</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5992">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5992">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5993">Dogodek nam pove, ali je uporabnik zagnal sistem v načinu DarkMode in ali je uporabnik prepisal nastavitev sistema DarkMode v Officeu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5993">The event tells us if user is running a System on DarkMode and whether the user overwrote the DarkMode System setting in Office.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5994">Ta dogodek nam pomaga zagotoviti dostopnost in prednostno obravnavo optimizacije uporabniške izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5994">We use this event to help ensure accessibility and prioritize user-experience optimization.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5995">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5995">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5996">**Data_DarkModeIsEnabled** – označuje, ali je v sistemu omogočen način DarkMode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5996">**Data_DarkModeIsEnabled** - Whether DarkMode is enabled in the system.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5997">**Data_RequiresAquaSystemAppearanceEnabled** – označuje, ali je v Officeu prepisan način DarkMode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5997">**Data_RequiresAquaSystemAppearanceEnabled** - Whether DarkMode is overwritten in Office.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-5999">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-5999">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6000">Dogodek nam pove, da ima uporabnik na svojo prenosno napravo priključeno tipkovnico.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6000">The event tells us that a user is attaching a keyboard to their mobile device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6001">Dogodek nam pomaga pri izboljšanju dostopnosti in optimizaciji uporabniške izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6001">The event helps us improve accessibility and optimize our user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6002">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6002">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6003">**Data_CollectionTime** – časovni žig, ki označuje čas zbiranja dogodka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6003">**Data_CollectionTime** - A timestamp denoting the event collection time.</span></span>

### <a name="privacy-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6043">*Podvrsta zasebnosti*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6043">*Privacy subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6044">Nastavitve zasebnosti za Office</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6044">Office privacy settings</span></span> 

#### <a name="officeintelligentserviceprivacyconsentprivacyevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6045">Office.IntelligentService.PrivacyConsent.PrivacyEvent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6045">Office.IntelligentService.PrivacyConsent.PrivacyEvent</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6046">Ta dogodek predstavlja dejanje uporabnika ali sistema, ki je del uporabniške izkušnje z zasebnostjo za Office.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6046">This event represents a user or system initiated action that is part of the privacy User experience for Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6047">Aktivira se v pogovornih oknih zasebnosti ob prvem zagonu, pogovornem oknu zasebnosti računa in obvestilih o zasebnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6047">It is triggered on the privacy First Run dialogs, Account Privacy dialog, and privacy notifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6048">Dogodek se uporablja za naslednje: razumevanje soglasja uporabnikov za nastavitve zasebnosti za Office, uporabnikovo spreminjanje nastavitev zasebnosti za Office in za posodabljanje nastavitev zasebnosti za Office v uporabniških sejah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6048">The event is used to understand the following: users consenting to Office privacy settings, users changing Office privacy settings, and Office privacy settings getting updated in user sessions.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6049">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6049">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6050">**Data_ActionId –** dejanje uporabnika v pogovornem oknu zasebnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6050">**Data_ActionId -** User action in a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6051">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState –** nastavitev pravilnika uporabnika za dodatne izbirne povezane izkušnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6051">**Data_ControllerConnectedServicesState -** User policy setting for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6052">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState –** nastavitev uporabnika za preneseno vsebino</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6052">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for downloaded content</span></span> 
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6053">**Data_ForwardLinkId –** povezava do dokumentacije o zasebnosti za scenarij uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6053">**Data_ForwardLinkId -** Link to privacy documentation for the user scenario</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6054">**Data_HRESULT –** zapisovanje napak med interakcijo v pogovornem oknu zasebnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6054">**Data_HRESULT -** Record of errors during interaction with a privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6055">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser –** kategorija licenc uporabnikov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6055">**Data_IsEnterpriseUser -** User license category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6056">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState –** nastavitev uporabnika za povezane storitve</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6056">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState -** User setting for connected services</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6057">**Data_RecordRegistry –** zapis, ki prikazuje pogovorno okno zasebnosti podjetja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6057">**Data_RecordRegistry -** Record of showing the enterprise privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6058">**Data_Scenario –** prvi scenarij, izveden glede na licenco uporabnika in kategorijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6058">**Data_Scenario -** First run scenario based on the user license and category</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6059">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog –** zapis, ki prikazuje pogovorno okno zasebnosti za člane programa Insider</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6059">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog -** Record of showing the Insiders privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6060">**Data_SendTelemetryOption –** nastavitev uporabnika za telemetrijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6060">**Data_SendTelemetryOption -** User setting for telemetry</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6061">**Data_SendTelemetryOptionPolicy –** nastavitev pravilnika uporabnika za telemetrijo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6061">**Data_SendTelemetryOptionPolicy -** User policy setting for telemetry</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6062">**Data_UserCategory –** vrsta uporabniškega računa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6062">**Data_UserCategory -** User account type</span></span>  

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6063">**Data_UserCCSDisabled –** preglasitev uporabnika za dodatne izbirne povezane izkušnje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6063">**Data_UserCCSDisabled -** User override for additional optional connected experiences</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6064">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState –** nastavitev uporabnika za analizo vsebine</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6064">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for analyzing content</span></span>

## <a name="product-and-service-performance-data-events"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6066">Dogodki podatkov o učinkovitosti delovanja izdelkov in storitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6066">Product and service performance data events</span></span>
