- [<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6068">Nepričakovan izhod iz aplikacije (zrušitev)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6068">Unexpected application exit (crash)</span></span>](#unexpected-application-exit-crash-subtype)
- [<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6069">Učinkovitost delovanja funkcije aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6069">Application feature performance </span></span>](#application-feature-performance-subtype)
- [<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6070">Napaka pri dejavnosti aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6070">Application activity error</span></span>](#application-activity-error-subtype)

### <a name="unexpected-application-exit-crash-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6071">*Podvrsta nepričakovanega izhoda iz aplikacije (zrušitev)*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6071">*Unexpected application exit (crash) subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6072">Aplikacija se nepričakovano zapre in stanje te aplikacije, ko pride do tega.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6072">Unexpected application exits and the state of the application when that happens.</span></span>

#### <a name="appstartupreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6073">app.startup.reason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6073">app.startup.reason</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6074">S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo in odpravljamo težave, zaradi katerih se je Outlook zrušil med zagonom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6074">This event lets us detect and fix issues where Outlook crashed during app start up.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6075">Ta dogodek vključuje informacije o zrušitvi, tako da lahko težavo hitro odpravimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6075">This event includes information on why the crash happened so we can fix the issue quickly.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6076">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6076">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6077">**app_background_time** – čas, ko je bila aplikacija v ozadju med zadnjo sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6077">**app_background_time** - duration of how long app was in background last session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6078">**startup_reason_type** – prikaže razlog za zagon aplikacije, npr. zaradi prisilne zaustavitve ali drugega razloga.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6078">**startup_reason_type** - indicates why the app is starting up, this will indicate if it was due to force quit, or other reason.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6079">**watch_status_info** – spremlja naslednje informacije (če so na voljo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6079">**watch_status_info** - keeps track of the following information, if applicable.</span></span> 

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6080">**is_watch_app_installed** – ugotovi, ali je uporabnik namestil aplikacijo Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6080">**is_watch_app_installed** - determines if the user has the Watch app installed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6081">**is_watch_paired** – ugotovi, ali je naprava iOS seznanjena z uro.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6081">**is_watch_paired** - determines if iOS device is paired to a watch</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6082">**is_watch_supported_and_active** – prikaže, ali je ura podprta in aktivna med sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6082">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - indicates whether a watch is supportive and active during the session</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6083">Ta polja so zbrana samo za aplikacijo Outlook Mobile za iOS:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6083">The following fields are collected for only Outlook Mobile for iOS:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6084">**clean_exit_reason** – niz besed, ki ponazarjajo, ali je bil na voljo razlog za ustavitev aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6084">**clean_exit_reason** - A string of words indicating why if there was a reason for the app stop</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6085">**is_agenda_user** – prikaže, ali je uporabnik pred kratkim odprl dnevni red, kar pomeni, da med zagonom zapisujemo podatke na disk.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6085">**is_agenda_user** - Indicates if the user has opened the agenda recently which indicates if we are writing disk on the startup</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6086">**is_watch_supported_and_active** – prikaže, ali je ura podprta in aktivna med sejo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6086">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - indicates whether a watch is supportive and active during the session</span></span>


#### <a name="applicationcrash"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6087">application.crash</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6087">application.crash</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6088">Se uporablja za nadzor kritičnih zrušitev aplikacije. S tem dogodkom zbiramo informacije o razlogih za zrušitev aplikacije in o tem, kako preprečiti zrušitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6088">Used for monitoring critical app crashes and helps us collect information on why the app has crashed and how to prevent it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6089">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6089">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6090">**android.hardware.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6090">**android.hardware.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6091">– vrednosti za konfiguracijo strojne opreme, ki jih posreduje okolje Android (npr. android.hardware.bluetooth).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6091">- (e.g. android.hardware.bluetooth) Hardware configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6092">**android.software.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6092">**android.software.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6093">– vrednosti za konfiguracijo programske opreme, ki jih posreduje okolje Android (npr. android.software.device_admin).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6093">- (e.g. android.software.device_admin) Software configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6094">**android_version** – ime različice naprave Android, kot ga navaja android.os.Build.VERSION#RELEASE.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6094">**android_version** - Device android version name as indicated by android.os.Build.VERSION#RELEASE</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6095">**application_package_name** – ime paketa aplikacije, kot ga navaja android.content.Context#getPackageName().</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6095">**application_package_name** - Application package name as indicated by android.content.Context#getPackageName()</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6096">**application_stack_trace** – sled sklada zrušitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6096">**application_stack_trace** - the stack trace of the crash</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6097">**application_version_code** – koda različice aplikacije, ki jo določa aplikacija Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6097">**application_version_code** - Application version code defined by the Outlook app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6098">**application_version_name** – ime različice aplikacije, ki jo določa aplikacija Outlook.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6098">**application_version_name** - Application version name defined by the Outlook app</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6099">**com.**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6099">**com.**</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6100">– konfiguracijske vrednosti proizvajalca, ki jih posreduje okolje Android (npr. com.google.android.feature.FASTPASS_BUILD, com.amazon.feature.PRELOAD, com.samsung.android.bio.face).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6100">(e.g. com.google.android.feature.FASTPASS_BUILD, com.amazon.feature.PRELOAD, com.samsung.android.bio.face) Manufacturer specific configuration values provided by the Android platform</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6101">**crash_report_sdk** -SDK za pošiljanje dnevnikov zrušitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6101">**crash_report_sdk** - SDK to send crash logs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6102">Hokejski ali AppCenter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6102">Either Hockey or AppCenter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6103">**crash_type** – crash_type bo vsebovala Javo kot vrste, ki niso usodne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6103">**crash_type** - crash_type will have java, native, non-fatal as types.</span></span>

     - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6104">Java – IF je bila zabeležena na plast aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6104">java - if crash recorded on application Layer.</span></span>

     - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6105">izvorno – če je bila zrušitev zabeležena na izvorni ravni v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6105">native - if crash recorded on native layer within the app.</span></span> 

     - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6106">ne-usodne zrušitve so zapisana, da odpravijo katerokoli značilnost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6106">non-fatal - crashes being recorded to debug any feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6107">Aplikacija ne bo trčila, vendar bo naložila dnevnike neusodne zrušitve za pomoč pri odpravljanju težav s funkcijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6107">Application won’t crash but it will upload non-fatal crash logs to help in debugging a feature.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6108">**device_brand** – blagovna znamka naprave (proizvajalec ali operater), kot jo navaja android.os.Build#BRAND.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6108">**device_brand** - Device brand (manufacturer or carrier) as indicated by android.os.Build#BRAND</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6109">**device_ID** – enolični ID naprave (IMEI).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6109">**device_ID** - Device unique ID (IMEI)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6110">**device_manufacturer** – proizvajalec naprave, kot ga navaja android.os.Build#MANUFACTURER.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6110">**device_manufacturer** - Device manufacturer as indicated by android.os.Build#MANUFACTURER</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6111">**device_model** – model naprave, kot ga navaja android.os.Build#MODEL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6111">**device_model** - Device model as indicated by android.os.Build#MODEL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6112">**device_name** – ime naprave, kot ga navaja android.os.Build#DEVICE.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6112">**device_name** - Device name as indicated by android.os.Build#DEVICE</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6113">**device_total_memory** – ocena skupne velikosti pomnilnika naprave glede na statistične podatke datotečnega sistema.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6113">**device_total_memory** - Estimation of the total device memory size based on filesystem stats.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6114">**glEsVersion** – ključ različice za vdelane sisteme OpenGL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6114">**glEsVersion** - OpenGL Embedded Systems version key</span></span>


#### <a name="crashevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6115">crash.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6115">crash.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6116">Omogoča, da zaznamo in odpravimo primere, pri katerih je prišlo do kritičnih zrušitev aplikacije. S tem dogodkom zbiramo informacije o razlogih za zrušitev aplikacije in o tem, kako preprečiti zrušitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6116">Allows us to detect and fix situations where critical app crashes have occurred and helps us collect information on why the app has crashed and how to prevent it.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6117">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6117">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6118">**crashTime** – datum in čas zrušitve, ki sta nam v pomoč pri preiskavi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6118">**crashTime** - Date and time the crash occurred to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6119">**crash_time_from_start** – Čas, ki je pretekel od zagona aplikacije do zrušitve, za namene podpore pri raziskavi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6119">**crash_time_from_start** – The elapsed time from app start to the crash occurred, to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6120">**exceptionName** – Ime izjeme, ki je sprožila zrušitev, za namene podpore pri raziskavi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6120">**exceptionName** - The name of the exception that triggered the crash to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6121">**exception_reason** – Razlog izjeme, ki je sprožila zrušitev, za namene podpore pri raziskavi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6121">**exception_reason** – The reason of the exception that triggered the crash to help with investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6122">**hasHx** – dogodek, ki ponazarja, da račun uporablja našo novo storitev sinhronizacije, s katerim je mogoče zaznati težave, ki jih povzroči naša storitev sinhronizacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6122">**hasHx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6123">**incidentIdentifier** – Enolični ID za poročilo o zrušitvi, da bomo lahko našli ustrezno težavo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6123">**incidentIdentifier** - A unique ID for the crash report so we can find the corresponding issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6124">**isAppKill** – Pomaga nam ugotoviti, ali je bila aplikacija prisilno zaustavljena ali zaprta v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6124">**isAppKill** - Helps us understand if that app was killed or close on the device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6125">**is_crashloop** – Pomaga nam razumeti, ali gre pri zrušitvi morda za zanko zrušitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6125">**is_crashloop** – Helps us understand if the crash could likely be a crash loop.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6126">**reportKey** – Enoličen ID za namestitev aplikacije iz naprave za namene preiskave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6126">**reportKey** - A unique ID for the application installation om the device for issue investigation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6127">**signal** – signal, ki je povzročil zrušitev, in vsebuje podrobnosti za preiskavo te zrušitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6127">**signal** - A signal that caused the crash to give us more details to investigate this crash</span></span>


#### <a name="error"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6128">Napaka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6128">Error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6129">Pomaga nam razumeti težave, do katerih lahko pride, ko mobilne aplikacije poskušajo pridobiti nastavitve zasebnosti iz strežnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6129">Allows us to understand the issues that mobile apps are facing when attempting to fetch privacy settings from the server.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6130">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6130">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6131">**correlationId** – enoličen identifikator za storitev povezave, ki je javila napako. Omogoča nam, da diagnosticiramo morebiten vzrok napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6131">**correlationId** - a unique identifier for a service connection that resulted in an error, allowing us to diagnose what might have gone wrong</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6132">**errorCode** – prepozna ustrezno kodo napake, prejeto iz storitve, ki jo lahko uporabimo za diagnosticiranje težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6132">**errorCode** - identifies the relevant error code received from the service that could be used to diagnose the problem</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6133">**exceptionType** – vrsta napake, na katero je naletela knjižnica med pridobivanjem nastavitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6133">**exceptionType** - type of error that the library encountered when fetching the setting</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6134">**message** – prepozna sporočilo napake, prejeto od storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6134">**message** - identifies the error message received from the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6135">**roamingSettingType** – prepozna mesto, s katerega smo poskušali prebrati nastavitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6135">**roamingSettingType** - identifies the location from which we attempt to read settings</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6136">**settingId** – nastavitev, ki jo je sitem poskušal pridobiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6136">**settingId** - the setting that was attempted to be fetched</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappdomainunhandledexceptionhandlerfailed"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6137">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6137">Office.AppDomain.UnhandledExceptionHandlerFailed</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6138">Zbira informacije za morebitne neobravnavane izjeme z orodjem za pretakanje podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6138">Collects information for any unhandled exceptions using the Data Streamer App.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6139">Ti podatki se uporabljajo za nadzor stanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6139">This data is used to monitor the health of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6140">Ta dogodek ustvari Microsoftovo orodje za pretakanje podatkov za Excelov dodatek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6140">This event is generated by Microsoft Data Streamer for Excel Add-in.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6141">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6141">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6142">**Exception** – nabor klicev za izjemo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6142">**Exception** - Call stack for the Exception</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6143">**Event Name** – Kategorija dogodka in oznaka dogodka predstavljata ime dogodka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6143">**Event Name** - Event Name is the Event Category and Event Label.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappleidentitydomainname"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6144">Office.Apple.IdentityDomainName</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6144">Office.Apple.IdentityDomainName</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6145">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6145">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6146">Dogodek uporabljamo za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja sistema in preiskovanje vzrokov napak nekaterih uporabnikov domene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6146">The event is used to monitor the health of our system as well as investigating causes of failures by certain domain users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6147">Zbiramo podatke o domeni, ki jo uporabljajo naši uporabniki pri preverjanju pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6147">We collect the domain used by our users when they authenticate.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6148">Ti podatki nam pomagajo prepoznati in odpraviti težave, ki se morda na širši ravni ne zdijo preveč vplivne, za določeno domeno uporabnikov pa se izkažejo za zelo vplivne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6148">We use this data to help identify and fix those issues that might not seem too impactful at a broader level, but that turn out to be very impactful to a certain domain of users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6149">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6149">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6150">**Data_Domain** – domena, ki se uporablja za preverjanje pristnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6150">**Data_Domain** - the domain used for authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6151">**Data_IdentityProvider** – ime ponudnika identitete za preverjanje pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6151">**Data_IdentityProvider** - The authentication identity provider name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6152">(npr. LiveId ali ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6152">(i.e. LiveId or ADAL)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6153">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** – koda ponudnika identitete za preverjanje pristnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6153">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** - The authentication identity provider code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6154">(Število)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6154">(A number)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeapplesystemhealthappexitmacandios"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6155">Office.Apple.SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6155">Office.Apple.SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6156">Ta dogodek zbiramo za Officeove aplikacije, ki se izvajajo na platformah Apple.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6156">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6157">Dogodek uporabljamo za nadzorovanje ustreznosti stanja Officeovih aplikacij in preiskovanje vzrokov napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6157">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6158">Zbiramo podatke o posameznem izhodu iz aplikacije, da bi ugotovili, ali se je aplikacija zaprla brez napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6158">We collect data on each application exit to determine whether an application exited gracefully.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6159">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6159">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6160">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** – identifikator seje, pri kateri je prišlo do izhoda iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6160">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** - The identifier for the session that experience the application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6161">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** – podrazličica aplikacije, pri kateri je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6161">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6162">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** – dolžina seje od začetka do izhoda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6162">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** - The length of the session from start to exit</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6163">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** – kazalnik ustreznosti stanja telemetrije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6163">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6164">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** – kazalnik ustreznosti stanja telemetrije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6164">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6165">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** – območne nastavitve operacijskega sistema, v katerem je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6165">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** - The Locale of the OS under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6166">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** – različica operacijskega sistema, v katerem je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6166">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** - The OS version under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6167">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** – prostor v stalnem pomnilniku, ki je bil zaseden, ko je prišlo do izhoda iz aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6167">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of resident memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6168">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** – identifikator, ki označuje določeno napako, do katere je prišlo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6168">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** - An identifier that will denote the specific error being hit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6169">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** – čas, ko se je začela seja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6169">**Data_AffectedSessionStartTime** - The time at which the session started.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6170">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** – vrsta zaznanega izhoda iz aplikacije (če gre za izhod z napako, ta koda označuje vrsto zaznane napake)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6170">**Data_AffectedSessionUAEType** - The type of application exit observed (if it was an ungraceful exit, this code will denote the type of error observed)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6171">**Data_AffectedSessionVersionr** – glavna različica aplikacije, pri kateri je bil zaznan izhod iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6171">**Data_AffectedSessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6172">**Data_AffectedSessionVirtualMemoryOnCrash** – prostor v navideznem pomnilniku, ki je bil zaseden, ko je prišlo do izhoda iz aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6172">**Data_AffectedSessionVirtualMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of virtual memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6173">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** – označuje, ali je šlo za izhod iz aplikacije brez napak ali z napakami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6173">**Data_ExitWasGraceful** - Whether the application Exit was graceful or ungraceful.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitycomaddinunhandledexception"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6174">Office.Extensibility.COMAddinUnhandledException</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6174">Office.Extensibility.COMAddinUnhandledException</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6175">Dogodek, ustvarjen ob zrušitvah dodatka COM v potrošniški različici Officeovih aplikacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6175">Event generated when COM Add-in crashes on a consumer version of Office applications.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6176">Uporaba: s to funkcijo izračunate globalne programe, ki niso značilni za Microsoft 365, za podjetja »posvojitve« za dodatek, ki ga nato uporabljajo orodja, kot je orodje za pripravljenost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6176">Usage: this is used to compute a global, non-enterprise-specific Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise "adoption" for an add-in which is then used by tools like the Readiness Toolkit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6177">S tem strankam podjetja dovolite, da preverijo, ali so dodatki, ki so uvedeni v svojih organizacijah, združljivi z najnovejšimi različicami aplikacij Microsoft 365 za podjetja in da bodo ustrezno načrtovali njihove nadgradnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6177">This allows enterprise customers to validate if the add-ins they have deployed in their organizations are compatible with the latest versions of Microsoft 365 Apps for enterprise and plan their upgrades accordingly.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6178">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6178">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6179">**ScopeId** – obseg trenutne niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6179">**ScopeId** – the current thread scope</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6180">**Method** – Officeov način, kjer je prišlo do izjeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6180">**Method** – Office method where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6181">**Interface** – Officeov vmesnik, kjer je prišlo do izjeme</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6181">**Interface** – Office interface where exception occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6182">**AddinId** – ID razreda za dodatek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6182">**AddinId** – the add-in Class Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6183">**AddinProgId** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6183">**AddinProgId** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6184">**AddinFriendlyName** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6184">**AddinFriendlyName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6185">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – časovni žig dodatka iz metapodatkov DLL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6185">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6186">**AddinVersion** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6186">**AddinVersion** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6187">**AddinFileName** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6187">**AddinFileName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6188">**VSTOAddIn** – ali je dodatek vrste VSTO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6188">**VSTOAddIn** – whether add-in is VSTO</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6189">**AddinConnectFlag** – vedenje trenutnega nalaganja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6189">**AddinConnectFlag** – current load behavior</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6190">**LoadAttempts** – število poskusov za nalaganje izdelka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6190">**LoadAttempts** – number of attempts to load add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6195">**ScopeId** – obseg trenutne niti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6195">**ScopeId** – the current thread scope</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6198">**AddinId** – ID razreda za dodatek</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6198">**AddinId** – the add-in Class Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6199">**AddinProgId** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6199">**AddinProgId** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6200">**AddinFriendlyName** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6200">**AddinFriendlyName** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6201">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – časovni žig dodatka iz metapodatkov DLL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6201">**AddinTimeDateStamp** – the add-in timestamp from the DLL metadata</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6202">**AddinVersion** – zastarelo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6202">**AddinVersion** – deprecated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6204">**VSTOAddIn** – ali je dodatek vrste VSTO</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6204">**VSTOAddIn** – whether add-in is VSTO</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationheartbeat"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6207">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6207">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHeartbeat</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6208">Dodatki za Office se zaženejo v peskovniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6208">Office Add-ins run in a sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6209">Ta dogodek zbira informacije o signalih obveščanja o izvajanju programa ob aktiviranjih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6209">This event collects heartbeat information on activations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6210">Ko pride do zrušitve dodatka, ta dogodek zbira podatke o tem, zakaj je prišlo do zrušitve v primeru, ki je povezan z našim peskovnikom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6210">When an add-in crashes, this event collects why it crashed in the case it's related to our sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6211">Uporablja se za preiskovanje, ko stranke stopnjujejo težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6211">Used to investigate when customers escalate issues.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6212">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6212">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6213">**AppId** – ID aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6213">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6214">**AppInfo** – podatki glede vrste dodatka (podokno opravil ali UILess ali znotraj vsebine itd.) in vrste ponudnika (Omen, SharePoint, datotečni sistem itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6214">**AppInfo** - Data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6215">**AppInstanceId** – ID primerka aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6215">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6216">**AssetId** – ID sredstva aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6216">**AssetId** - Asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6217">**ErrorCode** – skupni porabljeni čas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6217">**ErrorCode** - Total time spent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6218">**IsAugmentationScenario** – označuje, ali je razširitvena zanka odgovorna za inicializacijo nadzora Officeovih rešitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6218">**IsAugmentationScenario** – indicates if the augmentation loop is responsible for initializing the Office Solutions Framework control</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6219">**IsDebug** – označuje sejo za odpravljanje napak</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6219">**IsDebug** - indicates if session is a debug session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6220">**IsPreload** – Označuje, ali je dodatek vnaprej naložen v ozadju za izboljšanje učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6220">**IsPreload** – indicates if the add-in is being preloaded in background for improving activation perf.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6221">**IsWdagContainer** – Označuje, ali se je začel postopek aktivacije dodatka v vsebniku tehnologije Windows Defender Application Guard.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6221">**IsWdagContainer** – indicates if the add-in activation is being taken place in a Windows Defender Application Guard container.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6222">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** – Števec aktiviranih dodatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6222">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - Counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6223">**RemoterType** – določa vrsto remoterja (zaupanja vreden, ni vreden zaupanja, Win32webView, zaupanja vreden UDF itd.), ki se uporablja za aktiviranje dodatka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6223">**RemoterType** - Specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF, etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>
