#### <a name="officeperformanceboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6842">Office.Performance.Boot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6842">Office.Performance.Boot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6843">Zbrano, ko je zagnana Officeova aplikacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6843">Collected when an Office application is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6844">Vključuje podatke o tem, kdaj je bil zagnan inicializiran z odpiranjem datoteke ali z zagonom prek začetnega menija, ali je bil to prvi zagon aplikacije, koliko pomnilnika porablja aplikacija in ali je bil uporabniku prikazan UV, ki je oviral pogled.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6844">Includes whether the boot was initiated by opening a file or launching via the Start menu, whether this was the first boot of the application, how much memory the application is using, and whether there was any blocking UI shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6845">Uporabljeno za merjenje hitrosti zagona Officeovih aplikacij in koliko pomnilnika porabijo, ko se zaženejo. Na ta način je zagotovljena sprejemljiva uporabniška izkušnja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6845">Used to measure how fast Office applications boot and how much memory they use when they start, to ensure there is an acceptable user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6846">Zbrana so ta polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6846">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6847">**ActivationKind** – ali je bila aplikacija zagnana z zagonom v začetnem meniju, z odpiranjem datoteke ali avtomatizacijo OLE.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6847">**ActivationKind** - Whether the application was started by launching from the Start menu, by opening a file, or through OLE Automation.</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6848">**BootToStart** – ali se je uporabnik odločil za prikaz začetnega zaslona, ko se ta aplikacija zažene.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6848">**BootToStart** - Whether the user has chosen to show the start screen when this application starts.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6849">**ColdBoot** – ne glede na to, ali se Officeov program prvič zažene, ko je bil vnovični zagon sistema ali binarna aplikacija naložena z diska.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6849">**ColdBoot** - Whether is first time Office application runs after a system restart or application binary had to be loaded from disk.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6850">**DeviceModel** – model naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6850">**DeviceModel** - The model of the device.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6851">**Data_DocumentLocation** – pri odpiranju dokumenta označuje, v kateri storitvi je na voljo dokument (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint itd.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6851">**DocLocation** -  When opening a document, indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6852">**DurationUntilMso20Initialization** – trajanje, ki je bilo uporabljeno v mikrosekundah med inicializacijo Officeovega postopka, in mso20win32client. dll je bil naložen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6852">**DurationUntilMso20Initialization** - The duration in microseconds it took between when the Office process was initialized and mso20win32client.dll was loaded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6853">**Embedding** – Ali je bila aplikacija odprta za vdelovanje OLE.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6853">**Embedding** – Whether the app was opened for OLE embedding.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6854">**FirstBoot** – ali je bil to prvi zagon aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6854">**FirstBoot** - Whether this was a first boot of the application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6855">**InitializationDuration** – koliko časa v mikrosekundah je preteklo za prvo inicializacijo Officeovega postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6855">**InitializationDuration** - The duration in microseconds it took to first initialize the Office process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6856">**InterruptionMessageId** – ID pogovornega okna, če je zagon prekinilo pogovorno okno, ki je uporabnika pozivalo k vnosu podatkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6856">**InterruptionMessageId** - If the boot was interrupted by a dialog asking for user input, the ID of the dialog.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6857">**LegacyDuration** – Trajanje izvajanja dejavnosti, izmerjeno z drugimi začetnimi in končnimi točkami, kot so na voljo za »Activity.Duration«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6857">**LegacyDuration** - The length of time the activity took to execute, measured using different starting and ending points than Activity.Duration.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6858">**OpenAsNew** – Ali je bila aplikacija zagnana z odpiranjem obstoječega dokumenta kot predloge za novega.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6858">**OpenAsNew** – Whether the app was started by opening an existing document as the template for a new one.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6859">**TotalWorkingSetMB** – količina pomnilnika v megabajtih v delovnem naboru postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6859">**TotalWorkingSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process's working set.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6860">**VirtualSetMB** – količina pomnilnika v megabajtih v navideznem naboru postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6860">**VirtualSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process's virtual set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6861">(Samo MacOS/iOS)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6861">(MacOS / iOS only)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6862">**WorkingSetPeakMB** – največja količina pomnilnika v megabajtih, ki je bila doslej v delovnem naboru postopka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6862">**WorkingSetPeakMB** - The largest amount of memory in megabytes that was ever in the process's working set so far.</span></span>


#### <a name="officepowerpointpptandroidrehearseview"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6863">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6863">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Android.RehearseView</span></span>

PowerPoint. PPT. Android. RehearseView. #### <a name="officepowerpointrehearsalsessionmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6909">Office.PowerPoint.Rehearsal.SessionMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6909">Office.PowerPoint.Rehearsal.SessionMetrics</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6910">Dogodek, ki je sprožen, ko je seja govora ustavljena za inštrukcije za predstavitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6910">Event triggered when the speech session is stopped for Presenter Coach.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6911">S tem dogodkom lahko zajamemo nekatere metrične podatke za sejo vaje v inštrukcijah za predstavitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6911">This event helps us in capturing some metrics for a rehearsal session in Presenter Coach.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6912">Uporabili ga bomo za vzdrževanje visoke kakovosti te funkcije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6912">It will help in maintaining a high quality of service for this feature.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6913">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6913">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6914">**ActualRehearseBootTimeInMs** – Dejanski čas, potreben za ustvarjanje povezav.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6914">**ActualRehearseBootTimeInMs** – This is the actual time taken for the connections to be created.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6915">**AdaptationTextSize** – Velikost besedila, ki je poslano v storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6915">**AdaptationTextSize** – This is the size of the text that is send to service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6916">**AuthDurationInMs** – To je čas v milisekundah, potreben za preverjanje pristnosti (osvežite žeton za preverjanje pristnosti).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6916">**AuthDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for authentication (refresh the auth token).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6917">**AuthError** – To opisuje napako preverjanja pristnosti, do katere je prišlo (če je prišlo do nje).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6917">**AuthError** – This describes the authentication error that occurred (if at all).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6918">**AvgFragmentLatencyInMs** – To je povprečen čas, ki ga sporočila govora potrebujejo za povratno pot v omrežju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6918">**AvgFragmentLatencyInMs** – This is the average round-trip time for network speech messages.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6919">**ConnectDurationInMs** – To je čas v milisekundah, ki ga seja potrebuje za dokončanje povezave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6919">**ConnectDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for the session to complete the connection.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6920">**FirstAudioDelayInMs** – To je čas v milisekundah, potreben za prejem prve zvočne datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6920">**FirstAudioDelayInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds for the first audio data to be received.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6921">**FRetriedOnOpenConnection** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bil ponovni poskus izveden za odprto povezavo ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6921">**FRetriedOnOpenConnection** – This is a Boolean which indicates whether retry happen for openconnection or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6922">**InitMediaCaptureLayerDurationInMs** – to je čas, ki ste ga odstranili v milisekundah, da inicializirate plast »Media/Audio Capture«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6922">**InitMediaCaptureLayerDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to initialize the media/audio capture layer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6923">**LocallyDroppedMessageCount** – To je skupno število sporočil, opuščenih lokalno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6923">**LocallyDroppedMessageCount** – This is the total number of messages dropped locally.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6924">**NumReconnectAttemptsDuringSession** – To označuje število poskusov ponovnega povezovanja s storitvijo govora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6924">**NumReconnectAttemptsDuringSession** – This indicates how many times the attempt was made to reconnect to speechservice.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6925">**NumTriesDuringEachReconnectAttempt** – To je polje, ki označuje število poskusov, izvedenih med posameznim poskusom ponovnega povezovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6925">**NumTriesDuringEachReconnectAttempt** – This is an array that indicates number of tries that were done during each reconnect attempt.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6926">**OpenFrontDoorConnectionDurationInMs** – To je čas v milisekundah, potreben za odpiranje povezave do storitve FrontDoor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6926">**OpenFrontDoorConnectionDurationInMs** – This is the time in milliseconds taken to open the connection to the FrontDoor service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6927">**SendAdaptationTextDurationInMs** – To je čas v milisekundah, ki je bil potreben za pošiljanje besedila adaptacije v storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6927">**SendAdaptationTextDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to send the adaptation text to the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6928">**ServiceDroppedMessageCount** – To je skupno število sporočil, ki jih je opustila storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6928">**ServiceDroppedMessageCount** – This is the total number of messages dropped by the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6929">**SessionDurationInMs** – Trajanje celotne seje od trenutka, ko je uporabnik kliknil možnost začetka, do trenutka, ko je kliknil možnost ustavitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6929">**SessionDurationInMs** – This is the time duration of entire session from when user clicked start to when user clicked stop.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6930">**Sessionid** – To je ID seje sprednjih vrat govora. To lahko uporabimo za odpravljanje napak v dnevnikih storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6930">**SessionId** – This is the speech frontdoor session id. We can use this to debug service logs.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6931">**SpeechClientResultEventsWithTimestamps** – To je polje kod napak, prejetih skupaj s časovnimi žigi, ki so lahko v pomoč pri odpravljanju napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6931">**SpeechClientResultEventsWithTimestamps** – This is an array of error codes received along with the timestamps which can help in debugging.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6932">**SpeechHResultsWithTimestamps** – To je polje kod napak, prejetih skupaj s časovnimi žigi, ki so lahko v pomoč pri odpravljanju napak.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6932">**SpeechHResultsWithTimestamps** – This is an array of error codes received along with the timestamps which can help in debugging.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6933">**StartSpeechCaptureDurationInMs** – To je čas v milisekundah, potreben za začetek zajema govora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6933">**StartSpeechCaptureDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to start speech capture.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6934">**StartSpeechServiceDurationInMs** – To je polje časa, potrebnega za začetek seje govora pri vsakem ponovnem povezovanju, vključno s trajanjem prvega zagona seje govora.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6934">**StartSpeechServiceDurationInMs** – This is an array of time taken to start speech session every time there is reconnect, including first start speech session duration also.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6935">**TotalMessageCount** – To je skupno število zvočnih sporočil, poslanih v storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6935">**TotalMessageCount** – This is the total number of audio messages sent to the service.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6936">**WebSocketConnectDurationInMs** – To je čas v milisekundah, potreben za dokončanje povezave s spletno vtičnico.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6936">**WebSocketConnectDurationInMs** – This is the time taken in milliseconds to complete the web socket connection.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6948">**Data_RegisterInsider** – stanje registracije programa Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6948">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6958">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** – raven programa Insider pri zapiranju pogovornega okna »Pridružite se programu Office Insider«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6958">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** - Insider level on closing of "Join Office Insider" dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6959">**Data_IsInternalUser** – označuje, ali se aplikacija izvaja s poverilnicami Microsoftovega poslovnega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6959">**Data_IsInternalUser** - Indicates whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6960">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** – označuje, ali lahko koda določi, ali se aplikacija izvaja s poverilnicami Microsoftovega poslovnega računa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6960">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** - Indicates whether the code could determine whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6961">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** – označuje, ali je bila povezava do naročnine na glasilo »Office Insider« sprožena pod pogojem, da se je uporabnik pridružil programu »Office Insider«, da je omogočena funkcija »Naročnina na glasilo« in da uporabnik ni preklical odpiranja spletne strani z naročnino na glasilo »Office Insider«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6961">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** - Indicates whether Office Insider Newsletter Subscription link was triggered under condition that user has joined Office Insider program, Newsletter Subscription feature is enabled, and the user have not canceled opening of Office Insider Newsletter Subscription webpage.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6962">**Data_RegisterInsider** – stanje registracije programa Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6962">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6963">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** – koda rezultata za registracijo v programu Office Insider.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6963">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** - Result code for Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-6964">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** – trenutno stanje registracije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-6964">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7013">Kritični signal, ki se uporablja za spremljanje odzivanja uporabnikov, ko se prikaže pogovorno okno varni zagon.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7013">The critical signal used to track user response when he/she sees a safe boot dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7014">Pogovorno okno »Safe boot« je prikazano, ko ni bilo mogoče večkrat zagnati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7014">Safe boot dialog is shown when we were unable to launch repeatedly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7015">Uporabnik, ki je na varnem zagonu, se uporablja kot dovoljenje za počistitev podatkov programa za uspešno uvedbo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7015">User choice to safe boot is used as permission to clear app data to launch successfully.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7016">Uporablja se za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7016">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7017">Uporabnik si ogleda, ko naleti na kritično napako z zagonskim zrušitvijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7017">User sees when they encounter critical boot crash bug.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7018">S temi informacijami boste sledili odpravljanju vzrokov zrušitve in ali je uporabnik uspešno zagnal aplikacijo ali ne.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7018">This info will help track if they crash cause has been resolved and user can launch the app successfully or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7020">**DIALOG_ACTION** – kateri gumb »pogovornega okna« je uporabnik kliknil – gumb » pozitivna« ali »negativni gumb«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7020">**DIALOG_ACTION** - Which dialog button did the user click on – Positive button or negative button</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7022">Kritični signal se uporablja za pravilno nastavitev in uporabo zvezkov, po tem, ko se je uporabnik vpisal v aplikacijo OneNote za sistem Android, za omogočanje dostopa do zvezkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7022">The critical signal used to ensure that after a user signs-into a OneNote Android App, notebooks are properly provisioned so that they can be easily accessed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7023">Uporablja se za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7023">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7024">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7024">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7025">**AppSuspendedDuringEvent** – vrne logično vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bila aplikacija prekinjena med omogočanjem uporabe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7025">**AppSuspendedDuringEvent** - Returns Boolean to indicate if app was suspended during provisioning</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7026">**NetworkConnection** – vrsta omrežne povezave za uporabljeno napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7026">**NetworkConnection** - The type of network connectivity of the device in use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7027">**NetworkDataExchange** – zabeleži število bajtov, izmenjanih med omogočanjem uporabe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7027">**NetworkDataExchange** - Records the number of bytes exchanged during provisioning.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7028">**ServerType** – vrne vrsto strežnika, ki ponuja storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7028">**ServerType** - Returns the type of the server offering the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7029">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds** – vrne čas, zahtevan za dokončanje omogočanja uporabe, v milisekundah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7029">**TimeTakenInMilliSeconds** - Returns time taken to complete provisioning in millisecond</span></span>

#### <a name="onenotesyncprovisioningstarted-previous-name-officeonenoteandroidsyncprovisioningstarted"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7030">OneNote.Sync.ProvisioningStarted *(prejšnje ime)* , Office.OneNote.Android.Sync.ProvisioningStarted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7030">OneNote.Sync.ProvisioningStarted *(previous name)* , Office.OneNote.Android.Sync.ProvisioningStarted</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7031">Kritični signal se uporablja za pravilno nastavitev in uporabo zvezkov, po tem, ko se je uporabnik vpisal v aplikacijo OneNote za sistem Android, za omogočanje dostopa do zvezkov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7031">The critical signal used to ensure that after a user signs into a OneNote Android App, notebooks are properly provisioned so that they can be easily accessed.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7032">Uporablja se za zagotavljanje zaznavanja kritične regresije za aplikacijo OneNote in stanja storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7032">This is used to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7033">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7033">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7034">**NetworkConnection** – vrsta omrežne povezave za uporabljeno napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7034">**NetworkConnection** - The type of network connectivity of the device in use</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7035">**ServerType** – vrne vrsto strežnika, ki ponuja storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7035">**ServerType** - Returns the type of the server offering the service</span></span>

#### <a name="perfevent"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7036">perf.event</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7036">perf.event</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7037">Uporablja se za nadzor negativnega učinka pri nalaganju različnih komponent aplikacije, na primer za zagotovitev, da se pri prvem zagonu aplikacije vaš indeks čim prej naloži.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7037">Used for monitoring possible negative impact on performance of loading different parts of the app, for example to ensure when you first open the app, your inbox loads as quickly as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7038">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7038">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7039">**app_start_show_message_list** – pojavila se je težava pri učinkovitosti delovanja med zagonom aplikacije, zaradi katere se je seznam sporočil v mapi »Prejeto« nalagal dolgo časa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7039">**app_start_show_message_list** - that means there was a performance issue with the app start-up causing your inbox message list to take a long time to load</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7040">**event_type** – prikaže vrsto dogodka učinkovitosti delovanja, zaradi katerega se je pojavila težava pri učinkovitosti delovanja. S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo težave, povezane z določeno vrsto.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7040">**event_type** - tells us the type of performance event that caused a performance issue to help us detect issues related to a specific type.</span></span>   

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7041">**extra_params** – razvijalec lahko doda dodatne parametre, s pomočjo katerih izvemo več podrobnosti o tem, kaj je lahko vzrok za težavo pri učinkovitosti delovanja, npr. začetek/konec tega dejanja itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7041">**extra_params** - A developer can add additional parameters here to help give us more details about what could be causing this performance issue, i.e. when did this action start and end, etc.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7042">**profiling_summary** – ponuja informacije o skupini opravil, številu opravil in povprečnem času za te skupine, s katerimi lahko lažje razumete morebitna regresija na določenih območjih pri nalaganju aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7042">**profiling_summary** - provides information about the group of tasks, the number of tasks and the average time for those groups to help understand potential regressions in specific areas when loading the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7043">**total_time_elapsed** – čas trajanja dogodka učinkovitosti delovanja, s katerim ugotovimo resnost težave pri učinkovitosti delovanja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7043">**total_time_elapsed** - Tells us how long the performance event took to help us understand the severity of the performance issue</span></span>

#### <a name="performancerecord"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7044">performance.record</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7044">performance.record</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7045">Ta dogodek zbira metriko učinkovitosti delovanja aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7045">This event collects performance metrics of the app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7046">To nam omogoča, da zaznamo in odpravimo primere, kjer je poraba pomnilnika in CPE-ja izjemno visoka ali je prišlo do drugih težav z učinkovitostjo delovanja, kar lahko povzroči upočasnitev delovanja vaše naprave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7046">This allows us to detect and fix situations where the app memory usage and CPU usage becomes critically high or has other performance issues which could cause your device to slow down.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7047">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7047">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7048">**app_exit_metric** – Prikaže metriko o številu različnih vrst zapiranj aplikacij v ospredju in ozadju, kar nam služi za lažje razumevanje nepričakovanih zapiranja aplikacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7048">**app_exit_metric** - Tell us the metrics about counts of different performance types of foreground and background app exits, to help us understand app exits unexpectedly with negative performance reasons.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7049">**average_suspended_memory** – Prikaže povprečno količino pomnilnika, ki ga porabi aplikacija, ko je začasno prekinjena, kar nam služi za primerjavo ter lažje razumevanje negativnega vpliva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7049">**average_suspended_memory** - Tells us the average amount of memory in use by the app when it’s suspended so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7050">**category** – prikaže, ali se aplikacija trenutno izvaja v ospredju ali ozadju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7050">**category** - Tells us if the app is in the foreground or background at the time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7051">Možni vrednosti sta »ospredje« in »ozadje«.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7051">Possible values include foreground and background.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7052">**cpu_usage** – prikaže, koliko CPE-ja porabi aplikacija. S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo morebiten negativni učinek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7052">**cpu_usage** - Tells us how much CPU was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7053">**cumulative_CPU_time** – Prikaže, koliko časa CPE je porabila aplikacija, kar nam služi za primerjavo ter lažje razumevanje negativnega vpliva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7053">**cumulative_CPU_time** - Tells us the total amount of CPU the app used with the measurement of duration of time, so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7054">**cumulative_GPU_time** – Prikaže, koliko časa GPE je porabila aplikacija, kar nam služi za primerjavo ter lažje razumevanje vpliva na skrajšan časa delovanja baterije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7054">**cumulative_GPU_time** - Tells us the total amount of GPU time used by the app, so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative battery life impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7055">**is_watch_app_installed** – prikaže, ali uporabnik trenutno uporablja napravo Apple Watch in ali je ta nameščena. S tem dogodkom ugotovimo negativni učinek zaradi naprave Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7055">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is installed to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7056">**is_watch_paired** – prikaže, ali uporabnik trenutno uporablja napravo Apple Watch in ali je ta seznanjena z uporabnikovo napravo. S tem dogodkom ugotovimo negativni učinek zaradi naprave Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7056">**is_watch_paired** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is paired with the device to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7057">**is_watch_supported_and_active** – prikaže, ali uporabnik trenutno uporablja napravo Apple Watch in ali je ta aktivna. S tem dogodkom ugotovimo negativni učinek zaradi naprave Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7057">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is active to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7058">**memoAry_used_percentage** – prikaže odstotek pomnilnika, ki ga aplikacija porabi. S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo morebiten negativni učinek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7058">**memoAry_used_percentage** - Tells us what percentage of memory was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7059">**memory_used** – prikaže, koliko pomnilnika porabi aplikacija. S pomočjo tega dogodka lahko ugotovimo morebiten negativni učinek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7059">**memory_used** - Tells us how much memory was used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7060">**peak_memory_usage** – Prikaže največjo količino pomnilnika, ki ga porabi aplikacija, kar nam služi za primerjavo ter lažje razumevanje negativnega vpliva.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7060">**peak_memory_usage** - Tells us the largest amount of memory used by the app so we have something to compare, to help us understand the negative performance impact.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7061">**scroll_hitch_time_ratio** – Prikaže razmerje časa, porabljenega za težave med pomikanjem po uporabniškem vmesniku, kar nam služi za lažje razumevanje negativnega vpliva na delovanje uporabniškega vmesnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7061">**scroll_hitch_time_ratio** - Tells us the ratio of the time spent hitching while scrolling on UI, to help us understand the negative UI performance impact.</span></span>


### <a name="application-activity-error-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7062">*Podvrsta napake pri dejavnosti aplikacije*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7062">*Application activity error subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7063">Napake v delovanju funkcije ali uporabniške izkušnje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7063">Errors in functionality of a feature or user experience.</span></span>

#### <a name="assertion"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7064">assertion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7064">assertion</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7065">S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo, kdaj se pojavijo kritične napake aplikacije, ki lahko povzročijo zrušitev aplikacije ali resne težave, kot so prazne vrstice v vašem nabiralniku.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7065">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred that would cause your app to crash or experience serious issues like causing you to see empty rows in your inbox.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7066">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7066">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7067">**count** – skupno število elementov, povezanih z napako; na primer število koledarjev z napakami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7067">**count** - Total number of items associated with the error; for example, number of calendars that have errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7068">**has_hx** – dogodek, ki ponazarja, da račun uporablja našo novo storitev sinhronizacije, s katerim je mogoče zaznati težave, ki jih povzroči naša storitev sinhronizacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7068">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7069">**host_name** – ime gostitelja storitve, ki je bil vključen v napako. Ta dogodek nam pomaga odkriti težave, povezane z določenim gostiteljem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7069">**host_name** - the name of the service host that was involved in the error to help us detect issues related to a specific host</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7070">**host_type** – vrsta gostitelja, ki je bil vključen v napako. Ta dogodek nam pomaga odkriti težave, povezane z določeno vrsto gostitelja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7070">**host_type** - the type of host that was involved in the error to help us detect issues related to a specific host type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7071">**message** – sporočilo po meri za izjavo, uporabljeno za diagnosticiranje težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7071">**message** - custom message for the assertion that is used to diagnose the issue</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7072">**origin** – izvor napake v kodi za zaznavanje težav, povezanih z določenim delom kode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7072">**origin** - the origin of the error in the code to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7073">**stacktrace** – sled sklada, kjer se je pojavila izjava, za zaznavanje težav, povezanih z določenim delom kode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7073">**stacktrace** - the stack trace where the assertion occurred to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7074">**type** – vrsta zaznane napake v izjavi, npr. null_folder_name, compose_selected_null_account, za pomoč pri zaznavanju težav, povezanih z določenim delom kode.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7074">**type** - the type of assertion error that occurred, e.g. null_folder_name, compose_selected_null_account, to help us detect issues related to a certain part of the code</span></span>

#### <a name="editcontacterror"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7075">edit.contact.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7075">edit.contact.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7076">Omogoča nam, da zaznamo in odpravimo primere, v katerih je prišlo do napak pri ogledu oziroma urejanju stikov v naši aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7076">Allows us to detect and fix situations where errors were caused when you're trying to view or edit contacts through our app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7077">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7077">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7078">**errorType** – vrsta zaznane napake za pomoč pri diagnosticiranju težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7078">**errorType** - the type of error that occurred to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7079">**field** – polje stika, ki ga je uporabnik želel urediti, za pomoč pri diagnosticiranju te težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7079">**field** - The contact field that the user was trying to edit to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7080">**version** – različica za storitev kartice stika, ki jo uporabljamo za pomoč pri diagnosticiranju težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7080">**version** - The version of the contact card service we are using to help us diagnose the issue</span></span>

#### <a name="errorreport"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7081">error.report</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7081">error.report</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7082">S tem dogodkom lahko zaznamo kritične napake aplikacije in tako preprečimo težave, ki bi lahko povzročile zrušitev vaše aplikacije ali vam preprečevala branje e-pošte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7082">This event lets us detect when critical app errors occurred so that we can prevent issues that could cause your app to crash or prevent you from reading email.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7083">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7083">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7084">**client-request-id** – identifikator zahteve odjemalca za zahtevo, ki je povzročila napako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7084">**client-request-id** - the client request identifier for the request which caused the error</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7085">**date** – časovni žig zahteve, ki je povzročila napako.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7085">**date** - the datestamp of the request which caused the error</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7086">**error** – vrsta napake, npr get_mailbox_location_failed.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7086">**error** - the type of error, e.g. get_mailbox_location_failed</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7087">**error_body** – telo sporočila o napaki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7087">**error_body** - the body of the error message</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7088">**is_x_mailbox_anchor_set** – ali je bila v zahtevi uporabljena lastnost X-AnchorMailbox.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7088">**is_x_mailbox_anchor_set** - whether the X-AnchorMailbox property was set on the request</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7089">**reason** – vzrok napake, npr. sporočilo o napaki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7089">**reason** - the reason for the error, i.e. an error message</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriversofthang"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7092">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7092">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7093">Microsoftu pomaga razlikovati dolgotrajne neodzivnosti gonilnika grafične kartice od kratkotrajnih. Na ta način je lažje določiti, pri katerih gonilnikih grafične kartice se je pojavila napaka.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7093">Helps Microsoft separate long video card driver hangs from short ones, which in turn helps make decisions about which video card drivers may be having problems.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7094">Gonilnik grafične kartice uporabnika je povzročil neodzivnost Officea, vpliv neodzivnosti pa še ni določen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7094">The user's video card driver has caused Office to hang, but the impact of the hang is not known yet</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7096">**Data\_InDeviceCall** – poklicani način grafične kartice, ki je povzročil neodzivnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7096">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - The method called on the video card that produced the hang</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7105">**SignInResultCode** – Označuje kodo rezultata za končanje poziva za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7105">**SignInResultCode** - Indicates the result code of sign-in prompt end.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7106">**UseCache** – Označuje, ali smo uporabnika pozvali k ponovnemu vpisu gesla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7106">**UseCache** - Indicates if we force prompted the user to provide the password again.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7115">**BlockingUIShown** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je bil v toku prikazan blokiran uporabniški vmesnik.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7115">**BlockingUIShown** - Boolean to indicate if blocking UI was shown in the flow anywhere.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7116">**ContentUriAuthority** – overitelj URL-ja vsebina iz SAF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7116">**ContentUriAuthority** - the authority of the content URL from SAF</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7119">**DocInstanceId** – ID primerka dokumenta, ki ga je ustvaril AppDocs, glede na obseg primerka operacije v dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7119">**DocInstanceId** - DocInstanceId the document instance ID generated by AppDocs that is scoped to an operation instance on a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7120">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je dokument zaščiten.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7120">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** - Boolean to indicate if document is protected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7121">**DocUserId** – ID uporabnika iz plasti MS auth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7121">**DocUserId** - user ID from the MS auth layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7122">**DocUserIdProvider** – Oštevilčenje, ki predstavlja ponudnika ID-ja uporabnika, 0 = neznano, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7122">**DocUserIdProvider** - enumeration that represents the user ID provider, 0 = Unkown, 1 = LiveId, 2 = OrgId, 3 = SSPI, 4 = ADAL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7126">**ErrorCode** – Koda napake za delovanje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7126">**ErrorCode** - error code for the file operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7127">**Extension** – Razširitev datoteke, ki jo želite odpreti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7127">**Extension** - extension of the file being opened.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7135">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** – Zadnja napaka v odjemalcu BCS (binarna storitev pretvorbe).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7135">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** - last error of BCS (binary conversion service) client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7136">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** – Zastavica stanja za zahtevo spletne storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7136">**OfficeWebServiceApiStatusFlag** - status flag for the web service request</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidautherror"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7150">Office.Android.AndroidAuthError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7150">Office.Android.AndroidAuthError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7151">Ta dogodek ponazarja ključne napake pri preverjanju pristnosti med tiho osvežitvijo žetona, nalaganjem vpisne strani iz storitve itd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7151">This event denotes core authentication failures during silent token refresh, loading sign in page from service and so on.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7152">Ta dogodek omogoča lažje razumevanje stanja vpisa naših aplikacij, poskusov vpisov in izvedbo ustreznih dejanj, ko zaznamo nepričakovane pozive za vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7152">This event helps in understanding the health of signed in state of our apps, sign in attempts that are made, and take appropriate actions, when we notice unexpected failures.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7154">**ADALErrorCode** – Označuje kodo napake, pri čemer je prikazan poziv za vpis ali poskus tihega pridobivanja žetona za službeni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7154">**ADALErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt or silent token fetch attempt for work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7155">**ADALRawErrorCode** – Označuje neobdelano kodo napake, pri čemer je prikazan poziv za vpis ali poskus tihega pridobivanja žetona za službeni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7155">**ADALRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code while showing sign-in prompt or silent token fetch attempt for work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7156">**ErrorGroup** – Označuje vrsto računa, kot je osebni ali službeni račun oziroma službeni račun na mestu uporabe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7156">**ErrorGroup** - Indicates the type of account like personal account or work account or on-premise work account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7157">**IDCRLErrorCode** – Označuje kodo napake, pri čemer je prikazan poziv za vpis v osebni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7157">**IDCRLErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7158">**IDCRLRawErrorCode** – Označuje neobdelano kodo napake, pri čemer je prikazan poziv za vpis v osebni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7158">**IDCRLRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code while showing sign-in prompt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7159">**LiveOAuthErrorCode** – Označuje kodo napake med poskusom tihega osveževanja žetona za osebni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7159">**LiveOAuthErrorCode** - Indicates error code during silent token refresh attempt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7160">**LiveOAuthRawErrorCode** – Označuje neobdelano kodo napake med poskusom tihega osveževanja žetona za osebni račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7160">**LiveOAuthRawErrorCode** - Indicates raw error code during silent token refresh attempt for personal account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7161">**NTLMErrorCode** – Označuje kodo napake, pri čemer je prikazan poziv za vpis v službeni račun na mestu uporabe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7161">**NTLMErrorCode** - Indicates error code while showing sign-in prompt for on-premise work account.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidfileasyncsavestatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7162">Office.Android.AndroidFileAsyncSaveStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7162">Office.Android.AndroidFileAsyncSaveStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7163">Vključuje podatke o stanju asinhronega shranjevanja datoteke in različne kode napak iz različnih komponent.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7163">Captures File async save status data and various error codes from different components.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7164">Microsoft s temi podatki analizira, ali prihaja do izgube podatkov uporabnikov v aplikaciji med shranjevanjem datotek v aplikacijah Word, Excel ali PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7164">Microsoft uses this data to analyze if there is any user data loss in the app during saving of files in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7165">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7165">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7167">**FileIOSaveHResult** – HResult za operacijo shranjevanja datotek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7167">**FileIOSaveHResult** - HResult for file save operation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7173">Vključuje podatke o stanju odpiranja datoteke in različne kode napak za prepoznavanje različnih vrst napak pri odpiranju datotek v primerjavi z nepričakovanimi napakami ter, kateri deli v kodi jih sporočajo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7173">This captures File open status data and various error codes to identify what file open failures are expected versus unexpected and which part of the code are reporting them.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7174">Microsoft s temi podatki analizira vzroke za napake pri odpiranju datotek in izračuna kritične podatke meritev, kot je stopnja uspešnosti za odpiranje datoteke v aplikacijah Word, Excel ali PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7174">Microsoft uses this data to analyze the reasons for file open failures and calculate critical metric like file open success rate in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7179">**DownloadCsiError** – Sporočilo o napaki iz CSI-ja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7179">**DownloadCsiError** - download error message from CSI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7180">**FileExtension** – Datotečna pripona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7180">**FileExtension** - file extension</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7181">**FileOpenEndErrorCode** – Koda napake za napako pri odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7181">**FileOpenEndErrorCode** - Error code for file open failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7183">**FileSize** – Velikost datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7183">**FileSize** - file size</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7187">**InitializationReason** – Oštevilčenje za vnosno točko odpiranja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7187">**InitializationReason** - enumeration for the entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7189">**IsFileEmpty** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je datoteka prazna.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7189">**IsFileEmpty** - Boolean to indicate if file is empty</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7198">**State** – Oštevilčenje stanja pri odpiranju datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7198">**State** - File open state enumeration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7199">**UriScheme** – Shema URL-ja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7199">**UriScheme** - Scheme of the URL</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7201">**WordFileCorruptionReason** – Vzrok za poškodbo datoteke, zaradi katere Wordove datoteke ni bilo mogoče odpreti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7201">**WordFileCorruptionReason** - Reason for corruption due to which word file can fail in opening</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidandroidofficeactivationlatency"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7234">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7234">Office.Android.AndroidOfficeActivationLatency</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7235">Kritični podatki za zbiranje celovitega časa, zahtevanega za odpiranje datoteke, za vsa odpiranja datotek v sistemu Windows ter Excelovih in PowerPointovih aplikacijah.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7235">Critical data to collect end-to-end file open time for all file opens in Windows, Excel, PowerPoint apps.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7236">Ta dogodek Microsoft uporablja za določanje metrike za učinkovitost pri odpiranju datoteke naših aplikacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7236">This is used by Microsoft to find out the metric for file open performance of our apps</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7237">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7237">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7238">**AppBootingOccured** – Logična vrednost za preverjanje, ali je zagon aplikacije končan.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7238">**AppBootingOccured** - Boolean to check if app boot is complete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7239">**ApplicationBootTime** – Čas, zahtevan za določeno stopnjo zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7239">**ApplicationBootTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7240">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** – Logična vrednost za preverjanje, ali je bila aplikacija prekinjena med zagonom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7240">**AppSuspendedDuringBoot** - Boolean to check if app was suspended during boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7241">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je med odpiranjem datoteke prišlo do blokiranja pogovornih oken.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7241">**BlockingUIShownDuringFileOpen** - Boolean to indicate if there was any blocking dialog during the file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7242">**CachedInfoAvailable** – Logična vrednost za iskanje predpomnjenih informacij, značilnih za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7242">**CachedInfoAvailable** - Boolean to look for cached info specific to file open operation</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7243">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je na voljo dokument, ki čaka na obnovitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7243">**DocumentRecoveryInvoked** - Boolean to indicate if there was a document pending for recovery</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7244">**EndToEndActivationTime** – Čas, zahtevan za upodobitev datoteke za datoteke, zagnane zunaj aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7244">**EndToEndActivationTime** - time taken to render the file for files opened from outside the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7245">**EndToEndFileOpenTime** – Čas, zahtevan za upodobitev datoteke za datoteke, zagnane v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7245">**EndToEndFileOpenTime** - time taken to render the file for files opened from inside the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7246">**FileOpenPhaseDurationInMs** – Čas za odpiranje datoteke, ki ga porabi določena faza.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7246">**FileOpenPhaseDurationInMs** - file open operation time consumed by specific phase</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7247">**FileSourceLocation** – Vrednost oštevilčenja za mesto datoteke, kot so: None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7247">**FileSourceLocation** - enumeration value for File location such as None, Local, UncOrMappedNetworkDrive, SkyDrive, App, SharePoint, UnknownServer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7248">**InitalizationReason** – Vstopna točka za odpiranje datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7248">**InitalizationReason** - entry point for file open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7249">**InitialBootPhaseTime** – Čas, zahtevan za določeno stopnjo zagona aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7249">**InitialBootPhaseTime** - time required during a specific phase of app boot</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7272">**DocInstanceId** – ID primerka dokumenta, ki ga je ustvaril AppDocs, glede na obseg primerka operacije v dokumentu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7272">**DocInstanceId** - DocInstanceId the document instance ID generated by AppDocs that is scoped to an operation instance on a document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7273">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je dokument zaščiten.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7273">**DocIsEnterpriseProtected** - Boolean to indicate if document is protected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7274">**DocUserId** – ID uporabnika iz plasti MS auth.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7274">**DocUserId** - user ID from the MS auth layer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7285">**HttpStatusCode** – Koda odziva HTTP za zahtevo spletne storitve.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7285">**HttpStatusCode** - HTTP response code for web service request</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7288">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** – Zadnja napaka v odjemalcu BCS (binarna storitev pretvorbe).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7288">**LastBCSClientError_TagId** - last error of BCS (binary conversion service) client</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidauthaceerrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7303">Office.Android.AuthACEErrors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7303">Office.Android.AuthACEErrors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7304">Ta dogodek uporablja Microsoftov račun (MSA), da določi, kateri uporabnik se poskuša vpisati v aplikacijo, in med tem, katere telemetrijo v razpravi je treba sprožiti kot del neuspešnega poskusa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7304">This event uses the Microsoft Account (MSA) to determine which user is attempting to sign-in to the app and during that which telemetry in discussion is getting triggered as part of an unsuccessful attempt.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7305">Ta dogodek vam pomaga pri analizi napake pri vpisu v storitvi MSA, ki pomaga pri razumevanju razlogov za neuspešen potek dela v storitvi MSA.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7305">This event helps with MSA sign-in error distribution analysis, which helps in understanding reasons behind unsuccessful MSA sign-in flow end.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7306">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7306">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7307">**ExceptionsName** – označuje izjemne razrede glede na oznake izjem, ki se pojavijo med potekom vpisov v Microsoftov račun.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7307">**ExceptionsName** - indicates exception classes with regard to exception tags that occur during Microsoft account sign-in flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7308">**ExceptionsTag** – označuje, katere izjeme za prilive v uniji so prisotne v storitvi v storitvi v storitvi MSA-vpis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7308">**ExceptionsTag** - indicates which inflow exceptions present in union are occurring for MSA-sign in flow.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7309">**IDCRLACEErrorCode** – daje kodo napake, ki se pojavi med vpisom v storitvi MSA.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7309">**IDCRLACEErrorCode** - Gives error code occurring during MSA sign-in flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7310">Različne kode napake, navedene na naslovu%SRCROOT%\identity\coreapi\public\IdentityData.h</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7310">Different error codes mentioned at %SRCROOT%\identity\coreapi\public\IdentityData.h</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7311">**IDCRLAuthenticationStatusErrorCode** – označuje koda napake za neveljavno stanje rezultata preverjanja pristnosti, ki prihaja iz Microsoftovega računa (MSA).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7311">**IDCRLAuthenticationStatusErrorCode** - Indicates error codes for invalid status of Authentication result coming from Microsoft Account (MSA).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7312">**IDCRLUserInteractionMissingError** – označuje, ali se je v Microsoftov račun (MSA), na katerega se je priklicala showUI zastavica, priklicana z zastavico, ki je napačno.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7312">**IDCRLUserInteractionMissingError** - Indicates if Microsoft Account (MSA) sign-in flow invoked with showUI flag as false causing the hit.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7316">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7316">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7317">**DocumentFileSize** – Velikost datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7317">**DocumentFileSize** - File size.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7318">**FileExtension** – Prvi štirje znaki razširitve datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7318">**FileExtension** - First four characters of the extension of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7319">**IsFileDirty** – Logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je v datoteki prišlo do neshranjenih sprememb.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7319">**IsFileDirty** - Boolean to indicate if there were unsaved changes in the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7320">**Location** – Oštevilčenje mesta datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7320">**Location** - File location enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7321">Vrednosti: OneDrive, SharePoint, Dropbox, Others.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7321">Values: OneDrive, SharePoint, Dropbox, Others</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7322">**PDFConversionError** – Oznaka, pri kateri se pojavi napaka pri pretvorbi datoteke PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7322">**PDFConversionError** - Tag at which error occurs for PDF conversion</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7323">**PdfConversionErrorCode** – Koda napake pri pretvorbi PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7323">**PdfConversionErrorCode** - PDF conversion error code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7324">**PdfConversionHRStatus** – Koda stanja pretvorbe PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7324">**PdfConversionHRStatus** - PDF conversion status code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7325">**PdfConversionResult** – Oštevilčenje rezultata pretvorbe datoteke PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7325">**PdfConversionResult** - PDF Conversion result enumeration.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7326">Vrednosti: »uspeh«, »ni uspelo« in »preklicano«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7326">Values: "Success", "Failed" and "Canceled"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7327">**PdfFileSize** – Velikost datoteke PDF.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7327">**PdfFileSize** - Size of the PDF</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidclientsideiap"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7328">Office.Android.ClientSideIAP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7328">Office.Android.ClientSideIAP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7329">Telemetrija kritične napake za napake zbirke podatkov med brskanjem datotek in dodajanje mest.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7329">Critical Error telemetry for Database Failure while file browsing and adds places.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7330">Microsoft s tem dogodkom prepozna težave s poškodbami zbirk podatkov v aplikacijah, ki uporabniku morda preprečujejo dodajanje ali brskanje mest v aplikaciji za aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7330">Microsoft uses this to identify DB corruption issues in the apps which might hinder user to add places or browse through them from within the app in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7331">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7331">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7332">**ClientTransactionId** – GUID je posredovan na DSC za določeno zahtevo za prevzem.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7332">**ClientTransactionId** - GUID passed to DSC for a specific Redemption request.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7344">**PurchaseOrderId** – Identifikator naročila za nakup v trgovini Google/Samsung.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7344">**PurchaseOrderId** - Purchase order identifier from Google/Samsung store</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7348">**SubscriptionType** – Oštevilčenje za vrsto naročnine ali inventarne številke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7348">**SubscriptionType** - enumeration for subscription type or SKUs.</span></span>
