#### <a name="officeandroiddbfailurecause"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7350">Office.Android.DBFailureCause</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7350">Office.Android.DBFailureCause</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7351">Telemetrija kritične napake za napake zbirke podatkov med brskanjem datotek in dodajanje mest.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7351">Critical Error telemetry for Database Failure while file browsing and adds places.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7352">Microsoft s tem dogodkom prepozna težave s poškodbami zbirk podatkov v aplikacijah, ki uporabniku morda preprečujejo dodajanje ali brskanje mest v aplikaciji za aplikacije Word, Excel ali PowerPoint.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7352">Microsoft uses this to identify DB corruption issues in the apps which might hinder user to add places or browse through them from within the app in Word, Excel, or PowerPoint.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7353">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7353">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7354">**ErrorAt** – Vrednost oznake: Informacije o mestu, kjer je prišlo do napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7354">**ErrorAt** - Tag Value: Information about the place where the Failure happened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7355">**ExceptionErrorMessage** – obširno sporočilo o napaki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7355">**ExceptionErrorMessage** - verbose error message</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryexpansionfileserrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7356">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesErrors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7356">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExpansionFilesErrors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7357">Razširitvene datoteke kompleta Android Package Kit (APK) za Officeovo mobilno aplikacijo so dodatne datoteke sredstev, ki jih lahko razvijalci aplikacije Android objavijo skupaj z aplikacijo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7357">Android Package Kit (APK) expansion files for the Office mobile app are supplementary resource files that Android app developers can publish along with their app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7358">Ker želimo poskrbeti, da bo naš mehanizem za prenos razširitvenih datotek bolj zanesljiv, v dnevnik zapisujemo vzrok napak, do katerih pride bodisi med prenosom razširitvenih datotek bodisi med branjem prenesenih razširitvenih datotek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7358">To make our Expansion files download mechanism more reliable, we are logging the cause of errors that occur either in downloading the expansion files or while reading the downloaded expansion files.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7359">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7359">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7360">**Data_ClassName** – besedilo, ki predstavlja ime datoteke izvorne kode, kjer je prišlo do napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7360">**Data_ClassName** - Text representing the source code file name where there is an error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7361">**Data_ErrorMessage** – besedilo, ki predstavlja postopek, ki ni uspel.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7361">**Data_ErrorMessage** - Text representing the operation that has failed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7362">**Data_ExceptionMessage** – izbirno polje z besedilom, ki predstavlja vzrok izjeme.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7362">**Data_ExceptionMessage** - An optional text field representing the cause of the exception.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7363">**Data_ExceptionType** – izbirno polje z besedilom, ki predstavlja ime izjeme, ki jo poda izvorna koda.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7363">**Data_ExceptionType** - An optional text field representing the name of the exception thrown from source code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7364">**Data_MethodName** – Besedilo, ki predstavlja ime načina v izvorni kodi, kjer je prišlo do napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7364">**Data_MethodName** - Text representing the method name in source code where there is an error.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryextractionerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7365">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExtractionError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7365">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.ExtractionError</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7366">Če želite zmanjšati velikost programov sistema Office Android, uporabite stiskanje za vire v končnem paketu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7366">To reduce the size of Office Android apps, we apply compression to the resources in the final package.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7367">Ko zaženete čas, najprej izvlečemo te vire, preden jih uporabimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7367">At run time, we first extract these resources before using them.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7368">Med izvajanjem izvlečkov je včasih prišlo do nepričakovanih napak, kar povzroča zrušitve programa.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7368">Sometimes there are unexpected errors while performing extractions, which leads to app crashes.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7369">S tem dogodkom pridobivamo nekatere diagnostične informacije, ki so povezane z ekstrakcijo, na primer ime vira, ki je bil pridobljen, pot, na kateri je izvlečena itd. Ti podatki so zbrani le, kadar pride do napak pri pridobivanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7369">Through this event we are collecting some diagnostic information related to extraction, like name of the resource being extracted, path where its extracted etc., free disk space available etc. This data is collected only when there are extraction errors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7370">Te podatke uporabljamo, da bi razumeli vzrok za težave z ekstrakcijo in izboljšali uporabniško izkušnjo naših aplikacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7370">We use this data to understand the cause of extraction failures, and to improve the user experience of our apps.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7371">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7371">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7372">**Data_ArchiveName** – ime vira, ki ga pridobivate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7372">**Data_ArchiveName** - Name of the resource that is being extracted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7373">**Data_ArchivePath** – pot, kjer je vir začasno predpomnjen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7373">**Data_ArchivePath** - Path where the resource is temporarily cached.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7374">**Data_ArchiveSizeKB** – velikost vira, ki ga pridobivate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7374">**Data_ArchiveSizeKB** - Size of the resource that is being extracted.</span></span>
 
- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7375">**Data_ClassName** – ime datoteke v izvorni kodi, pri kateri je prišlo do napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7375">**Data_ClassName** - File name in source code where the error is encountered.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7376">**Data_ErrorDetail** – besedilo, ki opisuje več podrobnosti o vzroku napake, kot je koda napake ipd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7376">**Data_ErrorDetail** - Text describing more details about the cause of the error, like the error code etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7377">**Data_ErrorMessage** – besedilo z opisom vrste napake, ki je bila med ekstrakcijo naletela.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7377">**Data_ErrorMessage** - Text describing the type of error encountered during extraction.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7378">**Data_ExtractionDestinationPath** – pot, kjer naj bo vir shranjen po ekstrakciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7378">**Data_ExtractionDestinationPath** - Path where the resource is to be saved after extraction.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7379">**Data_FreeDiskSpaceMB** – količina prostega prostora na disku, ki je na voljo v napravi, merjeni v Mega bajtih.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7379">**Data_FreeDiskSpaceMB** - The amount of free disk space available on the device measured in Mega Bytes.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7380">**Data_ItemToExtract** – ime vira, ki ga pridobivate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7380">**Data_ItemToExtract** - Name of the resource that is being extracted.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7381">**Data_MethodName** – ime metode v izvorni kodi, pri kateri je prišlo do napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7381">**Data_MethodName** - Method name in source code where the error is encountered.</span></span>


#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetryregistryerrors"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7382">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.RegistryErrors</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7382">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.RegistryErrors</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7383">Ta dogodek zajame morebitne napake, do katerih je prišlo med dostopom do registra sistema Android.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7383">This event captures any errors faced during Android registry access.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7384">S podatki tega dogodka lahko razumemo napake uporabnika in ustvarimo bolj trpežno funkcijo registra.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7384">This event data helps us in understanding the user errors and making the registry feature more robust.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7385">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7385">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7386">**App** – Postopek aplikacije, ki pošilja dogodek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7386">**App** – The application process sending the event.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7387">**AppVersionLong** – Različica aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7387">**AppVersionLong** – The application version.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7388">**Data_StackTrace** – Sled sklada napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7388">**Data_StackTrace** – The stacktrace of the error.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidearlytelemetrysharedlibraryloadersearchandloadlibraryerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7389">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.SharedLibraryLoadersearchAndloadLibraryError</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7389">Office.Android.EarlyTelemetry.SharedLibraryLoadersearchAndloadLibraryError</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7390">Ta dogodek beležimo v primeru napak pri nalaganju knjižnic v skupni rabi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7390">We log this event in case there are errors while loading shared libraries.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7391">Do napak pri nalaganju knjižnic lahko pride zaradi dveh vzrokov 1) nameščeni APK ni združljiv z napravo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7391">There can be library loading errors for two reasons 1) Installed Apk is incompatible with the device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7392">2) Knjižnica, ki jo skušamo naložiti, je morda poškodovana, zaradi napak pri ekstrahiranju, nastalih zaradi premalo prostora na disku ali premalo pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7392">2) The library that we are trying to load may be corrupt, because of errors in extracting it due to low disk space, or low memory.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7393">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7393">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7394">**Data_ExceptionMessage** – Sporočilo izjeme, ki ga aktivira Android API Szstem.loadlibrary.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7394">**Data_ExceptionMessage** - Exception message thrown by Android API System.loadlibrary</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7395">**Data_FreeSpaceInMB** – Prostor, ki je na voljo v napravi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7395">**Data_FreeSpaceInMB** - Free space available on device</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7396">**Data_nickName** – Ime knjižnice, ki je ni bilo mogoče naložiti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7396">**Data_nickName** - Name of the library which couldn't be loaded.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunejavacopyfailedattempts"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7397">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneJavaCopyFailedAttempts</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7397">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneJavaCopyFailedAttempts</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7398">Telemetrija kritične napake za spremljanje napak za posamezne vmesnike API Intune; ta telemetrija se zapisuje v dnevnike v primeru napak pri shranjevanju lokalne kopije dokumentov v oblaku, zaščitenih s storitvijo Intune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7398">Critical Error telemetry to track failures for individual Intune APIs; This telemetry gets logged in case of errors to save local copy of Intune protected Cloud documents.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7399">Microsoft s temi podatki prepoznava napake med in po vpisu v storitev Intune v aplikaciji in po vpisu v aplikacijo s službenim računom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7399">Microsoft uses this data to identify errors during and after Intune enrollment within the app, post signing into the app with a work account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7401">**Data_FileCreationFailedErrorCode** – Koda napake, povezana s tokom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7401">**Data_FileCreationFailedErrorCode** - Error code associated with the flow</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7403">Telemetrija kritične napake za spremljanje napak za posamezne vmesnike API Intune; ta telemetrija se zapisuje v dnevnike v primeru napak pri pridobivanju žetona ADAL za vire Intune.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7403">Critical Error telemetry to track failures for individual Intune APIs; This telemetry gets logged in case of errors to obtain the ADAL token for Intune resources.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7404">Microsoft s temi podatki prepoznava napake med vpisom v storitev Intune v aplikaciji in po vpisu v aplikacijo s službenim računom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7404">Microsoft uses this data to identify errors during Intune enrollment within the app, post signing into the app with a work account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7406">**Data_ErrorCode** – Koda napake, povezana s tokom.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7406">**Data_ErrorCode** - Error code associated with the flow</span></span>

#### <a name="officeandroidintuneintunejavaexceptionapppolicy"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7407">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneJavaExceptionAppPolicy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7407">Office.Android.Intune.IntuneJavaExceptionAppPolicy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7565">Dogodka Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult in Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning sta zbrana, ko odkrijemo poškodbe v datotekah PST/OST uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7565">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NdbCorruptionResult and Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning are collected when we detect corruption in a user's PST/OST.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7566">Ko zaznamo poškodbe, Microsoft zbere obliko zapisa zbirke podatkov, mesto zaznavanja in majhen del konteksta o nepravilnosti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7566">When we detect corruption, Microsoft collects the format of the database, the place where detected it, and a small amount of context about the corruption.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7567">Poškodovane datoteke OST/PST uporabnikom preprečujejo dostop do svojih e-poštnih sporočil.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7567">OST/PST corruption prevents users from accessing their emails.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7568">Te podatke aktivno spremljamo, ali se v njih pojavi nenavadna dejavnost.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7568">We actively monitor this data for anomalous activity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7569">Želimo raziskovati in diagnosticirati težave in omejiti izgubo podatkov uporabnikov.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7569">We aim to investigate and diagnose issues to limit loss of customer data.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7570">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7570">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7571">**0 –** ime procesa, ki je sporočil poškodbo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7571">**0 -** The Process name which reported corruption</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7572">**1 –** logična vrednost, ki označuje, ali je uporabnik izbral novo datoteko</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7572">**1 -** Bool indicating if the user chooses new file or not</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7573">**2 –** število drugih procesov, ki imajo odprte zbirke podatkov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7573">**2 -** the number of other processes which have the database open</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktopndbcorruptstorewarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7574">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7574">Office.Outlook.Desktop.NDBCorruptStore.Warning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7580">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7580">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7581">**CollectionTime** – čas zbiranja</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7581">**CollectionTime** - collection time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7582">**Context** – kontekst poškodovane trgovine, v kateri je bila zaznana poškodba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7582">**Context** - Corrupt Store Context, where corruption was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7585">**NdbType** – vrsta trgovine; vrednosti so lahko 0 = NdbUndefined, 1 = NdbSmall, 2 = NdbLarge, 3 = NdbTardis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7585">**NdbType** - Store Type, can be 0 = NdbUndefined, 1 = NdbSmall, 2 = NdbLarge, 3 = NdbTardis</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7588">**Version** – različica oblike zapisa datoteke za trgovino</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7588">**Version** - Version of store file format</span></span>

#### <a name="renewidentityfailure"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7704">RenewIdentityFailure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7704">RenewIdentityFailure</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7705">Zbira, ko uporabnik poskuša odpreti dokument, zaščiten z upravljanjem pravic do informacij ali uporabiti zaščito za upravljanje pravic do informacij.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7705">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7706">Vsebuje informacije, potrebne za ustrezno raziskovanje in diagnosticiranje težav, do katerih pride, ko obnovitev uporabniških dovoljenj ne uspe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7706">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when failed to renew user certificates.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7707">Zbrana so naslednja polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7707">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7708">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – hierarhija odjemalcev, ki označuje, da se program izvaja v produkcijskem okolju ali v okolju razvijalcev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7708">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7709">**AppInfo.Name** – ime aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7709">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7710">**AppInfo.Version** – različica aplikacije</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7710">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7711">**Failure.Category** – Kategorija napake »UnhandledError«</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7711">**Failure.Category** - The category of the failure "UnhandledError"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7712">**Failure.Detail** – podrobnejše informacije o napaki</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7712">**Failure.Detail** - The detailed info of the failure</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7713">**Failure.Id** – ID napake</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7713">**Failure.Id** - Failure Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7714">**Failure.Signature** – podpis napake, ki je enaka kot ime dogodka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7714">**Failure.Signature** - The signature of the failure, which is same as the event name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7715">**iKey** – ID strežnika za storitev pisanja dnevnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7715">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7716">**RMS. HRESULT** – rezultat obnovitve potrdila uporabnika</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7716">**RMS.HRESULT** - The result of renewing user certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7717">**RMS.ScenarioId** – ID scenarija, ki ga je določil odjemalec storitve za upravljanje pravic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7717">**RMS.ScenarioId** - Scenario Id defined by Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7718">**RMS.SDKVersion** – različica odjemalca storitve za upravljanje pravic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7718">**RMS.SDKVersion** - The version of Rights Management Service Client</span></span>

#### <a name="saveerror"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7719">save.error</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7719">save.error</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7720">Omogoča nam, da zaznamo in odpravimo primere, ko je prišlo do napake med poskusom shranjevanja datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7720">Allows us to detect and fix situations where there was an error when you attempted to save a file.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7721">Ta dogodek spremlja napake, nastale zaradi neuspešnega shranjevanja datoteke, vključno z opisnim sporočilom o napaki. Dogodek nam je v pomoč pri odpravljanju težave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7721">It tracks errors caused by failures to save a file, including a descriptive error message to help us resolve the issue.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7722">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7722">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7723">**error** – vrsta nastale napake za pomoč pri zaznavanju in odpravljanju težav, povezanih z določeno vrsto napake.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7723">**error** - The type of error that happened to help us detect and resolve issues related to a specific error type</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7724">**file_type** – vrsta datoteke, ki jo je uporabnik poskusil shraniti (na primer. doc).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7724">**file_type** - The type of file the user tried to save (such as .doc)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7725">**origin** – izvor poskusa shranjevanja datoteke (npr. iz e-pošte), s katerim lahko zaznamo težave, povezane s shranjevanjem datoteke iz določenega mesta v aplikaciji.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7725">**origin** - Where the file save attempt originated from (such as from an email) so we can detect issues associated with saving a file from a specific place in the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7726">**token_type** – vrsta žetona, uporabljenega za preverjanje pristnosti računa za shranjevanje datoteke, s katero zaznavamo težave pri preverjanju pristnosti, povezane s shranjevanjem datoteke.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7726">**token_type** - the type of token used to authenticate the account in order to save the file to help us detect authentication issues associated with saving a file</span></span>

#### <a name="applicationdidreceivememorywarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7732">application.did.receive.memory.warning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7732">application.did.receive.memory.warning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7733">Ta dogodek je poslan, ko nam na družba Apple sporoči, da v aplikaciji ni na voljo dovolj pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7733">This event is sent when Apple tells us that the application is running out of memory.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7734">Iz dogodka je razvidno, da smo v vaši napravi uvedli težavo upravljanja pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7734">It tells us that we have introduced an issue with memory management on your device.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7735">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7735">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7736">**current_memory_used** – prikaže, koliko pomnilnika je porabila aplikacija na točki, kjer je sistem zaznal, da je aplikaciji zmanjkalo pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7736">**current_memory_used** - Tells us the amount of memory used by the application at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7737">**current_memory_used_percentage** – prikaže odstotek pomnilnika, ki ga porabi aplikacija, od skupno razpoložljivega pomnilnika na točki, kjer je sistem zaznal, da je aplikaciji zmanjkalo pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7737">**current_memory_used_percentage** - Tell us the percentage of memory used by the application out of the total memory available at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7738">**currentVC** – prikaže trenutni pogled, ko je aplikaciji zmanjkalo pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7738">**currentVC** - Tells us the view that is currently showing when the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7739">**has_hx** – dogodek, ki ponazarja, da račun uporablja našo novo storitev sinhronizacije, s katerim je mogoče zaznati težave, ki jih povzroči naša storitev sinhronizacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7739">**has_hx** - Tells us the account is using our new sync service to help us detect issues caused by our sync service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7740">**is_watch_app_installed** – prikaže, ali uporabnik trenutno uporablja napravo Apple Watch in ali je ta nameščena. S tem dogodkom ugotovimo negativni učinek zaradi naprave Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7740">**is_watch_app_installed** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is installed to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7741">**is_watch_paired** – prikaže, ali uporabnik trenutno uporablja napravo Apple Watch in ali je ta seznanjena z uporabnikovo napravo. S tem dogodkom ugotovimo negativni učinek zaradi naprave Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7741">**is_watch_paired** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is paired with the device to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7742">**is_watch_supported_and_active** – prikaže, ali uporabnik trenutno uporablja napravo Apple Watch in ali je ta aktivna. S tem dogodkom ugotovimo negativni učinek zaradi naprave Watch.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7742">**is_watch_supported_and_active** - Tells us if the user is currently using an Apple Watch and whether it is active to help us understand the negative performance impact due to the Watch</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7743">**rn_initialized** – prikaže, ali je bil zagnan React Native, ko je aplikaciji zmanjkalo pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7743">**rn_initialized** - Tell us if React Native has been initialized at the point the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7744">**running_time** – prikaže čas izvajanja aplikacije, ko je aplikaciji zmanjkalo pomnilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7744">**running_time** - Tell us the amount of time that app has spent running at the time the application has run out of memory.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorblocklistapp"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7820">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7820">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7821">Za grafično kartico uporabnika je bilo zaznano, da povzroča dolgotrajno neodzivnost in neodzivnost, ki je ni mogoče odpraviti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7821">User's video card has been detected as causing long or unrecoverable hangs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7822">Office ne bo uporabljal te grafične kartice v tej Officeovi seji (namesto tega se uporabi programska oprema za upodabljanje), dokler ne posodobite gonilnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7822">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7823">Obvesti Microsoft o gonilnikih grafične kartice, ki povzročajo težave v Officeu. Na ta način je mogoče prepoznati trende in analizirati učinek, ki ga imajo takšni gonilniki na uporabnika.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7823">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7824">Prav tako omogoča podatke o tem, koliko uporabnikov ni v optimalnem stanju.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7824">Also helps in informing how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7825">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7825">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorregistrywrite"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7827">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7827">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7828">Office je prepoznal, da je gonilnik grafične kartice uporabnika povzročil neodzivno stanje, ki ga je treba analizirati pri naslednjem zagonu Officeove aplikacije.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7828">Office has identified that the user's video card driver has caused a hang that should be analyzed at the next Office application boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7829">Se uporablja za odločitev, ali bi uporaba drugega gonilnika grafične kartice ali vmesnika zagotovila boljšo uporabniško izkušnjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7829">Used to determine whether using a different video card driver or adapter would offer a better user experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7830">Če se pojavijo vzorci, Microsoft lahko poskrbi za prilagoditve, s katerimi zagotovi čim bolj neovirano delovanje Officea.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7830">As patterns occur, Microsoft may make adjustments to keep the Office experience as smooth as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7831">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7831">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7832">**Data\_HangDetected** – ali je bila zaznana zrušitev</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7832">**Data\_HangDetected** - Whether a hang was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7833">**Data\_InDeviceCall** – kateri klic za upodabljanje grafične kartice je bil aktiviran za Office, ko je bila zaznana neodzivnost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7833">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - Which video card rendering call Office was in when the hang occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7834">**Data\_Timeout** – čas neodzivnosti, če je bila ta odpravljena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7834">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted, if it recovered</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7835">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** – ali je neodzivnost v tem ukazu za upodabljanje grafične kartice mogoče obnoviti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7835">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** - Whether the hang in this video card rendering command is typically recoverable.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptsharednointernetconnectivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7862">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7862">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7866">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** – prikaže, ali je stanje internetne povezave na voljo med klicanjem storitve Nexus (true) ali pri klicanju programskega vmesnika za splošno spletno storitev (false)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7866">**Data\_IsNexusDetected:bool** - shows whether we got the Internet connectivity status when calling Nexus service (value true) or when calling generic web service API call (value false)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeserviceabilitymanagerofficesvcmgrprofile"></a><span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7867">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7867">Office.ServiceabilityManager.OfficeSvcMgrProfile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7868">Ta dogodek je sprožen ob zagonu upravitelja za storitve v Officeu in ima ključno vlogo pri zagotavljanju natančnih vpogledov, povezanih s stanjem uvedbe in aplikacije ter zrušitvami zaradi dodatkov pri najemniku stranke ter nam omogoča, da ustvarjamo vpoglede za skrbnika za IT, ki bo lahko uvajal posodobitve za službene računalnike.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7868">This event is triggered when Office Serviceability Manager starts, and is critical for providing accurate insights related to Deployment Status and Application and Add-in crashes within customer's tenant by allowing us to generate insights for the IT Admin to be able to confidently roll out updates for their enterprise machines.</span></span>  

<span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7869">Zbrana so sledeča polja:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7869">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7870">**DeviceIdJoinToken** – Uporablja se za združitev podatkov telemetrije iz stanja storitve in uvedbe z drugimi funkcionalnimi podatki, zbranimi prek prodajnih lijakov storitev.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7870">**DeviceIdJoinToken** - used to join Telemetry data from Health and Deployment Status with other Functional Data which is collected via the Services pipeline.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a5e75-7871">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** – Zastavica logične vrednosti, ki se uporablja za določanje števila upravljanih naprav v Officeovim ekosistemu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a5e75-7871">**TenantAssociationKeyStamped** - a Boolean flag used to determine the number of Managed devices in the Office eco-system.</span></span>
